body:
 Ek Ajeeb Dastan Hai, Mere Afsane Kee;
Maine Pal Pal Kee Koshish, Uske Pass Jaane Kee;
Naseeb The Mere Ya, Sazish Zamane Kee;
Door Hui Mujhse Utni, Jitni Umeed Thi Kareeb Aane Kee!

 Tuje Dekhe Bina Teri Tasveer Bana Du;
Tuje Mile Bina Tera Haal Bata Du;
Hai Meri Dosti Mein Itna Dum;
Teri Aankhon Ke Aansu Apni Aankhon Se Gira Du!

 Fir Wahi Fasaana Afsaana Sunaati Ho;
Dil Ke Paas Hun Keh Kar Dil Jalaati Ho;
Beqaraar Hai Aatish-e-Nazar Se Milne Ko;
To Fir Kyon Nahi Pyaar Jataati Ho!

 Haadson Ke Shehar Mein Haadson Se Darta Hai;
Mitti Ka Khilona Hai Fanaa Hone Se Darta Hai;
Mere Dil Ke Kone Mein Masoom Sa Bachha;
Bado Ki Dekh Ke Ye Duniya, Bada Hone Se Darta Hai!

 Teri Gali Mein Main Na Chalun Aur Saba Chale;
Yun Hi Khuda Jo Chahe To Bande Kee Kya Chale;
Kis Kee Ye Mauj-e-Husan Hui Jalvagar Ki Yun;
Dariya Mein Jo Habab The Aankhein Chuppa Chale!

 Barbaad Kar Gaye Wo Zindagi Pyaar Ke Naam Se;
Bewafai Hi Mili Sirf Wafa Ke Naam Se;
Zakham Hi Zakham Diye Uss Ne Dawa Ke Naam Se;
Aasman Bhi Ro Pada Meri Mohabbat Ke Anjam Se!

 Hum Tere Hijr Mein Andar Se Bikhar Jate Hain;
Zinda Lagte Hain Magar Asal Mein Mar Jate Hain;
Jab Kabhi Bolta Hai Hans Ke Kisi Aur Se Tu;
Kitne Khanjar Mere Seene Mein Utar Jate Hain!

 Barish Hui To Phoolon Ke Tan Chaak Ho Gaye;
Mausam Ke Haath Bheeg Ke Saffak Ho Gaye;
Baadal Ko Kya Khabar Hai Ki Barish Ki Chaah Mein;
Kaise Buland-o-Baala Shajar Khaak Ho Gaye!

 Vaade Pe Woh Mere Aitbaar Nahi Karte;
Hum Zikar Mohabbat Ka Sare Bazaar Nahi Karte;
Darta Hai Dil Unki Ruswai Se;
Aur Woh Sochte Hain Ki Hum Unse Pyaar Nahi Karte!

 Aankh Ladate Hi Hua Ishq Ka Aazaar Mujhe;
Chashm Beemaar Teri Kar Gayi Beemaar Mujhe;
Dil Ko Zakhmi To Vah Karte Hain Magar Hairat Hai;
Nazar Aati Nahi Chalti Hui Talwar Mujhe!

 Wo Dushmani Se Dekhte Hain Dekhte To Hain;
Main Shaad Hi sahi, Hoon To Kisi Ki Nigaah Mein!

Shaad = Delighted/Cheerful

 Andhera Bahut Ab Suraj Nikalna Chahiye;
Jaise Bhi Ho Yeh Mausam Badalna Chahiye;
Aur Jo Chehre Roz Badalte Hai Naqabo Ki Tarah;
Ab Janaza Dhoom Se Unka Nikalna Chahiye!

 Chandni Raat Badi Der Ke Baad Aayi;
Yeh Mulaqat Badi Der Ke Baad Aayi;
Aaj Aaye Hain Woh Milne Ko Badi Der Ke Baad;
Aaj Kee Raat Badi Der Ke Baad Aayi!

 Waqt Aur Khushi Tere Ghulam Honge;
Yeh Pal Yeh Pehlu Tere Hi Naam Honge;
Dekhna Kabhi Jhuk Kar Neeche Bhi Ae Humsafar;
Tere Har Kadam Ke Neeche, Mere Haathon Ke Nishan Honge!

 Raah Dekhenge Na Duniya Se Guzarne Wale;
Hum To Jaate Hain Thehar Jaye Thehrne Wale;
Ek To Husn Bala Usspe Banawat Aafat;
Ghar Bigdenge Hazaron Ke Sanwarne Wale!

 Chehre Ki Hansi Se Har Gham Ko Chupao;
Bahut Kuch Bolo Par Kuch Na Batao;
Khud Na Kabhi Rootho Par Sabko Manao;
Raaz Hai Yeh Zindgi Ka, Bas Jeete Chale Jao!

 Sar Jhukane Ki Aadat Nahi Hai;
Aansu Bahane Ki Aadat Nahi Hai;
Hum Kho Gaye To Pachtaoge Bahut;
Kyon Ki Humein Laut Ke Aane Ki Aadat Nahi Hai!

 Parchayi Aapki Hamare Dil Mein Hai;
Yaadein Aapki Hamari Aankhon Mein Hain;
Kaise Bhulaye Hum Aapko;
Pyaar Aapka Hamari Saanson Mein Hai!

 Dil Ki Nahi Jaan Ki Zarurat Ho Tum;
Zameen Ki Nahi Aasman Ki Inayat Ho Tum;
Aur Ab Hum Kya Tareef Karen Aapki;
Husn Ki Nahi Qayanat Ki Murat Ho Tum!

 Jinko Chaha Tha Humnein Apna Banana;
Na Jaane Kyon Woh Hum Se Door Ho Gaye;
Humnein Socha Tha Bitaayenge Zindagi Hans Kar;
Magar Ghamon Ko Apnaane Par Mazboor Ho Gaye!

 Maine Kaha Unse Chhod Do Ya Tod Do Mujhe;
Muskura Kar Sitam Dhaya Unhone;
Chhod To Diya Hi Hai Tum Ko;
Toot Tum Khud-Ba-Khud Jaoge!

 Bin Baat Ke Hi Roothne Ki Aadat Hai;
Kisi Apne Ka Saath Paane Ki Chahat Hai;
Aap Khush Rahe, Mera Kya Hai;
Main To Aaina Hun, Mujhe Tootne Ki Aadat Hai!

 Dard Hai Dil Mein Par Ehsaas Nahi Hota;
Rota Hai Dil Jab Woh Pass Nahi Hota;
Barbad Ho Gaye Hum Unki Mohabbat Mein;
Aur Wo Kahte Hain Is Tarah Se Pyaar Nahi Hota!

 Tere Pyaar Ne Diya Sukoon Itna;
Ki Tere Baad Koi Achha Na Lage;
Tujhe Karni Hai Bewafai Toh Is Ada Se Kar;
Ki Tere Baad Koi Bewafa Na Lage!

 Zindagi Ko Gale Lagane Ko Dil Chahta Hai;
Maut Se Hath Milane Ko Dil Chahta Hai;
Jab Kabhi Aa Jati Hai Yaad Tumhari Toh;
Pass Tumhare Aa Jane Ko Dil Chahata Hai!

 Kasoor Unka Nahi Jo Dhokha Diya Unhone;
Aadat To Humein Hi Hai Dhokhe Khane Ki;
Tutega Dil Ek Din Jaante The Hum;
Fir Bhi Bhool Ki Unko Chahne Ki!

 Kaash Ye Dil Shishe Ka Bana Hota;
Chot Lagti To Beshak Yeh Fanah Hota;
Par Sunte Jab Wo Aawaz Iske Tutne Ki;
Tab Unhein Bhi Apne Gunah Ka Ehsaas Hota!

 Utar Kar Dekho Mere Pyaar Ki Gehrai Mein; 
Sochna Mere Bare Mein Raat Ki Tanhai Mein;  
Agar Ho Jaye Mere Pyaar Ka Ehsaas Tumhein;  
Milega Mera Aks Tumhein Apni Parchai Mein!

 Paani Se Pyaas Na Bujhi;
Toh Maikhane Ki Taraf Chal Nikla;
Socha Shikayat Karun Teri Khudha Se;
Par Khudha Bhi Tera Aashiq Nikla!

 Tanha Rehna To Seekh Liya Hum Ne;
Par Khush Na Kabhi Reh Payengein;
Teri Doori To Phir Bhi Seh Leta Hai Yeh Dil;
Per Teri Mohabbat Ke Bin Na Jee Payengein!

 Kaash Yeh Sapna Bhi Pura Ho Jaye;
Hum Bhi Kisi Ke Sapno Mein Aa Jayein;
Ho Hamara Bhi Zikar Unke Laboon Par;
Hum Bhi Unke Dil Mein Bas Jayein!

 Dil Ki Khwahish Ko Naam Kya Doon;
Pyaar Ka Usse Paigam Kya Doon;
Is Dil Mein Dard Nahi Yaadein Hai Uski;
Ab Yaadein Hi Mujhe Dard De Toh Usse Ilzam Kya Doon!

 Yaad Karte Hain Tumhein Tanhai Mein;
Dil Dooba Hai Ghamoon Ki Gehrai Mein;
Humein Mat Dhundna Duniya Ki Bheed Mein;
Hum Milenge Tumhein Tumhari Hi Parchai Mein!

 Saza Humein Yeh Kaisi Mili Dil Lagane Ki;
Ro Rahe Magar Tamanna Thi Muskurane Ki;
Apna Dard Kise Dikhau Aye Dost;
Dard Bhi Ussne Diya Jo Wajah Thi Muskurane Ki!

 Chehre Ki Hansi Se Har Gham Chupao;
Bahut Kuch Bolo Par Kuch Na Batao;
Khud Na Rutho Kabhi Par Sabko Manao;
Yeh Raaz Hai Zindagi Ka, Bas Jeete Jao!

 Hum To Tere Dil Ki Mehfil Sajane Aaye The;
Teri Kasam Tujhe Apna Banane Aaye The;
Kis Baat Ki Saza Di Tumne Humko;
Bewafa Hum To Tere Dard Ko Apnane Aaye The!

 Maine Kabhi Ek Chand Ko Pana Chaha Tha;
Us Door Akash Ke Ek Sitare Ko Gale Lagana Chaha Tha;
In Namumkin Si Cheezon Ko Main Mumkin Banane Chala Tha;
Jane Kyon Us Din Main Kisi Se Dil Lagane Ko Chala Tha!

 Tannha Rehna To Seekh Liya Humne;
Par Khush Na Kabhi Reh Payenge;
Teri Doori To Phir Bhi Seh Leta Hai Ye Dil;
Par Teri Mohabbat Ke Bin Na Jee Payenge!

 Mehfil Na Sahi Tanhai Toh Milti Hai;
Milan Na Sahi Judai Toh Milti Hai;
Kaun Kehta Hai Ki Pyaar Mein Kuch Nahi Milta;
Wafa Na Sahi Bawafai Toh Milti Hai!

 Mere Dil Ne Jab Bhi Dua Mangi Hai;
Tujhe Manga Hai Teri Wafa Mangi Hai;
Jis Mohabbat Ko Dekh Ke Dunia Ko Rashk Aye;
Tere Pyar Karne Ki Wo Ada Mangi Hai!

 Ada Labon Se Dil Ki Baat Ho Jane Do;
Qabool Aaj Dil Ki Ibadat Ho Jane Do;
Tanha Chal Rahe Ho Dasht e Zeest Mein;
Do Pal Mujhko Zara Saath Ho Jane Do!

 Ishq Paane Ki Tamanna Mein Sanam;
Zindagi Barbad Bankar Reh Gai;
Jis Surat Ko Dil Mein Basaya Tha Kabhi
Aaj Woh Surat Ek Yaad Ban Kar Reh Gai!

 Kuch Nasha To Aapki Baat Ka Hai;
Kuch Nasha To Dheemi Barsaat Ka Hai;
Humein Aap Yoon Hi Sharabi Na Kahiye;
Is Dil Par Asar To Aap Se Mulakat Ka Hai!

 Rishta Banao To Dhokha Mat Dena;
Kisi Ko Ansoon Ka Tohfa Mat Dena;
Dil Se Roye Koi Tumhe Yaad Karke;
Aisa Kisi Ko Tum Moka Mat Dena!

 Kai Baar Jaan Bujh Kar Dil Toda Uska;
Shayad Ab Wo Faisla Kar Le Juda Hone Ka;
Par Har Baar Wo Paas Aate Gaye;
Meri Galtiyon Ko Apna Banate Gaye!

 Zindagi Ki Har Fizaon Mein Yaad Rakhna;
Dil Ki Sadaon Mein Yaad Rakhna;
Yeh Tohfa Bohat Hai Mere Liye;
Khaloos-e-Dil Se Duaon Mein Yaad Rakhna!

 Tere Bina Hum Jeena Bhool Jaate Hain;
Zakhmon Ko Seena Bhool Jate Hain;
Tu Zindagi Main Sabse Azeez Hai Hamein;
Tujhse Har Bar Yeh Kehna Bhool Jaate Hain!

 Roye To Bahut Teri Bewafai Ke Baad; 
Teri Yaad Na Gai Tere Jaane Ke Baad;
Tum Hamesha Khush Rehna;
Bas Mere Saath Kiya Yeh Ek Wada Nibhana!

 Udaas Na Hona Kyon Ki Main Sath Hoon;
Samne Na Sahi Par Aas Paas Hoon;
Aankhon Ko Band Karo Dil Se Yaad Karo;
Main Hamesha Aap Ke Liye Ek Ehsaas Hoon!

 Sabhi Naghme Saaz Mein Gaaye Nahi Jate;
Sabhi Log Mehfil Mein Bulae Nahi Jate;
Kuch Pass Reh Kar Bhi Yaad Nahi Aate;
Kuch Dur Rehkar Bhi Bhulaye Nahi Jate!

 Apni To Zindagi Ki Ajeeb Kahani Hai;
Jis Cheez Ko Chaha Wo Hi Begani Hai;
Haste Hain Dunia Ko Hasane Ke Liye Warna;
Dunia Doob Jaye In Ankhon Main Itna Pani Hai!

 Humne Bhi Kisi Se Pyar Kiya Tha;
Hatho Me Phool Lekar Intezar Kiya Tha;
Bhul Unki Nahi Bhul Toh Hamari Thi;
Kyon Ki Unho Ne Nahi, Humne Unse Pyar Kiya Tha!

 Jab Kisi Ke Sapne Kisi Ke Armaan Ban Jaye;
Jab Kisi Ki Hassi Kisi Ki Muskaan Ban Jaye;
Pyaar Kehte Hai Usse;
Jab Kisi Ki Saanse Kisi Ki Jaan Ban Jaye!

 Zakhm Itne Bade Hain Izhaar Kya Karein;
Hum Khud Nishana Ban Gaye Vaar Kya Karein;
Mar Gaye Hum Lekin Khuli Reh Gai Ankhen;
Ab Isse Zyada Kisi Ka Intezaar Kya Karein!

 Pyaar Aur Dosti Mein Itna Fark Paya Hai;
Pyaar Ne Sahaara Diya Aur Dost Ne Nibhaaya Hai;
Kis Rishte Ko Gehara Kahu;
Ek Ne Zindagi Di Aur Dusre Ne Jeena Sikhaaya Hai!

 Pyar Ke Panno Se Bhari Kitab Ho Tum;
Rishton Ke Phulo Mein Gulab Ho Tum;
Kuch Log Kehte Hai Ki Pyar Sacha Nahi Hota;
Unn Logon Ke Har Sawaal Ka Jawab Ho Tum!

 Mohabbat Ke Sapne Dikhatae Bohat Hain;
Wo Raaton Main Hum Ko Jagate Bohat Hain;
Main Ankhon Main Kajal Lagaon To Kaise;
Inn Ankhon Ko Log Rulatae Bohat Hain!

 Jeene Ki Khwaish Mein Har Roz Marte Hain;
Wo Aaye Na Aaye Hum Intezaar Karte Hain;
Jutha Hi Sahi Mere Yaar Ka Vaada Hai;
Hum Sach Maankar Aitbar Karte Hain!

 Kisi Ki Yaadon Ko Rok Paana Mushkil Hai;
Rote Hue Dil Ko Manana Mushkil Hai;
Yeh Dil Apno Ko Kitna Yaad Karta Hai;
Yeh Kuch Lafzon Mein Bayan Kar Paana Mushkil Hai!

 Zindagi Ke Liye Jaan Jaroori Hai;
Jeene Ke Liye Armaan Jaroori Hai;
Hamare Paas Chahe Ho Kitne Bhi Gham;
Tere Chehre Par Muskan Jaroori Hai!

 Ruth Jao Kitna Bhi Mana Lenge;
Dur Jao Kitna Bhi Bula Lenge;
Dil Aakhir Dil Hai Sagar Ki Ret Toh Nahi;
Ki Naam Likh Kar Usse Mita Denge!

 Aap Ne Nazar Se Nazar Kab Mila Di;
Hamari Zindagi Jhoomkar Muskura Di;
Zubaan Se To Hum Kuch Bhi Na Keh Sakey;
Par Nigahon Ne Dil Ki Kahani Suna Di!

 Pyaar Jab Milta Nahi Toh Hota Kyon Hai;
Agar Khwabon Mein Wo Aaye Toh Insaan Sota Kyon Hai;
Jab Yahi Pyaar Aankhon Ke Samne Kisi Aur Ka Ho Jaye;
Toh Dil Itna Rota Kyon Hai!

 Har Lamha Aapke Honthon Pe Muskan Rahe;
Khuda Kare Har Gham Se Aap Anjaan Rahe;
Mehak Uthe Jis Se Zindagi Aapki;
Hamesha Aapke Pas Wo Insaan Rahe!

 Meri Kabar Pe Mat Gulaab Le Kar Aana;
Na Hi Haathon Mein Chiraag Le Kar Aana;
Payasa Hu Main Barso Se Jaanam;
Botal Sharab Ki Aur Ek Glass Le Kar Aana!

 Apni Aankhon Ke Samandar Mein Utar Jaane De;
Tera Mujrim Hun Mujhe Doob Kar Mar Jaane De;
Zakham Kitne Diye Hain Teri Chaahat Ne Mujko;
Sochta Hun Tujh Se Kahoon Magar Jaane De!

 Mil Kar Bichadna Dastoor Hai Zindagi Ka;
Ek Ye Hi Qissa Mashoor Hai Zindagi Ka;
Beete Hue Pal Laut Kar Nahi Aate;
Yehi Sabse Bada Kasoor Hai Zindagi Ka!

 Aap Bhulakar Dekho, Hum Phir Bhi Yaad Aayenge;
Aapke Chahne Walon Mein Aapko Hum Hi Nazar Aayenge;
Aap Thak Jaoge Pee-Pee Kar Paani;
Par Hum Hichki Bankar Aapko Yaad Aayenge!

 Us Ke Saath Rehte-Rehte, Us Ki Chahat Si Ho Gayi Hai;
Us Se Baat Karte Karte, Uski Aadat Si Ho Gayi Hai;
Ek Pal Na Mile Toh Bechani Si Lagti Hai,
Dosti Nibhate-Nibhate, Us Se Mohabbat Si Ho Gayi Hai!

 Sirf Nazdeekiyon Se Mohabbat Hua Nahi Karti;
Fasle Jo Dilon Mein Ho To Fir Chahat Hua Nahi Karti;
Agar Naraz Ho Khafa Ho To Shikayat Karo Humse;
Khamosh Rehne Se Dilon Kee Dooriyan Mita Nahi Karti!

 Jisne Kabhi Chahaton Ka Paigaam Likha Tha;
Jisne Apna Sab Kuch Mere Naam Likha Tha;
Suna Hai Aaj Use Mere Zikar Se Bhi Nafrat Hai;
Jisne Kabhi Apne Dil Par Mera Naam Likha Tha!

 Mohabbat Kee Hawa Jism Kee Dawa Ban Gayi;
Doori Aapki Meri Chahat Kee Saza Ban Gayi;
Kaise Bhulun Aapko Ek Pal Ke Liye;
Aapki Yaad Hamare Jeene Kee Wajah Ban Gayi!

 Tum Aaye  Ho, Na Shab-e-Intezar Guzri Hai,      
Talash Mein Hai Sahar, Baar, Baar Guzri Hai;
                                                                                 
Junoon Mein Jitni Bhi Guzri Bekar Guzri Hai,
Agarche Dil Pe Kharabi Hazaar Guzri Hai;

Woh Baat Sare Fasane Mein Jiska Zikr Na Tha,
Woh Baat Un Ko Bahut Nagavar Guzri Hai;

Na Gul Khile Hain, Na Un Se Mile Hain, Na Mai Pi Hai,
Ajeeb Rang Mein Ab Ke Bahaar, Guzri Hai;

Chaman Pe Gharat-e-Gulchin Se Jane Kya Guzri,
Qafas Se Aaj Saba Be-Qarar Guzri Hai!

 Ulti Ho Gayi Sab Tadbeerein Kuchh Na Dawa Ne Kaam Kiya,
Dekha ! Is Beemaari-E-Dil Ne Aakhir Kaam Tammam Kiya;



Ahad-E-Jawaani Ro Ro Kaata, Peeri Mein Li Aankhein Moond,
Yaani Raat Bahut The Jaage, Subah Huyi Aaraam Kiya;



Naahak Ham Majbooron Par Yeh Tohmat Hai Mukhtaari Ki,
Chaahte Hain So Aap Kare Hain Hamko Abas Badnaam Kiya;



Yaan Ke Sapaid-O-Siyaah Mein Hamko Dakhl Jo Hai So Itna Hai,
Raat Ko Ro Ro Subah Kiya Ya Din Ko Jun Tun Shaam Kiya;



'Meer' Ke Deen-O-Mazhab Ko Ab Poocho Kya Ho Un Ne To,
Kashqaan Khaincha, Deher Mein Baitha, Kab Ka Tarq-Islaam Kiya!

 Yeh Narm Narm Hawa Jhilmila Rahe Hain Chirag,

Tere Khyal Kee Khushboo Se Bas Rahe Hain Dimag;

Dilon Ko Tere Tabassum Kee Yaad Yun Aayi,

Ki Jagmaga Uthe Jis Tarah Mandiron Mein Chirag;

Tamaam Shola-E-Gul Hai Tamaam Mauj-E-Bahaar,

Ki Taa-Had-E-Nigaah-E-Shauq Lahlahate Hain Baag;

Nayi Zameen, Naya Aasmaan, Nayi Duniya,

Suna To Hai Ki Mohabbat Ko In Dinon Hai Farag;

Dilon Mein Daag-E-Mohabbat Ka Ab Yeh Aalam Hai,

Ki Jaise Neend Mein Doobe Hon Pichali Raat Chirag;

Firaq Bazm-E-Chiragan Hai Mehfil-E-Rindan,

Saje Hain Pighli Hui Aag Se Chalkate Ayaag!

 Itna To Dosti Ka Silaah Dijiye Mujhe,
Apna Samajh Ke Zeher Pila Dijiye Mujhe;

Uthe Na Taa-Ke Aap Ki Janib Nazar Koi,
Jitni Bhi Tohmtain Hain Lagaa Dijiye Mujhe;

Kyon Aap Ki Khushi Ko Mera Gham Kare Udaas,
Ik Talkhh Haadsa Hun Bhula Dijiye Mujhe;

Main Aap Ke Kareeb Hi Hota Hun Har Ghadi,
Mauka Kabhi Pade To Sada Dijiye Mujhe;

Har Cheez Dastiyaab Hai Bazaar Mein Adam,
Jhoothi Khushi Khareed Ke La Dijiye Mujhe!

 Tamanaaon Main Uljhaaya Geya Hoon,
Khilone De Ke Behlaaya Geya Hoon;

Hoon Iss Kuuche Ke Har Zaray Se Waqif,
Idhar Se Mudatton Aaya Geya Hoon;

Nahin Uthte Qadam Kyun Jaanib-E-Dair,
Kisi Masjid Main Behkaaya Geya Hoon;

Dil-E-Muztar Se Pooch Ae Raunak-E-Bazm,
Main Khud Aaya Nahin Laaya Geya Hoon;

Savera Hai Bohat Ae Shor-E-Mehshar,
Abhi Bekaar Uthvaaya Geya Hoon;

Sataya Aa Ke Pehron Aarzuu Ne,
Jo Dum Bhar Aap Main Paaya Geya Hoon;

Kuja Main Aur Kuja Ae Shad Duniya,
Kahan Se Kis Jagah Laaya Geya Hoon!

 Hum Musaafir Yun Hi Masroof-E-Safar Jaayen Ge,
Be-Nishaan Ho Gaye Jab Shehar To Ghar Jaayen Ge;

Kis Kadar Hoga Yahan Mehr-O-Wafa Ka Maatam,
Hum Teri Yaad Se Jis Roz Utar Jaayen Ge;

Jauhri Band Kiye Jaate Hain Bazaar-E-Sukhan,
Hum Kise Bechne Almaas-O-Gauhar Jayen Ge;

Nemat-E-Zeest Ka Yeh Karz Chukega Kaise,
Laakh Ghabra Ke Yeh Kehte Hain Rahen Mar Jaayen Ge;

Shayad Apna Bhi Koi Bait Hudi-Khvan Ban Kar,
Saath Jaaye Ga Mere Yaar Jidhar Jaayen Ge;

Faiz Aate Hain Rah-E-Ishq Main Jo Sakht Maqaam,
Aane Walon Se Kaho Hum To Guzar Jaayen Ge!

 Na Ho Yaa Rabb Aisi Tabiyat Kisi Kee,
Ki Hans Hans Ke Dekhe Museebat Kisi Kee;

Jafaa Un Se Mujh Se Wafa Kaise Chhute,
Ye Sach Hai Nahi Chhutati Aadat Kisi Kee;

Achhoota Jo Gham Ho To Is Mein Bhi Khush Hun,
Nahi Mujh Ko Manzoor Shirkat Kisi Kee;

Haseeno Kee Dono Adayein Hain Dil-Bar,
Kisi Kee Haya To Shararat Kisi Kee;

Mujhe Gum-Shuda Dil Ka Gham Hai To Ye Hai,
Ke Is Mein Bhari Thi Mohabbat Kisi Kee;

Bahut Roye Hum Yaad Mein Apne Dil Kee,
Jahan Dekhi Nanhi Si Turbat Kisi Kee!

 Mujhse Milne Ke Wo
Mujhse Milne Ke Wo Karta Thaa Bahane Kitne,
Ab Guzarega Mere Saath Zamaane Kitne;
 
Main Gira Tha To Bahut Log Ruke The Lekin, 
Sochta Hun Mujhe Aaye The Uthane Kitne;
 
Jis Tarah Maine Tujhe Apna Bana Rakha Hai, 
Sochte Honge Yahi Baat Na Jaane Kitne;
 
Tum Naya Zakham Lagao Tumhein Is Se Kya Hai,
Bharne Wale Hain Abhi Zakham Purane Kitne!

 Jhonka Idhar Na Aaye Naseem-e-Bahaar Ka,
Naazuk Bahut Hai Phool Charaag-e-Mazaar Ka; 

Phir Baithe-Baithe Vaad-e-Vasl Us Ne Kar Liya, 
Phir Uth Khada Hua Vahi Rog Intezaar Ka; 

Shaakhon Se Barg-e-Gul Nahi Jhadte Hain Baag Mein, 
Zevar Utaar Raha Hai Uroos-e-Bahaar Ka; 

Har Gul Se Laalazaar Mein Ye Puchta Hun Main, 
Tu Hi Pata Bata De Dil-e-Daagdaar Ka; 

Is Pyaar Se Fishaar Diya Gor-e-Tang Ne, 
Yaad Aa Geya Maza Mujhe Aagosh-e-Yaar Ka; 

Hilti Nahi Hawa Se Chaman Mein Ye Daaliyan,
Munh Choomte Hain Phool Uroos-e-Bahaar Ka; 

Uthta Hai Naza Mein Vo Sarhane Se Ai 'Ameer', 
Mitta Hai Aasra Dil-e-Ummeedvaar Ka!

 Koi Naata Na Mohabbat Ke Barabar Nikla,
Toot Kar Chaha Jise Woh Sitamgar Nikla;

Yun To Har Lehar Se Thi Apni Shanasayi Bahut,
Samjha Sahil Jise Woh Gham Ka Samandar Nikla;

Rooh Mein Jhaanka To Yeh Mehsoos Hua Mujh Ko,
Itna Zarkhaiz Jo Lagta Tha Woh Banjar Nikla;

Narmi Hathon Mein Na Garmi Saanson Mein Magar,
Maine Chuu Kar Use Dekha To Woh Patthar Nikla!

 Deedaar Ki Hawas Hai Na Shauq-E-Visaal Hai,
Azaad Har Khayal Se Mast-E-Khayal Hai;

Keh Do Yeh Kohkan Se Hi Marna Nahi Kamaal,
Mar Mar Ke Hijr-E-Yaar Main Jeena Kamaal Hai;

Fatva Diya Hai Mufti Abr-E-Bahaar Ne,
Tauba Ka Khooon Baada-Kashon Ko Halaal Hai;

Aankhen Bata Rahi Hain Jaage Ho Raat Ko,
In Saaghron Mein Buu-E-Sharab-E-Visaal Hai;

Barsaao Teer Mujh Pe Par Itna Jaan Lo,
Pehlu Mein Dil Hai Dil Mein Tumhara Khayal Hai;

Aankhen Lada Ke Un Se Hum Aafaat Mein Pad Gaye,
Aankhon Ki Har Zubaan Pe Dil Ka Sawaal Hai;

Bhutt Keh Diya Jo Maine To Ab Bolte Nahin,
Itni Si Baat Ka Tumhe Itna Khayal Hai;

Pucha Jo Unse Jaante Ho Tum Jaleel Ko,
Bole Ke Haan Woh Shayer-E-Naazuk-Khayal Hai!

 Khayaal-e-Yaar Mein Mujh Ko Yun Hi Madhosh Rehne Do,
Na Pucho Raat Ka Qissa Mujhe Khamosh Rehne Do;

Sunaya Vasl Ka Qissa To Mere Dost Yun Bole,
Kahan Tum Kahan Us Kee Haseen Aghosh Rehne Do;

Mujhe Maloom Hai Us Ne Mera Hona Nahin Lekin,
Meri Umeed Mat Todo Mujhe Pur-Josh Rehne Do;

Mohabbat Jurm Hai Mera Mujhe Iqraar Hai Iska,
Wafaa Ilzaam Hai To Phir Mere Sar Dosh Rehne Do;

Kitaab-e-Ishq Se Hum Par Yehi Raaz Khula Hai,
Paaye Jo Jaam Ulfat Ka Usse Meh-Nosh Rehne Do!

 Muddat Se Lapata Hai Khudaa Jaane Kya Hua,
Phirta Tha Ek Shakhs Tumhein Puchta Huaa;

Wo Zindgi Thi Aap The Ya Koi Khwab Tha,
Jo Kuch Tha Ek Lamhe Ko Bas Samna Hua;

Hum Ne Tere Bagair Bhi Jee Kar Dikha Diya,
Ab Ye Sawal Kya Hai Ki Phir Dil Ka Kya Hua;

So Bhi Wo Tu Na Dekh Saki Ai Hawa-e-Dahar,
Seene Mein Ik Charag Rakha Tha Jala Hua;

Duniya Ko Zid Numaish-e-Zakhm-e-Jigar Se Thi,
Fariyad Maine Kee Na Zamana Khafa Hua;

Har Anjuman Mein Dhyaan Usi Anjuman Ka Hai,
Jagaa Ho Jaise Khwaab Koi Dekhta Hua;

Ye Iztiraab-e-Shauq Hai 'Akhtar' Ki Gum-Rahi,
Main Apne Kaafile Se Hun Koson Badha Hua!

 Ab Woh Ghar Tak Viraana Tha Bas Viraana Zinda Tha,
Sab Aankhen Damm Tod Chuki Thi Aur Main Tanha Zinda Tha;

Saari Gali Sunsaan Padi Thi Baad-E-Fana Ke Pehre Mein,
Hijr Ke Dalaan Aur Aangan Mein Bas Ik Saaya Zinda Tha;

Woh Dopeher Apni Rukhsat Ki Aisa Waisa Dhoka Thi,
Apne Andar Apni Laash Uthaaye Main Jhootha Zinda Tha;

Thi Woh Ghar Raatein Bhi Kahani Vaade Aur Phir Din Ginna,
Aana Tha Jaane Wale Ko Jaane Wala Zinda Tha;

Dastak Dene Wale Bhi The Dastak Sunne Wale Bhi,
Tha Abaad Mohalla Sara Har Darwaza Zinda Tha;

Peele Patton Ko Seh-Pehr Ki Vehshat Pursa Deti Thi,
Aangan Mein Ik Aundhe Ghade Par Bas Ik Kava Zinda Tha!

 Zara Si Der Ko Aaye The Khwab Aankhon Mein,
Phir Us Ke Baad Musalsal Azaab Aankhon Mein;

Wo Jis Ke Naam Kee Nisbat Se Roshani Tha Wujood,
Khattak Raha Hai Wohi Aaftaab Aankhon Mein;

Jinhen Mata-E-Dil-O-Jaan Samajh Rahe The Hum,
Wo Aaine Bhi Hue Behijab Aankhon Mein;

Ajab Tarah Ka Hai Mausam Kee Khak Udti Hai,
Wo Din Bhi The Ki Khile The Gulab Aankhon Mein;

Mere Ghazal Teri Wahshaton Kee Khair, Ke Hai,
Bahut Dinon Se Bahut Iztarab Aankhon Mein;

Na Jane Kaisi Qayamat Ka Peshkhema Hai,
Ye Uljhanein Teri Be-Intasaab Aankhon Mein!

 Aye Dost Teri Aankh Jo Nam Hai To Mujhe Kya,
Main Khoob Hansunga Tujhe Gham Hai To Mujhe Kya;

Kya Main Ne Kaha Tha Ki Zamane Se Bhala Kar,
Ab Tu Bhi Sazavar-e-Sitam Hai To Mujhe Kya;

Haan Le Le Kasam Gar Mujhe Qatra Bhi Mila Ho,
Tu Shaaki-e-Arbaab-e-Karam Hai To Mujhe Kya;

Jis Dar Se Nidamat Ke Siva Kuch Nahi Milta,
Us Dar Pe Tera Sar Bhi Jo Khham Hai To Mujhe Kya;

Maine To Pukara Hai Mohabbat Ke Ufaq Se,
Raaste Mein Tere Sang-e-Haram Hai To Mujhe Kya;

Bhoola To Na Hoga Tujhe Suqraat Ka Anjaam,
Haathon Mein Tere Saaghar-e-Sam Hai To Mujhe Kya;

Patthar Na Paden Gar Sar-e-Bazaar To Kehna,
Tu Motarif-e-Husn-e-Sanam Hai To Mujhe Kya;

Main Sarmad-o-Mansoor Bana Hun Teri Khaatir,
Yeh Bhi Teri Umeed Se Kam Hai To Mujhe Kya!

 Ik Aaalam-E-Hijraan Hi Ab Hum Ko Pasand Aaya,
Yeh Khaana-E-Viraaan Hi Ab Hum Ko Pasand Aaya;

Benaaam-O-Nishaan Rehna Ghurbat Ke Ilaaqe Main,
Yeh Sheher Bhi Dilkash Tha Tab Hum Ko Pasand Aaya;

Tha Laal Hua Manzar Sooraj Ke Nikalne Se,
Woh Waqt Tha Woh Chehra Jab Hum Ko Pasand Aaya;

Hai Qataa-E-Talluq Se Dil Khush To Bahut Apna,
Ik Hadh Hi Banaa Lena Kab Hum Ko Pasand Aaya;

Aana Woh 'Munir' Us Ka Be-Khauf-O-Khatar Hum Tak,
Yeh Turfaa Tamaasha Bhi Shab Hum Ko Pasand Aaya!

 Hans Ke Farmaate Hain Wo Dekh Kar Halat Meri, 
Kyon Tum Aasaan Samajhate The Mohabbat Meri; 

Baad Marane Ke Bhi Chhodi Na Rafaaqat Meri,
Meri Turbat Se Lagi Baithi Hai Hasrat Meri; 

Maine Aagosh-e-Tasavur Mein Bhi Khencha To Kaha, 
Pis Gayi Pis Gayi Bedard Nazakat Meri; 

Aaina Subah-e-Shab-e-Vasl Jo Dekha To Kaha,
Dekh Zaalim Ye Thi Shaam Ko Soorat Meri; 

Yaar Pehalu Mein Hai Tanhayi Hai Keh Do Nikle, 
Aaj Kyon Dil Mein Chhupi Baithi Hai Hasrat Meri; 

Husn Aur Ishq Hum Aagosh Nazar Aa Jaate, 
Teri Tasveer Mein Khinch Jaati Jo Hairat Meri; 

Kis Dhitaayi Se Vo Dil Chheen Ke Kehte Hain 'Ameer',
Vo Mera Ghar Hai Rahe Jis Mein Mohabbat Meri!

 Dushman Kee Dosti Hai Ab Ahale Vatan Ke Saath,
Hai Ab Khijaan Chaman Mein Naye	 Pairahan Ke Saath; 

Sar Par Hawaye Zulm Chale Sau Yatan Ke Saath, 
Apni Kulaah Kaj Hai Usi Baankpan Ke Saath; 

Kisne Kaha Ki Toot Geya Khanzare Phirang, 
Seene Pe Zakhme Nau Bhi Hai Daage Kuhan Ke Saath; 

Jhonke Jo Lag Rahe Hain Naseeme Bahaar Ke, 
Jumbish Mein Hai Kafas Bhi Aseere Chaman Ke Saath; 

Majrooh Kaafale Ki Mere Daastaan Ye Hai, 
Rehbar Ne Mil Ke Loot Liya Raahajan Ke Saath!

 Khamosh Chehre Par Hazaron Pehre Hote Hain;
Hansti Aankhon Mein Bhi Zakham Gehre Hote Hain;
Jinse Aksar Rooth Jaate Hain Hum;
Asal Mein Unse Hi Rishte Gehre Hote Hain!

 Meri Saari Zindagi Ko Be'samar Iss Ne Kiya;
Umar Meri Thi Magar,Isko Basar Iss Ne Kiya;

Main Bahut Kamzor Tha Iss Mulq Mein Hijrat Ke Baad;
Par Mujhe Iss Mulq Mein Kamzor'tar Iss Ne Kiya;

Rehbar Mera Bana Gumraah Karne Ke Liye;
Mujhko Seedhe Raaste Se Darbadar Iss Ne Kiya;

Shehar Mein Woh Moatbir Meri Gawahi Se Hua;
Phir Mujhe Iss Shehar Mein Na'moatbir Iss Ne Kiya;

Shehar Ko Barbaad Kar Ke Rakh Diya Iss Ne 'Munir';
Shehar Per Yeh Zulm Mere Naam Par Iss Ne Kiya!

 Ye Aarzoo Thi Tujhe Gul Ke Rubaru Karte,
Hum Aur Bulbul-e-Betaab Guftagu Karte;

Payaam Bar Na Mayassar Hua To Khoob Hua, 
Zubaan-e-Gair Se Kya Shar Kee Aarzoo Karte;

Meri Tarah Se Maah-o-Mahar Bhi Hain Aawara, 
Kisi Habeeb Ko Ye Bhi Hain Justaju Karte;

Jo Dekhte Teri Zanjeer-e-Zulf Ka Aalam, 
Aseer Hone Ke Aazaad Aarzoo Karte; 

Na Puch Aalam-e-Bargashta Tali-e-"Aatish", 
Barasati Aag Mein Jo Baaraan Kee Aarzoo Karte!

 Wo Mohabbat Bhi Teri Thi, Wo Nafrat Bhi Teri Thi;
Wo Apnapan Aur Thukrane Ki Ada Bhi Teri Thi;
Hum Apni Wafa Ka Insaf Kisse Maangte,
Wo Shehar Bhi Tera Tha Aur Adalat Bhi Teri Thi!

 Dhoop Bahut Hai Mausam Jal-Thal Bhejo Na,
Baba Mere Naam Ka Baadal Bhejo Na;

Molsari Kee Shaakhon Par Bhi Diye Jalen,
Shaakhon Ka Kesaraya Aanchal Bhejo Na;

Nanhi Munni Sab Chehkarein Kahaan Gayi,
Moron Ke Pairon Kee Payaal Bhejo Na;

Basti Basti Dehshat Kisne Bo Di Hai,
Galiyon Bazaaron Kee Hulchal Bhejo Na;

Saare Mausam Ek Umas Ke Aadi Hain,
Chhaanv Kee Khushbu, Dhoop Ka Sandal Bhejo Na;

Main Basti Mein Aakhir Kis Se Baat Karun,
Mere Jaisa Koi Paagal Bhejo Na!

 Ek Pal Mein Ek Sadi Ka Maza Humse Puchiye,
Do Din Kee Zindagi Ka Maza Humase Puchiye;

Bhoole Hai Raftaa-Raftaa Unhe Muddaton Mein Hum,
Kishto Mein Khudkushi Ka Maza Humse Puchiye; 
 
Aagaaz-e-Aashiqui Ka Maza Aap Jaaniye,
Anzaam-e-Aashiqui Ka Maza Humse Puchiye;

Jalte Diyo Mein Jalte Gharon Jaisi Lau Kahan,
Sarkaar Roshani Ka Maza Humase Puchiye;

Wo Jaan Hi Gaye Ki Humein Unse Pyaar Hai,
Aankhon Kee Mukhbari Ka Maza Humse Puchiye;

Hansne Ka Shaunk Humko Bhi Tha Aap Kee Tarah!

 Kahaan Tak Aankh Roegi Kahaan Tak Kiska Gham Hoga,
Mere Jaisa Yahan Koi Na Koi Roz Kam Hoga;

Tujhe Paane Kee Koshish Mein Kuch Itna Ro Chuka Hun Main,
Ki Tu Mil Bhi Agar Jaye To Ab Milne Ka Gham Hoga;

Samandar Kee Galatfehmi Se Koi Puch To Leta,
Zameen Ka Haunsala Kya Aise Toofaano Se Kam Hoga;

Mohabbat Naapne Ka Koi Paimana Nahi Hota,
Kahin Tu Badh Bhi Sakta Hai, Kahin Tu Mujh Se Kam Hoga!

 Yaad Nahi Kya Kya Dekha Tha Sare Manzar Bhool Gaye;
Ush Ke Galiyon Se Jab Laute Apna Bhi Ghar Bhool Gaye;
Khub Gaye Pardes Ki Apne Deewar-o-Dar Bhool Gaye;
Sheesh-Mahal Ne Aisa Ghera Matti Ke Ghar Bhool Gaye!

 Yaad Mein Apne Yaar-e-Jaani Kee,
Hum Ne Mar Mar Ke Zindagani Kee;

Dosto Ko Adu Kiya Hum Ne,
Kar Ke Taarif Yaar-e-Jaani Kee;

Kyon Na Ruswaa Kare Zamaane Mein,
Ye Kahani Gham-e-Nahani Kee;

Rooh Hoyegi Hashar Mein Sahab,
Ek Nishani Sara-e-Faani Kee;

Khaak-Saari Se Badh Geya Insaan,
Arz Par Sair Aasmaani Kee;

Zard Surat Pe Hijr Mein Na Hanso,
Sharah Hai Rang-e-Zaafaraani Kee;

Aaj Kal Lakhnow Mein Ai 'Akhtar',
Dhoom Hai Teri Khush-Bayaani Kee!

 Yaaro Kisi Qatil Se Kabhi Pyaar Na Maango,
Apne Hi Gale Ke Liye Talwar Na Maango;

Gir Jaoge Tum Apne Maseeha Kee Nazar Se,
Mar Kar Bhi Ilaaz-e-Dil-e-Beemar Na Maango;

Khul Jayega Is Tarah Nigahon Ka Bharam Bhi,
Kaanton Se Kabhi Phool Kee Mehakaar Na Maango;

Sach Baat Pe Milta Hai Sada Zehar Ka Pyala,
Jeena Hai To Phir Jeene Ke Izhaar Na Maango;

Us Cheez Ka Kya Zikar Jo Mumkin Hi Nahi Hai,
Sehara Mein Kabhi Sayaa-e-Deewar Na Maango!

 Kabhi Khaamosh Baithoge Kabhi Kuch Gungunaoge,
Main Utana Yaad Aaunga Mujhe Jitna Bhulaoge;

Koi Jab Puch Baithega Khamoshi Ka Sabab Tumse,
Bahut Samjhana Chahoge Magar Samjha Na Paoge;

Kabhi Duniya Mukkamal Ban Ke Aayegi Nigaahon Mein,
Kabhi Mere Kabhi Duniya Kee Har Ek Shah Mein Paoge;

Kahin Par Bhi Rahen Hum Tum Mohabbat Phir Mohabbat Hai,
Tumhein Hum Yaad Aayenge Humein Tum Yaad Aaoge!

 Kab Woh Zahir Hoga Aur Hairan Kar Dega Mujhe;
Jitni Bhi Mushkil Mein Hun Aasan Kar Dega Mujhe;
Roo-b-Roo Kar Ke Kabhi Apne Mehakte Surkh Honth;
Ek Do Pal Ke Liye Guldaan Kar Dega Mujhe!

 Nafrat Na Kabhi Karna Humse;
Yeh Hum Seh Nahi Paayenge;
Ek Baar Keh Dena Humse Zaroorat Nahi Ab Tumhari;
Kasam Khuda Kee Tumhari Duniya Se Hans Kar Chale Jayenge!

 Kuch Sochta Hun To Tera Khayal Aa Jata Hai;
Kuch Bolta Hun To Tera Naam Aa Jata Hai;
Kab Tak Chupa Ke Rakhun Dil Kee Baat Ko;
Uski Har Ada Par Mujhe Pyaar Aa Jata Hai!

 Ishq Ne Humein Benaam Kar Diya;
Har Khushi Se Humein Anjaan Kar Diya;
Humne To Kabhi Nahi Chaha Ki Humein Bhi Mohabbat Ho;
Lekin Aap Kee Ek Nazar Ne Humein Nilaam Kar Diya!

 Mil Bhi Jate Hain Toh Katara Ke Nikal Jaate Hain;
Haye Mausam Kee Tarah Dost Badal Jaate Hain;

Hum Abhi Tak Hain Giraftar-e-Mohabbat Yaaro;
Thokarein Kha Ke Suna Tha Ki Sambhal Jaate Hain;

Ye Kabhi Apni Jafa Par Na Hua Sharminda;
Hum Samajhate Rahe Patthar Bhi Pighal Jaate Hain;

Umar Bhar Jin Kee Wafaon Pe Bharosa Kije;
Waqt Padane Pe Wohi Log Badal Jaate Hain!

 Ye Din Bahaar Ke Ab Ke Bhi Raas Na Aa Sake,
Ki Gunche Khil To Sake Khil Ke Muskura Na Sake; 

Meri Tabahi Dil Par To Reham Kha Na Saki, 
Jo Roshani Mein Rahe Roshani Ko Pa Na Sake; 

Na Jaane Aah! Ki Un Aansuon Pe Kya Guzari, 
Jo Dil Se Aankh Tak Aaye Mishgaan Tak Aa Na Sake; 

Rahen Khulus-e-Mohabbat Ke Haadsaat Jahan,
Mujhe To Kya Mere Naqsh-e-Kadam Mita Na Sake;

KarenNge Mar Ke Baqa-e-Dawaam Kya Hasil, 
Jo Zindaa Reh Ke Muqaam-e-Hayat Pa Na Sake; 

Naya Zamanaa Banane Chale The Deewane,
Nayi Zameen, Naya Aasmaan Bana Na Sake!

 Main Bura Hi Sahi Bhala Na Sahi,
Par Teri Kaun See Jafaa Na Sahi;

Dard-e-Dil Hum To Un Se Keh Guzare,
Gar Unhone Nahi Suna Na Sahi;

Shab-e-Gham Mein Bala Se Shugal To Hai,
Naala-e-Dil Mera Rasa Na Sahi;

Dil Bhi Apna Nahi Raha Na Rahe,
Ye Bhi Ai Charkh-e-Fitnaa-Zaa Na Sahi;

Dekh To Lenge Wo Agar Aaye,
Taaqat-e-Arz-e-Muddaa Na Sahi;

Kuch To Aashiq Se Chhed-chhaad Rahi,
Kaj-Adaayi Sahi Adaa Na Sahi;

Kyon Bura Manate Ho Shikwa Mera,
Chalo Be-Jaa Sahi B-Jaa Na Sahi;

Uqada-e-Dil Hamara Ya Kismat,
Na Khula Tujh Se Ai Saba Na Sahi;

Vaaizo Band-e-Khuda To Hai 'Aish',
Hum Ne Maana Wo Parasa Na Sahi!

 Ishq Kee Duniya Mein Ek Hungama Barpaa Kar Diya;
Ai Khayal-e-Dost Ye Kya Ho Gaya Kya Kar Diya;

Zarre Zarre Ne Mera Afsana Sun Kar Daad Dee;
Main Ne Vahshat Mein Jahaan Ko Tera Shaida Kar Diya;

Toor Par Raah-e-Wafa Mein Bo Diye Kaante Kaleem;
Ishq Kee Vusaat Ko Masdood-e-Taqazaa Kar Diya;

Bistar-e-Mashriq Se Sooraj Ne Uthayaa Apana Sar;
Kis Ne Ye Mehfil Mein Zikr-e-Husn-e-Yaktaa Kar Diya;

Chashm-e-Nargis Jaa-e-Shabnam Khoon Royegi Nadeem;
Maine Jis Din Gulasitan Ka Raaz Ifsaa Kar Diya;

Mudda-e-Dil Kahun 'Ehasaan' Kis Umeed Par;
Wo Jo Chahenge Karenge Aur Jo Chaha Kar Diya!

 Khayaal-e-Husn Mein Yun Zindagi Tamaam Hui,
Haseen Subah Hui Aur Haseen Shaam Hui;

Baqaar-e-Ishq Bas Ab Sar Jhuka De Kadamon Par,
Udhar Se Tere Liye Sabaqat-e-Salaam Hui;

Har Ek Apni Jagah Khush Har Ek Yahi Samajha,
Nigah-e-Khaas B-Tarz-e-Nigaah-e-Aam Hui;

Nazar Mili To Tabassum Raha Khamoshi Par,
Nazar Phiri To Zara Himmat-e-Kalaam Hui;

Bas Ab To Tum Ne Mohabbat Ka Le Liya Badla,
Maaf Karna Jo Takleef-e-Inteqam Hui;

Hai Dekhne Hi Ka Waqfa Jise Samajhte Hain,
'Raza' Wo Dhoop Chadhi Din Dhala Wo Shaam Hui!

 Uljhe Na Zulf Se Jo Pareshaniyon Mein Hum,
Karte Hain Is Pe Naaz Ada-Daniyon Mein Hum;

Saragarm-Raqs-Tazaa Hain Kurbaniyon Mein Hum,
Shokhi Se Kiski Aaye Hain Jolaniyon Mein Hum;

Sabit Hai Jurme-Shikwa Na Zahir Gunahe-Rashq,
Hairan Hain Aap Apni Pareshaniyon Mein Hum;

Maare Khushi Ke Mar Gaye Subahe-Shabe-Firaaq,
Kitne Subuk Hue Hain Garaan-Jaaniyon Mein Hum;

Aata Hai Khwaab Mein Bhi Teri Zulf Ka Khyaal,
Betaur Ghir Gaye Hain Pareshaniyon Mein Hum;

Dekha Idhar Ko Tune Ki Bas Dam Nikal Geya,
Utare Nazar Se Apni Nigahabaniyon Mein Hum!

 Din Muradon Ke Aish Kee Raatein,
Haye Kya Ho Gayi Wo Barsaatein;

Raat Ko Baag Mein Mulaqaatein,
Yaad Hain Jaise Khwaab Kee Baatein;

Hasratein Sard Aahein Garm Aansu,
Layi Hai Barshagaal Saugatein;

Khwar Hain Yun Mere Shabaab Ke Din,
Jaise Jaadon Kee Chandni Raatein;

Dil Ye Kehta Hai Kunj-e-Raahat Hun,
Dekhna Gham-Naseeb Kee Baatein;v

Jin Ke Dam Se Shabaab Tha Zinda,
Hai 'Akhtar' Wo Ishq Kee Ghaatein!

 Ye Keh Gaye Hain Musafir Lute Gharon Wale,
Dare Hawa Se Parinde Khule Paron Wale;

Ye Mere Dil Kee Hawas Dasht-e-Be-Karan Jaisi,
Vo Teri Aankh Ke Tevar Samandaron Wale;

Hawa Ke Haath Mein Kaase Hain Zard Patton Ke,
Kahan Gaye Vo Sakhi Sabz Chadaron Wale;

Kahan Milenge Vo Agle Dino Ke Shehzade,
Pahan Ke Tan Pe Libaade Gada-Garon Wale;

Pahadiyon Mein Ghire Ye Bujhe Bujhe Raaste,
Kabhi Idhar Se Guzarte The Lashkaron Wale;

Unhi Pe Ho Kabhi Nazil Azaab Aag Ajal,
Vahi Nagar Kabhi Theharen Pyambaron Wale;

Tere Supurd Karun Aaine Muqaddar Ke,
Idhar To Aa Mere Khush-Rang Pattharon Wale;

Kisi Ko Dekh Ke Chup Chup Se Kyon Hue 'Mohsin',
Kahan Gaye Vo Iraade Sukhan-Varon Wale!

 Jo Afsaane Dil Mein Rehte Hain, Wo Aankhon Mein Nahi Rehte;
Bahut Se Harf Aise Hain, Jo Lafzon Mein Nahi Rehte;
Kitabon Mein Likhe Jaate Hain, Duniya Bhar Ke Afsaane;
Magar Jin Mein Haqeeqat Ho, Wo Kitabon Mein Nahi Rehte!

 Gul Tera Rang Churaa Laye Hain Gulzaron Mein,
Jal Raha Hun Bhari Barsaat Kee Baucharon Mein;

Mujhse Katra Ke Nikal Ja, Magar Ai Jaan-e-Haya,
Dil Kee Lau Dekh Raha Hun Tere Rukhsaron Mein;v

Husn-e-Begana-e-Ehsaas-Jamaal Achhaa Hai,
Gunche Khilate Hain To Bik Jaate Hain Bazaaron Mein;

Jikr Karte Hain Tera Mujhse Ba-Unvaan-e-Jafaa,
Charagar Phool Piro Laye Hain Talwaron Mein;

Zakham Chhup Sakte Hain Lekin Mujhe Fan Hi Saugandh,
Gham Kee Daulat Bhi Hai Shaamil Mere Shahkaron Mein;

Mujhko Nafarat Se Nahi Pyaar Se Masloob Karo,
Main To Shaamil Hun Mohabbat Ke Gunahwaron Mein!

 Hijr Kee Shab Mein Qaid Kare Yaa Subh-e-Visal Mein Rakhe,
Achha Maula Teri Marzi Tu Jis Haal Mein Rakhe;

Khel Ye Kaisaa Khel Rahi Hai Dil Se Teri Mohabbat,
Ik Pal Kee Sarshari De Aur Dino Malaal Mein Rakhe;

Maine Sari Khushbuein Aanchal Se Baandh Ke Rakhi,
Shayad In Ka Jikr Tu Apne Kisi Sawal Mein Rakhe;

Kis Se Tere Aane Kee Sargoshi Ko Sunte Hi,
Maine Kitne Phool Chune Aur Apni Shaal Mein Rakhe;

Mushkil Ban Kar Toot Padi Hai Dil Par Ye Tanhayi,
Ab Jaane Ye Kab Tak Us Ko Apne Jaal Mein Rakhe!

 Unhe Sawal Hi Lagata Hai Mera Rona Bhi,
Ajab Saza Hai Jahaan Mein Gareeb Hona Bhi;

Ye Raat Bhi Hai Odhana-Bichona Bhi,
Is Ek Raat Mein Hai Jaagna Bhi Sona Bhi;

Ajeeb Shehar Hai Ki Ghar Bhi Raaston Kee Tarah,
Kaisa Naseeb Hai Raaton Ko Chup Ke Rona Bhi;

Khule Mein Soyenge Motiya Ke Phoolon Se,
Sajaa Lo Zulf Basa Lo Zara Bichona Bhi;

'Aziz' Kaisi Yeh Saudagaron Kee Basti Hai,
Garaan Hai Dil Se Yahan Kaath Ka Khilona Bhi!

 Paya Tumko To Hum Ko Laga Tumko Kho Diya;
Hum Dil Pe Roye Aur Yeh Dil Hum Pe Ro Diya;
Kyon Is Ke Fansle Humein Manzoor Ho Gaye;
Kitne Hue Kareeb Ki Hum Door Ho Gaye!

 Unki Tasveer Ko Seene Se Laga Lete Hain;
Iss Tarah Judai Ka Gham Mita Lete Hain;
Kisi Tarha Zikar Na Ho Jaye Unko Hamare Dard Ka;
Hans Kar Bheegi Palkon Mein Sab Dard Chupa Lete Hain!

 Chal Diye Uth Ke Su-e-Shehar-e-Wafa Ku-e-Habib;
Puch Lena Tha Kisi Khak Basar Se Pehle;

Ishq Pehle Bhi Kiya Hijr Ka Gham Bhi Dekha;
Itne Tadpe Hain Na Ghabraye Na Tarse Pehle;

Jee Bahalta Hi Nahin Ab Koi Saath Koi Pal;
Raat Dhalti Hi Nahin Char Pahar Se Pehle;

Ham Kisi Dar Pe Na Thithak Na Kahin Dastak Di;
Saikadon Dar The Meri Jaan Tere Dar Se Pehle;

Chand Se Ankh Mili Jee Ka Ujala Jaga;
Hum Ko So Bar Hui Subah Sahar Se Pehle!

 Is Ada Se Wo Wafaa Karte Hain;
Koi Jaane Ki Wafa Karte Hain;

Humko Chodoge To Pachtaoge;
Hansne Walon Se Hansa Karte Hain;

Ye Batata Nahi Koi Mujhko;
Dil Jo Aa Jaye To Kya Karte Hain;

Husn Ka Haq Nahi Rehta Baki;
Har Ada Mein Wo Ada Karte Hain;

Kis Kadar Hain Teri Aankhein Bebak;
In Se Fitne Bhi Hya Karte Hain;

Is Liye Dil Ko Laga Rakha Hai;
Is Mein Dil Ko Laga Rakha Hai;

'Daagh' Tu Dekh To Kya Hota Hai;
Jabr Par Jabr Kiya Karte Hain!

 Tere Khyaal Mein Kuch Aise Gum Raha Barson;
Main Apne Aap Se Bhi Mil Nahin Saka Barson;

Kahin Woh Zaaiqa Tehleel Hi Na Ho Jae;
Main Tum Se Mil Kar Kisi Se Nahi Mila Barson;

Kaha Tha Tum Ne Ke Tum Laut Ke Aaoge Ek Din;
So Main Jahaan Tha Wahin Par Khada Raha Barson;

Tere Baghair Meri Umar Raayegaan Guzri;
Koi Bhi Kaam Nahin Theek Se Hua Barson;

Tumhare Haath Kee Dastak Kee Aaas Mein 'Mohsin';
Main Apne Ghar Se Kahin Bhi Nahin Geya Barson!

 Koi Samajhaiye Ki Kya Rang Hai Maikhane Ka,
Aankh Saqi Ke Uthe, Naam Ho Paimane Ka;

Garmi-e-Shama Ka Afsana Sunane Walo,
Raqs Dekha Nahi Tum Ne Abhi Parwane Ka;

Chashm-e-Saqi Mujhe Har Gham Pe Yaad Aati Hai,
Raasta Bhool Na Jaun Kahin Maikhane Ka;

Ab To Har Sham Guzarti Hai Isi Kuche Mein,
Ye Nateeza Hua Naseh Tere Samajhane Ka;

Ab To Har Manzil Se Guzarna To Hai Aasan 'Iqbal',
Ishq Hai Naam Khud Apne Se Guzar Jane Ka!

 Chand Tahniyon Ke Kafan Pe, Syahi Ki Kaalikh Mal Dete Hain,
Khyaal "Raaz" Ke Bejeaa, Kyon Bezubaan Ki Laash Masal Dete Hain;

Daur-O-Jaam Ki Mehfilon Mein, Saagaro Minaa Tak Hain Sab Aziz,
Ashk Chalkein To Hum Sharminda, Woh Sar Jhatakte Hain, Chal Dete Hain;

Ghamgusaari To Ki Aksar, Sochta Hun Ki Chand Pareshaniyan Meri Bhi To Hain,
Hazi, Qazi, Niyazi Koi Ho, Kuch To Aise Milao Jo 'Hal' Dete Hain;

Nekdili, Saafgoi, Dayanat Ke Sab Jazbon Ko Kitabon Mein Hi Rehne Den,
Tazurba Hai, Bargalate Hain Aalim Kehkar, Ki Inka Farishte 'Fal' Dete Hain;

Ye Jalwa-E-Husn, Ye Chamak, Ye Nazare Jahan Ke, "Raaz" Ke Vaaste Na Bhi Sahi,
Itna To Humein Bhi Myssar, Maula Maula Kehte Bhi Khyaal To Machal Dete Hain!

 Ek Khwaish Sirhane Rakh Do Na;
Aaj Mujh Pe Tum Inayat Kar Do Na;
Zara Chupke Se Khamoshi Se;
Tum Izhar-e-Mohabbat Kar Do Na!

 Aashiqon Ko Ai Falak Devega Tu Aazaar Kya;
Dushman-e-Jaan Un Ka Thoda Hai Dil-e-Beemar Kya;

Rashk Aave Kyon Na Mujh Ko Dekhana Us Kee Taraf;
Takataki Baandhe Hue Hai Rozan-e-Deewar Kya;

Aah Ne To Kheema-e-Gardon Ko Phoonka Dekhen Ab;
Rang Laate Hain Hamare Deeda-e-Khoon-Baar Kya;

Murg-e-Dil Ke Vaaste Ai Hum-Safeero Kam Hai Kyon;
Kuch Kaza Ke Teer Se Teer-e-Nigah-e-Yaar Kya;

Chal Ke Mai-Khaane Hi Mein Ab Dil Ko Bahlao Zara;
'Aish' Yaa Baithe Hue Karte Ho Tum Begaar Kya!

 Ye Kya Jaane Mein Jana Hai, Jaate Ho Khafaa Hokar;
Main Tab Janu Mere Dil Se Chale Jao Juda Hokar;
Qayamat Tak Udegi Dil Se Uthkar Khaak Aankhon Tak;
Isi Raaste Geya Hai Hasraton Ka Kafila Hokar!

 Sehmi Si Nigahon Mein Khawab Hum Jaga Denge,
Sooni Si Rahon Mein Phool Hum Bicha Denge;
Hamare Sang Muskura Kar To Dekhiye;
Har Gham Aapka Hum Bhula Denge!

 Giri Is Tabassum Ki Bijali Ajal Par;
Andhere Ka Ho Noor Mein Kya Guzara;

Justjoo Jis Gul Ki Tarpati Thi Ai Bulbul Mujhe;
Khoobi-e-Qismat Se Aakhir Mil Gaya Woh Gul Mujhe;

Parwana Tujhse Karta Hai Ai Shama Pyaar Kyon;
Ye Jaane Beqaraar Hai Tujh Par Nisar Kyon;

Qismat Buri Sahi Par Tabiyat Buri Nahin;
Hai Shukr Ki Jagah Ki Shikayat Nahin Mujhe;

Zulm Hai Gar Na Do Sakun Ki Daad;
Qahar Hai Gar Karona Mujhko Pyaar;

Hoga Koi Aisa Bhi Ki Ghalib Ko Na Jaane;
Shayar Toh Wah Achchha Hai Par Badnaam Bahut Hai!

 Sirf Itna Hi Kaha Hai, Pyaar Hai Tumse;
Jazbaton Kee Koi Numaish Nahi Kee;
Pyaar Ke Badle Sirf Pyaar Manga Hai;
Rishte Kee To Koi Guzarish Nahi Kee!

 Dil Mein Mehak Rahe Hain Kisi Aarzoo Ke Phool;
Palkon Pe Khilnewale Hain Shayad Lahoo Ke Phool;

Ab Tak Hai Koi Baat Mujhe Yaad Harf-Harf;
Ab Tak Main Chun Raha Hoon Kisi Guftagoo Ke Phool;

Kaliyan Chatak Rahi Thi Ki Aawaz Thi Koi;
Ab Tak Sma-Ato Mein Hai Ik Khushguloo Ke Phool;

Mere Lahoo Ka Rang Hai Har Noke-Khar Par;
Sehra Mein Har Taraf Hai Meri Justaju Ke Phool;

Deewane Kal Jo Log The Phoolon Ke Ishq Mein;
Ab Unke Daaman Mein Bharein Hain Rafoo Ke Phool!

 Kyon Phir Rahe Ho Kaif Ye Khatre Ka Ghar Liye,
Ye Kaanch Ka Shareer Ye Kaagaz Ka Sar Liye;

Sholey Nikal Rahe Hain Gulabon Ke Jism Se,
Titali Na Ja Kareeb Ye Resham Ke Par Liye;

Jaane Bahaar Naam Hai Lekin Ye Kaam Hai,
Kaliyan Taraash Lee To Kabhi Gul Qatar Liye;

Ranjhaa Bane Hain, Kais Bane, Kohakan Bane,
Humne Kisi Ke Vaaste Sab Roop Dhar Liye;

Na Meharabane Shehar Ne Thukra Diya Mujhe,
Main Phir Raha Hun Apna Makaan Dar-B-Dar Liye!

 Wo Khafa Hain To Koi Baat Nahi,
Ishq Mohtaaj-e-Iltfhaq Nahi; 

Dil Bujha Ho Agar To Din Bhi Hai Raat Nahi,
Din Ho Roshan To Raat Raat Nahi;

Dil-e-Saaki Main Todu-e-Vaail,
Ja Mujhe Khwahish-e-Najaat Nahi; 

Aisi Bhuli Hai Qaynaat Mujhe,
Jaise Main Jisb-e-Qaynaat Nahi;

Peer Kee Basti Ja Rahi Hai Magar, 
Sabko Ye Veham Hai Ki Raat Nahi;

Mere Layak Nahi Hayaat 'Khumar';
Aur Main Layak-e-Hayaat Nah!

 Phool The Baadal Bhi Tha Aur
Phool The Baadal Bhi Tha Aur Vo Haseen Soorat Bhi Thi,
Dil Mein Lekin Aur Hi Ek Shakal Kee Hasrat Bhi Thi;

Jo Hawa Mein Ghar Banaye Kaash Koi Dekhta,
Dasht Mein Rehte The Par Taameer Kee Aadat Bhi Thi;

Keh Geya Main Samane Us Ke Jo Dil Ka Mudda,
Kuch To Mausam Bhi Ajab Tha Kuch Meri Himmat Bhi Thi;

Ajanabi Sheharon Mein Rehte Umr Saari Kat Gayi,
Go Zara Se Fansale Par Ghar Kee Har Rahat Bhi Thi;

Kya Qayamat Hai 'Munir' Ab Yaad Bhi Aate Nahi,
Vo Purane Aashna Jin Se Humein Ulfat Bhi Thi!

 Yun Hi Si Ek Baat Thi, Us Ka Malal Kya Karein,
Meer-e-Kharaab Haal Sa Apna Bhi Haal, Kya Karein;

Aisi Fiza Ke Qahar Mein Aisi Hawa Ke Zehar Mein,
Zinda Hain Aise Shehar Mein Aur Kamaal Kya Karein;

Aur Bahut See Ulajhane Tuk-o-Ras Se Badh Ke Hain,
Zikr-e-Zamal Kya Kare, Fikr-e-Visaal Kya Karein;

Dhoondh Liye Hain Charagar Humne Diyar-e-Gair Mein,
Ghar Mein Hamara Kaun Hai, Ghar Ka Khyal Kya Karein;

Chunte Hai Dil Kee Kirachiyan Bikhari Hain Jo Yahan-Vahan,
Hona Tha Ek Din Yahi, Ranj-Maal Kya Karein;

Uski Nazar Mein Qaid Hain Apni Tamaam Muntakin,
Tek-e-Khyaal Kya Karein, Harf Kee Dhaal Kya Karein!

 Kisi Dard Ko Sambhal Pana Aasan Nahi;
Hanste Hue Har Lamha Bitana Aasan Nahi;
Zindgi Mein Har Koi Dil Mein Basta Nahi,
Aur Jo Bas Jaye Usko Dil Se Bhulana Aasan Nahi!

 Koi Keh De

Koi Keh De Mere Dil Ki Baat Unse;
Har Taraf Se Hui Dil Ki Maat Unse;

Jaan-Pehchan Hi Kara De Gar Koi;
Ek-Ek Lamhe Ki Ho Shuruaat Unse;

Log Puchte Hain Muskuraht Ki Wajah;
Hamne Kaha Hui Hai Mulakat Unse;

Khoya Hua Raha Main Aaz Talak;
Ab Mila Do Mere Jazbaat Unse;

Karenge Chand Se Kuchh Baatein Hum Bhi;
Milte Hue Dekha Hai Har Raat Unse!

 Rooh Pyaasi Kahan Se Aati Hai;
Ye Udasi Kahan Se Aati Hail;

Dil Hai Shab Do Ka To Ai Umeed;
Tu Nidasi Kahan Se Aati Hai;

Shauk Mein Aish-e-Vatl Ke Hangaam;
Naashiphasi Kahan Se Aati Hai;

Ek Zindaan-e-Bedili Aur Shaam;
Ye Sabasi Kahan Se Aati Hai;

Tu Hai Pehalu Mein Phir Teri Khushbu;
Hoke Baasi Kahan Se Aati Hai!

 Roshni Kab Kam Hui Pata Na Chala;
Khushi Kab Ghum Hui Pata Na Chala;
Aap Kee Yaad Mein Khoye Kuch Is Tarha;
Aankh Kab Nam Hui Pata Na Chala!

 Nigahein Naaz Ne Parde Uthaye Hain Kya-Kya;
Hijaab Ahle Mohabbat Ko Aaye Hain Kya-Kya;

Jahaan Mein Thi Bas Ek Afwah Tere Jalwon Kee;
Charag-e-Dair-o-Haram Jhilmilaein Hai Kya-Kya;

Kahin Charag, Kahin Gul, Kahin Dil Barbaad;
Kheramein Naaz Ne Kitne Uthaye Hain Kya-Kya;

Payamein Husn, Payamein Junoon, Payamein Fana;
Teri Nigah Ne Phasane Sunaye Hain Kya-Kya;

'Firaq' Raahe Wafa Mein Sabak Ravi Teri;
Bade Badon Ke Kadam Dagmagaein Hain Kya-Kya!

 Aur Bhi Ho Gaye Begana Wo Gaflat Karke;
Aazamaya Jo Unhein Tark-e-Mohabbat Karke;

Dil Ne Chhodaa Hai Na Chhode Tere Milne Ka Khayal;
Baaraha Dekh Liya Humne Malamat Karke;

Ruh Ne Payi Hai Takleef-e-Judai Se Nijaat;
Aapki Yaad Ko Saramaya-e-Rahat Karke;

Chhed Se Ab Wo Ye Kehte Hain Ki Sambhlo 'Hasarat';
Sabr-o-Taab-e-Dil-Beemaar Ko Garat Karke!

 Dil Ne Ek Ek Dukh Saha Tanha;
Anjuman Anjuman Raha Tanha;

Dhalte Saayon Mein Tere Kooche Se;
Koi Guzra Hai Badha Tanha;

Teri Aahat Kadam Kadam Aur Main;
Is Maiyat Mein Bhi Raha Tanha;

Kehana Yaadon Ke Barf-Zaaron Se;
Ek Aansu Baha Baha Tanha;

Doobte Sahilon Ke Mod Pe Dil;
Ik Khandar Sa Raha Saha Tanha;

Goonjta Reh Geya Khalaon Mein;
Waqt Ka Ek Kehkaha Tanha!

 Naam Uska Likh Kar Mita Raha Tha Main;
Dil Ko Apne Yun Behla Raha Tha Main;
Na Thi Jisko Mere Pyaar Ki Kadar Dosto,
Na Chahte Hue Bhi Bas Usi Ko Chah Raha Tha Main!

 Baat Karni Mujhe Mushkil Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;
Jaisi Ab Hai Teri Mehfil Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;

Le Geya Cheen Ke Kaun Aaj Tera Sabr-o-Qaraar;
Beqarari Tujhe Ai Dil Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;

Chashm-e-Qatil Meri Dushman Thi Hamesha Lekin;
Jaise Ab Ho Gayi Qatil Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;

Un Kee Aankhon Ne Khudaa Jaane Kiya Kya Jadoo;
Ki Tabiyat Meri Maail Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;

Aks-e-Rukh-e-Yaar Ne Kis Se Hai Tujhe Chamakaya;
Taab Tujh Mein Maah-e-Kaamil Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;

Kya Sabab Tu Jo Bigadta Hai 'Zafar' Se Har Baar;
Khoo Teri Hoor-e-Shamaail Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi!

 Aag Se Seekh Liya Humne Yeh Qareena Bhi;
Bujh Bhi Jana Par Badi Der Tak Sulagte Rehna;
Jaane Kis Umar Mein Jayegi Ye Aadat Apni;
Roothna Usse Aur Auron Se Uljhate Rehna!

 Koi Kaanta Chubha Nahi Hota;
Dil Agar Phool Sa Nahi Hota;

Kuch To Majabooriyan Rahi Hongi;
Yun Koi Bewafa Nahi Hota;

Guftagu Un Se Roz Hoti Hai;
Muddaton Saamana Nahi Hota;

Jee Bahut Chahta Sach Bole;
Kya Karein Haunsala Nahi Hota;

Raat Ka Intezar Kaun Kare;
Aaj Kal Din Mein Kya Nahi Hota!

 Taaron Se Mera Jaam Bharo Main Nashe Mein Hun;
Ai Sakinaan-e-Khuld Suno Main Nashe Mein Hun;

Kuch Phool Khil Rahe Hain Sar-e-Shakh-e-May-Kada;
Tum Hi Zara Ye Phool Chuno Main Nashe Mein Hun;

Thehro Abhi To Subah Ka Maara Hai Zau-Phishan;
Dekho Mujhe Fareb Na Do Main Nashe Mein Hun;

Nasha To Maut Hai Gham-e-Hasti Kee Dhoop Mein;
Bikhara Ke Zulf Saath Chalo Main Nashe Mein Hun;

Mela Yun Hi Rahe Ye Sar-e-Rahguzar-e-Zeest;
Ab Jaam Saamne Hi Rakho Main Nashe Mein Hun;

Payal Chanak Rahi Hai Nigaar-e-Khayal Kee;
Kuch Ehatimaam-e-Raqs Karo Main Nashe Mein Hun;

Main Dagmaga Raha Hun Bayabaan-e-Hosh Mein;
Mere Abhi Kareeb Raho Main Nashe Mein Hun;

Hai Sirf Ek Tabasum-e-Rangeen Bahut Mujhe;
'Saghar' B-Dosh Lala-Rukhon Main Nashe Mein Hun!

 Har Ek Chehre Ko Zakhmon Ka Aaina Na Kaho;
Ye Zindagi To Hai Rahmat Ise Saza Na Kaho;
Na Jaane Kaun Si Mazburion Ka Qaidi Ho;
Wo Saath Chhod Geya Hai To Bewafa Na Kaho!

 Nigahon Se Wo Is Dil Mein Samaye;
Jab Ashk Bahe To Palko Par Aaye;
Darr Hai Kahin Wo Kho Hi Na Jaye;
Palko Ko Ab Hum Kaise Jhukaye!

 Aankhon Mein Raha Dil Mein Utar Kar Nahi Dekha;
Kashti Ke Musafir Ne Samandar Nahi Dekha;
Pathar Mujhe Kehta Hai Mera Chahne Wala;
Main Mom Hun Usne Mujhe Chhu Kar Nahi Dekha!

 Kuch Fainsla To Ho Ki Kidhar Jana Chahiye;
Pani Ko Ab To Sar Se Guzar Jana Chahiye;

Har Baar Aidiyon Pe Gira Hai Mera Lahoo;
Maqtal Mein Ab B-Tarz-E-Digar Jana Chahiye;

Kya Chal Sakenge Jin Ka Faqat Masla Yeh Hai;
Jaane Se Pehle Rakht-E-Safar Jana Chahiye;

Sara Jvar-Bhata Mere Dil Mein Hai Magar;
Ilzam Ye Bhi Chaand Ke Sar Jana Chahiye;

Jab Bhi Gaye Azaab-E-Dar-O-Baam Tha Wahi;
Aakhir Ko Kitni Der Se Ghar Jana Chahiye;

Tohmat Laga Ke Maa Pe Jo Dushman Se Daad Le;
Aise Sukhanfarosh Ko Mar Jana Chaahiye!

 Hum Ne Sab Sher Mein Sanware The;
Hum Se Jitne Sukhan Tumhare The;

Rang-o-Khusbhu Ke Husn-o-Khoobi Ke;
Tum Se The Jitne Istiare The;

Tere Kaul-o-Karar Se Pehle;
Apne Kuch Aur Bhi Sahare The;

Jab Wo Laal-o-Gohar Hisab Kiye;
Jo Tere Gham Ne Dil Pe Vaare The;

Mere Daaman Mein Aa Gire Saare;
Jitne Tasht-E-Falak Mein Taare The;

Umar-E-Jaaved Kee Dua Karte;
'Faiz' Itne Wo Kab Hamare The!

 Tanhai Mere Dil Mein Samati Chali Gayi;
Kismat Bhi Apna Khel Dikhati Chali Gayi;
Mehkti Fiza Kee Khushbu Mein Jo Dekha Pyaar Ko;
Bas Yaad Unki Aayi Aur Rulati Chali Gayi!

 Betab Se Rehte Hain Teri Yaad Mein Aksar;
Raat Bhar Nahi Sote Teri Yaad Mein Aksar;
Jism Mein Dard Ka Bahana Sa Bana Kar;
Hum Toot Ke Rote Hain Teri Yaad Mein Aksar!

 Dil Soz Se Khali Hai Nigah Paak Nahi Hai;
Phir Is Mein Ajab Kya Ki Tu Be-Baak Nahi Hai;

Hai Zauq-e-Tajalli Bhi Isi Khaak Mein Pinhan;
Gafil Tu Nira Sahib-e-Idraak Nahi Hai;

Wo Aankh Ke Hai Surma-e-Afarng Se Roshan;
Pur-Kaar O Sukhan-Saaz Hai Nam-Naak Nahi Hai;

Kya Sufi O Mulla Ko Khabar Mere Junoon Kee;
Un Ka Sar-e-Daman Bhi Abhi Chaak Nahi Hai;

Kab Tak Rahe Mahkumi-e-Anjum Mein Meri Khaak;
Ya Main Nahi Ya Gardish-e-Aflaak Nahi Hai;

Bijli Hun Nazar Koh O Bayaban Pe Hai Meri;
Mere Liye Shayaan Khas O Khaashak Nahi Hai;

Aalam Hai Faqat Momin-e-Janbaz Kee Meeras;
Momin Nahi Jo Sahib-e-Laulak Nahi Hai!

 Tum Door Ho To Pyaar Ka Mausam Na Aayega;
Ab Ke Baras Bahaar Ka Mausam Na Aayega;

Chumunga Kis Kee Zulf Ghataon Ko Dekh Kar;
Ik Jurm-e-Khush-Gawar Ka Mausam Na Aayega;

Chalake Sharab Barq Gire Ya Jalein Charag;
Zikr-e-Nigah-e-Yaar Ka Mausam Na Aayega;

Vaada-Khilafiyon Ko Taras Jayega Yakeen;
Raaton Ko Intezar Ka Mausam Na Aayega;

Tujh Se Bichhad Ke Zindagi Ho Jayegi Taveel;
Ehasas Ke Nikhar Ka Mausam Na Aayega!

 Vasl Kee Banti Hain In Baaton Se Tadbeerein Kahin;
Aarzuon Se Phira Karti Hain Taqdeerein Kahin;

Bezubani Tarjumane-Shauq-e-Behad Ho Na Ho;
Varna Pesh-e-Yaar Kaam Aati Hain Taqreerein Kahin;

Mit Rahi Hain Dil Se Yaadein Rozagar-e-Aish Kee;
Ab Nazar Kaahe Ko Aayengi Ye Tasveerein Kahin;

Iltifaat-e-Yaar Tha Ik Khwab-w-Aagaz-e-Wafa;
Sach Hua Karti Hain In Khwabon Kee Tabeerein Kahin; 

Teri Besabri Hai 'Hasrat' Khaamkari Kee Daleel;
Giriya-e-Ushaq Mein Hoti Hain Taseerein Kahin!

 Na Dard Ne Kisi Ko Sataya Hota;
Na Aankhon Ne Kisi Ko Rulaya Hota;
Khushi Hi Khushi Hoti Har Jagah;
Agar Banane Wale Ne Dil Hi Na Banaya Hota!

 Dekha Hua Sa Kuch Hai To Socha Hua Sa Kuch;
Har Waqt Mere Saath Hai Uljha Hua Sa Kuch;

Hota Hai Yun Bhi Rasta Khulta Nahi Kahin;
Jungle Sa Phail Jata Hai Khoya Hua Sa Kuch;

Sahil Kee Geeli Ret Par Bachhon Ke Khel Sa;
Har Lamha Mujh Mein Banta Bikharta Hua Sa Kuch;

Fursat Ne Aaj Ghar Ko Sajaya Kuch Is Tarah;
Har Shay Se Muskurata Hai Rota Hua Sa Kuch;

Dhundhli Si Ek Yaad Kisi Qabar Ka Diya;
Aur Mere Aas-Paas Chamakta Hua Sa Kuch!

 Mehak Utha Hai Aangan Is Khabar Se;
Wo Khushbu Laut Aayi Hai Safar Se; 

Judai Ne Use Dekha Sar-e-Baam;
Dareech Par Shafaq Ke Rang Barse; 

Main Is Deewar Par Chadh To Geya Tha; 
Utare Kaun Ab Deewar Par Se; 

Gila Hai Ek Gali Se Shehar-e-Dil Kee; 
Main Ladta Phir Raha Hun Shehar Bhar Se; 

Use Dekhe Zamane Bhar Ka Ye Chaand;
Hamari Chandni Chaye To Tarse; 

Mere Maanan Guzra Kar Meri Jaan;
Kabhi Tu Khud Bhi Apni Rehguzar Se!

 Kisi Ne Humein Rulaya To Kya Bura Kiya;
Dil Ko Dhukaya To Kya Bura Kiya;
Hum To Pehle Se Hi Tanha The;
Kisi Ne Ehsaas Dilaya To Kya Bura Kiya!

 Yahi Nahi Koi Toofan Meri Talash Mein Hai;
Ki Mausam-e-Gham-e-Jaana Meri Talash Mein Hai;

Visal-Rutt Hai Magar Dil Ko Aisa Lagta Hai;
Sitara-e-Shab-e-Hijran Meri Talash Mein Hai;

Main Fainsle Kee Ghadi Se Guzar Chuki Hun Magar;
Kisi Ka Deeda-e-Hairan Meri Talash Mein Hai;

Ye Be-Yaqeen See Aasoodgi Batati Hai;
Ki Ek Qarya-e-Veeran Meri Talash Mein Hai;

Main Teergi Mein Mohabbat Kee Ek Kahani Hun;
Mui Charaag Saar Unvan Meri Talash Mein Hai;

Ye Kaisa Khwab Tha Dhdaka Sa Lag Geya Dil Ko;
Ki Ek Shakhs Pareshan Meri Talash Mein Hai!

 Pyaar Ke Panno Se Bhari Kitab Ho Tum;
Rishto Ke Phoolon Mein Gulab Ho Tum;
Jo Log Kehte Hain Ki Pyaar Saccha Nahi Hota;	
Un Logo Ke Har Sawaal Ka Jawab Ho Tum!

 Tere Sheher Teri Soch Se Nikal Jaungi;
Kisi Udaas Sham Mein Dhal Jaungi;

Tu Jo Mukar Geya Hai Har Baat Se Apni;
Dekh Lena Ek Din Main Bhi Badal Jaungi;

Mat Dikha Mujh Ko Apna Ye Masoom Chehra;
Jab Ki Tu Janta Hai Main Pighal Jaungi;

Chahe Laakh Tadpun Tere Intezar Mein;
Mat Lout Ke Aana Main Sambhal Jaungi;

Tera Hona Itna Zaroori To Nahi Hai;
Main To Yaadon Ke Khilauno Se Behel Jaungi!

 Har Ek Chehre Pe Ghuman Uska Tha;
Basa Na Koi Dil Mein Ye Khaali Makaan Uska Tha;
Tamam Dukh Mit Gaye Mere Dil Se Lekin;
Jo Na Mit Saka Woh Ek Naam Uska Tha!

 Kuch Aarazi Ujale Bachaye Hue Hain Log;
Mutthi Mein Juganuon Ko Chupaye Hue Hain Log;

Us Shakhs Ko To Qatal Hue Der Ho Gayi;
Ab Kis Liye Ye Bheed Lagaye Hue Hain Log;

Barason Purane Dard Na Athkheliyan Karen;
Ab To Naye Ghamon Ke Sataye Hue Hain Log;

Aankhein Ujad Chuki Hain Magar Rang Rang Ke;
Khwabon Kee Ab Bhi Fasal Lagaye Hue Hain Log;

Kya Reh Geya Hai Shehar Mein Khandaraat Ke Siva;
Kya Dekhne Ko Ab Yahan Aaye Hue Hain Log;

Kuch Din Se Be-Dimagi-e-'Azahar' Hai Rang Par;
Basti Mein Us Ko 'Meer' Banaye Hue Hain Log!

 Mujhko Aisa Dard Mila Jiski Dawa Nahi;
Phir Bhi Khush Hun Mujhe Us Se Koi Gila Nahi;
Aur Kitne Aansu Bahaun Ab Us Ke Liye;
Jisko Khuda Ne Mere Naseeb Main Likha Hi Nahi!

 Unhein Chahana Hamari Kamzori Hai;
Unse Keh Nahi Pana Hamari Majboori Hai;
Wo Kyon Nahi Samajhte Hamari Khamoshi Ko;
Kya Pyaar Ka Izhaar Karna Itna Zaroori Hai!

 Wo Bulayein To Kya Tamasha Ho;
Hum Na Jaayein To Kya Tamasha Ho;

Ye Kinaron Se Khelne Wale;
Doob Jaayein To Kya Tamasha Ho;

Banda Parwar Jo Hum Pe Guzari Hai;
Hum Batayein To Kya Tamasha Ho;

Aaj Hum Bhi Teri Wafaon Par;
Muskurayein To Kya Tamasha Ho;

Teri Soorat Jo Itefaaq Se Hum;
Bhool Jaayein To Kya Tamasha Ho;

Waqt Kee Chand Satein 'Saghar';
Laut Aayein To Kya Tamasha Ho!

 Unse Milne Ko Jo Sochun Ab Wo Zamana Nahi;
Ghar Bhi Kaise Jaun Ab To Koi Bahana Nahi;
Mujhe Yaad Rakhna Kahin Tum Bhula Na Dena;
Mana Ki Barson Se Teri Gali Me Aana Jana Nahi!

 Har Chand Sitare Mein Teri Tasveer Nazar Aayi;
Phir Is Tanha Raat Mein Teri Yaad Chali Aayi;
Door Tujhse Rehkar Ye Saans Tham Chuki Thi;
Jo Kahin Naam Tera Aaya To Saans Chali Aayi!

 Haath Khaali Hain Tere Shehar Se Jaate Jaate;
Jaan Hoti To Meri Jaan Lutate Jaate;

Ab To Har Haath Ka Pathar Humnein Pahunchta Hai;
Umar Guzri Hai Tere Shehar Mein Aate Jaate;

Ab Ke Mayus Hua Yaaron Ko Rukhsat Karke;
Ja Rahe The To Koi Zakham Lagate Jaate;

Reengne Kee Bhi Izazat Nahi Hum Ko Warna;
Hum Jidhar Jaate Naye Phool Khilate Jaate;

Main To Jalte Hue Sehraon Ka Ek Pathar Tha;
Tum To Dariya The Meri Pyaas Bujhate Jaate;

Hum Se Pehle Bhi Musafir Kayi Guzre Honge;
Kam Se Kam Raah Ke Pathar To Hatate Jaate!

 Is Kadar Hum Yaar Ko Manane Nikle;
Uski Chahat Ke Hum Deewane Nikle;
Jab Bhi Use Dil Ka Haal Batana Chaha;
To Uske Hothon Se Waqt Na Hone Ke Bahane Nikle!

 Duriya Hote Hue Bhi Safar Vahi Rahega;
Door Hote Hue Bhi Dostana Vahi Rahega;
Bahot Mushkil Hai Yeh Safar Zindgi Ka;
Agar Aapka Sath Hoga To Ehsaas Vahi Rahega!

 Meri Yaadon Mein Tum Ho Ya Mujh Mein Hi Tum Ho;
Mere Khwabon Mein Tum Ho Ya Mera Khwab Hi Tum Ho;
Dil Mera Dhadak Ke Puche Baar-Baar Ek Hi Baat;
Meri Jaan Mein Tum Ho Ya Meri Jaan Hi Tum Ho!

 Koi Soorat Nikalti Kyon Nahi Hai;
Yahan Halat Badalti Kyon Nahi Hai; 

Ye Bujhta Kyon Nahi Hai Unka Sooraj;
Hamari Shama Jalti Kyon Nahi Hai;

Agar Hum Jhel Hi Baithe Hain Isko;
To Phir Ye Raat Dhalti Kyon Nahi Hai;

Mohabbat Sar Ko Chadh Jati Hai, Aksar; 
Mere Dil Mein Machalti Kyon Nahi Hai!

 Rukne Ka Samay Guzar Geya Hai;
Jana Tera Ab Thehar Geya Hai; 

Rukhsat Kee Ghadi Khadi Hai Sar Par; 
Dil Koi Do-Neem Kar Geya Hai; 

Maatam Kee Fazaa Hai Shehar-e-Dil Mein; 
Mujh Mein Koi Shakhs Mar Geya Hai; 

Bujhne Ko Hai Phir Se Chashm-e-Nargis; 
Phir Khwaab-e-Sabaa Bikhar Geya Hai; 

Bas Ek Nigaah Kee Thi Us Ne; 
Saraa Chehra Nikhar Geya Hai!

 Zara Sa Qatra Kahin Aaj Agar Ubharta Hai,
Samandaron Hi Ke Lehje Mein Baat Karta Hai;
Khuli Chhaton Ke Diye Kab Ke Bujh Gaye Hote,
Koi To Hai Jo Hawaon Ke Par Qatarta Hai;
Ye Dekhna Hai Ki Sehra Bhi Hai Samandar Bhi,
Wo Meri Tashna-Labi Kis Ke Naam Karta Hai!

 Jis Tarah Bhi Ho Saka Us Tarah Toda Mujhe;
Zindagi Ne Maut Ke Qabil Nahi Samjha Mujhe;

Zindagi Maankar Chalati Rahi Ghoda Mujhe;
Har Kadam Par Maarti Hai Ek Naya Koda Mujhe;

Zindagi Har Waqt Meri Peeth Par Baithi Rahi;
Apni Marzi Ke Mutabiq Har Taraf Moda Mujhe;

Is Tarah Apno Ke Ehsaan Hai Mujh Par Bahut;
Chot De Kar Dil Ko Sheeshe Ki Tarah Joda Mujhe;

He Zindagi Meri Tujhse Iltiza Itni Hai Bus;
Chodhkar Nafrat Ki Bhasha Pyar De Thoda Mujhe;

Warna Ek Din Jalti Hui Aag Se Bolegi Meri Laash Yoon;
Zindagi Ne Aag Ke Dariya Me Laa Chhoda Mujhe!

 Ai Mohabbat Tere Anjaam Pe Rona Aaya;
Jaane Kyon Aaj Tere Naam Pe Rona Aaya;

Yun To Har Shaam Umeedon Mein Guzar Jati Hai;
Aaj Kuch Baat Hai Jo Shaam Pe Rona Aaya;

Kabhi Taqdeer Ka Maatam Kabhi Duniya Ka Gila;
Manzil-e-Ishq Mein Har Ghum Pe Rona Aaya;

Mujh Pe Hi Khatam Hua Silsila-e-Nauhagari;
Is Kadar Gardish-e-Ayyam Pe Rona Aaya;

Jab Hua Zikar Zamane Mein Mohabbat Ka "Shakeel";
Mujh Ko Apne Dil-e-Nakaam Pe Rona Aaya!

 Saans Lene Se Bhi Teri Yaad Aati Hai;
Har Saans Mein Teri Khushboo Bas Jati Hai;

Kaise Kahun Ki Saans Se Main Zinda Hun;
Jab Ki Saans Se Pehle Teri Yaad Aati Hai!

 Mulaqat Bhi Kabhi Aansu De Jati Hai;
Nazrein Bhi Kabhi Dhokha De Jati Hain;
Gujre Hue Lamhon Ko Yaad Karke Dekhiye;
Tanhai Bhi Kabhi Kabhi Sukoon De Jati Hai!

 Wahi Aankhon Mein Aur Aankhon Se Poshidaa Bhi Rehta Hai;
Meri Yaadon Mein Ek Bhula Hua Chehra Bhi Rehta Hai;

Jab Us Kee Sard-Mehari Dekhta Hun Bujhne Lagta Hun;
Mujhe Apni Adakari Ka Andaza Bhi Rehta Hai;

Main Un Se Bhi Mila Karta Hun Jin Se Dil Nahi Milta;
Magar Khud Se Bichhad Jane Ka Andesha Bhi Rehta Hai;

Jo Mumkin Ho To Pur-Asraar Duniyaon Mein Dakhil Ho;
Ki Har Deewar Mein Ek Chor Darwaza Bhi Rehta Hai;

Bas Apni Be-Basi Kee Saatvi Manzil Mein Zinda Hun;
Yahan Par Aag Bhi Rehti Hai Aur Nauha Bhi Rehta Hai!

 Hum Aap Ki Har Cheez Se Pyaar Kar Lenge;
Aapki Har Baat Par Aitbaar Kar Lenge;
Bas Ek Bar Keh Do Ki Tum Sirf Mere Ho;
Hum Zindagi Bhar AapKa Intezar Kar Lenge!

 Jee Chahta Hai Tum Se Pyaari Si Baat Ho;
Haseen Chand Tare Ho, Lambi Si Raat Ho;
Fir Raat Bhar Yahi Guftagu Rakhe Hum Dono;
Tum Meri Zindagi Ho, Tum Meri Kayanat Ho!

 Jahan Katre Ko Tarsaya Geya Hun;
Wahin Dooba Hua Paya Geya Hun;

Ba-Haal-e-Gham-Rahi Paya Geya Hun;
Haram Se Deir Mein Laya Geya Hun;

Balaa Kaafi Na Thi Ek Zindagi Kee;
Dobara Yaad Pharmaya Geya Hun;

Ba-Rang-e-Lala-e-Veerana Bekaar;
Khilaya Aur Murjhaya Geya Hun;

Agarche Abr-e-Gauhar-Baar Hun Main;
Magar Aankhon Se Barsaya Geya Hun;

'Hafeez' Ahal-e-Zubaan Kab Maante The;
Bade Zoron Se Manvaya Geya Hun!!

 Kahun Kis Se Main Ki Kya Hai, Shab-e-Gham Buri Bala Hai;
Mujhe Kya Bura Tha Marna Agar Ek Baar Hota;
Hue Mar Ke Jo Hum Ruswa, Hue Kyon Na Gharq-e-Dariya;
Na Kabhi Janaza Uthta Na Kahin Mazaar Hota!

 Qatil Teri Adaaon Ne Loota Hai;
Mujhe Teri Jafaaon Ne Loota Hai;
Shaunk Nahi Tha Mujhe Mar-Mitne Ka;
Mujhe To In Nashili Nigahon Ne Loota Hai!

 Sirf Nazdeekiyon Se Mohabbat Hua Nahi Karti;
Fansle Jo Dilon Mein Ho To Fir Chahat Hua Nahi Karti;
Agar Naraz Ho Khafa Ho To Shikayat Karo Humse;
Khamosh Rehne Se Dilon Kee Dooriyan Mita Nahi Karti!!

 Lab Pe Pabandi To Hai Ehsas Par Pehra To Hai;
Phir Bhi Ahl-e-Dil Ko Ahval-e-Bashar Kehna To Hai;

Khoon-e-Adaa Se Na Ho Khoon-e-Shahidaan Se Hi Ho;
Kuch Na Kuch Is Daur Mein Rang-e-Chaman Nikhra To Hai;

Apni Ghairat Bech Daalen Apna Maslak Chhod Den;
Rehnumaon Mein Bhi Kuch Logon Ka Ye Mansha To Hai;

Bhuj Rahe Hain Ek Ek Kar Ke Aqidon Ke Diye;
Is Andhere Ka Bhi Lekin Saamna Karna To Hai;

Juth Kyon Bole Farogh-E-Maslahat Ke Naam Par;
Zindagi Pyari Sahi Lekin Humein Marna To Hai!

 Assi Nazuk Dil De Lok Haan, Sada Dil Na Yaar Dukhaya Kar;
Na Jhoothe Vaade Kareya Kar, Na Jhoothi Kasmaan Khaya Kar;
Tainu Kinni Vaari Main Aakheya Hai, Mainu Baar Baar Na Aazmaya Kar;
Teri Yaad De Vich Main Mar Java Ga, Mainu Inna Na Yaad Aaya Kar!

 Zara Si Der Ko Aaye The Khwab Aankhon Mein; 
Phir Us Ke Baad Musalsal Azab Aankhon Mein; 

Wo Jis Ke Naam Kee Nisbat Se Roshan Tha Wujud; 
Khatak Raha Hai Wahi Aftab Aankhon Mein; 

Jinhe Mata-e-Dil-o-Jan Samajh Rahe The Hum; 
Wo Aaine Bhi Hue Behijab Aankhon Mein; 

Ajab Tarah Ka Hai Mausam Ki Khak Udti Hai; 
Wo Din Bhi The Ki Khile The Gulab Aankhon Mein; 

Meri Ghazal Teri Vahshaton Kee Khair Kee Hai; 
Bahut Dino Se Bahut Iztarab Aankhon Mein; 

Na Jane Kaisi Qayamat Ka Peshkhema Hai; 
Ye Uljhane Teri Be-Intasab Aankhon Mein!

 Yeh Zulf Agar Khul Ke Bikhar Jaye To Achha;
Is Raat Kee Taqdeer Badal Sanwar Jaye To Achha;
Jis Tarah Se Thodi Si Tere Saath Kati Hai;
Baki Bhi Isi Tarah Guzar Jaye To Achha!

 Jisne Kabhi Chahton Ka Paigaam Likha Tha;
Jisne Apna Sab Kuch Mere Naam Likha Tha;
Suna Hai Aaj Use Mere Zikar Se Bhi Nafrat Hai;
Jisne Kabhi Apne Dil Par Mera Naam Likha Tha!

 Sar-e-Sehra Musafir Ko Sitara Yaad Rehta Hai;
Main Chalta Hun Mujhe Chehra Tumhara Yaad Rahta Hai;

Tumhara Zarf Hai Tum Ko Mohabbat Bhool Jati Hai;
Humein To Jis Ne Hans Kar Bhi Pukara Yaad Rehta Hai;

Mohabbat Mein Jo Doobaa Ho Use Sahil Se Kya Lena;
Kise Is Bahaar Mein Ja Kar Kinara Yaad Rehta Hai;

Bahut Leharon Ko Pakda Doobane Wale Ke Haathon Ne;
Yahi Bas Ek Dariya Ka Nazara Yaad Rehta Hai;

Sadayein Ek Si Yaksaniyat Mein Doob Jati Hain;
Zara Sa Mukhtalif Jis Ne Pukara Yaad Rehta Hai;

Main Kis Tezi Se Zinda Hun Main Ye To Bhool Jata Hun;
Nahi Aanaa Hai Duniya Mein Dobaraa Yaad Rehta Hai!

 Kitna Bhi Chaho Na Bhool Paoge Humein;
Jitni Door Jaoge Nazdik Paoge Humein;
Mita Sakte Ho To Mita Do Yaadein Meri;
Magar Kya Sanson Se Bhi Juda Kar Paoge Humein!

 Aap Ko Paa Kar Ab Khona Nahi Chahte;
Itna Khush Ho Kar Ab Rona Nahi Chahte;
Ye Aalam Hai Humara Aap Kee Judai Mein;
Aankhon Mein Hai Neend Par Sona Nahi Chahte!

 Band Aankh Se Sapne

Band Aankh Se Sapne Bunte Bunte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni;
Tootey Dil Ke Raizey Chunte Chunte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni;

Woh Hum Se Bichar Kar Kaise Jeeta Hoga;
Bass Yehi Sochte Sochte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni;

Us Ki Talaash Mein Nikle, Apna Pata Bhool Gaye;
Phir Khud Ko Khojte Khojte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni;

Shamaa Ban To Gaye Roshni Ki Khatir;
Magar Phir Jalte Jalte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni;

Uss Ne Manaa Ki Deewaar Torr Kar Pukaara To Sahi;
Lekin Rukte Rukte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni;

Ab Yeh Zindagi Ussi Ki Amaanat Hai Waqas;
Jiss Ki Raah Takte Takte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni!

 Yun Kisi Kee Yaad Mein Rona Fizool Hai;
Itne Anmol Aansu Khona Fizool Hai;
Rona To Unke Liye Jo Hum Par Nisaar Hain;
Unke Liye Kya Rona Jinke Aashiq Hazaar Hain!

 Asaani Se Dil Lagaaye Jaate Hain;
Magar Mushkil Se Vaade Nibhaye Jaate Hain;
Mohabbat Le Aati Hai Un Raahon Pe;
Jahan Diyon Ke Badle Dil Jalaye Jaate Hain!

 Kis Ne Mujhko Sada Dee Bata Kaun Hai;
Ai Hawa Tere Ghar Mein Chhupa Kaun Hai;

Baarishon Mein Kisi Ped Ko Dekhna;
Shaal Odhe Hue Bheegta Kaun Hai;

Main Yahan Dhoop Mein Tap Raha Hun Magar;
Wo Paseene Mein Doobaa Hua Kaun Hai;

Aasmano Ko Humne Bataya Nahi;
Doobti Shaam Mein Doobta Kaun Hai;

Khushbun Mein Nahayi Hui Shaakh Par;
Phool-Sa Muskurata Hua Kaun Hai;

Dil Ko Patthar Hue Ik Zamana Hua;
Is Makaan Mein Magar Bolta Kaun Hai;

Tum Bhi Mazboor Ho Hum Bhi Mazboor Hain;
Bewafa Kaun Hai Bawafa Kaun Hai!

 Kabhi Khud Pe To Kabhi Halaat Pe Hansi Aayi;
Tanha Baithe Baithe Beeti Baat Pe Hansi Aayi;
Wo Yaad Aaye To Kuch Pal Ka Rona Aaya;
Phir Agle Hi Pal Mujhe Haal-e-Dil Pe Hansi Aayi!

 Jee Uthe Hashar Mein
Jee Uthe Hashar Mein Phir Jee Se Guzarne Wale;
Yaan Bhi Paida Hue Phir Aap Pe Marne Wale;

Hai Udasi Shab-e-Matam Kee Suhani Kaisi;
Chaanv Mein Taaron Kee Nikale Hain Sanwarne Wale;

Hum To Samjhe The Ki Dushman Pe Uthaya Khanjar;
Tumne Jana Ki Humin Tum Pe Hain Marne Wale;

Sabr Kee Mere, Mujhe Daad Zara De Dena;
O Mere Hashar Ke Din Faisala Karne Wale;

Kya Maza Deti Hai Bijli Kee Chamak Mujhko 'Riyaz';
Mujhse Lipatate Hain, Mere Naam Se Darne Wale!

 Kitna Dilkash Manzar Ho Jab Hum;
Qayamat Ke Din Karein Shikwa Teri Bewafai Ka;
Aur Tum Lag Ke Gale Se Mere;
Dheere Se Kaho, Chup Raho Khudaa Ke Liye!

 Guzre Hue Taveel

Guzre Hue Taveel Zamane Ke Baad Bhi;
Dil Mein Raha Woh Chhod Ke Jaane Ke Baad Bhi;

Pehlu Mein Reh Ke Dil Ne Diya Hai Bahut Fareb;
Rakha Hai Us Ko Yaad Bhulaane Ke Baad Bhi;

Qurbat Ke Baad Or Bhi Qurbat Ki Talaash;
Dil Mutmain Nahin Hai Tere Aane Ke Baad Bhi;

Jo Tu Yahan Nahin Hai Magar Tu Yahin Pe Hai;
Tera Hi Zikar Hai Tere Jaane Ke Baad Bhi;

Lagta Hai Kuch Kaha Hi Nahi Hai Usey Faraz;
Dil Ka Tamaam Haal Sunane Ke Baad Bhi!

 Nafrat Bhi Hai Tumse, Mohabbat Bhi Hai Tumse;
Par Meri Mohabbat Nafrat Pe Haavi Ho Jati Hai;
Tumse Door Jaane Kee Meri Har Koshish;
Na Jaane Kyon Mujhe Tere Aur Kareeb Le Aati Hai!

 Zakham Aisa Diya Ki Koi Dawa Kaam Na Aayi;
Aag Aisi Lagai Ki Paani Se Bhi Bujh Na Paayi;
Aaj Bhi Rote Hain Hum Unki Yaad Mein;
Jo Chod Kar Chale Gaye Aur Unhe Hamari Yaad Tak Na Aayi!

 Ishq Ko Taqleed Se Aazad Kar;
Dil Se Giraya Aankh Se Fariyaad Kar;

Baaz Aa Ai Banda-e-Husn Majaz;
Yun Na Apni Zindagi Barbaad Kar;

Ai Khayalon Ke Makeen Nazron Se Door;
Meri Veeran Khalvatein Abaad Kar;

Naza Mein Hichki Nahi Aayi Mujhe;
Bhulne Wale Khudaa-Raa Yaad Kar;

Husn Ko Duniyaa Kee Aankhon Se Na Dekh;
Apni Ik Tarz-e-Nazar Izaad Kar;

Ishrat-e-Duniya Hai Ik Khwab-e-Bahar;
Kabaa-e-Dil Dard Se Abaad Kar;

Ab Kahan 'Ehsaan' Duniya Mein Wafa;
Tauba Kar Nadan Khuda Ko Yaad Kar!

 Tujhe Inkar Hai Mujse Mujhe Iqraar Hai Tujhse;
Tu Khafa Hai Mujse Mujhe Chahat Hai Tujhse;
Tu Mayoos Hai Mujhse Mujhe Khushi Hai Tujhse;
Tujhe Nafrat Hai Mujhse Aur Mujhe Pyaar Hai Tujhse!

 Rulane Ke Baad Kyon Hansate Hain Log;
Jaane Ke Baad Kyon Bulate Hain Log;
Zindagi Mein Kya Kuch Kasar Baaki Thi;
Jo Marne Ke Baad Bhi Jalate Hain Log!

 Kat Gayi Jhagde Mein Sari Raat Vasl-e-Yaar Kee;
Shaam Ko Bosa Liya Tha, Subah Tak Taqarar Kee;

Zindagi Mumkin Nahi Ab Aashiq-e-Beemar Kee;
Chhid Gayi Hain Barchiyan Dil Mein Nigah-e-Yaar Kee;

Hum Jo Kehte The Na Jana Bazm Mein Agayaar Kee;
Dekh Lo Neechi Nigahein Ho Gayi Sarkaar Kee;

Zehar Deta Hai To De, Zaalim Magar Taskeen Ko;
Is Mein Kuch To Chashni Ho Sharab-e-Deedaar Kee;

Baad Marne Ke Mili Jannat Khudaa Ka Shukr Hai;
Mujhko Dafnaya Rafeeqon Ne Gali Mein Yaar Kee;


Haal-e-'Akbar' Dekh Kar Bole Buri Hai Dosti;
Aise Rusvayi, Aise Rind, Aise Khudayi Khwaar Kee!

 Kaise Bayan Karun Alfaaz Nahi Hain;
Dard Ka Mere Tujhe Ehsaas Nahi Hai;
Puchte Ho Kya Dard Hai Mujhe;
Mujhe Dard Ye Hai Ki Tu Mere Pass Nahi Hai!

 Woh Kuch Gehri Soch Mein Aise Doob Geya Hai;
Baithe Baithe Nadi Kinare Doob Geya Hai;

Aaj Kee Raat Na Jaane Kintni Lambi Hogi;
Aajka Suraj Shaam Se Pehle Doob Geya Hai;

Woh Jo Pyasa Lagta Tha Sailab-Zada Tha;
Paani Paani Kehte Kehte Doob Geya Hai;

Shor To Yun Utha Tha Jaise Ik Toofan Ho;
Sanaate Mein Jaane Kaise Doob Geya Hai;

Aakhiri Khawhish Poori Kar Ke Jeena Kaisa;
"Anees" Bhi Sahil Tak Aa Ke Doob Geya Hai!

 Khaali Sheeshe Bhi Nishaan Rakhte Hain;
Toote Hue Dil Bhi Armaan Rakhte Hain;
Jo Khamoshi Se Guzar Jaye;
Woh Dariya Bhi Dil Mein Toofan Rakhte Hain!

 Ishq Karo To Ye Bhi Socho Arz-e-Sawal Se Pehle;
Hijr Kee Poori Raat Aati Hai Subah-e-Visaal Se Pehle;

Dil Ka Kya Hai Dil Ne Kitne Manzar Dekhe Lekin;
Aankhein Pagal Ho Jati Hain Ek Khyaal Se Pehle;

Kis Ne Ret Udaai Shab Mein Aankhein Khol Ke Rakhi;
Koi Misaal To Hona Us Kee Misaal Se Pehle;

Kaar-e-Mohabbat Ek Safar Hai Is Mein Aa Jata Hai;
Ek Zavaal-Aasaar Sa Rasta Baab-e-Kamaal Se Pehle;

Ishq Mein Resham Jaise Vaadon Aur Khwabon Ka Rastaa;
Jitna Mumkin Ho Tay Kar Le Gard-e-Malal Se Pehle!

 Raat Din Rulata Hai Intezar Tera;
Kat Gayi Umar Lekin Kam Na Hua Pyaar Tera;
Ab To Aa Jao Ke Bahut Udas Hai Yeh Dil;
Sanson Kee Hi Tarha Lazmi Hai Deedar Tera!

 Apni Pyari Aankhon Mein

Apni Pyari Aankhon Mein Chupa Lo Mujh Ko;
Mohabbat Tum Se Hai, Chura Lo Mujh Ko;

Dhup Ho Ya Sehra Tera Sath Chalenge Hum;
Yaqeen Na Ho To Aazma Lo Mujh Ko;

Tere Har Dukh Ko Seh Lenge Hans Ke Hum;
Apne Wazood Kee Chadar Bana Lo Mujh Ko;

Zindagi Bhi Tere Naam Kar Di Hai Humne;
Bas Chand Lamhe Seene Se Laga Lo Mujh Ko!

 Raat Kee Khamoshi Raas Nahi Aati;
Meri Parchayi Bhi Ab Mere Paas Nahi Aati;
Aati Hai To Bas Aapki Yaad;
Jo Aakar Ek Pal Bhi Mujhse Door Nahi Jaati!

 Mohabbat Kee Hawa Jism Kee Dawa Ban Gayi;
Doori Aapki Meri Chahat Kee Saza Ban Gayi;
Kaise Bhulun Aapko Ek Pal Ke Liye;
Aapki Yaad Hamare Jeene Kee Wajah Ban Gayi!

 Aankh Se Aankh

Aankh Se Aankh Milata Hai Koi; 
Dil Ko Khinche Liye Jata Hai Koi; 

Va-e-Hairat Ke Bhari Mehfil Mein; 
Mujh Ko Tanha Nazar Aata Hai Koi;

Chahiye Khud Pe Yakeen-e-Kaamil; 
Haunsla Kis Ka Badhata Hai Koi;

Sab Karishmat-e-Tasavur Hai 'Shakeel'; 
Varna Aata Hai Na Jata Hai Koi!

 Maut Ke Aagosh Mein Sone Ko Jee Karta Hai;
Dil To Kho Diya Ab Zindagi Khone Ko Jee Karta Hai;
Uski Yaad Aati Hai Jab Bhi Mujhe Na Jane Kyon;
Kahin Pe Tanha Baith Ke Rone Ko Jee Karta Hai!

 Nigahon Se Wo Is Dil Mein Samaye;
Jab Ashk Bahe To Palko Par Aaye;
Dar Hai Kahin Wo Kho Hi Na Jaye;
Palko Ko Ab Hum Kaise Jhukaye!

 Raat Apne Khwab Kee Keemat Ka Andaza Hua;
Ye Sitara Neend Kee Tehzeeb Se Paida Hua;

Zehan Kee Zarakhez Mitti Se Naye Chehre Uge; 
Jo Meri Yaadon Mein Zinda Hai Saraseema Hua;

Meri Aankhon Mein Anokhe Zurm Kee Tazveez Thi;
Sirf Dekha Tha Use Us Ka Badan Maila Hua;

Wo Koi Khushbu Hai Meri Saans Mein Behti Hui;
Main Koi Aansu Hun Us Kee Rooh Mein Girta Hua;

Us Ke Milne Aur Bichad Jane Ka Manzar Ek Hai;
Kaun Itne Fansalon Mein Be-Hijaab Aisa Hua!

 Kabhi Alfaaz Bhool Jaun Kabhi Khyaal Bhool Jaun;
Tujhe Is Kadar Chahun Ki Apni Saans Bhool Jaun;
Uth Kar Tere Paas Se Jo Main Chal Dun;
To Jaate Hue Khud Ko Tere Paas Bhool Jaun!

 Do Baatein Unse Kee To Dil Ka Dard Kho Geya;
Logon Ne Humse Pucha Ke Tumhein Kya Ho Geya;
Bekarar Aankhon Se Sirf Hans Ke Reh Geya;
Ye Bhi Na Keh Sake Ki Humein Pyaar Ho Geya!

 Jab Aap Ka Naam Zuban Par Aata Hai;
Pata Nahi Dil Kyon Muskurata Hai;
Tasalli Hoti Hai Mann Ko Koi To Hai Apna;
Jo Hanste Hue Har Waqt Yaad Aata Hai!

 Tum Na Aaye Ek Din Ka Vadaa Kar

Tum Na Aaye Ek Din Ka Vadaa Kar Do Din Talak;
Ham Pade Tadpa Kiye Do-Do Pahar Do Din Talak;

Dard-e-Dil Apna Sunata Hun Kabhi Jo Ek Din;
Rehta Hai Us Naazneen Ko Dard-e-Sar Do Din Talak;

Dekhte Hain Khwab Mein Jis Din Kisoo Kee Chashm-e-Mast;
Rehte Hain Hum Do Jahaan Se Bekhabar Do Din Talak;

Gar Yaqeen Ho Ye Humein Aayega Tu Do Din Ke Baad;
To Jiyen Hum Aur Is Ummeed Par Do Din Talak;

Kya Sabab Kya Vaasta Kya Kaam Tha Batalaiye;
Ghar Se Jo Nikale Na Apne Tum "Zafar" Do Din Talak!

 Ye Mat Kehna Ki Teri Yaad Se Rishta Nahi Rakha;
Main Khud Tanha Raha Dil Ko Magar Tanha Nahi Rakha;
Tumhari Chahton Ke Phool To Mehfooz Rakhe Hain;
Tumhari Nafrato Kee Peedh Ko Zinda Nahi Rakha!

 Dhoop Ho Chhaaon Ho Tum Saath Nibhaaya Karna;
Mere Chehre Pe Sada Palkoon Ka Saaya Karna;

Raah Dekhungi Tumhaari Main Sar-e-Shaam Yunhi;
Kabhi Jaldi Kabhi Der Se Aaya Karna;

Daant Lena Sar-E-Mehfil Koi Baat Nahin;
Phir Akele Mein Gale Laga Kar Manaaya Karna;

Jaan Jaungi Mein Khushboo Se Tumhaari Tum Ko;
Tum Peeche Se Meri Aankhoon Ko Chupaaya Karna;

Jaagna Chahun To Raat Bhar Baatein Karna;
Neend Aa Jaaye To Mujhe Apne Seene Par Sulaaya Karna!

 Mohabbat Yahan Bikti Hai Ishq Nilaam Hota Hai;
Bharose Ka Katal Yahan Khule Aam Hota Hai;
Zamaane Se Mili Jab Thokar To Maikhaane Chale Gaye Hum;
Aaj Wahi Zamaana Humein Sharabi Ka Naam Deta Hai!

 Dil Tod Kar Hamara Tumko Rahat Bhi Na Milegi;
Hamare Jaisi Tumko Kahin Chahat Bhi Na Milegi;
Yun Itni Berukhi Na Dikhlaiye Humein;
Hum Agar Ruthe To Hamari Aahat Bhi Na Milegi!

 Log Kehte Hain Jise Hadh Se Zyada Pyaar Karo;
Woh Pyaar Kee Kadar Nahi Karta;
Par Sach To Ye Hai Ki Pyaar Kee Kadar Jo Bhi Karta Hai;
Use Koi Pyaar Hi Nahi Karta!

 Usi Se Aaye Hain Aashob Aasman Wale;
Jise Gubaar Samajhate The Karavan Wale;

Main Apni Dhun Mein Yahan Aandhiyan Uthata Hun;
Magar Kahan Wo Maze Khaak-e-Aashiyan Wale;

Mujhe Diya Na Kabhi Mere Dushmano Ka Pata;
Mujhe Hawa Se Ladhate Rahe Jahan Wale;

Mere Saraab-e-Tamanna Pe Rashk Tha Jin Ko;
Bane Hain Aaj Wahi Bahar-e-Be-Karaan Wale;

Main Nala Hun Mujhe Apne Labon Se Door Na Rakh;
Mujhi Se Zinda Hai Tu Mere Jism-o-Jaan Wale;

Ye Musht-e-Khaak 'Zafar' Mera Pairahan Hi Tu Hai;
Mujhe Zameen Se Darayein Na Kehakashan Wale!

 Tu Mera Sapna Mera Armaan Hai;
Par Shayad Tu Apni Ahmiyat Se Anjaan Hai;
Mujhse Kabhi Bhi Ruth Mat Jana;
Kyonki Meri Duniya Tere Bina Veeraan Hai!

 Kitni Zulfein Kitne Aanchal Ude

Kitni Zulfein Kitne Aanchal Ude Chaand Ko Kya Khabar;
Kitna Matam Hua Kitne Aansu Bahe Chaand Ko Kya Khabar;

Muddaton Us Kee Khwahish Se Chalte Rahe Haath Aata Nahi;
Chaah Mein Us Kee Pairon Mein Hain Aabale Chaand Ko Kya Khabar;

Wo Jo Nikla Nahi To Bhatakate Rahe Hain Musafir Kayi;
Aur Lutte Rahe Hain Kayi Kafile Chaand Ko Kya Khabar;

Us Ko Davaa Bahut Meethe-Pan Ka 'Wasi' Chandni Se Kaho;
Us Kee Kirano Se Kitne Hi Ghar Jal Gaye Chaand Ko Kya Khabar!

 Ye Duniya Wale Bhi Bade Ajeeb Hain;
Kabhi Humse Door To Kabhi Kareeb Hain;
Dard Na Bataye To Humein Qayar Kehte Hain;
Aur Dard Bata De To Shayar Kehte Hain!

 Zindagi Mein Bas Ek Dil Se Chaha Unhe;
Akele Ho Kar Bhi Unke Khayalon Ke Sang Jiya Humne;
Gham Dard Sab Mein Bhi Muskaraya Humne;
Par Na Jane Kyon Hamari Mohabbat Ka Yakin Hua Na Unhe!

 Mohabbaton Mein Dikhave Kee Dosti Na Mila;
Agar Gale Nahi Milata To Haath Bhi Na Mila;

Gharon Pe Naam The, Naam Ke Saath Ahude The;
Bahut Talaash Kiya Koi Aadmi Na Mila;

Tamaam Rishton Ko Main Ghar Pe Chhod Aaya Tha;
Phir Iske Baad Mujhe Koi Ajnabi Na Mila;

Bahut Ajeeb Hai Ye Kurbaton Kee Doori Bhi;
Wo Mere Saath Raha Aur Mujhe Kabhi Na Mila;

Khuda Kee Itni Badi Kayanaat Mein Maine;
Bas Ek Shakhs Ko Maanga Mujhe Wahi Na Mila!

 Badi Mushkil Se Bane Hain Toot Jane Ke Baad;
Hum Aaj Bhi Ro Dete Hain Muskurane Ke Baad;
Aapse Mohabbat Thi Humein Be-inteha;
Magar Yeh Mehsoos Hua Aap Se Bichhad Jane Ke Baad!

 Ho Judai Ka Sabab Kuch Bhi Magar;
Hum Use Apni Khata Kehte Hain;
Woh Ton Saanson Mein Dhali Hai Mere;
Jaane Kyon Log Use Mujhse Juda Kehte Hain!

 Waqt Jab Raah Kee Deewar Hua;
Koi Sailaab Numudaar Hua;

Us Ne Pedon Se Hata Li Shakhein;
Baag Mein Se Tu Kayi Baar Hua; 

Maine Jo Dil Mein Chupana Chaha; 
Mere Chehre Se Numudaar Hua; 

Sahili-Shaam Ka Faila Manzar;
Kuch Lakiron Mein Giraftar Hua; 

Raat Ek Shakhs Bahut Yaad Aaya; 
Jis Ghadi Chaand Numudaar Hua!

 Kisi Kee Yaad Dil Mein Aaj Bhi Hai;
Bhool Gaye Wo Magar Pyaar Aaj Bhi Hai;
Hum Khush Rehne Ka Daawa To Karte Hain Magar;
Unki Yaad Mein Behte Aansu Aaj Bhi Hain!

 Apno Ne Zehar Ka Jaam De Diya;
Gairon Ne Bewafa Naam De Diya;
Jo Kehte The Humein Bhool Na Jana;
Unhi Ne Bhoolne Ka Paigam De Diya!

 Nikli Mohabbat Kee Jo Baat...

Nikli Mohabbat Kee Jo Baat To Tum Yaad Aa Gaye;
Uthe Dil Mein Wo Jazbat To Tum Yaad Aa Gaye;

Garmi Ne Sukha Diya Tha Teri Yaadon Ko;
Hui Jab Phir Pyaar Ki Barsat To Tum Yaad Aa Gaye;

Yun To Dil Mera Bebas Na Rehta Tha;
Badle Jab Halaat To Tum Yaad Aa Gaye;

Sone-Chandi Se Sazi Rehti Thi Kalai Meri;
Khali Dekhe Jab Apne Haath To Tum Yaad Aa Gaye!

 Dil Ne Ek Ek Dukh Saha Tanha;
Anjuman Anjuman Raha Tanha;

Dhalte Saayon Mein Tere Kooche Se;
Koi Guzara Hai Barha, Tanha;

Teri Aahat Kadam Kadam, Aur Main;
Us Maiyat Mein Bhi Raha Tanha;

Kuhna Yaadon Ke Barf-e-Jaaron Se;
Ek Aansu Baha, Baha Tanha;

Doobte Sahil Ke Mod Pe Dil;
Ek Khandhar Sa Raha Saha, Tanha;

Goonjta Reh Geya Khalaon Mein;
Waqt Ka Ek Kehkaha, Tanha!

 Tere Khyalon Se Dhadkan Ko Chupa Ke Dekha Hai;
Dil-o-Nazar Ko Bahut Rula Ke Dekha Hai;
Teri Kasam Tu Nahi To Kuch Bhi Nahi;
Kyonki Maine Kuch Pal Tujhe Bhula Ke Dekha Hai!

 Kahan Koi Aisa Mila Jis Pe Hum Dil Luta Dete;
Har Ek Ne Dhokha Diya Kis-Kis kK Bhula Dete;
Apne Dil Ka Dard Dil Hi Mein Dabaye Rakhe Hain;
Karte Bayan To Mehfil Ko Rula Dete!

 Kadmo Kee Doori Se Dilon Ke Fansle Nahi Badhte;
Door Hone Se Dil Ke Ehsaas Nahi Marte;
Kuch Kadmon Ka Fansla Hi Sahi Hamare Beech;
Lekin Aisa Koi Pal Nahi Jab Hum Aapko Yaad Nahi Karte!

 Chaman Mein Subah Ye Kehti Thi Ho Kar Chashm-e-Tar Shabnam; 
Bahaar-e-Baag To Yun Hi Rahi Lekin Kidhar Shabnam; 

Arq Kee Boond Us Kee Zulf Se Rukhsaar Par Tapki; 
Tazub Kee Hai Jaage Ye Padi Khurshid Par Shabnam; 

Humein To Baag Tujh Bin Khana-e-Matam Nazar Aaya; 
Idhar Gul Phadte The Jeb, Roti Thi Udhar Shabnam; 

Kare Hai Kuch Na Kuch Taseer Sohbat Saaf Taabon Kee; 
Hui Aatish Se Gul Ke Baithte Rashq-e-Sharar Shabnam;

Bhala Tuk Subah Hone Do Ise Bhi Dekh Levenge; 
Kisi Aashiq Ke Rone Se Nahi Rakhti Khabar Shabnam;

Na Samjha 'Dard' Humne Bhed Ya Kee Shadi-o-Gham Ka; 
Sehar Khandaan Hai Kyon Roti Hai Kis Ko Yaak Kar Shabnam!

 Kuch Log Toot Kar Chahte Hain;
Kuch Log Chah Kar Toot Jaate Hain;
Humein Tumse Hai Kitni Mohabbat;
Kabhi Aao Hamare Paas Tumhein Batate Hain!

 Ab Khushi Hai Na Koi Gham Rulane Wala;
Humne Apna Liya Har Rang Zamane Wala;

Har Be-Chehra Si Ummeed Hai Chehra Chehra;
Jis Taraf Dekhi Aane Ko Hai Aane Wala;

Usko Rukhsat To Kiya Tha Mujhe Maloom Na Tha;
Sara Ghar Le Geya Ghar Chhod Ke Jaane Wala;

Door Ke Chaand Ko Dhundo Na Kisi Aanchal Mein;
Ye Ujala Nahi Aangan Mein Samane Wala;

Ek Musafir Ke Safar Jaisi Hai Sabki Duniya;
Koi Jaldi Mein Koi Der Mein Jaane Wala!

 Tujhe Chahne Wale Kum Na Honge;
Waqt Ke Sath Shayad Hum Na Honge;
Chahe Kisi Ko Kitna Bhi Pyaar Dena;
Lekin Teri Yaadon Ke Haqdar Sirf Hum Hi Honge!

 Udas Na Baitho Fiza Tang Karegi;

Gujre Hue Lamho Ki Sazaa Tang Karegi;

Kisi Ko Na Lao Dil Ke Itna Kareeb;

Kyonki Uske Jaane Ke Baad Uski Har Adaa Tang Karegi!

 Ishq Ko Taqleed Se Azaad Kar;
Dil Se Giraya Aankh Se Fariyad Kar;

Baaz Aa Ai Banda-e-Husn Mizaz;
Yun Na Apni Zindagi Barbaad Kar;

Ai Khayalon Ke Makeen Nazron Se Door;
Meri Veeraan Khalvatein Aabaad Kar;

Nazaz Mein Hichki Nahi Aayi Mujhe;
Bhoolne Wale Khuda-Raa Yaad Kar;

Husn Ko Duniya Kee Aankhon Se Na Dekh;
Apni Ek Tarz-e-Nazar Izaad Kar;

Ishrat-e-Duniya Hai Ek Khwab-e-Bahar;
Kabaa-e-Dil Dard Se Aabaad Kar;

Ab Kahan 'Ehsaan' Duniya Mein Wafa;
Tauba Kar Nadaan Khuda Ko Yaad Kar!

 Dil Toot Jata Hai Par Khanak Nahi Hoti;
Har Dhadkan Roti Hai Par Palak Nahi Roti;
Mohabbat Naam Hai Khuda Kee Bandagi Ka;
Jo Sharton Pe Mile Woh Mohbbat Nahi Hoti!

 Ek Jurm Hua Hai Hum Se Ek Yaar Bana Baithe Hain;
Kuch Apna Sa Us Ko Samajh Kar Sab Raaz Bata Baithe Hain;
Phir Us Ke Pyaar Kee Raah Mein Dil-o-Jaan Gawa Baithe Hain;
Woh Yaad Bahut Aate Hain Jo Hum Ko Bhula Baithe Hain!

 Itni Shiddat Se Chaha Use Ki Khud Ko Bhi Bhula Diya;
Unke Liye Apne Dil Ko Kitni Hi Baar Rula Diya;
Ek Baar Hi Thukraya Unhone;
Aur Humne Khud Ko Maut Kee Neend Sula Diya!

 Wo Aayi Nahi Kabhi Mujhe Yaad Karke;
Wo Gayi Jab Bhi Mujhe Barbaad Karke;
Agar Wo Aaye Meri Maut Pe To Use Keh Dena;
Abhi Soya Hai Tujhe Yaad Karke!

 Agar Wo Khush Hai Dekh Kar Aansu Meri Aankhon Mein;
To Rab Kee Kasam Hum Muskurana Chhod Denge;
Tadapte Rahenge Use Dekhne Ko;
Lekin Us Kee Taraf Nazrein Uthana Chhod Denge!

 Ye Zamane Kee Wafaye

Ye Zamane Kee Wafaye Mere Kaam Kee Nahi;
Mujhe Uski Wafa Chahiye Kisi Aam Kee Nahi;

Uski To Ek Muskurahat Bhi Anmol Thi;
Ye Tamam Muskurahate Kisi Daam Ki Nahi;

Mujhe Gham Hai To Uske Chale Jaane Ka;
Parwah Mujh Par Lage Kisi Ilzaam Kee Nahi;

Mera Haath Dekh Kar Rabb Ye Bola;
Bahut Si Chahate Tere Liye Hai Baki;

Lekin, Tere Haath Mein Koi Bhi Lakir Uske Naam Kee Nahi!

 Zakham Kee Baat Nahi Hai Jaane Dard Kyon Hota Hai;
Dhokhe Kee Baat Nahi Hai Jaane Ehaas Kyon Hota Hai;
Jante Hue Ki Wo Bewafa Hain;
Na Jane Phir Bhi Pyaar Kyon Hota Hai!

 Rooh Ko Tadpa Rahi Hai

Rooh Ko Tadpa Rahi Hai Un Kee Yaad;
Dard Ban Kar Chaa Rahi Hai Un Kee Yaad;

Ishq Se Ghabra Rahi Hai Un Kee Yaad;
Rukte-Rukte Aa Rahi Hai Un Kee Yaad;

Wo Hanse Wo Zer-e-Lab Kuch Keh Uthe;
Khwab Se Dikhla Rahi Hai Un Kee Yaad;

Main To Khudari Ka Qayal Hun Magar;
Kya Karun Phir Aa Rahi Hai Un Kee Yaad;

Ab Khyal-e-Tark-e-Rabt Zabt Hi Se Hai;
Khud B Khud Sharma Rahi Hai Un Kee Yaad!

 Bewafai Karke Niklun Ya Wafa Kar Jaunga;
Shehar Ko Har Zaike Se Aashna Kar Jaunga;
Tu Bhi Dhoondega Mujhe Shauq-e-Saza Mein Ek Din;
Main Bhi Koi Khoobsurat Si Khata Kar Jaunga!

 Kab Tak Reh Paoge Aakhir Yun Door Hum Se;
Milna Padega Aakhir Kabhi Zaroor Hum Se;
Nazrein Churane Wale Ye Berukhi Hai Kaisi;
Keh Do Agar Hua Hai Koi Kasoor Hum Se!

 Tamana Hai Meri Ki Aapki Aarzoo Ban Jaun;
Aapki Aankh Ka Tara Na Sahi Aapki Aankh Ka Aansu Ban Jaun;
Main Aap Kee Zindagi Kee Khushi Banu Ya Na Ban Sakun;
Aapke Gham Mein Aapka Sahara Ban Jaun!

 Fizao Ka Mausam Jaane Ke Baad Baharo Ka Mausam Aaya;
Gulab Se Gulab Ka Rang Tere Gaalon Par Aaya;
Tere Naino Ne Kaali Ghata Ka Jab Kajal Lagaya;
Jawani Jo Tum Par Aayi To Nasha Meri Aankhon Mein Aaya!

 Tere Naam Se Mohabbat

Tere Naam Se Mohabbat Kee Hai;
Tere Ehsaas Se Mohabbat Kee Hai;

Tum Pass Nahi Ho Mere Phir Bhi;
Tumhari Yaad Se Mohabbat Kee Hai;

Kabhi Tumne Bhi Mujhe Yaad Kiya Hoga;
Maine Un Lamhaat Se Mohabbat Kee Hai;

Tum Se Milna To Ek Khwaab Sa Lagta Hai;
Maine Tumhare Intezar Se Bhi Mohabbat Kee Hai!

 Nikli Mohabbat Ki Baat To Tum Yaad Aa Gaye;
Uthe Dil Mein Wo Zazbat To Tum Yaad Aa Gaye;
Garmi Ne Sukha Diya Tha Teri Yaadon Ko;
Hui Jab Pyaar Kee Barsat To Tum Yaad Aa Gaye!

 Kaha Ye Kisi Ne Kee Phoolon Se Dil Lagau Main;
Agar Tera Khayal Na Sochun To Mar Jaun Main;
Maang Na Mujhse Tu Hisaab Meri Mohabbat Ka;
Aa Jaun Imtihan Pe To Hadd Se Guzar Jaun Main!

 Tumhari Yaad Ke Jab Zakhm Bharne Lagte Hain;
Kisi Bahane Tumhein Yaad Karne Lagte Hain;

Hadis-e-Yaar Ke Unavan Nikharane Lagte Hain;
To Har Harim Mein Gesu Sanwarne Lagte Hain;

Har Ajnabi Humein Mehram Dikhai Deta Hai;
Jo Ab Bhi Teri Gali Se Guzarne Lagte Hain;

Saba Se Karte Hain Gurbat-Nasib Zikr-e-Vatan;
To Chashm-e-Subah Mein Aansu Ubharne Lagte Hain;

Wo Jab Bhi Karte Hain Is Nutq-o-Lab Kee Bakhiyagari;
Faza Mein Aur Bhi Nagme Bikharne Lagte Hain;

Dar-e-Qafas Pe Andhere Kee Mohar Lagti Hai;
To 'Faiz' Dil Mein Sitare Utarane Lagte Hain!

 Lekar Hum Dusro Kee Hansi Kya Karein;
Jo Apni Nahi Wo Khushi Kya Karein;
Tanha Jeene Se Behtar Hai Mar Jayein Hum;
Jab Saath Tum Nahi To Zindagi Jee Kar Kya Karein!

 Raat Kee Tanhai Mein Akele The Hum;
Dard Kee Mehfilon Mein Ro Rahe The Hum;
Aap Hamare Bhale Hi Kuch Nahi Lagte;
Par Fir Bhi Aapke Bina Bilkul Adhoore Hain Hum!

 Baat Karni Mushkil

Baat Karni Mushkil Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;
Jaisi Ab Hai Teri Mehfil Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;

Le Geya Cheen Ke Kaun Aaj Tera Sabr-o-Qarar;
Be Qarari Tujhe Ai Dil Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;

Teri Aankhon Ne Khuda Jane Kya Kya Jadu;
Ki Tabiyat Meri Mayal Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;

Kya Sbab Tu Jo Bigadta Hai 'Zafar' Se Har Baar;
Kho Teri Hoor Shmail Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi!

 Rahon Pe Nazar Rakhna Honthon Pe Dua Rakhna;
Aa Jaye Koi Shayad Darwaza Khula Rakhna;

Ehsaas Kee Shamaa Ko Is Tarah Jalaa Rakhna;
Apni Bhi Khabar Rakhna Us Ka Bhi Pata Rakhna;

Raaton Ko Bhatakne Kee Deta Hai Saza Mujhe;
Dushwaar Hai Pehlu Mein, Dil Tere Bina Rakhna;

Logon Ko Nigaahon Se Padh Lene Kee Aadat Hai;
Logon Kee Tehreeron Ko Logon Se Bacha Rakhna;

Bhuloon Main Agar Aye Dil, Tu Yaad Dila Dena;
Tanhai Ke Lamhon Ka Har Zakham Hara Rakhna;

Ik Boond Bhi Ashkon Kee Daaman Na Bhigo Paaye;
Gham Us Kee Amaanat Hai, Palkon Pe Sajaa Rakhna;

Iss Tarah 'Qateel' Us Se Bartaao Rahe Apna;
Woh Bhi Na Bura Maane, Dil Ka Bhi Kaha Rakhna!

 Har Sitam Seh Kar Kitne Gham Chipaye Humne;
Teri Khatir Har Din Aansu Bahaye Humne;
Tu Chhod Geya Jaha Humein Raahon Mein Akela;
Bas Tere Diye Zakhm Har Ek Se Chipaye Humne!

 Har Roz Koi Khwaab Toot Jata Hai;
Har Roz Koi Apna Rooth Jata Hai;
Na Jaane Meri Kismat Mein Kya Hai;
Jise Main Yaad Karun Wohi Mujhe Bhool Jata Hai!

 Ye Hum Bhi Gawara Karte Hain;
Ye Tum Bhi Gawara Kar Lena;

Ro-Ro Ke Guzari Hai Humne;
Tum Hans Ke Guzara Kar Lena;

Betabi Had Se Badh Jaye;
Aur Nind Na Aaye Raaton Ko;

To Doob Ke Meri Yaadon Main;
Duniya Se Kinara Kar Lena;

Jis Waqt Janaza Guzrega;
Us Shaks Ka Tere Kooche Se;

Jazbat Pe Kabu Kar Lena;
Khidki Se Nazara Kar Lena!

 Khafa Bhi Rehte Hain Aur Wafa Bhi Karte Hain;
Is Tarha Apne Pyaar Ko Bayan Bhi Karte Hain;
Jane Kaisi Narazgi Hai Meri Unse;
Khona Bhi Chahte Hain Aur Pane Kee Dua Bhi Karte Hain!

 Aaj Achanak Teri Yaad Ne Mujhe Rula Diya;
Kya Karu Tum Ne Jo Mujhe Bhula Diya;
Na Karte Wafa To Na Milti Ye Saza;
Shayad Meri Wafaon Ne Hi Tujhe Bewafa Bana Diya!

 Mil Bhi Jaate Hain Toh

Mil Bhi Jate Hain Toh Katara Ke Nikal Jaate Hain;
Haye Mausam Kee Tarah Dost Badal Jaate Hain;

Hum Abhi Tak Hain Giraftar-e-Mohabbat Yaaro;
Thokarein Kha Ke Suna Tha Ki Sambhal Jaate Hain;

Ye Kabhi Apni Jafa Par Na Hua Sharminda;
Hum Samajhate Rahe Patthar Bhi Pighal Jaate Hain;

Umar Bhar Jin Kee Wafaon Pe Bharosa Kije;
Waqt Padane Pe Wohi Log Badal Jaate Hain!

 Maana Ke Mujhse Woh Khafa Rahe Honge;
Ho Sakta Hai Woh Mujhe Aazma Rahe Honge;
Hum Utni Hi Shiddat Se Yaad Karenge Unhein;
Jitni Shiddat Se Woh Humein Bhula Rahe Honge!

 Taraste The Jo Humse Milne Ko Kabhi;
Na Jaane Kyon Aaj Humare Saye Se Bhi Katrate Hain;
HUm bhi Wahi Hain Yeh Dil Bhi Wahi Hai;
Na Jaane Phir Kyon Aise Log Badal Jaate Hain!

 Dard Mein Is Dil Ko Tadapte Dekha;
Apne Samne Har Rishte Ko Bikharte Dekha;
Kitne Pyaar Se Sajai Thi Khwabon Kee Duniya;
Use Apni Aankon Ke Samne Ujadte Hue Dekha!

 Itni Muddat Baad

Itni Muddat Baad Mile Ho;
Kin Socho Mein Gum Rahate Ho;

Tez Hawaa Ne Mujh Se Puchaa;
Ret Pe Kya Likhte Rehte Ho;

Kaun Si Baat Hai Tum Mein Aisi;
Itne Achchhe Kyon Lagte Ho;

Hum Se Na Poocho Hijr Ke Qisse;
Apni Kaho Ab Tum Kaise Ho!

 Nahi Jo Dil Mein Jagah To Nazar Mein Rehne Do;
Meri Hayaat Ko To Apne Asar Me Rehne Do;
Main Apni Soch Ko Teri Gali Me Chhod Aaya Hun;
Mere Wazood Ko Khwabon Ke Ghar Mein Rehne Do!

 Is Ada Se Wo Wafaa Karte Hain;
Koi Jaane Ki Wafa Karte Hain;

Humko Chodoge To Pachtaoge;
Hansne Walon Se Hansa Karte Hain;

Ye Batata Nahi Koi Mujhko;
Dil Jo Aa Jaye To Kya Karte Hain;

Husn Ka Haq Nahi Rehta Baki;
Har Ada Mein Wo Ada Karte Hain;

Kis Kadar Hain Teri Aankhein Bebaak;
In Se Fitne Bhi Hya Karte Hain;

Is Liye Dil Ko Laga Rakha Hai;
Is Mein Dil Ko Laga Rakha Hai;

'Daag' Tu Dekh To Kya Hota Hai;
Jabr Par Jabr Kiya Karte Hain!

 Wo Mohabbtein Jo Tumhare Dil Mein Hain;
Usse Zubaan Par Lao Aur Bayan Kar Do;
Aaj Bas Tum Kaho Aur Kehte Hi Jao;
Hum Bas Sunein Aise Be-Zuban Kar Do!

 Baat Phoolon Ki Suna Karte The;
Hum Kabhi Sher Kaha Karte The;

Mashalein Lekar Tumhare Gham Kee;
Hum Andheron Mein Chala Karte The;

Ab Kahan Aisi Tabiyat Wale;
Chot Kha Kar Jo Jiya Karte The;

Tark-e-Ehsas-e-Mohabbat Mushkil;
Haan Magar Ahl-e-Wafa Karte The;

Bikhri Bikhri Hui Zulfon Wale;
Kaafile Rok Liya Karte The;

Aaj Gulshan Mein Shagufe "Saghar";
Shikwa Ai Baad-e-Sabaa Karte The!

 Jis Tarah Ragon Mein Khoon Rehta Hai;
Ussi Tarah Mujhe Teri Chahat Ka Junoon Rehta Hai;
Zindagi Kee Har Khushi Mansoob Hai Tumse;
Baat Ho Tum Se To Dil Ko Sukoon Rehta Hai!

 Pyaar Karte Hain Tumse Kitna Kabhi Dikha Na Sake;
Tum Kya Ho Hamare Liye Yeh Kabhi Bata Na Sake;
Kya Hu Jo Aaj Tum Sath Nahi Ho Fir Bhi;
Tumhari Kisi Bhi Yaad Ko Hum Bhula Na Sake!

 Tumhari Khamoshi Hamari Aadat Hai;
In Dooriyon Mein Bhi Hamari Chahat Hai;
Hamari Zindagi Agar Khoobsurat Hai;
To Uski Wajah Bhi Aapki Muskurahat Hai!

 Kab Ta Dil Kee Khair Manayein Kab Tak Raah Dikhlaoge;
Kab Tak Chain Kee Mohlat Doge Kab Tak Yaad Naa Aaoge;

Beeta Deed Umeed Ka Mausam Khak Udti Hai Aankhon Mein;
Kab Bhejoge Dard Ka Baadal Kab Barkha Barsaoge;

Ahd-E-Wafa Ya Tark-E-Mohabbat Jo Chaho So Aap Karo;
Apne Bas Kee Baat Hi Kya Hai Hum Se Kya Manwaoge;

Kis Ne Vasl Ka Suraj Dekha Kis Par Hijr Kee Raat Dhali;
Gesuon Wale Kaun The Kya The Un Ko Kya Jatlaoge;

'Faiz' Dilon Ke Baag Mein Hai Ghar Bharnaa Bhi Lut Jana Thi;
Tum Is Husn Ke Lutf-o-Karam Par Kitne Din Itraoge!

 Ek Kahani Si Dil Par Likhi Reh Gayi;
Wo Nazar Jo Mujhe Dekhti Reh Gayi;
Log Aakar Bazaar Mein Bik Bhi Gaye;
Meri Keemat Lagi Kee Lagi Reh Gayi!

 Sirf Itna Hi Kaha Hai, Pyaar Hai Tumse;
Jazbaton Kee Koi Numaish Nahi Kee;
Pyaar Ke Badle Sirf Pyaar Manga Hai;
Rishte Kee To Koi Guzarish Nahi Kee!

 Socha Nahi Achha Bura

Socha Nahi Achha Bura Dekha Suna Kuch Bhi Nahi;
Manga Khuda Se Raat Din Tere Siwa Kuch Bhi Nahi;

Dekha Tujhe Socha Tujhe Chaha Tujhe Puja Tujhe;
Meri Khata Meri Wafa Teri Khata Kuch Bhi Nahi;

Jis Par Hamari Aankh Ne Moti Bichaye Raat Bhar;
Bheja Wahi Kagaz Use Hum Ne Likha Kuch Bhi Nahi;

Ek Sham Kee Dehleez Par Baithe Rahe Wo Der Tak;
Aankhon Se Kee Baatein Bahut Munh Se Kaha Kuch Bhi Nahi;

Do Chaar Din Kee Baat Hai Dil Khak Mein So Jayega;
Jab Aag Par Kagaz Rakha Baki Bacha Kuch Bhi Nahi;

Ehsaas Kee Khushbu Kahan, Aawaz Ke Jugnu Kahan;
Khamosh Yaadon Ke Siwa, Ghar Mein Raha Kuch Bhi Nahi!

 Khushbu Mangi Thi Rabb Se;
Wo Humein Lajawab Phool Thama Gaye;
Thodi Khushi Mangi Thi Dua Mein;
Wo Humein Aapse Milakar Sabse Khush Nasib Bana Gaye!

 Zindagi Mujhse Yun Daga Na Kar;
Main Zinda Rahu Bin Uske Ye Dua Na Kar;
Dekhta Hai Use Koi To Hoti Hai Jalan;
Ai Hawa Tu Bhi Use Chuaa Na Kar!

 Roti Hui Aankhon Mein Intezar Hota Hai;
Na Chahte Hue Bhi Pyaar Hota Hai;
Kyon Dekhte Hain Hum Woh Sapne;
Jinke Tutne Par Bhi Unke Sach Hone Ka Intezar Hota Hai!

 Dil Geya Tumne Liya Hum Kya Karen;
Jaane Wali Cheez Ka Gham Kya Karen;

Hum Ne Mar Kar Hijr Mein Payi Shifa;
Aise Achhon Ka Maatam Kya Karen;

Apne Hi Gham Se Nahi Milti Najaat;
Is Binaa Par Fikr-E-Aalam Kya Karen;

Ek Saaghar Par Hai Apni Zindagi;
Rafta Rafta Is Se Bhi Kam Kya Karen;

Kar Chuke Sab Apni Apni Hikamtein;
Dum Nikalta Ho To Humdum Kya Karen;

Kehte Hain Ahl-E-Sifarish Mujh Se 'Daag';
Teri Kismat Hai Buri Hum Kya Karen!

 Kaha Ye Kisne Kee Phoolon Se Dil Lagau Main;
Agar Tera Khayal Na Sochu To Mar Jaun Main;
Maang Na Mujhse Tu Hisaab Meri Mohabbat Ka;
Aa Jaau Imtehaan Par To Hadd Se Guzar Jaun Main!

 Soch Nahi Sakte Ek Pal Bhi Door Rehna Tumse;
Agar Tu Bhool Jaaye To Toot Ke Bikhar Jaun Main;
Kabhi Jannat Bhi Mile Mujhe Tere Pyaar Ke Badle;
Mohabbat Kee Kasam Wahan Bhi Mukar Jaun Main!

 Ik Umar Dil Kee Ghaat Se Tujh Par Nigaah Kee;
Tujh Par Teri Nigaah Se Chhup Kar Nigaah Kee;

Roohon Mein Jalti Aag Khayalon Mein Khilte Phool;
Saari Sadakatein Kisi Kaafir Nigaah Kee;

Jab Bhi Gham-e-Zamana Se Aankhein Hui Do-Chaar;
Munh Pher Kar Tabassum-e-Dil Par Nigaah Kee;

Baagen Khinchi Masafatein Kadki Faras Ruke;
Maazi Kee Rath Se Kis Ne Palat Kar Nigaah Kee;

Dono Ka Rabt Hai Meri Mauj-e-Khiram Se;
Lagzish Khayal Kee Ho Ke Thokar Nigaah Kee!

 Zikar Hua Jab Khuda Ki Rehmaton Ka;
Humne Khud Ko Khushnaseeb Paya;
Tamanna Thi Ek Pyaare Se Dost Ki;
Khuda Khud Dost Bankar Chala Aaya!

 Waqt Aur Khushi Tere Gulam Honge;
Ye Pal Ye Pehlu Tere Hi Naam Honge;
Dekhna Kabhi Jhuk Kar Neeche Bhi Ai Humsafar;
Tere Har Kadam Ke Neeche, Mere Haathon Ke Nishan Honge!

 Chupa Loon Is Tarah Tujhe Apni Baahon Mein;
Ki Hawa Bhi Guzarne Ki Izazat Maange;
Ho Jaun Itna Madhosh Tere Ishq Mein;
Ki Hosh Bhi Aane Ki Izazat Manage!

 Jahan Katre Ko Tarsaya Geya Hun;
Wahin Dooba Hua Paya Geya Hun;

Ba-Haal-e-Gham-Rahi Paya Geya Hun;
Haram Se Deir Mein Laya Geya Hun;

Balaa Kaafi Na Thi Ek Zindagi Kee;
Dobara Yaad Pharmaya Geya Hun;

Ba-Rang-e-Lala-e-Veerana Bekaar;
Khilaya Aur Murjhaya Geya Hun;

Agarche Abr-e-Gauhar-Baar Hun Main;
Magar Aankhon Se Barsaya Geya Hun;

'Hafeez' Ahal-e-Zubaan Kab Maante The;
Bade Zoron Se Manvaya Geya Hun!

 Mohabbat Mein Kuch Is Tarah Wafa Karun;
Woh Bhool Bhi Jaye To Yaad Karun;
Mohabbat Ne Bas Itna Sikhaya Hai Mujhe;
Ki Khud Se Pehle Unke Liye Dua Karun!

 Baat Umar Bhar Kee Thi Do Pal Kee Nahi;
Baat Saath Kee Thi Halaat Kee Nahi;
Jahan Ke Mele Mein Haath Chhod Diya Tune;
Baat Zubaan Kee Thi Kismat Kee Nahi!

 Lab Pe Pabandi To Hai Ehsas Par Pehra To Hai;
Phir Bhi Ahl-e-Dil Ko Ahval-e-Bashar Kehna To Hai;

Khoon-e-Adaa Se Na Ho Khoon-e-Shahidaan Se Hi Ho;
Kuch Na Kuch Is Daur Mein Rang-e-Chaman Nikhra To Hai;

Apni Ghairat Bech Daalen Apna Maslak Chhod Den;
Rehnumaon Mein Bhi Kuch Logon Ka Ye Mansha To Hai;

Bhuj Rahe Hain Ek Ek Kar Ke Aqidon Ke Diye;
Is Andhere Ka Bhi Lekin Saamna Karna To Hai;

Juth Kyon Bole Farogh-E-Maslahat Ke Naam Par;
Zindagi Pyari Sahi Lekin Humein Marna To Hai!

 Yaad Rukti Nahi Rok Paane Se;
Dil Maanta Nahi Kisi Ke Manane Se;
Ruk Jaati Hain Dhadkane Aapko Bhool Jaane Se;
Isliye Aapko Yaad Karte Hain Jeene Ke Bahane Se!

 Dukh Dete Ho Aur Khud Hi Swaal Karte Ho;
Tum Bhi O Sanam Kamaal Karte Ho;
Dekh Kar Puch Liya Hai HaaL Mera;
Chalo Shukr Hai Kuch To Khyaal Karte Ho!

 Saanson Kee Hararat Se Pighal Jaane Ka Mausam;
Aaya Hai Teri Aanch Mein Jal Jaane Ka Mausam;

Hum Ko Nahi Maaloom Tha Ishq Ka Aaghaaz;
Yaadon Mein Kahin Door Nikal Jaane Ka Mausam;

Lagta Hai Ki Chehre Pe Tere Thehar Geya Hai;
Yak Lakht Kayi Rang Badal Jaane Ka Mausam;

Ai Shehar Tasalli Tere Mashkoor Hain Hum;
Aaya Hi Nahi Dil Ke Sambhal Jaane Ka Mausam;

Ye Shehar-e-Tamanna Bhi Anokha Hai Ki Is Par;
Barsaat Mein Bhi Rehta Hai Thal Jaane Ka Mausam;

Chehre Pe Agarche Hain Mere Subah Ka Ujaala;
Aankhon Mein Magar Shaam Ke Dhal Jaane Ka Mausam!

 Kash Koi Mile Is Tarah Ke Phir Judaa Na Ho;
Wo Samjhe Mere Mizaz Ko Aur Kabhi Khafa Na Ho;
Apne Ehsaas Se Baant Le Saari Tanhayi Meri;
Itna Pyaar De Jo Pehle Kabhi Kisi Ne Diya Na Ho!

 Tujhe Chahte Hain Be-Inteha Par Chahna Nahi Aata;
Ye Kaisi Mohabbat Hai Ki Humein Kehna Nahi Aata;
Zindagi Mein Aa Jao Hamari Zindagi Ban Kar;
Ki Tere Bin Humein Zinda Rehna Nahi Aata!

 Ab Woh Galiyan Wo Makaan Yaad Nahi;
Kaun Rehta Tha Kahan Yaad Nahi;

Jalwa-e-Husn-e-Azal The Woh Dayaar;
Jin Ke Ab Naam-o-Nishaan Yaad Nahi;

Koi Ujala Sa Bhalaa Sa Ghar Tha;
Kis Ko Dekha Tha Wahan Yaad Nahi;

Yaad Hai Zeena-e-Pechaan Us Ka;
Dar-o-Deewar-e-Makaan Yaad Nahi;

Yaad Hai Zamzama-e-Saaz-e-Bahaar;
Shor-e-Awaaz-e-Khizaan Yaad Nahi!

 Aisa Nahi Hai Ki Ab Teri Mujhko Zaroorat Nahi Rahi;
Bas Toot Toot Kar Ab Bikhrne Kee Himmat Nahi Rahi;
Aisa Nahi Hai Ki Tere Peeche Teri Yaad Aati Nahi Rahi;
Bas Ab Foot Foot Kar Rone Kee Himmat Nahi Rahi!

 Mujhse Na Sahi, Gairon Se Hi Sahi;
Tumhein Dil Ko Lagana Aa To Geya;
Duniya Mein Kisi Ke Tum Ho To Gaye;
Chalo Tumhein Pyaar Nibhana Aa To Geya!

 Tumne Dekha To Humein Pyaar Se Bas Itna Hi Sahi;
Tera Bas Ho Geya Deedar Bas Itna Hi Sahi;
Tera Aashiq Hun Tumne Humein Chaha Na Sahi;
Kabhi Mujhko Pehchaan Liya Bas Itna Hi Sahi!

 Koi Soorat
Koi Soorat Nikalti Kyon Nahi Hai;
Yahan Halat Badalti Kyon Nahi Hai; 

Ye Bujhta Kyon Nahi Hai Unka Sooraj;
Hamari Shama Jalti Kyon Nahi Hai;

Agar Hum Jhel Hi Baithe Hain Isko;
To Phir Ye Raat Dhalti Kyon Nahi Hai;

Mohabbat Sar Ko Chadh Jati Hai, Aksar; 
Mere Dil Mein Machalti Kyon Nahi Hai!

 Chaand Sa Yeh Chehra Dekhne Ke Izazat De Do;
Mujhe Ye Shaam Sajane Kee Izazat De Do;
Mujhe Qaid Kar Lo Apne Ishq Mein Ya Fir;
Mujhe Ishq Karne Kee Izazat De Do!

 Kuch Cheezein Hum Purani Chhod Aaye;
Aate Aate Uski Aankhon Mein Paani Chhod Aaye;
Ye Aisa Dard Hai Jo Bayaan Ho Hi Nahi Sakta;
Dil To Saath Le Aaye Lekin Dhadkan Wahin Chhod Aaye!

 Phool Hun Main Meri Khusbu Tum Ho;
Dil Hun Main Meri Dhadkan Tum Ho;
Jaan Hun Main Aur Meri Rooh Tum Ho;
Jism Hun Main Aur Meri Zindagi Tum Ho!

 Aate Jaate Mujhe Ilzaam

Aate Jaate Mujhe Ilzaam To Dete Jao;
Aate Jaate Mujhe Ilzaam To Dete Jao;

Damm Nikal Jaye Jo Uth Ker Shab-E-Tunhaai Main;
Mujh Ko Wapis Dil-E-Nakaam To Dete Jao;

Main Kisi Aur Ka Ehsaan Naheen Lay Sakti;
Meri Qismat Mera Anjaam To Dete Jao;

Phool Mehkaon -k- Daaman Main Sajaon Kante;
Mere Hisse Ka Mujhe Kaam To Dete Jao!

 Nibha Sakta Hun Main Tamam Umar Saath Tera;
Magar Aapni Zindagi Par Mujhe Yaqeen Nahi;
Mere Marne Par Bhi Rahogi Tum Pass Mere;
Magar Hunga Us Waqt Bhi Main Tumhare Saath Nahi!

 Dil Mein Ho Aap To Koi Aur Khaas Kaise Hoga;
Yaadon Mein Aapke Siva Koi Pass Kaise Hoga;
Hichkiyan Kehti Hain Aap Yaad Karte Ho;
Par Bologe Nahi To Humein Ehsas Kaise Hoga!

 Kahan Se Layein Hunar Use Manane Ka;
Koi Jawab Nahi Tha Uske Rooth Ke Chale Jane Ka;
Milni Thi Mujhe Hi Saza Is Mohabbat Mein;
Kyon Ki Juram Maine Hi Kiya Tha Us Se Dil Lagane Ka!

 Jis Tarah Bhi Ho Saka Us Tarah Toda Mujhe;
Zindagi Ne Maut Ke Qabil Nahi Samjha Mujhe;

Zindagi Maankar Chalati Rahi Ghoda Mujhe;
Har Kadam Par Maarti Hai Ek Naya Koda Mujhe;

Zindagi Har Waqt Meri Peeth Par Baithi Rahi;
Apni Marzi Ke Mutabiq Har Taraf Moda Mujhe;

Is Tarah Apno Ke Ehsaan Hai Mujh Par Bahut;
Chot De Kar Dil Ko Sheeshe Ki Tarah Joda Mujhe;

He Zindagi Meri Tujhse Iltiza Itni Hai Bus;
Chodhkar Nafrat Ki Bhasha Pyar De Thoda Mujhe;

Warna Ek Din Jalti Hui Aag Se Bolegi Meri Laash Yoon;
Zindagi Ne Aag Ke Dariya Me Laa Chhoda Mujhe!

 Mat Puch Sabar Kee Inteha Kahan Tak Hai;
Tu Sitam Kar Le Teri Taqat Jahan Tak Hai;
Wafa Kee Umeed Kisi Aur Ko Hogi;
Humein To Dekhna Hai Tu Bewafa Kahan Tak Hai!

 Zindagi Nu Pyaar Assi Tere To Jyada Nahi Karde;
Kise Hor Te Aitbar Assi Tere To Jyada Nahi Karde;
Tu Jee Sake Mere Bin Eh Ta Changi Gall Hai Sajjna;
Par Assi Jee Lavange Tere Bin Eh Vaada Nahi Karde!

 Chaand Ko Sitaron Se Aur Mujhe Tum Se Mohabbat Hai;
Phoolon Ko Baharon Se Aur Mujhe Tum Se Mohabbat Hai;
Milo Jo Kabhi Kisi Mehfil Mein To Nazarein Jhuka Lena;
Koi Samjh Hi Na Paaye Ki Mujhe Tum Se Mohabbat Hai!

 Kuchh Faisala To Ho Ki Kidhar Jana Chahiye;
Paani Ko Ab To Sar Se Guzar Jana Chahiye;

Har Baar Aidiyon Pe Gira Hai Mera Lahoo;
Maqtal Mein Ab Ba-Tarz-e-Digar Jana Chahiye;

Kya Chal Sakenge Jin Ka Faqat Masla Ye Hai;
Jaane Se Pehle Rakht-e-Safar Jana Chahiye;

Sara Jvaar-Bhata Mere Dil Mein Hai Magar;
Ilzaam Ye Bhi Chaand Ke Sar Jana Chahiye;

Jab Bhi Gaye Azaab-e-Dar-o-Baam Tha Wahi;
Aakhir Ko Kitni Der Se Ghar Jana Chahiye;

Tohmat Laga Ke Maa Pe Jo Dushman Se Daad Le;
Aise Sukhanafarosh Ko Mar Jan Chahiye!

 Tujhse Ru-b-Ru Hokar Baatein Karu;
Nigahein Milakar Wafa Ke Vaade Karu;
Thaam Kar Tera Hath Baith Jaun Tere Samne;
Teri Haseen Surat Ke Nazare Karu!

 Zindagi Tasveer Bhi Bhi Hai Aur Taqdeer Bhi;
Farak To Bas Iske Rango Ka Hai;
Mann Chahe Rango Se Bane To Hai Tasveer;
Aur Aanjane Rango Se Bane To Hoti Hai Taqdeer!

 Nazarein Mile To Pyaar Ho Jata Hai;
Palkein Uthe To Izhaar Ho Jata Hai;
Na Jaane Kya Kasish Hai Chahat Mein;
Ki Koi Anjaan Bhi Hamari Zindagi Ka Haqdaar Ho Jata Hai!

 Ai Mohabbat Tere Anjaam Pe Rona Aaya;
Jaane Kyon Aaj Tere Naam Pe Rona Aaya;

Yun To Har Shaam Umeedon Mein Guzar Jati Hai;
Aaj Kuch Baat Hai Jo Shaam Pe Rona Aaya;

Kabhi Taqdeer Ka Maatam Kabhi Duniya Ka Gila;
Manzil-E-Ishq Mein Har Gham Pe Rona Aaya;

Mujh Pe Hi Khatam Hua Silsila-e-Nauhagri;
Is Kadar Gardish-e-Ayyam Pe Rona Aaya;

Jab Hua Zikar Zamaane Mein Mohabbat Ka 'Shakeel';
Mujh Ko Apne Dil-e-Naqaam Pe Rona Aaya!

 Ishq Ne Humein Benaam Kar Diya;
Har Khushi Se Humein Anjaan Kar Diya;
Humne To Kabhi Nahi Chaha Ki Humein Bhi Mohabbat Ho;
Lekin Aap Kee Ek Nazar Ne Humein Nilaam Kar Diya!

 Bas Ek Choti Si Tum Haan Kar Do;
Hamare Naam Is Tarha Sara Jahan Kar Do;
Wo Mohabbtein Jo Tumhare Dil Mein Hain;
Un Ko Zuban Par Lao Aur Bayan Kar Do!

 Teri Gali Mein Main Na Chalun

Teri Gali Mein Main Na Chalun Aur Sabaa Chale;
Yun Hi Khuda Jo Chahe To Bande Kee Kya Chale;

Kis Kee Ye Mauj-e-Husn Hui Jalvagaar Ki Yun;
Dariya Mein Jo Habab The Aankhein Chuppa Chale;

Hum Bhi Jaras Kee Tarah To Is Qafile Ke Saath;
Naale Jo Kuch Bisaat Mein The So Suna Chale;

Keh Baithiyo Na 'Dard' Ki Ahl-e-Wafaa Hun Main;
Us Bewafa Ke Aage Jo Zikr-e-Wafaa Chale!

 Mil Kar Judaa Hue To Na Soya Karenge Hum;
Ek Dusre Kee Yaad Mein Roya Karenge Hum;
Aansu Jhalak Jhalak Ke Satayenge Raat Bhar;
Moti Palak Palak Mein Piroya Karenge Hum!

 Kitab-e-Ishq Mein Jitne Alfaz Likhe Hain;
Dil Mein Mere Utne Ehsaas Rakhe Hain;
Tum Keh Kar Dekhte Sitamgar, Zalim;
Mere Labon Par Kitne Tere Naam Rakhe Hain!

 Kuch Sochta Hun To Tera Khayal Aa Jata Hai;
Kuch Bolta Hun To Tera Naam Aa Jata Hai;
Kab Tak Chupa Ke Rakhun Dil Kee Baat Ko;
Uski Har Ada Par Mujhe Pyaar Aa Jata Hai!

 Nafrat Na Kabhi Karna Humse;
Yeh Hum Seh Nahi Paayenge;
Ek Baar Keh Dena Humse Zaroorat Nahi Ab Tumhari;
Kasam Khuda Kee Tumhari Duniya Se Hans Kar Chale Jayenge!

 Tere Daaman Kee Hawa Mangte Hain;
Hum Bhi Jeene Kee Dua Mangte Hain; 

Mutaribo Koi Achuta Nagma; 
Saaz Aahang-o-Sadaa Mangte Hain;

Maah-o-Anjum Ke Jharokhe Aksar;
Kisi Ke Aariz Kee Dua Mangte Hain;

Phir Patangon Mein Khudayi Jagi; 
Sholay Hashr-Numa Mangte Hain; 

Banda-Parwar Koi Khairat Nahi; 
Hum Wafaon Ka Sila Mangte Hain; 

Maikada Ho Ke Kaleesa 'Saghir';
Sari Duniya Ka Bhala Mangte Hain!

 Kab Woh Zahir Hoga Aur Hairan Kar Dega Mujhe;
Jitni Bhi Mushkil Mein Hun Aasan Kar Dega Mujhe;
Roo-b-Roo Kar Ke Kabhi Apne Mehakte Surkh Honth;
Ek Do Pal Ke Liye Guldaan Kar Dega Mujhe!

 Holi Ke Din Ki Ye Mulaqat Yaad Rahegi;
Rango Ki Ye Barsaat Yaad Rahegi;
Aap Ko Mile Rangeen Duniya Aise Hamesha;
Is Toote Hue Dil Ki Rabb Se Yahi Fariyad Rahegi!

 Tujhe Chahte Hain Be-inteha Par Chahna Nahi Aata;
Ye Kaisi Mohabbat Hai Ki Humein Kehna Nahi Aata;
Zindagi Mein Aa Jao Hamari Zindagi Ban Kar;
Ki Tere Bin Humein Zinda Rehna Nahi Aata!

 Shayad Aaghaz Hua Phir

Shayad Aaghaz Hua Phir Kisi Afsane Ka;
Hukm Aadam Ko Hai Jannat Se Nikal Jane Ka;

Un Se Kuch Keh To Raha Hun Magar Allah Na Kare;
Wo Bhi Mafhoom Na Samjhe Mere Afsane Ka;

Dekhna Dekhna Yeh Hazrat-e-Vaiz Hi Na Hon;
Raasta Puch Raha Hai Koi Maikhane Ka;

Betalluq Tere Aage Se Guzar Jata Hun;
Yeh Bhi Ek Husn-e-Talab Hai Tere Deewane Ka;

Hashr Tak Garmi-e-Hungama-e-Hasti Hai 'Shakeel';
Silsila Khatm Na Hoga Mere Afsane Ka!

 Kabhi Yeh Chup Mein Kabhi Meri Baat Baat Mein Tha;
Tumhara Akss Meri Saari Qayenaat Mein Tha;
Hum Ehl-e-Ishq Bahut Bad-Guhmaan Hote Hain;
Isi Tarah Ka Koi Vasf Teri Jaat Mein Tha!

 Pehli Mohabbat Thi Hamari, Hum Jaan Na Sake;
Pyaar Hota Hai Kya Hum Pehchan Na Sake;
Humne Unhe Dil Mein Basaya Hai Iss Kadar Ki;
Chah Kar Bhi Hum Unhe Apne Dil Se Nikaal Na Sake!

 Bhula Kar Mujhe Agar Tum Ab Bhi Ho Salamat;
To Bhula Kar Tumhein Sambhalna Mujhe Bhi Aata Hai;
Meri Fitrat Mein Nahi Hai Bas Ye Aadat Varna;
Teri Tarah Yun Badalna Mujhe Bhi Aata Hai!

 Apna Deewana Bana Kar Le Jaye;
Kabhi Wo Aaye Aur Aa Kar Le Jaye;

Roz Buniyad Uthata Hun Nayi;
Roz Sailab Baha Kar Le Jaye;

Husn Walon Mein Koi Aisa Ho;
Jo Mujhe Mujh Se Chura Kar Le Jaye;

Rang-e-Rukhsaar Pe Itarao Nahi;
Jaane Kab Waqt Udaa Kar Le Jaye;

Kise Maloom Kahan Kaun Kise;
Apne Raaste Pe Laga Kar Le Jaye;

'Aftab' Ek To Aisa Ho Kahin;
Jo Humein Apna Bana Kar Le Jaye!

 Bahut Door Magar Bahut Paas Rehte Ho;
Aankhon Se Door Magar Dil Ke Paas Rehte Ho;
Mujhe Bas Itna Bata Do Ai Sanam;
Kya Tum Bhi Mere Bina Udaas Rehte Ho!

 Raaz Dil Ka Dil Mein Chupate Hain Woh;
Samne Aate Hi Nazar Jhukate Hain Woh;
Baat Karte Nahi, Ya Hoti Nahi;
Par Shukar Hai Jab Bhi Milte Hain Muskurate Hain Woh!

 Giri Is Tabassum Ki Bijli...


Giri Is Tabassum Ki Bijali Ajal Par;
Andhere Ka Ho Noor Mein Kya Guzara;

Justjoo Jis Gul Ki Tarpati Thi Ai Bulbul Mujhe;
Khoobi-e-Qismat Se Aakhir Mil Gaya Woh Gul Mujhe;

Parwana Tujhse Karta Hai Ai Shama Pyaar Kyon;
Ye Jaane Beqaraar Hai Tujh Par Nisar Kyon;

Qismat Buri Sahi Par Tabiyat Buri Nahin;
Hai Shukr Ki Jagah Ki Shikayat Nahin Mujhe;

Zulm Hai Gar Na Do Sakun Ki Daad;
Qahar Hai Gar Karona Mujhko Pyaar;

Hoga Koi Aisa Bhi Ki Ghalib Ko Na Jaane;
Shayar Toh Wah Achchha Hai Par Badnaam Bahut Hai!

 Aankh Ladate Hi Hua Ishq Ka Aazaar Mujhe;
Chashm Beemaar Teri Kar Gayi Beemaar Mujhe;

Dil Ko Zakhmi To Vah Karte Hain Magar Hairat Hai;
Nazar Aati Nahi Chalti Hui Talwar Mujhe!

 Lafzon Mein Kaise Tareef Karun,
Lafzon Mein Aap Kaise Sama Paoge;
Jab Bhi Puchenge Kabhi Log Aapke Baare Mein;
Hamari Aakhein Dekh Kar Wo Sab Jaan Jayenge!

 Zinda Rahe To Kya Hai, Jo Mar Jayein Hum To Kya;
Duniya Se Khamoshi Se Guzar Jayein Hum To Kya;
Hasti Hi Apni Kya Hai Zamane Ke Samne;
Ek Khwab Hain Jahan Mein Bikhar Jayein Hum To Kya!

 Ishq Mein Dil Ne Bahut Kaam Nikala Apna;
Sach Hai, Milta Hai Kahaan, Chahne Wala Apna;

Main Uthta Hun Sahare Ke Liye Uske;
Reh Na Geya Ho Raah Mein, Kahin Dard Apna!

 Ishq Ko Taqleed Se Aazad Kar;
Dil Se Giraya Aankh Se Fariyaad Kar;

Baaz Aa Ai Banda-e-Husn Majaz;
Yun Na Apni Zindagi Barbaad Kar;

Ai Khayalon Ke Makeen Nazron Se Door;
Meri Veeran Khalvatein Abaad Kar;

Naza Mein Hichki Nahi Aayi Mujhe;
Bhulne Wale Khudaa-Raa Yaad Kar;

Husn Ko Duniyaa Kee Aankhon Se Na Dekh;
Apni Ik Tarz-e-Nazar Izaad Kar;

Ishrat-e-Duniya Hai Ik Khwab-e-Bahar;
Kabaa-e-Dil Dard Se Abaad Kar;

Ab Kahan 'Ehsaan' Duniya Mein Wafa;
Tauba Kar Nadan Khuda Ko Yaad Kar!

 Ye Husn-e-Raaz Mohabbat Chupa Raha Hai Koi;
Hai Ashk Aankhon Mein Aur Muskura Raha Hai Koi;
Nazar Nazar Mein Tajalli Dikha Raha Hai Koi;
Nafaz Nafaz Pe Mujhe Yaad Aa Raha Hai Koi!

 Ret Pe Naam Kabhi Likhte Nahin;
Kyonki Ret Pe Likhe Naam Kabhi Tikte Nahin;
Aap Kehte Ho Tum Patthar Dil Ho;
Par Patthar Pe Likhe Naam Kabhi Mitte Nahin!

 Agar Talaash Karun Koi Mil Hi Jayega;
Magar Tumhaari Tarah Kaun Mujhe Chahega;
Tumhen Zaruur Koi Chahaton Se Dekhega;
Magar Vo Aankhein Hamari Kahaan Se Layega!

 Har Ek Baat Pe Kehte Ho

Har Ek Baat Pe Kehate Ho Tum Ki Tu Kya Hai;
Tum Hi Kaho Ki Ye Andaaz-e-Guftgu Kya Hai;

Ragon Mein Daudte Phirane Ke Hum Nahi Qaayal;
Jab Aankh Hi Se Na Tapka To Phir Lahoo Kya Hai;

Chipak Raha Hai Badan Par Lahoo Se Pairaahan;
Hamari Jeb Ko Ab Haajat-e-Rafoo Kya Hai;

Jalaa Hain Jism Jahaan, Dil Bhii Jal Geya Hoga;
Kuredte Ho Jo Ab Raakh, Justajuu Kya Hai!

 Hans Ke Farmaate Hai Woh, Dekh Ke Haalat Meri;
Kyon Tum Aasaan Samajhte The Mohabbat Meri;
Baad Marne Ke Bhi Chhori Na Rafaaqat Meri;
Meri Turbat Se Lagi Baithi Hai Hasrat Meri!

 Sanu Lodh Teri Hai Kinni Assi Dasde Nahi;
Sach Jaani Tere Bina Assi Kakh De Nahi;
Tasveer Teri Rakh Layi Hai Dil De Vich;
Bhul Ke Vi Kise Hor Nu Assi Takde Nahi!

 Aatish-e-Ishq Mein Jal Jaun Tujhe Is Se Kya;
Mausam Kee Tarah Badal Jaun Tujhe Is Se Kya;
Chot Khaun Ya Zakham Lage, Ya Ehsas-e-Gham Mein Tarpun;
Main Gir Jaun Ya Sambhal Jaun Tujhe Is Se Kya!

 Bas Ek Baar Kar Ke Aitbaar Likh Do;
Kitna Hai Mujh Se Pyaar Likh Do;
Kat Ti Nahi Ab Yeh Zindagi Bin Tere;
Aur Kitna Karun Main Intezar Likh Do!

 Kisi Ranjish Ko Hawa Do
Kisi Ranjish Ko Hawa Do Ke Mein Zinda Hoo Abhi;
Mujhe Koi Ahsaas Dila Do Ke Mein Zinda Hoon Abhi;

Mere Rukane Se Meri Saanse Bhi Ruk Jaayegi;
Fasale Aur Badha Do Ke Mein Zinda Hoon Abhi;

Zehar Peene Ki Toh Aadat Thi Zamanewalo;
Ab Koi Aur Dava Do Ke Mein Zinda Hoon Abhi;

Chalti Raho Mein Yuhi Aankh Lagi Hai 'Faakir';
Bheed Logo Ki Hata Do Ke Mein Zinda Hoon Abhi!

 Na Haara Hai Ishq Na Duniya Thaki Hai;
Diya Jal Raha Hai Hawa Chal Rahi Hai;
Sukoon Hi Sukoon Hai Khushi Hi Khushi Hai;
Tera Gham Salamat Mujhe Kya Kami Hai!

 Kisi Ko Pyaar Itna Dena Ki Koi Had Na Rahe;
Magar Aitbaar Bhi Itna Rakhna Ki Koi Shak Na Rahe;
Wafa Itni Karna Ki Bewafai Na Ho;
Aur Dua Bas Itni Karna Ki Kabhi Judai Na Ho!

 Paya Tumko To Hum Ko Laga Tumko Kho Diya;
Hum Dil Pe Roye Aur Yeh Dil Hum Pe Ro Diya;
Kyon Is Ke Fansle Hume Manzoor Ho Gaye;
Kitne Hue Kareeb Ke Hum Door Ho Gaye!

 Tanhaiyon Mein Muskurana Ishq Hai;
Kisi Baat Ko Sab Se Chupana Ishq Hai;
Yun To Neend Nahi Aati Humein Raat - Raat Bhar;
Magar Sote - Sote Jagna Aur Phir Jaagte - Jaagte Sona Hi Ishq Hai!

 Barish Hui to Phoolon Ke Tan Chaak Ho Gaye;
Mausam Ke Haath Bheeg Ke Saffak Ho Gaye;

Baadal Ko Kya Khabar Hai Ki Barish Kee Chaah Mein;
Kaise Buland-o-Baala Shajar Khaak Ho Gaye;

Jugnu Ko Din Ke Waqt Parakhne Kee Zidd Karein;
Bachhe Hamare Ahad Ke Chalaak Ho Gaye;

Lehra Rahi Hai Barf Kee Chaadar Hata Ke Ghaas;
Suraj Kee Sheh Pe Tinke Bhi Bebaak Ho Gaye;

Basti Mein Jitne Aab-Gazida The Sab Ke Sab;
Dariya Ke Rukh Badalte Hi Tairaak Ho Gaye;

Suraj Dimag Log Bhi Ablaagh-e-Fikar Mein;
Zulf-e-Shab-e-Firaaq Ke Pechaak Ho Gaye;

Jab Bhi Gharib-e-Shehar Se Kuch Guftguu Hui;
Lahje Hawa-e-Shaam Ke Namnaak Ho Gaye!

 Aapka Intezar Humein Har Pal Rehta Hai;
Har Lamha Humein Aapka Ehsas Rehta Hai;
Aap Bin Dhadkane Ruk Si Jaati Hain;
Kyonki Aap Hamare Dil Mein Hamari Dhadkan Banke Rehte Ho!

 Mohabbat Aankhon Se Nikle Ashkon Ko Moti Bana Deti Hai;
Mohabbat Gehre Zakhmon Par Bhi Marham Laga Deti Hai;
Jab Jeene Kee Koi Bhi Wajah Hi Na Bachi Ho;
Tab Mohabbat Maut Ko Bhi Zindagi Bana Deti Hai!

 Ruthi Jo Zindagi To Mana Lenge Hum;
Mile Jo Gham Wo Seh Lenge Hum;
Bas Aap Rehna Hamesha Saath Hamare To;
Nikalte Hue Aansuon Mein Bhi Muskura Lenge Hum!

 Door Se Aaye The Saqi
Door Se Aaye The Saqi Sun Ke Maykhane Ko Hum;
Bas Taraste Hi Chale Afsos Paimane Ko Hum;

May Bhi Hai, Meena Bhi Hai, Sagar Bhi Hai Saqi Nahi;
Dil Mein Aata Hai Laga Den, Aag Maykhane Ko Hum;

Humko Phansna Tha Kafaz Mein, Kya Gila Sayyad Ka;
Bas Taraste Hi Rahe Hain, Aab Aur Daane Ko Hum;

Baag Mein Lagta Nahi Sehara Mein Ghabrata Hai Dil;
Ab Kahan Le Jaake Bithayein Aise Deewane Ko Hum;

Taak-e-Aabru Mein Sanam Ke Kya Khudayi Reh Gayi;
Ab To Pujenge Usi Kaafir Ke Butkhane Ko Hum;

Kya Hui Takseer Hum Se, Tu Bata De Ai 'Nazeer'
Taaki Shadi Marg Samajhe, Aise Mar Jaane Ko Hum!

 Uski Chahat Ne Rulaya Bahut Hai;
Uski Yaadon Ne Tadpaya Bahut Hai;
Hum Usse Karte Hain Mohabbat Beintehaa;
Iss Baat Ko Usne Aazmaya Bahut Hai!

 Koi Na Mita Sakega Dil Ke Iss Fasane Ko;
Teri Chahat Mein Bhool Jata Hun Zamane Ko;
Uthe Jo Meri Nazar Tere Chehre Pe Muskan Aaye;
Teri Deewangi Mein Bhool Jaate Hain Nazrein Jhapkane Ko!

 Sar Jhukaoge To...

Sar Jhukaoge To Patthar Devta Ho Jayega; 
Itanaa Mat Chaho Use Wo Be-Wafa Ho Jayega; 

Hum Bhi Dariya Hain Humein Apana Hunar Maloom Hai; 
Jis Taraf Bhii Chal Padenge Raasta Ho Jayega; 

Kitani Sachayi Se Mujh Se Zindagi Ne Keh Diya; 
Tu Nahi Mera To Koi Doosra Ho Jayega; 

Main Khuda Ka Naam Le Kar Pee Rahaa Hun Dosto;
Zehar Bhi Iss Mein Agar Hoga Dawa Ho Jayega; 

Rooth Janaa To Mohabbat Kee Alamat Hai Magar; 
Kya Khabar Thi Mujh Se Wo Itna Khafa Ho Jayega!

 Kehte Hain Woh Majbur Hain Hum;
Na Chahte Hue Bhi Door Hain Hum;
Chura Lee Hai Unhone Dhadkane Hamari;
Phir Bhi Kehte Hain Ki Bekasoor Hain Hum!

 Humne Manga Tha Saath Unka;
Woh Judai Ka Gham De Gaye;
Hum Unki Yaadon Ke Sahare Hi Jee Lete;
Par Woh Bhool Jaane Kee Kasam De Gaye!

 Unki Tasveer Ko Seene Se Laga Lete Hain;
Iss Tarah Judai Ka Gham Mita Lete Hain;
Kisi Tarha Zikar Ho Jaye Unko Hamare Dard Ka Agar;
Hans Kar Bheegi Palkon Mein Sab Dard Chupa Lete Hain!

 Jag Mein Aakar

Jag Mein Aakar Idhar Udhar Dekha;
Tu Hi Aaya Nazar Jidhar Dekha;

Jaan Se Ho Gaye Badan Khali;
Jis Taraf Tune Aankh Bhar Dekha;

Nala, Fariyad, Aah Aur Zaree;
Aap Se Ho Saka So Kar Dekha;

Un Labon Ne Kee Na Maseehayi;
Hum Ne Sau-Sau Tarah Se Mar Dekha;

Zor Aashiq Mizaaj Hai Koi;
'Dard' Ko Kissa-e-Mukhtsar Dekha!

 O Sheesha Ban Ke Jad Vi Sahmne Aa Behnde;
Mainu Meriya Kamiya De Parchawe Dikh Painde;
Tere Vaang Ta Sajjna Laare Laune Aaye Na;
Kaash! Ki Tere Kolo Kuj Ta Sikh Lainde!

 Mujhe In Patharo Ka Dar Na Hota;
Agar Sheeshe Ka Mera Ghar Na Hota;
Yakeenan Hum Bhi Khelte Ishq Ki Bazi;
Agar Dil Tootne Ka Dar Na Hota!

 Nibhaoge Tum Kasmein Yeh Wada Na Karo; 
Mohabbat Humse Itni Zyada Na Karo;
Dekhe Hain Maine Bhi Daur Tabahi Ke; 
Aur Humein Sataane Ka Irada Na Karo!

 Tanhaiyon Mein

Tanhaiyon Mein Khayaal Aata;
Khayaalon Mein Wo Naam Chala Aata;

Beqarar Dil Ko Qarar Nahi Aata;
Milne Ka Humein Kyon Unko Khayaal Nahi Aata;

Jaage Bhi Wo Soye Bhi Wo, Ye Silsila Tham Hi Nahi Pata;
Soche To Kya Soche, Koi Vichar Aur Samajh Nahi Aata;

Rab Se Aziz Wo Kaisa Saaya Hai, Itna Kya Mann Ko Bhaya;
Naam Lena Chahu Rab Ka Aur Uska Hi Naam Zubaan Pe Aa Jata!

 Kaayi Si Jam Gayi Hai Aankhon Par;
Sara Manzar Hara Sa Rehta Hai;
Sehma Sehma Daraa Sa Rehta Hai;
Jaane Kyon Dil Bhara Sa Rehta Hai!

 Aansu Na Hote To Aankhein Itni Khoobsurat Na Hoti;
Dard Na Hota To Khushiyon Kee Koi Keemat Na Hoti;
Poori Karta Jo Rabb Yun Hi Sab Muradein;
To Ibadat Kee Kabhi Zaroorat Na Hoti!

 Sab Fasane Hain Duniya Daari Ke;
Kis Ne Kis Ka Sukoon Loota Hai;
Sach To Yeh Hai Ki Iss Zamane Mein;
Main Bhi Jhootha Hun Tu Bhi Jhootha Hai!

 Koi Din Gar Zindgani

Koi Din Gar Zindgani Aur Hai;
Apne Jee Mein Hum Ne Thaani Aur Hai;

Aatish-e-Dozakh Mein Yeh Garmi Kahaan;
Soz-e-Ghumhaae Nihaani Aur Hai;

Baarha Dekhi Hain Unki Ranjishen;
Par Kuch Ab Ke Sargaraani Aur Hai;

De Ke Khat Munh Dekhta Hai Naama Bar;
Kuch To Paigham-e-Zabaani Aur Hai;

Qaata-e-Aamaar Hain Aksar Nazoom;
Woh Balaa-e-Aasmaani Aur Hai;

Ho Chukin Ghalib Balayein Sab Tamaam;
Ek Marg-e-Naagahaani Aur Hai!

 Mohabbat Se Rihaa Hona Zaroori Ho Geya Hai;
Mera Tujh Se Judaa Hona Zaroori Ho Geya Hai;
Wafaa Ke Tazurbey Karte Hue To Umar Guzri;
Zara Sa Bewafa Hona Zaroori Ho Geya Hai!

 Khyal Aata Hai Jab Bhi Uska Chehra;
To Labon Pe Aksar Fariyad Aati Hai;
Bhool Jata Hun Saare Gham Aur Sitam Uske;
Jab Bhi Uski Thodi Si Mohabbat Yaad Aati Hai!

 Taluq Rakh Liya Baaki
Taluq Rakh Liya Baaki Yakeen Tod Aaya Hun;
Kisi Ka Saath Dena Tha Kisi Ko Chod Aaya Hun;

Tumhare Saath Jeene Kee Kasam Khane Se Kuch Pehle;
Main Kuch Vaade, Kayi Kasmein, Kahin Pe Tod Aaya Hun;

Mohabbat Kaanch Ka Zinaaan Thi, Yun Sang-e-Garaan Kab Thi;
Jahan Sir Phod Sakta Tha, Wahan Sir Phod Aaya Hun;

Palat Kar Aa Geya Lekin Yun Lagta Hai Ki Apna Aap;
Jahan Tum Mujh Se Bichde The Wahin Rakh Chod Aaya Hun;

Use Jaane Kee Jaldi Thi So Main Aankhon Hi Aankhon Mein;
Jahan Tak Chod Sakta Tha, Wahan Tak Chod Aaya Hun!

 Zindagi Tujh Se Har Ek Saans Pe Samjhauta Karun;
Shaunk Jeene Ka Hai Mujh Ko Magar Itna To Nahi;
Rooh Ko Dard Mila Dard Ko Aankhein Na Mili;
Tujh Ko Mehsoos Kiya Hai Tujhe Dekha To Nahi!

 Zinda Rahein To Kya Hai, Jo Mar Jaayein Hum To Kya;
Duniya Se Khamoshi Se Guzar Jaayein Hum To Kya;
Hasti Hi Apni Kya Hai Zamaane Ke Saamne;
Ek Khwab Hain Jahaan Mein Bikhar Jaayein Hum To Kya!

 Hontho Pe Dil Ke Tarane Nahi Aate;
Sahil Pe Samundar Ke Fasane Nahi Aate;
Neend Mein Bhi Khul Uthti Hain Palkein;
Aankhon Ko Khwab Chupane Nahi Aate!

 Badla Tere Sitam Ka

Badla Tere Sitam Ka Koi Tujh Se Kya Kare;
Apna Hi Tu Farefta Hove, Khuda Kare;

Qaatil Hamari Naash Ko Tash-Hir Hai Zarur;
Aainda Ta Koi Na Kisi Se Wafa Kare;

Fikr-e-Maash, Ishq-e-Butaan, Yaad-e-Raftgaan;
Do Din Ki Zindagi Mein Ab Koi Kya Kya Kiya Kare;

Aalam Ke Beech Phir Na Rahe Rasm-e-Aashiqui;
Gar Neem Lab Koi Tere Shikwe Se Waa Kare;

Gar Ho Sharaab-o-Khilwat-o-Mahboob-e-Khub Roo;
Zaahid Kasam Hai Tujh Ko Jo Tu Ho To Kya Kare;

Khaakastr-o-Patang-o-Mashahd Meri Ki Khaak;
Sham-o-Shafaq Ajab Ho Jo Mil Kar Uda Kare;

Ai Waae Bar Aseer, Ke Par Tod Kar Jise;
Sayyaad Fasl-e-Gul Mein Chaman Se Riha Kare!

 Ye Dil Bhulata Nahi Hai Mohabbatein Uski;
Padi Hui Thi Mujhe Kitni Aadatein Uski;
Ye Mera Sara Safar Uski Khushbu Mein Kata;
Mujhe To Raah Dikhaati Thi Chahatein Uski!

 Tere Bina Tutkar Bikhar Jayenge;
Tum Mil Gaye To Gulshan Ki Tarah Khil Jayenge;
Tum Na Mile To Jeete Ji Mar Jayenge;
Tumhe Paa Liya To Mar Ke Bhi Jee Jayenge!

 Aao Kisi Shab Mujhe Toot Ke Bikharta Dekho;
Meri Ragon Mai Zehar Judaai Ka Utarta Dekho;
Kis Kis Adaa Se Tujhe Maanga Hai Khuda Se;
Aao Kabhi Mujhe Sajdon Mai Sisakta Dekho!

 Abke Khafa Hua Hai Itna

Abke Khafa Hua Hai Itna Khafa Bhi Ho;
Tu Bhi Ho Aur Tujh Mein Koi Doosra Bhi Ho;

Aankh Na Chheen Meri Nakabe Badlata Chal;
Yun Ho Ki Tu Karib Bhi Ho Aur Juda Bhi Ho;

Rishton Ke Registan Mein Har Sar Par Dhoop Hai;
Har Paanv Mein Safar Hai Magar Raasta Bhi Ho;

Duniya Ke Kehne Sunane Par Insaniyat Na Chhod;
Insan Hai Toh Saath Mein Koi Khata Bhi Ho!

 Hans Ke Farmaate Hain Woh, Dekh Ke Haalat Meri;
Kyon Tum Aasaan Samajhte The Mohabbat Meri;
Baad Marne Ke Bhi Chhori Na Rafaaqat Meri;
Meri Turbat Se Lagi Baithi Hai Hasrat Meri!

 Galtiyon Se Juda Tu Bhi Nahi, Main Bhi Nahi;
Dono Insaan Hain, Khuda Tu Bhi Nahi, Main Bhi Nahi;
Tu Mujhe Aur Main Tujhe Ilzaam Deta Hun Magar;
Apne Andar Jhankta Tu Bhi Nahi,  Main Bhi Nahi!

 Wohi Gardishein Wohi Paich-o-Kham Tere Baad Bhi;
Wohi Haunsle Mere Dum Ba Dum Tere Baad Bhi;
Tere Sath Thi Teri Jafa Mujhe Moatabar;
Tere Saare Gham Mujhe Mohtaram Tere Baad Bhi!

 Ek Khwaish Sirhane Rakh Do Na;
Aaj Mujh Pe Tum Inayat Kar Do Na;
Zara Chupke Se Khamoshi Se;
Tum Izhar-e-Mohabbat Kar Do Na!

 Ek Baar

Ek Baar Kar Ke Aitbaar Likh Do;
Kitna Hai Mujh Se Pyaar Likh Do;

Kat Ti Nahi Yeh Zindagi, Ab Tere Bin;
Kitna Karoon Aur Intezar Likh Do;

Taras Rahi Hun Badi Muddat Se;
Iss Bar Apni Mohabbat Ka Izhaar Likh Do;

Deewane Ho Jayein Jise Padh Ke Hum;
Kuch Aisa Tum Mere Naam Likh Do;

Zayada Nahi Likh Sakte To Mat Likho;
Mohabbat Bhare Lafz Do Chaar Likh Do;

Ek Baar Likho Mohabbat Hai Tum Se;
Phir Yehi Jumla Baar Baar Likh Do!

 Ai Maut, Main Tujhe Gale Lagana Chahta Hun;
Kitni Wafa Hai Tujh Mein Yeh Aazmana Chahta Hun;
Rulaya Hai Bahut Duniya Mein Logo Ne Mujhe;
Mile Jo Tera Saath To Main Logo Ko Rulana Chahta Hun!

 Har Phool Kee Ajab Kahani Hai;
Chup Rehna Bhi Pyaar Kee Nishani Hai;
Kahin Koi Zakhm Nahi Phir Bhi Kyon Dard Ka Ehsas Hai;
Lagta Hai Dil Ka Ek Tukda Aaj Bhi Uske Paas Hai!

 Dil Daba Jata Hai
Dil Daba Jata Hai Kitna Aaj Gam Ke Bhaar Se;
Kaisi Tanhayi Tapakti Hai Dar-o-Deewar Se;

Manzil-e-Iqrar Apni Aakhiri Manzil Hai Ab;
Hum Ke Aaye Hain Guzar Kar Jaada-e-Inkaar Se;

Tarjuman Tha Aks Apne Chehra-e-Ghum-Gashta Ka;
Ik Sada Aati Rahi Aaina-e-Asrar Se;

Mand Padte Ja Rahe The Khwab-Tasveeron Ke Rang;
Raat Utarti Ja Rahi Thi Dard Kee Deewar Se;

Main Bhi 'Akbar' Karb-Aagin Jaanta Hun Zeest Ko;
Munsalik Hai Fikr Meri Fikr-e-Shopnah Aahur Se!

 Mil Bhi Jaate Hain To Katra Ki Nikal Jaate Hain;
Hai Mausam Kee Tarah Dost Badal Jaate Hain;
Hum Abhi Tak Hain Giraftar-e-Mohabbat Yaroo;
Thokaren Kha Ke Suna Tha Ki Sambhal Jaate Hain!

 Khamosh Hothon Ka Agar Ishara Mil Jaaye;
In Dilkash Nagmon Ka Sahara Mil Jaaye;
Aapki Mast Nazarein Bekaraar Lagti Hain;
Dekh Kar Inhe Mujhe Bhi Shayad Koi Sahara Mil Jaaye!

 Zindagi Jeete Jeete Hum Marna Seekh Gaye;
Khade The Maut Kee Raah Pe Magar Jeena Seekh Gaye;
Ab To Is Zindagi Pe Bhi Taras Aane Laga Hai;
Jo Jeete Hue Marna Aur Marte Hue Jeena Seekh Gaye!

 Hasane Ke Baad Kyon Rulati Hai Duniya;
Jaane Ke Baad Kyon Bhulati Hai Duniya;
Zindagi Mein Kya Koi Kasar Baaki Thi;
Jo Mar Jaane Ke Baad Bhi Jalati Hai Duniya!

 Kasam Hai Aapke...

Kasam Hai Aapke Har Roz Rooth Jaane Kee;
Ki Ab Hawas Hai Ajal Ko Gale Lagane Kee;

Wahan Se Hai Meri Himmat Kee Ibtidaa Allah; 
Jo Intiha Hai Tere Sabr Aazmane Kee;

Phoonka Hua Hai Mere Aashiyan Ka Har Tinka;
Falak Ko Khoo Hai To Hai Bijliyan Girane Kee;

Hazaar Baar Hui Go Malalegul Se Dochaar;
Kalee Se Khoo Na Gayi Phir Bhi Muskurane Kee;

Mere Guroor Ke Maathe Pe Aa Chali Hai Shikan;
Badal Rahi Hai To Badle Hawa Zamane Kee;

Chiraag-e-Dair-o-Harm Kab Ke Bujh Gaye Ai 'Josh';
Hanoz Shammaa Hai Roshan Sharab Khaane Kee!

 Is Se Pehle Ki Bewafa Ho Jayein;
Kyon Na Ai Dost Hum Judaa Ho Jayein;
Tu Bhi Heere Se Ban Geya Pathar;
Hum Bhi Kal Jaane Kya Se Kya Ho Jayein!

 Apni Aakhon Ke Samander Mein Utar Jaane De;
Tera Mujrim Hun, Mujhe Doob Ke Mar Jaane De;
Zakham Kitne Teri Chaahat Se Mile Hain Mujhko;
Sochta Hun Kahun Tujhse, Phir Sochta Hun Ki Chod Jaane De!

 Aarzoo Hai Ki Unki Har Nazar Dekha Karein;
Woh Hi Apne Saamne Ho Hum Jidhar Dekha Karein;
Ek Taraf Ho Saari Duniya, Ek Taraf Surat Teri;
Hum Tujhe Duniya Se Hokar Bekhabar Dekha Karein!

 Najane Kab Tak Ye Aankhein Uska Intezar Karengi;
Uski Yaad Mein Kab Tak Khud Ko Bekarar Karengi;
Use To Ehsaas Tak Nahi Is Mohabbat Ka Yaaro;
Kab Tak Ye Dhadkane Uska Aitbaar Karengi!

 Jab Kisi Se

Jab Kisi Se Koi Gila Rakhna;
Samne Apne Aaina Rakhna;

Yun Ujaalon Se Waasta Rakhna;
Shama Ke Paas Hi Hawa Rakhna;

Ghar Kee Taameer Chaahe Jaisi Ho;
Is Mein Rone Ki Jagah Rakhna;

Masziden Hain Namaaziyon Ke Liye;
Apne Ghar Mein Kahin Khuda Rakhna;

Milna-Julna Jahan Zaroori Ho;
Milne-Julne Ka Haunsla Rakhna!

 Kabhi Ek Lamha Aisa Bhi Aata Hai;
Jis Mein Beeta Hua Kal Nazar Aata Hai;
Bas Yaadein Reh Jati Hain Yaad Karne Ke Liye;
Aur Waqt Sab Kuch Leke Guzar Jata Hai!

 Un Galiyon Se Jab Guzre To Manjar Ajeeb Tha;
Dard Tha Magar Wo Dil Ke Kareeb Tha;
Jise Hum Dhundte The Apni Haathon Kee Lakiron Mein;
Wo Kisi Dusre Kee Kismat, Kisi Aur Ka Naseeb Tha!

 Hamare Ashk Mein Apka Khwab Chupa Hai;
Hamari Khushi Mein Aapka Ehsas Chupa Hai;
Tum Hamari Dastan Mein Raho Ya Na Raho;
Lekin Is Dil Mein Hamesha Aapke Liye Pyaar Chupa Hai!

 Ashk Aankh Mein Phir
Ashk Aankh Mein Phir Atak Raha Hai;
Kankar Sa Koi Khatak Raha Hai;

Main Us Ke Khyaal Se Gurezaan;
Wo Meri Sada Jhatak Raha Hai;

Tahreer Usi Kee Hai Magara Dil;
Khat Padhte Hue Atak Raha Hai;

Hain Phone Pe Kis Ke Saath Baatein;
Aur Zehn Kahaan Bhatak Raha Hai;

Sadiyon Se Safar Mein Hai Samandar;
Saahil Pe Thakaan Tapak Raha Hai;

Ek Chaand Saleeb-E-Shaakh-E-Gul Par;
Baali Kee Tarah Latak Raha Hai!

 Aarzoo Ye Nahi Ki Gham Ka Toofan Tal Jaye;
FIkar To Yeh Hai Ki Kahin Aapka Dil Na Badal Jaye;
Kabhi Mujkhko Agar Bhulana Chaho To;
Dard Itna Dena Ki Mera Dum Nikal Jaye!

 Jisko Chaho Use Chahat Bata Bhi Dena;
Kitna Pyaar Hai Usse Yeh Jata Bhi Dena;
Yun Na Ho Ki Uska Dil Kahin Aur Lag Jaye;
Karke Izhaar Uske Dil Ko Chura Bhi Lena!

 Dil Soz Se Khali Hai Nigah Paak Nahi Hai;
Phir Is Mein Ajab Kya Ki Tu Be-Baak Nahi Hai;

Hai Zauq-e-Tajali Bhi Isi Khaak Mein Pinaha;
Gaafil Tu Nira Sahib-e-Idrak Nahi Hai;

Wo Aankh Ki Hai Surma-e-Afarang Se Roshan;
Pur-Kaar O Sukhan-Saaz Hai Nam-Naak Nahi Hai;

Kya Sufi-O-Mullaa Ko Khabar Mere Junoon Kee;
Un Ka Sar-e-Daaman Bhi Abhi Chaak Nahi Hai;

Kab Tak Rahe Mahakumi-e-Anjum Mein Meri Khaak;
Yaa Main Nahi Yaa Gardish-e-Aflaak Nahi Hai;

Bijli Hun Nazar Koh O Bayaabaan Pe Hai Meri;
Mere Liye Shayan Khaas-o-Khashak Nahi Hai;

Aalam Hai Faqat Momin-e-Jaanbaaz Kee Meeraas;
Momin Nahi Jo Sahib-e-Laulaak Nahi Hai!

 Saans Lene Se Bhi Teri Yaad Aati Hai;
Har Saans Mein Teri Khushboo Bas Jati Hai;
Kaise Kahoon Ki Saans Se Main Zinda Hun;
Jab Ki Saans Se Pehle Teri Yaad Aati Hai!

 Na Meri Koi Manzil Hai Na Mera Koi Kinara;
Tanhayi Meri Mehfil Aur Yaadein Mera Sahara;
Tum Se Bichhad Kar Kuch Yun Waqt Guzara;
Kabhi Zindagi Ko Tarse To Kabhi Maut Ko Pukara!

 Bechain Bahut Phirna

Bechain Bahut Phirna Ghabraye Hue Rehna;
Ik Aag Si Jazbon Ki Dehkaaye Hue Rehna;

Chalkaaye Hue Khushbuu Lab-e-Laleen Ki;
Ik Baag Sa Sath Apne Mehkaaye Hue Rehna;

Ik Shaam Si Kar Rakhna Kaajal Ke Karishme Se;
Ik Chaand Sa Aankhon Mein Chamkaaye Hue Rehna;

Aadat Hi Bana Li Hai Tum Ne To 'Munir' Apni;
Jis Sheher Mein Bhi Rehna Uktaaye Hue Rehna!

 Kyon Hijr Ke Shikwe Karta Hai Kyon Dard Ke Rone Rota Hai;
Ab Ishq Kiya To Sabr Bhi Kar Is Mein To Yahi Kuch Hota Hai;
Aaghaz-e-Musibat Hota Hai Apne Hi Dil Kee Shaamat Se;
Aankhon Mein Phool Khilaata Hai Talvon Mein Kaante Bota Hai!

 Koi Hai Jiska Is Dil Ko Intezar Hai;
Khyalon Mein Ab To Bas Usi Ka Khayal Hai;
Khushiyan Main Is Jahan Kee Saari Us Par Luta Du;
Kab Aayega Wo Jiska Is Dil Ko Intezar Hai!

 Tujhe Bhule Magar Teri Yaadon Ko Na Bhula Paaye;
Saare Sansar Ko Jeet Liya Bas Ek Tujhse Na Jeet Paaye;
Teri Yaadon Mein Aise Kho Gaye Ki Kisi Ko Yaad Na Kar Paaye;
Tumne Mujhe Is Kadar Tanha Kar Diya Ki, Ab Tak Kisi Aur Ke Na Ho Paaye!

 Chal Diye Uth Ke

Chal Diye Uth Ke Su-e-Shehar-e-Wafa Ku-e-Habib;
Puch Lena Tha Kisi Khak Basar Se Pehle;

Ishq Pehle Bhi Kiya Hijr Ka Gham Bhi Dekha;
Itne Tadpe Hain Na Ghabraye Na Tarse Pehle;

Jee Bahalta Hi Nahin Ab Koi Saath Koi Pal;
Raat Dhalti Hi Nahin Char Pahar Se Pehle;

Ham Kisi Dar Pe Na Thithak Na Kahin Dastak Di;
Saikadon Dar The Meri Jaan Tere Dar Se Pehle;

Chand Se Ankh Mili Jee Ka Ujala Jaga;
Hum Ko So Bar Hui Subah Sahar Se Pehle!

 Aankhon Mein Raha Dil Mein Utar Kar Nahin Dekha;
Kashti Ke Musafir Ne Samandar Nahin Dekha;
Be-Waqt Agar Jaunga Sab Chaunk Padenge;
Ek Umar Hui Din Mein Kabhi Ghar Nahin Dekha!

 Ek Pal Kee Judai Gawara Na Kar Sake;
Aisa Ishq Hum Dobara Na Kar Sake;
Zindagi Bhar Palat Ke Naa Dekha Kabhi;
Hum Phiir Bhi Shikwa Tumhara Naa Kar Sake!

 Jab Koi Khayal Dil Se Takrata Hai;
Dil Na Chah Kar Bhi Khamosh Reh Jata Hai;
Koi Sab Kuch Keh Kar Pyaar Jatata Hai;
To Koi Kuch Na Keh Kar Pyaar Nibhata Hai!

 Yahin Se Jaan Geya Main Ki Waqt Dhalne Lage;
Main Thak Haar Ke Baitha To Pair Jalne Lage;
Jo De Raha Tha Sahaare To Ik Hajoom Mein Tha;
Jo Gir Pada To Sabhi Raasta Badalne Lage!

 Aankhon Se Mere Is Liye Laali Nahin Jati;
Yaadon Se Koi Raat Jo Khaali Nahin Jati;

Ab Umar, Na Mausam, Na Woh Raaste Ki Woh Palte;
Iss Dil Ki Magar Khaam Khayali Nahin Jati;

Maange Tu Agar Jaan Bhi To Hans Ke Tujhe De Dein;
Teri To Koi Baat Bhi Taali Nahin Jati;

Aaye Koi Aa Ke Yeh Tere Dard Sambhaale;
Hum Se To Yeh Jageer Sambhaali Nahin Jati;

Maloom Humein Bhi Hain Bahut Se Tere Kisse;
Yeh Baat Teri Hum Se To Uchaali Nahin Jati;

Humraah Teri Phool Khilaati Jo Dil Mein;
Ab Shaam Wohi Dard Se Khaali Nahin Jati;

Hum Jaan Se Jaayen Ge Tabhi Baat Bane Gi;
Tum Se To Koi Raah Nikaali Nahin Jati!

 Chale Gaye Ho Door Kuch Pal Ke Liye;
Door Rehkar Bhi Kareeb Ho Har Pal Ke Liye;
Kaise Yaad Na Aaye Aapki Ek Pal Ke Liye;
Jab Dil Mein Rehte Ho Aap Har Pal Ke Liye!

 Chahne Se Koi Cheez Apni Nahi Hoti;
Har Muskuraht Khushi Nahi Hoti;
Armaan To Hote Hain Bahut Magar;
Kabhi Waqt To Kabhi Kismat Sahi Nahi Hoti!

 Bhool Se Kabhi Humein Bhi Yaad Kar Liya Karo;
Pyaar Na Sahi To Shikayat Hi Kar Liya Karo;
Itna Bhi Gair Na Samjho Ki Baat Hi Na Karo;
Mulaqat Na Sahi Par Milne Ka Vaada Hi Kar Liya Karo!

 Rahon Pe Nazar Rakhna Honthon Pe Dua Rakhna;
Aa Jaye Koi Shayad Darwaza Khula Rakhna;

Ehsaas Kee Shamaa Ko Is Tarah Jalaa Rakhna;
Apni Bhi Khabar Rakhna Us Ka Bhi Pata Rakhna;

Raaton Ko Bhatakne Kee Deta Hai Saza Mujhe;
Dushwaar Hai Pehlu Mein, Dil Tere Bina Rakhna;

Logon Ko Nigaahon Se Padh Lene Kee Aadat Hai;
Logon Kee Tehreeron Ko Logon Se Bacha Rakhna;

Bhuloon Main Agar Aye Dil, Tu Yaad Dila Dena;
Tanhai Ke Lamhon Ka Har Zakham Hara Rakhna;

Ik Boond Bhi Ashkon Kee Daaman Na Bhigo Paaye;
Gham Us Kee Amaanat Hai, Palkon Pe Sajaa Rakhna;

Iss Tarah 'Qateel' Us Se Bartaao Rahe Apna;
Woh Bhi Na Bura Maane, Dil Ka Bhi Kaha Rakhna!

 Wo Jo Aaye To Meri Zindagi Ko Zindagi Mili;
Dil Ke Viraan Shagufo Ko Phir Se Taazgi Mili;
Faila Hua Hai Noor Is Kadar Khaksaar Se Unke;
Gham-e-Zulmato Ko Unke Hi Dum Se Roshni Mili!

 Jane Kitni Umeedein Thi Tujhko Meri Yaadon Se;
Ki Jab Bhi Aayengi Haal Suna Jaya Karengi;
Hum Bhi Tere Liye Ek Khilona Bhar The;
Ki Yaadein Aayengi Aur Dil Behla Jaya Karengi!

 Saanson Kee Hararat Se Pighal Jaane Ka Mausam;
Aaya Hai Teri Aanch Mein Jal Jaane Ka Mausam;

Hum Ko Nahi Maaloom Tha Ishq Ka Aaghaaz;
Yaadon Mein Kahin Door Nikal Jaane Ka Mausam;

Lagta Hai Ki Chehre Pe Tere Thehar Geya Hai;
Yak Lakht Kayi Rang Badal Jaane Ka Mausam;

Ai Shehar Tasalli Tere Mashkoor Hain Hum;
Aaya Hi Nahi Dil Ke Sambhal Jaane Ka Mausam;

Ye Shehar-e-Tamanna Bhi Anokha Hai Ki Is Par;
Barsaat Mein Bhi Rehta Hai Thal Jaane Ka Mausam;

Chehre Pe Agarche Hain Mere Subah Ka Ujaala;
Aankhon Mein Magar Shaam Ke Dhal Jaane Ka Mausam!

 Kisi Ko Apna Banane Mein Der Lagti Hai;
Kya Hua Vaada Nibhane Mein Der Lagti Hai;
Pyaar To Pal Bhar Mein Ho Jata Hai;
Par Unhein Bhulane Mein Saari Umar Bhi Kam Pad Jati Hai!

 Intezaar To Bahut Tha Humein;
Lekin Aaye Na Woh Kabhi;
Hum To Bin Bulaaye Hi Aa Jaate;
Agar Hota Unhe Bhi Intezaar Kabhi!

 Zara Si Der Ko Aaye The

Zara Si Der Ko Aaye The Khwab Aankhon Mein;
Phir Us Ke Baad Musalsal Azaab Aankhon Mein;

Wo Jis Ke Naam Kee Nisbat Se Roshni Tha Wuzood;
Khatak Raha Hai Wohi Aaftaab Aankhon Mein;

Jinhe Mata-e-Dil-o-Jaan Samajh Rahe The Hum;
Wo Aaine Bhi Hue Behijaab Aankhon Mein;

Ajab Tarah Ka Hai Mausam Ki Khak Udti Hai;
Wo Din Bhi The Ki Khile The Gulab Aankhon Mein;

Mere Ghazal Teri Wahshaton Kee Khair, Ki Hai;
Bahut Dino Se Bahut Iztaraab Aankhon Mein;

Na Jaane Kaisi Qayamat Ka Peshkhema Hai;
Ye Uljhanein Teri Be-Intasaab Aankhon Mein!

 Gulshan Kee Baharon Pe Sar-e-Shaam Likha Hai;
Phir Uss Ne Kitabon Pe Mera Naam Likha Hai;
Yeh Dard Isi Tarah Meri Duniya Mein Rahe Ga;
Kuch Soch Ke Us Ne Mera Anjaam Likha Hai!

 Ye Kab Kaha Tha

Ye Kab Kaha Tha Nazaron Se Khauf Aata Hai;
Mujhe To Chaand Sitaaron Se Khauf Aata Hai;

Main Dushmanon Ke Kisi Vaar Se Nahi Darta;
Mujhe To Apne Hi Yaaron Se Khauf Aata Hai;

Khiza Ka Jabar To Seene Pe Rok Lete Hain;
Humein Udaas Baharon Se Khauf Aata Hai;

Mile Hain Dosto Besakhiyon Se Gham Itne;
Mere Badan Ko Saharon Se Khauf Aata Hai;

Main Iltifaat Kee Khandaq Se Door Rehta Hun;
Talluqaat Ke Gaaron Se Khauf Aata Hai!

 Hai Ishq Bhi Junoon Bhi, Masti Bhi Josh-e-Khoon Bhi;
Kahin Dil Mein Dard, Kahin Aah Sard, Kahin Rang Zard;
Hai Yun Bhi Aur Yun Bhi;
Lo Phir Basant Aayi, Phoolon Mein Rang Layi!

 Tum Ne Jo Chonk Kar Har Jagah Nigah Kee Hogi;
Mere Hi Dard-e-Mohabbat Ne Sada Di Hogi;
Ye Jo Moti Baraste Hain Teri Yaad Mein Aksar;
Badlon Ne Meri Aankhon Ko Dua Di Hogi

 Mehfil-e-Ishq Sajao To Koi Baat Bane;
Daulat-e-Ishq Lutao To Koi Baat Bane;
Jaam Haathon Se Nahi Hai Peena Mujhko;
Kabhi Aankhon Se Pilao To Koi Baat Bane!

 Kabhi Lafz Bhool Jaun Kabhi Baat Bhool Jaun;
Tujhe Is Kadar Main Chahun Ki Apni Zaat Bhool Jaun;
Uth Kar Jo Kabhi Tere Paas se Chal Dun To;
Jaate Hue Khud Ko Tere Paas Bhool Jaun!

 Zindagi Is Tarah

Zindagi Is Tarah Guzarate Hain;
Karz Hai Aur Use Utarate Hain;

Wasl Pe Shart Baandh Lete Hain;
Aur Yeh Shart Roz Haarte Hain;

Aaino Mein To Aks Hai Khud Ka;
Log Patthar Yeh Kisko Maarte Hain;

Kitne Dil Is Mein Gundh Lete Hain;
Zulf-e-Khugar Ko Jab Swarate Hain;

Ek Baazi Pe Bhool Mat Jana;
Pesh-e-Fatah Bhi Log Haarte Hain!

 Kitna Ajeeb Apni Zindagi Ka Safar Nikla;
Saare Jahan Ka Dard Apna Muqaddar Nikla;
Jiske Naam Apni Zindagi Ka Har Lamha Kar Diya;
Afsos Wo Hamari Chahat Se Bekhabar Nikla!

 Aankhon Ke Ishaare Samajh Nahi Paate;
Honthon Se Dil Kee Baat Keh Nahi Paate;
Bebasi Ka Aalam Ab Kuch Yun Ho Geya Ki;
Kuch Keh Bhi Nahi Paate Aur Chup Reh Bhi Nahi Paate!

 Mili Hawaon Mein Udne Ki Wo Saza Yaaro;
Ki Main Zameen Ke Rishton Se Kat Geya Yaaro;

We Be-Khayal Musafir Main Raasta Yaaro;
Kahan Tha Bas Mein Mere Use Rokna Yaaro;

Mere Kalam Pe Zamae Kee Gard Aisi Thi;
Ki Apne Baare Mein Kuch Bhi Na Likh Saka Yaaro;

Tamam Shehar Hi Uski Talaash Mein Ghum Tha;
Main Uske Ghar Ka Pata Kis Se Puchta Yaaro;

Jo Beshumar Dilon Ki Nazar Mein Rehta Hai;
Wo Apne Bachhon Ko Ek Ghar Na De Saka Yaaro;

Janab-e-Meer Ko Khudrajiyon Mein;
Miyan 'Wasim'Ke Kehne Ko Kya Bacha Yaaro!

 Jab Achanak Kabhi Unka Deedar Hota Hai;
Dil Mein Dhimi Si Dhandkan Ruk Jati Hai;
Itni Khoobsurat Hain Aankhein Unki;
Ki Nazar Milate Hi Nazar Jhuk Jati Hai!

 Aakhon Ke Saamne Har Dam Aapko Paya Hai;
Dil Mein Bas Aapko Hi Basaya Hai;
Aapke Bina Hum Jiyenge Bhi To Kaise;
Bhala Jaan Bina Bi Koi Jee Paya Hai!

 Gazab Kiya, Tere Vaade Pe Aitbaar Kiya;
Tamaam Raat Qayamat Ka Intezar Kiya;

Hansa Hansa Ke Shab-e-Vasl Ashkbaar Kiya;
Tasaliya Mujhe De De Ke Beqaraar Kiya;

Hum Aise Mahv-e-Nazara Na The Jo Hosh Aata;
Magar Tumhare Tagaful Ne Hoshiyar Kiya;

Fasana-e-Shab-e-Gham Unko Ek Kahani Thi;
Kuch Aitabaar Kiya Aur Kuch Na-Aitabaar Kiya;

Ye Kisne Jalwa Hamare Sar-e-Mazaar Kiya;
Ki Dil Se Shor Utha, Haaye! Beqaraar Kiya;

Tadap Phir Ai Dil-e-Nadan, Ki Gair Kehte Hain;
Aakhir Kuch Na Bani, Sabr Ikhtiyaar Kiya;

Kuch Aage Daawar-e-Mahshar Se Hai Umeed Mujhe;
Kuch Aap Ne Mere Kehne Ka Aitabaar Kiya!

 Khuli Jo Aankh To Wo Tha Na Wo Zamanaa Tha;
Dehakati Aag Thi Tanhayi Thi Fasanaa Tha;
Ye Kya Ki Chand Hi Kadmon Pe Thak Ke Baith Gaye;
Tumhein To Saath Mera Door Tak Nibhanaa Tha!

 Dard Se Hum Ab Khelna Seekh Gaye;
Bewafa Ke Saath Jeena Seekh Gaye;
Kya Batayein Kis Kadar Dil Toota Hai;
Maut Se Pehle Kafan Hum Odhna Seekh Gaye!

 Hamare Liye Unke Dil Mein Chahat Na Thi;
Kisi Khushi Mein Koi Dawaat Nahi Thi;
Maine Dil Unke Kadmon Mein Rakh Diya;
Magar Unhein Zameen Dekhne Kee Aadat Nahi Thi!

 Chaand Sitaron Se Kya Puchu Kab Din Mere Firte Hain;
Wo To Bechare Khud Hain Bikhari, Dere-Dere Firte Hain;

Jin Galiyon Mein Hum Ne Sukh Kee Sej Pe Raate Kaati Thi;
Un Galiyon Mein Vyakul Hokar Saanjh Savere Firte Hain;

Roop-Saroop Kee Jot Jagana Is Nagari Mein Zokhim Hai;
Chaaro Khunt Bagule Ban Kar Ghor Andhere Firte Hain;

Jin Ke Shaam-Badan Saaye Mein Mera Man Sustaya Tha;
Ab Tak Aankhon Ke Aage Wo Bal Ghanere Firte Hain;

Koi Humein Bhi Ye Samjha Do Un Par Dil Kyon Reejh Geya;
Teekhi Chitwan Baanki Shab Wale Bahutere Firte Hain;

Is Nagri Mein Baag Aur Ban Ki Yaaro Leela Nayari Hai;
Panchi Apne Sar Pe Uthakar Apne Basere Firte Hain;

Log To Daman Si Lete Hai Jaise Ho Jee Lete Hain;
'Abid' Hum Deewane Hain Jo Baal Bikhere Firte Hain!

 Kisi Ne Humein Aashiq Kaha;
Kisi Ne Humein Deewana Kaha;
In Aankho Mein Aansu Tab Aaye;
Jab Kuch Apno Ne Hi Humein Begana Kaha!

 Aansuon Ko Palko Tak Laya Mat Karo;
Dil Kee Baat Kisi Ko Bataya Mat Karo;
Log Muthi Mein Namak Liye Phirte Hain;
Zakham Ye Apne Kisi Ko Dikhaya Mat Karo!

 Barbaad Kar Gaye Wo Zindagi Pyaar Ke Naam Se;
Bewafai Hi Mili Sirf Wafa Ke Naam Se;
Zakham Hi Zakham Diye Us Ne Dawa Ke Naam Se;
Aasman Bhi Ro Pada Meri Mohabbat Ke Anjam Se!

 Phool Jaise Makhmali Talawo Mein

Phool Jaise Makhmali Talawo Mein Chhale Kar Diye;
Gore Suraj Ne Hazaro Jism Kaale Kar Diye;

Pyaas Kaise Bujhegi Humne Khud Hi Bhool Se;
Maikade Kamzarf Logo Ke Hawale Kar Diye;

Dekh Kar Tujh Ko Koi Manzar Na Dekha Umar Bhar;
Ek Ujaale Ne Meri Aankhon Mein Jaale Kar Diye;

Roshni Ke Devta Ko Pujta Tha Kal Talak;
Aaj Ghar Kee Khidkiyon Ke Kaanch Kaale Kar Diye;

Zindgi Ka Koi Bhi Tohfa Nahi Hai Mere Paas;
Khoon Ke Aansu To Ghazlo Ke Hawale Kar Diye!

 Uski Khamoshi Se Mujhe Darr Lagta Hai;
Door Na Ho Jaye Aisa Kyon Lagta Hai;
Duniya Se Use Cheen Lene Ka Haunsla To Hai Mujh Mein;
Lekin Wo Saath Na Dega Aisa Kyon Lagta Hai!

 Is Ishq Mein Wo Misaal Banayenge Hum;
Aankhein Band Karoge To Nazar Aayenge Hum;
Bhar Denge Itna Pyaar Aapke Dil Mein Ki;
Sab Se Pehle Yaad Aayenge Hum!

 Bikhre Ashkon Ke Moti Hum Piro Na Sake;
Teri Yaad Mein Saari Raat So Na Sake;
Mit Na Jaye In Ashkon Mein Teri Yaadein;
Yahi Soch Kar Hum Bas Ro Na Sake!

 Sirf Dhokha Tha Koi Tera

Sirf Dhokha Tha Koi Tera Ki Jo Tha Wo Na Tha;
Maine Socha Tha Tujhe Jaisa Ki Jo Tha Wo Na Tha;

Manzilo Kee Justju Mein Ghar Se Main Nikla Magar;
Tha Sabhi Kuch Theek Par Raasta Ki Jo Tha Wo Na Tha;

Saath Tha Din Bhar Wo Mere Ik Musafir Kee Tarah;
Shaam Jab Aayi To Ye Jana Ki Jo Tha Wo Na Tha;

Uske Bheetar Jhankte Hi Mujhko Andaza Hua;
Tha Wo Apni Jaat Mein Aisa Ki Jo Tha Wo Na Tha;

Tune Nahak Meri Baaton Ka Bura Maana Hai Dost;
Gaur Karna Bas Mera Kehna Ki Jo Tha Wo Na Tha!

 Yaad Mein Teri Aahein Bharta Hai Koi;
Har Saans Ke Saath Tujhe Yaad Karta Hai Koi;
Maut Sachhai Hai Ek Roz Aani Hai;
Lekin Teri Judaai Mein Har Roz Marta Hai Koi!

 Unki Mohabbat Ke Abhi Nishan Baki Hain;
Naam Lab Par Hai Aur Jaan Baki Hai;
Kya Hua Agar Dekh Kar Munh Pher Lete Hain;
Yeh Tasalli To Hai Ki Unhein Hamari Pehchan Baki Hai!

 Kashish Honi Chahiye Kisi Ko Yaad Karne Kee;
Lamhe To Apne Aap Hi Mil Jayenge;
Waqt Hona Chahiye Kisi Ko Milne Ka;
Bahane To Apne Aap Hi Mil Jaynege!

 Jab Agle Saal
Jab Agle Saal Yahi Waqt Aa Raha Hoga;
Ye Kaun Jaanta Hai Kaun Kis Jagah Hoga;

Tu Mere Saamne Baitha Hai Aur Main Sochta Hun;
Ki Aate Lamhon Mein Jeena Bhi Ik Saza Hoga;

Yahi Damakte Hue Pal Dhuan Dhuan Honge;
Yahi Chamakta Hua Din Bhujha Bhujha Hoga;

Isi Jagah Jahaan Aaj Mil Ke Baithe Hain;
Isi Jagah Par Khuda Jaane Kal Kya Hoga;

Bichhadne Wale Tujhe Dekh Kar Sochta Hun;
Tu Phir Milega To Kitna Badal Geyaa Hoga!

 Agar Talaash Karun Koi Mil Hi Jayega;
Magar Kaun Tumhari Tarah Mujh Ko Chahega;
Tumhein Zaroor Koi Chahaton Se Dekhega;
Magar Wo Aankhein Hamari Kahan Se Layega!

 Kuch Khabar Nahi Hum Ko Apna Ya Paraya Hai;
Dhoondne Ye Dil Jis Ko Is Gali Mein Aaya Hai;
Hum Duayein Dete Hain Tum Ko Phir Bhi Jaan-e-Jaan;
Magar Tum Ne Is Dil Ko Be-Panah Sataya Hai!

 Jabse Is Dil Par Tumhara Naam Aaya Hai;
Ek Suroor Sa Har Waqt Hum Pe Chhaya Hai;
Na Jaane Ye Pyaar Ka Nasha Hai Ya Kuch Aur;
Har Jagah Humein Bas Aapka Hi Chehra Nazar Aaya Hai!

 Aankhon Mein Rehne Walon Ko Yaad Nahi Karte;
Dil Mein Rehne Walon Kee Baat Nahi Karte;
Hamari To Rooh Mein Bas Chuke Hain Aap;
Tabhi To Milne Kee Hum Fariyad Nahi Karte!

 Apni Jannat Mujhe
Apni Jannat Mujhe Dikhla Na Saka Tu Waiz;
Kucha-e-Yaar Mein Chal Dekh Le Jannat Meri;

Sari Duniya Se Anokhi Hai Zamane Se Judaa;
Nemat-e-Khaas Hai Allah Re Kismat Meri;

Shikwa-e-Hijr Pe Sar Kaat Ke Farmaate Hain;
Phir Karoge Kabhi Is Munh Se Shikayat Meri;

Teri Kudrat Ka Nazara Hai Mera Izaz Gunah;
Teri Rehmat Ka Ishara Hai Nidamat Meri;

Lo Tabassum Bhi Sharik-e-Nigah-e-Naaz Hua;
Aaj Kuch Aur Badha Di Gayi Keemat Meri;

Faiz Yak Lamha-e-Deedar Salamat 'Fani';
Gham Kee Har Roz Hai Badhti Hui Daulat Meri!

 Kya Kahe Kuch Kaha Nahi Jaata;
Dard Milta Hai Par Saha Nahi Jaata;
Pyaar Ho Geya Hai Iss Kadar Aapse;
Ki Bin Dekhe Ab Raha Nahi Jaata!

 Main Aapke Pyaar Mein Kuch Aisa Kar Jaunga;
Ban Kar Khushbu Hawa Mein Bikhar Jaunga;
Bhulna Chaho To Saanson Ko Rok Lena;
Saans Loge To Main Dil Mein Utar Jaunga!

 Dil Mein Ab Yun Tere
Dil Mein Ab Yun Tere Bhule Hue Gham Aate Hain;
Jaise Bichhde Hue Kaabe Mein Sanam Aate Hain;

Ek Ek Kar Ke Hue Jaate Hain Taare Roshan;
Meri Manzil Kee Taraf Tere Kadam Aate Hain;

Raqs-e-Mai Tez Karo Saaz Kee Lai Tez Karo;
Su-e-Mai-Khana Safeeran-e-Haram Aate Hain;

Kuch Humin Ko Nahi Ehsan Uthane Ka Dimag;
Wo To Jab Aate Hain Mail-Ba-Karam Aate Hain;

Aur Kuch Der Na Guzre Shab-e-Furqat Se Kaho;
Dil Bhi Kam Dukhta Hai Wo Yaad Bhi Kam Aate Hain!

 Munh Kee Baat Sune Har Koi Dil Ke Dard Ko Jaane Kaun;
Aawazon Ke Bazaron Mein Khamoshi Pehchane Kaun;
Sadiyon Sadiyon Wahi Tamasha Raasta Raasta Lambi Khoj;
Lekin Jab Hum Mil Jaate Hain Kho Jaata Hai Jaane Kaun!

 Dard Kya Hota Hai Batayenge Ek Roz;
Pyaar Kee Ghazal Sunayege Kisi Roz;
Thi Unki Zidd Ki Main Jaun Unko Manane;
Mujhko Yeh Veham Tha Wo Bulayenge Kisi Roz!

 Koi Achhi Si Saza Do Mujhko;
Chalo Aisa Karo Rula Do Mujhe;
Tumhein Bhulun To Maut Aa Jaye;
Dil Kee Gehrai Se Yeh Dua Do Mujhko!

 Mehfil Mein Hansna Mera Mizaz Ban Geya;
Tanhai Mein Rona Ek Raaz Ban Geya;
Dil Ke Dard Ko Chehre Se Zahir Na Hone Diya;
Yahi Mere Jeene Ka Andaaz Ban Geya!

 Sarkati Jaye Hai Rukh Se

Sarkati Jaye Hai Rukh Se Naqab Aahista-Aahista;
Niklta Aa Raha Hai Aaftab Aahista-Aahista;

Jawan Hone lage Jab Wo To Hum Se Kar Liya Parda;
Hayaa Yaklakht Aayi Aur Shabab Aahista-Aahista;

Shab-e-Furkat Ka Jaaga Hu Farishto Ab To Sone Do;
Kabhi Fursat Mein Kar Lena Hisab Aahista-Aahista;

Sawal-e-Wasl Par Unko Adu Ka Khauf Hai Itna;
Dabe Hontho Se Dete Hain Jawab Aahista-Aahista;

Hamare Aur Tumhare Pyaar Mein Bas Fark Hai Itna;
Idhar To Jaldi-Jaldi Hai Udhar Aahista-Aahista;

Wo Bedardi Se Sar Kaate 'Ameer' Aur Main Kahun Unse;
Huzur Aahista-Aahista Janaab Aahista-Aahista!

 Badi Mushkil Se Bana Hun Toot Jaane Ke Baad;
Main Aaj Bhi Ro Deta Hun Muskurane Ke Baad;
Tujh Se Mohabbat Thi Mujhe Beinteha Lekin;
Aksar Yeh Mehsoos Hua Tere Jaane Ke Baad!

 Taras Gaye Aap Ke Deedar Ko;
Phir Bhi Dil Aap Hi Ko Yaad Karta Hai;
Humse Khush Naseeb To Hai Aapke Ghar Ka Aaina;
Jo Har Roz Aapke Husn Ka Deedar Karta Hai!

 Kabhi Aansu To Kabhi Khushi Dekhi;
Humne Aksar Mazboori Aur Bekasi Dekhi;
Unki Narazgi Ko Hum Kya Samjhe;
Humne To Khud Apni Taqdeer Kee Bebasi Dekhi!

 Khud Ko Kyon Jism Ka Zindani Kare;
Fikar Ko Takht-e-Sulemani Kare;

Der Tak Baith Ke Soche Khud Ko;
Aaj Fir Ghar Mein Biyabani Kare;

Apne Kamre Mein Sajaye Aafaq;
Jalsa-e-Be-Sar-o-Samani Kare;

Umar Bhar Sher Kahe Khoon Thuke;
Muntkhib Rasta-e-Nuksani Kare;

Khud Ke Liye Mol Le Izhar Ka Karz;
Dusron Ke Liye Aasani Kare;

Sher Ke Lab Pe Khamoshi Likhe;
Harf-e-Na-Gufta Ko La-Sani Kare;

Kimiyakari Hai Fan Apna 'Saaz';
Aag Ko Baithe Hue Paani Kare!

 Barabar Se Bach Kar Guzar Jaane Wale;
Yeh Naale Nahi Be-Asar Jaane Wale;
Nahi Jaante Kuch Ki Jaana Kahan Hai;
Chale Ja Rahe Hain Magar Jaane Wale!

 Mehek Hoti To Titliyan Zaroor Aati;
Koi Rota To Siskiyan Zaroor Aati;
Kehne Ko To Log Mujhe Bahut Yaad Karte Hain;
Magar Yaad Karte To Hichkiyan Zaroor Aati!

 Rasam-e-Wafa Nibhana To Gairat Kee Baat Hai;
Wo Mujhko Bhool Jayein Yeh Hairat Kee Baat Hai;
Sab Mujhko Chahte Hain Shohrat Kee Baat Hai;
Bas Wo Humein Nahi Chahte Yeh Hamari Kismat Kee Baat Hai!

 Ishq Aur Dosti Mere Do Jahaan Hain;
Ishq Meri Rooh To Dosti Mera Iman Hai;
Ishq Par To Fida Kar Dun Apni Sari Zindagi;
Magar Dosti Par To Mera Ishq Bhi Kurbaan Hai!

 Chup Ke Se Usne Jo Khud-Numai Kee;
Intiha Thi Ye Dilrubi Kee;

Mail-e-Ghamza Hai Wo Chashm-e-Siyaah;
Ab Nahi Khair Parsayi Kee;

Hum Se Kyonkar Wo Aastana Chhute;
Muddaton Jis Pe Jabha-Sai Kee;

Dil Ne Barson Ba-Justju-e-Kamaal;
Koocha-e-Ishq Mein Gadaai Kee;

Daam Se Un Ke Chutna To Kahan;
Ya Hawas Bhi Nahi Rihai Kee;

Ho Ke Nadim Wo Baithe Hain Khamosh;
Sulh Mein Shan Hai Ladai Kee;

Us Taghaful-Shiar Se 'Hasrat';
Hum Mein Taqat Nahi Judai Kee!

 Deedar Kee Aag Jab Dil Mein Bhadakne Lagti Hai;
Tujhe Dekhne Ko Meri Aankhein Tarsane Lagti Hain;
Baadlon Ke Barsane Ka Humein Intezar Nahi Rehta;
Teri Yaadon Mein Yeh Aankhein Khud Hi Barsane Lagti Hain!

 Yeh Hum Bhi Ganwara Karte Hain, Yeh Tum Bhi Ganwara Kar Lena;
Ro Ro Ke Guzari Hain Humne Raatein, Tum Hans Ke Guzara Kar Lena;
Betabi Hadh Se Badh Jaye Aur Neend Raaton Ko Aa Jaye;
To Doob Ke Meri Yaadon Mein Tum Duniya Se Kinara Kar Lena!

 Tumhari Yaadon Mein Beeti Har Baat Alag Hai;
Tumhare Saath Huii Har Mulaqaat Alag Hai;
Har Shakhs Meri Zindagi Chhu Kar Geya;
Magar Tumhari Mulaqat Kee Baat Alag Hai!

 Tere Daaman Kee Hawa Mangte Hain; 
Hum Bhi Jeene Kee Dua Mangte Hain; 

Mutaribo Koi Achuta Nagma; 
Saaz Aahang-o-Sadaa Mangte Hain;

Maah-o-Anjum Ke Jharokhe Aksar;
Kisi Ke Aariz Kee Dua Mangte Hain;

Phir Patangon Mein Khudayi Jagi; 
Sholay Hashr-Numa Mangte Hain; 

Banda-Parwar Koi Khairat Nahi; 
Hum Wafaon Ka Sila Mangte Hain; 

Maikada Ho Ke Kaleesa 'Saghir';
Sari Duniya Ka Bhala Mangte Hain!

 Pyaar Ne Yeh Kaisa Tohfa De Diya;
Mujhko Ghamo Ne Pathar Bana Diya;
Teri Yaadon Mein Hi Kat Gayi Umar Sari;
Aur Main Logon Se Kehta Raha Ki Tujhe Kab Ka Bhula Diya!

 Haathon Mein Ulfat Ka Naam Hota Hai;
Aankhon Mein Chalkta Jaam Hota Hai;
Khanjar Kee Jarurat Hai Yahan Kise;
Yahan Nazron Se Qatal-e-Aam Hota Hai!

 Na Wo Aa Sake Na Hum Ja Sake;
Na Dard Dil Ka Hum Kisi Ko Suna Sake;
Bas Khamosh Baithe Hain Unki Yaadon Mein;
Na Usne Yaad Kiya Na Hum Bhula Sake!

 Mil Kar Judaa Hue To Na Soya Karenge Hum;
Ek Dusre Kee Yaad Mein Roya Karenge Hum;

Aansu Jhalak Jhalak Ke Satayenge Raat Bhar;
Moti Palak Palak Mein Piroya Karenge Hum;

Jab Dooriyon Kee Aag Dilon Ko Jalayegi;
Jismon Ko Chandani Mein Bhigoya Karenge Hum;

Bin Kar Har Ek Bazm Ka Mauzu-e-Guftgu;
Sheron Mein Tere Gham Ka Samoya Karenge Hum;

Mazbooriyan Ke Zehar se Kar Lenge Khudkushi;
Ye Buzdili Ka Jurm Bhi Goya Karenge Hum;

Dil Jal Raha Hai Zard Shajar Dekh Dekh Kar;
Ab Chahton Ke Beej Na Boya Karenge Hum;

Gar De Geya Dagha Humein Toofan Bhi 'Qateel';
Sahil Pe Kashtiyon Ko Duboya Karenge Hum!

 Dil Kee Baatein Bata Deti Hain Aankhein;
Dhadkano Ko Jaga Deti Hain Aankhein;
Dil Pe Chalta Nahi Jadu Chehron Ka Kabhi;
Dil Ko Tu Deewana Bana Deti Hain Aankhein!

 Tanhai Le Jati Hai Jahan Tak Yaad Tumhari;
Wahin Se Shuru Hoti Hai Zindagi Hamari;
Nahi Socha Tha Hum Chahenge Tumhein Is Kadar;
Par Ab To Ban Gaye Ho Tum Kismat Hamari!

 Jahan Dariya Kahin

Jahan Dariya Kahin Apne Kinare Chhod Dete Hai;
Koi Uthta Hai Aur Toofan Ka Rukh Mod Deta Hai;

Mujhe Be-Dast-o-Paa Kar Ke Bhi Khauf Us Ka Nahi Jata;
Kahin Bhi Haadsa Guzre Wo Mujh Se Jod Deta Hai;

Bichhad Ke Tujh Se Kuch Jaana Agar To Is Kadar Jaana;
Wo Mitti Hun Jise Dariya Kinare Chhod Deta Hai;

Mohabbat Mein Zara Si Bewafai To Zaruri Hai;
Wahi Achha Bhi Lagta Hai Jo Vaade Tod Deta Hai!

 Jaane Lage Jab Wo Chhod Ke Daaman Mera;
Toote Hue Dil Ne Himaakat Kardi;
Socha Tha Ki Chhupa Lenge Gham Apna;
Magar Kambakht Ankhon Ne Bagawat Kar Di!

 Meri Nazaron Ko Aaj Bhi Talaash Hai Teri;
Bina Aapke Khushi Bhi Udaas Hai Meri;
Khuda Se Maanga Hai To Sirf Itna;
Ki Marne Se Pehle Aapse Mulaqat Ho Meri!

 Hum To Tere Dil Kee Mehfil Sajane Aaye The;
Teri Kasam Tujhe Apna Banane Aaye The;
Kis Baat Kee Saza Dee Tumne Humein Bewafa;
Hum To Tere Dard Ko Apna Banane Aaye The!

 Har Ek Chehre Ko Zakhmon Ka Aaina Na Kaho;
Ye Zindagi To Hai Rehmat Ise Saza Na Kaho;

Na Jaane Kaun Si Mazburiyon Ka Qaidi Ho;
Wo Saath Chhod Geya Hai To Bewafa Na Kaho;

Tamaam Shehar Ne Nezon Pe Kyon Uchala Mujhe;
Ye Itifaaq Tha Tum Is Ko Haadsa Na Kaho;

Ye Aur Baat Ki Dushman Hua Hai Aaj Magar;
Wo Mera Dost Tha Kal Tak Use Bura Na Kaho;

Hamare Aib Humein Ungaliyon Pe Ginwao;
Hamari Peeth Ke Peeche Humein Bura Na Kaho;

Main Waqiyat Kee Zanjeer Ka Nahi Qayal;
Mujhe Bhi Apne Gunahon Ka Silsila Na Kaho;

Ye Shehar Wo Hai Jahan Rakshas Bhi Hai 'Rahat';
Har Ek Tarashe Hue But Ko Devta Na Kaho!

 Dil Ke Behlane Kee Tadbeer To Hai;
Tu Nahi Hai Teri Tasveer To Hai;
Humsafar Chhod Gaye Mujh Ko To Kya;
Saath Mere Meri Taqdeer To Hai!

 Lamha Lamha Ye Waqt Guzar Jayega;
Jane Kab Tu Mujhse Bichad Jayega;
Jee Lene Do Mujhe Is Ek Pal Mein Zindagi;
Ek Tujhse Bichad Kar Yeh Dil Mar Jayega!

 Nafrat Kabhi Na Karna Humse;
Yeh Hum Seh Nahi Paayenge;
Ek Baar Keh Dena Humse Zaroorat Nahi Ab Tumhari;
Kasam Khuda Kee Tumhari Duniya Se Hans Kar Chale Jayenge!

 Kisi Na Kisi Pe Kisi Ko Aitbaar Ho Jata Hai;
Ajnabi Koi Shaks Bhi Yaar Ho Jata Hai;
Khoobiyon Se Nahi Hoti Mohabbat Sada;
Khamiyon Se Bhi Aksar Pyaar Ho Jata Hai!

 Apne Dil Kee Khoj Mein Kho Gaye Kya-Kya Log;
Aansu Tapti Ret Mein Bo Gaye Kya-Kya Log;

Kirnon Ke Toofan Se Bajre Bhar-Bhar Kar;
Roshniyan Us Ghaat Par Dho Gaye Kya-Kya Log!

Saanjh Samay Is Kunj Mein Zindagiyon Kee Aut;
Baj Gayi Kya-Kya Bansauri Ro Gaye Kya-Kya Log;

Maili Chaadar Taan Kar Is Chaukhat Ke Dwar;
Sadiyon Ke Kohraam Mein So Gaye Kya-Kya Log;

Gathdi Kaal Rain Kee Sonti Se Latkaye;
Apni Dhun Mein Dhyan Nagar Ko Gaye Kya-Kya Log;

Meethe Meethe Bol Mein Dohe Ka Hindol;
Sun Sun Us Ko Bhanware Ho Gaye Kya Kya Log!

 Meri Nazar Se Na Ho Door Ek Pal Ke Liye;
Tera Wajood Hai Lazim Meri Ghazal Ke Liye;
Kahan Se Dhoond Ke Laaun Charag Se Wo Badan;
Taras Gayi Hain Nigahein Kanwal Kanwal Ke Liye!

 Rang Dikhati Hai Yeh Zindagi Kitne;
Gair Bhi Ho Jate Hain Ek Pal Mein Apne;
Na Jaana Kabhi Tum Sapno Kee Duniya Mein;
Kyonki Toot Jata Hai Dil Jab Toote Hain Sapne!

 Khuda Ne Jab Tumhein Banaya Hoga;
Uske Dil Mein Bhi Sukun Aaya Hoga;
Socha Hoga Usne Ki Tumhein Apna Loon;

Phir Use Mera Khayal Aaya Hoga!

 Hairan Hai Jabeen Aaj

Hairan Hai Jabeen Aaj Kidhar Sajda Ravaa Hai;
Sar Par Hain Khudavand Sar-e-Arsh Khuda Hai;

Kab Tak Ise Seenchoge Tamanna-e-Samar Mein;
Ye Sabr Ka Pauda To Na Phula Na Phala Hai;

Milta Hai Khiraj Us Ko Teri Naan-e-Javin Se;
Har Baadshah-e-Waqt Tere Dar Ka Gadaa Hai;

Har Ek Uquubat Se Hai Takhi Mein Sava-Tar;
Wo Rang Jo Na-Karda Gunahon Kee Saza Hai;

Ehsaan Liye Kitne Maseeha-Nafson Ke;
Kya Kijiye Dil Ka Na Jala Hai Na Bujha Hai!

 Raah Dekhenge Na Duniya Se Guzarne Wale;
Hum To Jaate Hain Thehar Jaye Thehrne Wale;
Ek To Husn Bala Us Pe Banawat Aafat;
Ghar Bigdenge Hazaron Ke Sanwarne Wale!

 Wo Inkaar Karte Hain Iqraar Ke Liye;
Nafrat Bhi Karte Hain To Pyaar Ke Liye;
Ulti Chaal Chalte Hain Yeh Ishq Karne Wale Bhi;
Aankhein Band Karte Hain Deedar Ke Liye!

 Khuda Humko Kabhi Aisi Judai Na De;
Unki Yaadon Se Kabhi Humko Rihai Na De;
Dua Karna Dosto Mujhe Aisi Jannat Na Mile;
Jahan Se Mera Pyaar Mujhe Dikhai Na De!

 Mohabbat Karo Itni Ki Hadh Na Rahe;
Intezar Karo Itna Ki Waqt Na Rahe;
Bharosa Karo Itna Ki Shaq Na Rahe;
Nibaho Mohabbat Aise Ki Kisi Aur Ka Us Par Haq Na Rahe!

 Zindgi Is Tarah

Zindgi Is Tarah Guzarate Hain;
Karz Hai Aur Use Utarate Hain;

Wasl Pe Shart Baandh Lete Hain;
Aur Yeh Shart Roz Haarte Hain;

Aaino Mein To Aks Hai Khud Ka;
Log Patthar Yeh Kisko Maarte Hain;

Kitne Dil Is Mein Goondh Lete Hain;
Zulf-e-Khugar Ko Jab Sanwarte Hain;

Ek Baazi Pe Bhool Mat Jana;
Pesh-e-Fateh Bhi Log Haarte Hain!

 Teri Gali Mein Main Na Chalun Aur Saba Chale;
Yun Hi Khuda Jo Chahe To Bande Kee Kya Chale;
Kis Kee Ye Mauj-e-Husan Hui Jalvagar Kee Yun;
Dariya Mein Jo Habab The Aankhein Chuppa Chale!

 Roothi Jo Zindagi To Mana Lenge Hum;
Mile Jo Gham Wo Seh Lenge Hum;
Bas Aap Rehna Hamesha Saath Hamare To;
Nikalte Hue Aansuon Mein Bhi Muskura Lenge Hum!

 Is Duniya Mein Koi Kisi Ka Nahi Hota;
Lakh Nibhao Rishta Koi Apna Nahi Hota;
Galatfehmi Rehti Hai Kuch Dino Ke Liye;
Lekin Uske Baad Aankhon Mein Aansuon Ke Siwa Kuch Nahi Hota!

 Wo Zindagi Hi Kya Jisme Mohabbat Nahi;
Wo Mohabbat Hi Kya Jisme Yaaein Nahi;
Wo Yaaein Hi Kya Jisme Tum Nahi;
Aur Wo Tum Hi Kya Jiske Saath Hum Nahi!

 Musafir Ke Raaste Badalte Rahe;
Muqaddar Mein Chalna Tha Chalte Rahe;

Koi Phool Sa Haath Kandhe Pe Tha;
Mere Paanv Sholon Pe Chalte Rahe;

Mere Raaste Mein Ujala Raha;
Diye Us Kee Aankhon Ke Jalte Rahe;

Wo Kya Tha Jise Humne Thukara Diya;
Magar Umar Bhar Haath Malte Rahe;

Mohabbat Adavat Wafa Berukhi;
Kiraye Ke Ghar The Badalte Rahe;

Suna Hai Unhein Bhi Hawa Lag Gayi;
Hawaon Ke Jo Rukh Badalte Rahe;

Lipat Ke Charagon Se Wo So Gaye;
Jo Phoolon Pe Karvat Badalte Rahe!

 Kahan Tak Aankh Royegi Kahan Tak Kiska Gham Hoga;
Mere Jaisa Yahan Koi Na Koi Roz Kam Hoga;
Tujhe Paane Kee Koshish Mein Kuch Itna Ro Chuka Hun Main;
Ki Tu Mil Bhi Agar Jaye To Ab Milne Ka Gham Hoga!

 Kyon Koi Chaah Kar Mohabbat Nibha Nahi Paata;
Kyon Koi Chaah Kar Rishta Banaa Nahi Paata;
Kyon Leti Hai Zindagi Aisi Karvat;
Ki Koi Chaah Kar Bhi Pyaar Jataa Nahi Paata!

 Na Gul Na Yeh Gulistan Hamara Hai;
Jise Pujte Hain Na Woh Farishta Hamara Hai;
Chal Pade Hain Jis Manzil Kee Taraf;
Na Woh Manzil Na Woh Raasta Hamara Hai!

 Na Zindagi Mili Na Wafa Mili;
Na Jaane Kyon Har Khushi Humse Khafa Mili;
Jhoothi Muskaan Liye Apne Gham Chupaate Hain;
Sachhi Mohabbat Karne Kee Bhi Kya Khoob Saza Mili!

 Dukh Dard Mein Hamesha Nikale Tumhare Khat;
Aur Mil Gayi Khushi To Uchhale Tumhaare Khat;

Sab Choodiyan Tumhari Samandar Ko Saunp Dee;
Aur Kar Diye Hawa Ke Hawale Tumhare Khat;

Mere Lahoo Mein Goonj Raha Hai Har Ek Lafz;
Main Ne Ragon Ke Dasht Mein Paale Tumhare Khat;

Yun To Hain Be-Shumar Wafa Kee Nishaniyan;
Lekin Har Ek Shay Se Nirale Tumhare Khat;

Jaise Ho Umar Bhar Ka Asasa Gareeb Ka;
Kuch Is Tarah Se Main Ne Sambhale Tumhare Khat;

Ahal-e-Hunar Ko Mujhe Pe 'Wasi' Aitraz Hai;
Main Ne Jo Apne Sher Mein Dhaale Tumhare Khat;

Parwah Mujhe Nahi Hai Kisi Chaand Kee 'Wasi';
Zulmat Ke Dasht Mein Hain Ujaale Tumhare Khat!

 Baat Aisi Bhi Koi Nahi Ki Mohabbat Bahut Jyada Hai;
Lekin Hum Dono Se Us Kee Taqat Bahut Jyada Hai;
Aap Ke Peeche Peeche Phirne Se To Rahe Is Umar Mein Hum;
Raah Pe Aa Baithe Hain Ye Bhi Ghanimat Bahut Jyada Hai!

 Mohabbat Aankhon Se Nikle Ashko Ko Moti Bana Deti Hai;
Mohabbat Gehre Zakhmon Par Bhi Marham Laga Deti Hai;
Jab Jeene Kee Koi Bhi Wajah Hi Na Bachi Ho;
Tab Mohabbat Maut Ko Bhi Zindagi Bana Deti Hai!

 Parwah Kar Uski Jo Teri Parwah Kare;
Zindagi Mein Jo Kabhi Na Tanha Kare;
Jaan Ban Ke Utar Ja Uski Rooh Mein;
Jo Jaan Se Bhi Jyada Tujhse Wafa Kare!

 Door Se Aaye The Saqi Sun Ke Maykhane Ko Hum;
Bas Taraste Hi Chale Afsos Paimane Ko Hum;

May Bhi Hai, Meena Bhi Hai, Sagar Bhi Hai Saqi Nahi;
Dil Mein Aata Hai Laga Den, Aag Maykhane Ko Hum;

Humko Phansna Tha Kafaz Mein, Kya Gila Sayyad Ka;
Bas Taraste Hi Rahe Hain, Aab Aur Daane Ko Hum;

Baag Mein Lagta Nahi Sehara Mein Ghabrata Hai Dil;
Ab Kahan Le Jaake Bithayein Aise Deewane Ko Hum;

Taak-e-Aabru Mein Sanam Ke Kya Khudayi Reh Gayi;
Ab To Pujenge Usi Kaafir Ke Butkhane Ko Hum;

Kya Hui Takseer Hum Se, Tu Bata De Ai 'Nazeer'
Taaki Shadi Marg Samajhe, Aise Mar Jaane Ko Hum!

 Khata Ho Jaati Hai Jazbaat Ke Saath;
Unka Pyaar Yaad Aata Hai, Har Baat Ke Saath;
Khata Kuchh Bhi Nahi, Mahaz Pyaar Kiya Hai;
Unka Pyaar Yaad Aata Hai, Har Alfaaz Ke Saath!

 Har Pal Hanske Jiya Karte Hain;
Aap Se Dil Kee Har Baat Kiya Karte Hain;
Bahut Khaas Ho Aap Hamare Liye;
Isliye Har Waqt Aapko Yaad Kiya Karte Hain!

 Tera Intezar Mujhe Har Pal Rehta Hai;
Har Lamha Mujhe Tera Ehsas Rehta Hai;
Tujh Bin Dhadkane Ruk Si Jaati Hain;
Kyonki Tu Mere Dil Mein Meri Dhadkan Banke Rehta Hai!

 Dil Mein Mehak Rahe Hain
Dil Mein Mehak Rahe Hain Kisi Aarzoo Ke Phool;
Palkon Pe Khilnewale Hain Shayad Lahoo Ke Phool;

Ab Tak Hai Koi Baat Mujhe Yaad Harf-Harf;
Ab Tak Main Chun Raha Hoon Kisi Guftagoo Ke Phool;

Kaliyan Chatak Rahi Thi Ki Aawaz Thi Koi;
Ab Tak Sma-Ato Mein Hai Ik Khushguloo Ke Phool;

Mere Lahoo Ka Rang Hai Har Noke-Khar Par;
Sehra Mein Har Taraf Hai Meri Justaju Ke Phool;

Deewane Kal Jo Log The Phoolon Ke Ishq Mein;
Ab Unke Daaman Mein Bharein Hain Rafoo Ke Phool!

 Sard Raaton Ko Satati Hai Judai Teri;
Aag Bujhti Nahi Seene Mein Lagayi Teri;
Tum Jo Kehte The Bichar Kar Main Sukun Paa Lunga;
Phir Kyu Roti Hai Mere Dar Par Tanhayi Teri!

 Mom Kee Tarah Pighalti Ja Rahi Hai Zindagi;
Kyon Is Tarah Hath Se Fisal Rahi Hai Zindagi;
Hum Tumhein Pana Chahte Hain, Dil Mein Basana Chahte Hain;
Par Kyon Unchahe Sadmon Se Guzar Rahi Hai Zindagi!

 Koi Apna Hota To Bin Kahe Hi Samjh Leta;
Ab Kis Ko Bataun Ki Kya Hai Is Dil Mein;
Bhule Baithe Hain Wo Log Bhi Jinhe Apna Samjhta Hun;
Kabhi Mile To Dil Cheer Ke Dikha Dun Ki Kya Hai Is Dil Mein!

 Aisa Lagta Hai

Aisa Lagta Hai Zindagi Tum Ho;
Ajnabi Jaise Ajnabi Tum Ho;

Ab Koi Aarzoo Nahi Baki;
Just-Ju Meri Aakhiri Tum Ho;

Main Zameen Par Ghana Andhera Hun;
Aasmano Kee Chandni Tum Ho;

Doston Se Wafa Kee Ummeedein;
Kis Zamane Ke Aadmi Tum Ho!

 Dhadkan Dil Ki Ruk Jati Hai;
Sanse Aksar Tham Jati Hai;
Bahut Buri Halat Hoti Hai Yaaro;
Jab GF Se Shaadi Karne Ki Naubat Aati Hai!

 Kabhi Kabhi Yaad Mein Ubharte Hain Naqshe Mazi Mite Mite Se;
Wo Aazmaish Dil O Nazar Kee, Wo Kurbatein Si, Wo Fansle Se;
Kabhi Kabhi Aarzoo Ke Sehra Mein Aake Rukte Hain Kafile Se;
Wo Sari Baatein Lagav Kee Si, Wo Sare Unvaan Visal Ke Se!

 Jaam Pe Jaam Peene Ka Kya Fayda;
Sham Ko Pee, Subah Utar Jayegi;
Are Peeni Hai To Do Boond Dosti Ke Pee;
Sari Zindagi Fir Bas Nashe Mein Guzar Jayegi!

 Jab Nahi Aaye The Tum Tab Bhi To Tum Aaye The;
Aankh Mein Noor Kee Aur Dil Mein Lahoo Kee Surat;
Yaad Kee Tarah Dhadakte Hue Dil Kee Surat;

Tum Nahi Aaye Abhi Phir Bhi To Tum Aaye Ho;

Raat Ke Seene Mein Mehtab Ke Khanjar Kee Tarah;

Subah Ke Haath Mein Khurshid Ke Sagar Kee Tarah;

Tum Nahi Aaoge Jab Phir Bhi To Tum Aaoge;

Zulf Dar Zulf Bikhar Jayega Phir Raat Ka Rang;
Shab-e-Tanhayi Mein Bhi Lutf-e-Mulaqat Ka Rang;

Aao Aane Kee Karein Baat Ki Tum Aaye Ho;
Ab Tum Aaye Ho Main Kaun Si Shai Nazar Karu;
Ki Mere Paas Siva Mehr-o-Wafa Kuch Bhi Nahi;
Ek Dil Ek Tamanna Ke Siva Kuch Bhi Nahi!

 Main Talakhiye Hyaat Se Ghabra Ke Pee Geya;
Gham Kee Siyah Raat Se Ghabra Ke Pee Geya;
Itni Dakik She Koi Kaise Samajh Sake; 
Yazdan Ke Vakiyat Se Ghabra Ke Pee Geya!

 Kuch Sochun To Tera Khayal Aa Jata Hai;
Kuch Bolun To Tera Naam Aa Jata Hai;
Kab Tak Chupaon Dil Kee Baat;
Uski Har Ada Par Mujhe Pyaar Aa Jata Hai!

 Jab Kisi Ke Sapne Kisi Ke Armaan Ban Jaye;
Jab Kisi Kee Hansi Kisi Kee Muskaan Ban Jaye;
Pyaar Hi To Kehte Hain Use;
Jab Kisi Kee Saanse Kisi Kee Jaan Ban Jaye!

 Ishq Aisa Karo Ki Dhadkan Mein Bas Jaye;
Saans Bhi Lo To Khushbu Uski Hi Aaye;
Pyaar Ka Nasha Aankhon Pe Cha Jaye;
Baat Kuch Bhi Na Ho Par Naam Usi Ka Aaye!

 Khoon Bar Kar Munasib Nahi Dil Bahe;
Dil Nahi Maanta Kaun Dil Se Kahe;

Teri Duniya Mein Aaye Bahut Din Rahe;
Sukh Ye Paya Ki Hum Ne Bahut Dukh Sahe;

Bulbulein Gul Ke Aansu Nahi Chatati;
Un Ko Apni Hi Margoob Hain Chehchahe;

Aalam-e-Nazaa Mein Sun Raha Hun Mein Kya;
Ye Azizon Kee Cheekhe Hain Kya Kehkahe;

Is Naye Husn Kee Bhi Adaon Pe Hum;
Mar Mitenge Ba-Sharte Ke Zinda Rahe;

Tum 'Hafeez' Ab Ghisatne Kee Manzil Mein Ho;
Daur-e-Ayyaam Pahiya Hai Gham Hain Rahe!

 Kabhi Ro Ke Muskraye, Kabi Muskura Ke Roye;
Uski Yaad Jab Bhi Aayi, Use Bhula Ke Roye;
Ek Uska Hi Naam Tha, Jise Hazar Bar Likha;
Jitna Likh Ke Kush Hue, Usse Jyada Use Mita Ke Roye!

 Apne Dil Mein Tumhare Pyaar Kee Dastaan Likhi Hai;
Na Thodi Na Bahut Tamaam Likhi Hai;
Kabhi Hamare Liye Bhi Dua Kar Liya Karo;
Kyon Ki Humne Apni Har Ik Saans Tumhare Naam Likhi Hai!

 Naseeba De Lekh Koi Mod Nahi Sakda;
Hove Rabb Te Aitbar Koi Tod Nahi Sakda;
Sachha Pyaar Ta Milda Hai Naseeban De Naal;
Lakh Chah Ke Vi Kise Naal Rishta Koi Jod Nahi Sakda!

 Ishq Ko Taqleed Se Aazad Kar;
Dil Se Giraya Aankh Se Fariyaad Kar;

Baaz Aa Ai Banda-e-Husn Majaz;
Yun Na Apni Zindagi Barbaad Kar;

Ai Khayalon Ke Makeen Nazron Se Door;
Meri Veeran Khalvatein Abaad Kar;

Naza Mein Hichki Nahi Aayi Mujhe;
Bhulne Wale Khudaa-Raa Yaad Kar;

Husn Ko Duniyaa Kee Aankhon Se Na Dekh;
Apni Ik Tarz-e-Nazar Izaad Kar;

Ishrat-e-Duniya Hai Ik Khwab-e-Bahar;
Kabaa-e-Dil Dard Se Abaad Kar;

Ab Kahan 'Ehsaan' Duniya Mein Wafa;
Tauba Kar Nadan Khuda Ko Yaad Kar!

 Nafrat Bhi Hai Tumse, Mohabbat Bhi Hai Tumse;
Par Meri Mohabbat Nafrat Pe Haavi Ho Jati Hai;
Tumse Door Jaane Kee Meri Har Koshish;
Na Jaane Kyon Mujhe Tere Aur Kareeb Le Aati Hai!

 Zakham Aisa Diya Ki Koi Dawa Kaam Na Aayi;
Aag Aisi Lagai Ki Paani Se Bhi Bujh Na Paayi;
Aaj Bhi Rote Hain Hum Unki Yaad Mein;
Jo Chod Kar Chale Gaye Aur Unhe Hamari Yaad Tak Na Aayi!

 Tere Vaade Kee

Tere Vaade Kee Tere Pyaar Kee Mohtaj Nahi;
Ye Kahani Kisi Kirdaar Kee Mohtaj Nahi;

Khali Kashkol Pe Itarayi Hui Phirti Hai;
Ye Fakeeri Kisi Dastar Kee Mohtaj Nahi;

Log Honthon Pe Sajaye Hue Phirte Hain Mujhe;
Meri Shohrat Kisi Akhbaar Kee Mohtaj Nahi;

Ise Toofan Hi Kinare Se Laga Sakta Hai;
Meri Kashti Kisi Patvaar Kee Mohtaj Nahi;

Maine Mulkon Kee Tarah Logo Ke Dil Jeete Hain;
Ye Hukumat Kisi Talwar Kee Mohtaj Nahi!

 Koi Umeed Bar Nahi Aati;
Koi Soorat Nazar Nahi Aati;
Maut Ka Ek Din Muayyan Hai;
Neend Kyon Raat Bhar Nahi Aati!

Translation:
No longing can now be fulfilled,
No despite can now be envisaged.
The day of death has been appointed,
Why is the night crowded with sleeplessness?

 Jab Se Usne Shehar Choda Har Raasta Sunsan Hua;
Apna Kya Hai Sare Shehar Ka Ek Jaisa Nuksan Hua;
Ye Dil Ye Aaseb Kee Nagri Maskan Sochun Vehmon Ka;
Soch Raha Hun Is Nagri Mein Tu Kab Se Mehman Hua!

 Aaj Bhi Behta Hai Uska Diya Hua Zakham;
Main Chah Kar Bhi Use See Na Paaya;
Bas Kehne Ke Liye Hi Zinda Hun Main To Yaaro;
Par Marzi Ke Saath Kabhi Jee Na Paaya!

 Do Pal Da Hai Saath Pata Nahi Kado Vichad Jana;
Rishteya Da Kee Pata Kado Tut Jana;
Puch Liya Karo Kade Haal-Chaal Sade Dil Da;
Zindgi Da Kee Pata Asi Kado Muk Jana!

 Barsat Kee Bheegi Raaton Mein Phir Koi Suhani Yaad Aayi;
Kuch Apna Zamana Yaad Aaya Kuch Unki Jawani Yaad Aayi;
Hum Bhool Chuke The Jisne Humein Duniya Mein Akela Chora Tha;
Jab Gaur Kiya To Ek Surat Jaani Pehchani Si Yaad Aayi!

 Rakshas Tha Na

Rakshas Tha Na Khuda Tha Pehle;
Aadmi Kitna Bada Tha Pehle;

Aasmaan, Khet, Samandar Sab Laal;
Khoon Kagaz Pe Uga Tha Pehle;

Main Wo Maqtool Jo Qatil Na Bana;
Haath Mera Bhi Utha Tha Pehle;

Ab Kisi Se Bhi Shikayat Na Rahi;
Jane Kis-Kis Se Gila Tha Pehle;

Shehar To Baad Mein Veeran Hua;
Mera Ghar Khaak Hua Tha Pehle!

 Dil Tod Kar Hamara Tumko Rahat Bhi Na Milegi;
Hamare Jaisi Tumko Chaht Bhi Na Milegi;
Yun Itni Berukhi Na Humein Dikhlaiye;
Hum Agar Ruthe To Hamari Aahat Bhi Na Milegi!

 Tu Khush Rahe To Main Muskuraunga;
Kahin Bhi Ho Tu, Tujhe Na Bhula Paunga;
Mere Gham Ka Tu Dard Na Lena;
Ki Iss Dard Mein Bhi Main Sukun Paunga!

 Dil Daba Jata Hai Kitna Aaj Gam Ke Baar Se;
Kaisi Tanhayi Tapakti Hai Dar-o-Deewar Se;

Manzil-e-Iqrar Apni Aakhiri Manzil Hai Ab;
Hum Ke Aaye Hain Guzar Kar Jaada-e-Inkaar Se;

Tarjuman Tha Aks Apne Chehra-e-Ghum-Gashta Ka;
Ik Sada Aati Rahi Aaina-e-Asrar Se;

Maand Padte Ja Rahe The Khwab-Tasveeron Ke Rang;
Raat Utarti Ja Rahi Thi Dard Kee Deewar Se;

Main Bhi 'Akbar' Karb-Aagin Jaanta Hun Zeest Ko;
Munsalik Hai Fikr Meri Fikr-e-Shopnah Aahur Se!

 Har Bul-Hawas Ne Husn-Parasti Shiaar Kee;
Ab Aabroo-e-Sheva-e-Ahl-e-Nazar Gayi;
Nazare Ne Bhi Kaam Kiya Wan Naqaab Kee;
Masti Se Har Nigah Tere Rukh Par Bikhar Gayi!

Translation:
Each common lover has become a fake priest of beauty,
The distinction of the visionary lover has been erased.
Looking itself performed the function of secreting you,
Each blinded gaze refracted on the glories of your face.

 Zuban Khamosh Aankhon Mein Nami Hogi;
Yahi Bas Meri Ek Dastan-e-Zindagi Hogi;
Bharne Ko Toh Har Zakham Bhar Jayega;
Kaise Bharegi Wo Jagah Jahan Teri Kami Hogi!

 Kabhi Hum Tute To Kabhi Khwaab Tute;
Na Jane Kitne Tukdo Mein Armaan Tute;
Har Tukda Aaina Hai Zindgi Ka;
Har Aaine Ke Saath Laakhon Jazbaat Tute!

 Wo Bhi Din The Jab Hum Bhi Piya Karte The;
Yun Na Karo Humse Peene Pilane Kee Baat;
Jitni Tumhare Jaam Mein Hai Sharab;
Utni Hum Paimaney Mein Chod Diya Karte The!

 Raat Aadhi Se Jyada Gayi Thi, Sara Aalam Sota Tha;
Naam Tera Le Le Kar Koi Dard Ka Maara Rota Tha;

Charagaron, Ye Taskin Kaisi, Main Bhi Hun Is Duniya Mein;
Unko Aisa Dard Kab Utha, Jinko Bachana Hota Tha;

Kuch Ka Kuch Keh Jata Tha Main Furkat Kee Betabi Mein;
Sunane Wale Hans Padte The Hosh Mujhe Tab Aata Tha;

Tare Aksar Doob Chale The, Raat Ko Rone Walo Ko;
Aane Lagi Thi Neend Si Kuch, Duniya Mein Savera Hota Tha;

Tark-e-Mohabbat Karne Walo, Kaun Aisa Jag Jeet Liya;
Ishq Ke Pehle Ke Din Socho, Kaun Bada Sukh Hota Tha;

Uske Aansu Kisne Dekhe, Uski Aahein Kisne Suni;
Chaman Chaman Tha Husn Bhi Lekin Dariya Dariya Rota Tha;

Pichala Pahar Tha Hizr Kee Shab Ka, Jagta Rab, Sota Insan;
Taaron Kee Chanv Mein Koi 'Firaq' Sa Moti Pirota Tha!

 Tujhe Paane Ke Liye Kuchh Bhi Kar Sakta Hu;
Tere Pyaar Mein Jee Toh Kya, Mar Bhi Sakta Hu;
Phir Bhi Tu Nahi Mili To Koi Mujhe Gham Nahi;
Yeh Formula Kissi Dusri Pe Set Kar Sakta Hu!

 Woh Baada-e-Shabana Kee Sar-Mastiyan Kahan;
Uthiye Bas Ab Ke Lazzat-e-Khwab-e-Sehar Gayi;
Udti Phire Hai Khaak Meri Koo-e-Yaar Mein;
Baare Ab Aaye Hawa Hawas-e-Baal-o-Par Gayi!

Translation
Gone are those spirited nights of intoxication,
Arise! The blissful sleep of dawns that follow is also dispersed.
A cloud of my ashes rises in the street of  the other,
Finally oh wind, I no longer crave wings or plumage.

 Pyaar Koi Barish Nahi Jo Barse Aur Tham Jaaye;
Pyaar Suraj Bhi Nahi Jo Chamke Aur Doob Jaaye;
Pyaar To Naam Hai Saans Ka Jo Chale Toh Zindagi;
Aur Agar Ruke Toh Maut Ban Jaaye!

 Pyaar Ke Panno Se Bhari Kitab Ho Tum;
Rishton Ke Phulo Mein Ek Gulab Ho Tum;
Jo Log Kehte Hain Ki Pyaar Sacha Nahi Hota;
Un Logon Ke Har Sawal Ka Jawab Ho Tum!

 Takdeer Bata Tune Mujhko Kis Mod Pe Lake Chhod Diya;
Ek Mod Talak To Saath Diya Ek Mod Pe Lake Chhod Diya;
Khud Pyaar Kiya Khud Thukraya Phir Pyaar Bhara Dil Tod Diya;
Us Mod Talak To Saath Diya Is Mod Pe Lake Chhod Diya!

 Ye Dil Mein Vasvasa Kya Pal Raha Hai;
Tera Milna Bhi Mujh Ko Khal Raha Hai;

Jise Maine Kiya Tha Be-Khudi Mein;
Jabeen Par Ab Vo Sajda Jal Raha Hai;

Mujhe Mat Do Mubarak-Baad-e-Hasti;
Kisi Ka Hai Ye Saya Chal Raha Hai;

Sar-e-Sahara Sada Dil Ke Shajar Se;
Barasta Door Ik Badal Raha Hai;

Fasad-e-Lagzish-e-Takhleeq-e-Aadam;
Abhi Tak Haath Yazdaan Mal Raha Hai;

Dilon Kee Aag Kya Kafi Nahi Hai;
Jahanum Be-Zaroorat Jal Raha Hai!

 Kuch Pane Kee Chaahat Mein Bahut Kuch Choot Jata Hai;
Na Jane Sabr Ka Dhaga Kahan Par Toot Jata Hai;
Zara Batao Ki Tum Kise Humraah Kehte Ho;
Yahan To Apna Saya Bhi Saath Chod Jata Hai!

 Roz Dhalti Hui Shaam Se Dar Lagta Hai;
Ab Mujhe Ishq Ke Anjaam Se Dar Lagta Hai;
Jab Se Mili Hai Bewafai Mujhe Ishq Mein;
Tab Se Ishq Ke Naam Se Bhi Dar Lagta Hai!

 Surat Hamari Dekh Li Lekin Dil Hamara Dekh Na Sake;
Khushi Hamari Dekh Li Lekin Dukh Hamare Dekh Na Sake;
Pyaar Hum Se Kar Liya Aur Fikar Hamari Kar Na Sake;
Hansi Hamari Dekh Li Magar Aansu Hamare Dekh Na Sake!

 Teri Khushbu Ka

Teri Khushbu Ka Pata Karti Hai;
Mujh Pe Ehsaan Hawa Karti Hai;

Shab Kee Tanhai Mein Ab To Aksar;
Guftagu Tujh Se Raha Karti Hai;

Dil Ko Us Raah Pe Chalna Hi Nahi;
Jo Mujhe Tujh Se Juda Karti Hai;

Zindagi Meri Thi Lekin Ab To;
Tere Kehne Mein Raha Karti Hai;

Us Ne Dekha Hi Nahi Warna Ye Aankh;
Dil Ka Ehaval Kaha Karti Hai;

Sham Padte Hi Kisi Shakhs Kee Yaad;
Kucha-e-Jaan Mein Sada Karti Hai!

 Tujhe Chahte Hain Ai Sanam Bas Teri Aarzoo Hai;
Tu Zindagi Hai Meri, Tu Meri Har Khushi Hai;
Mujhe Duniya Se Garaj Kya Tu Meri Justju Hai;
Bas Tere Dam Se Hamdam Meri Duniya Mein Roshni Hai!

 Khamosh Hothhon Ka Agar Ishara Mil Jaaye;
In Dilkash Nagmon Ka Sahara Mil Jaaye;
Aapki Mast Nazarein Bekaraar Lagti Hain;
Dekh Kar Inhe Mujhe Bhi Shayad Koi Sahara Mil Jaaye!

 Ajnabi Thi Baatein Sabhi Uske Pyaar Kee;
Nahi Thi Khabar Ek Din Qayamat Zaroor Hogi;
Karte Rahe Fariyad Us Khuda Se Ai Sanam;
Milega Tu Mujhe, Khuda Kee Rehmat Zaroor Hogi!

 Ishq Mein Dil Ne Bahut Kaam Nikala Apna;
Sach Hai, Milta Hai Kahaan, Chahne Wala Apna;

Main Uthta Hun Sahare Ke Liye Uske;
Reh Na Geya Ho Raah Mein, Kahin Dard Apna;

Khakh Kis-Kis Kee Khuda Jaane Hui Ai Daman Wale;
Tune Chalte Hue Daman Na Sambhala Apna;

Dil Chune Wale Do Lafz Hi Likhe The Usne;
Kaam-Kaaz Sab Ulat Pher Ho Geya Apna;

Hain Bure Haal, Ki Sab Dekhne Waale Hain;
Koi Duniya Mein Nahi Haal Puchhne Wala Apna;

Ishq Mein Dil Ne Bahut Kaam Nikala Apna;
Sach Hai, Milta Hai Kahaan, Chahne Wala Apna!

 Gham Se Marta Hun Ki Itna Nahi Duniya Mein Koi;
Ki Kare Taziyat-e-Mehr-o-Wafa Mere Baad;
Aaye Hai Bekasi-e-Ishq Pe Rona Ghalib;
Kiske Ghar Jayega Sailab-e-Bala Mere Baad!

Translation:
I perish with grief, the world offers no companion,
To give rituals of succour for love and fidelity, in my aftermath.
I am weeping for that soul-sick, outcast love, Ghalib,
Whose habitat will be visited by its turmoil, in my aftermath.

 Husn Ghamze Kee Kashakash Se Chuta Mere Baad;
Bade Aaram Se Hain Ahl-e-Jafa Mere Baad;
Mansab-e-Sheftagi Ke Koi Qabil Na Raha;
Hui Mazooli-e-Andaz-o-Ada Mere Baad!

Translation:
The clash between beauty and seduction is assuaged in my aftermath,
The faithless are consequently at peace in my aftermath.
No one is left worthy of the eminence of deire's insanity,
The manner and the ways of love are banished in my aftermath.

 Zamane Se Nahi Main To Tanhai Se Darta Hun;
Pyaar Se Nahi Main To Ruswai Se Darta Hun;
Milne Kee Umang Bahut Hoti Hai Dil Mein;
Lekin Milne Ke Baad Teri Judai Se Darta Hun!

 Pehli Mohabbat Thi Hamari, Hum Jaan Na Sake;
Pyaar Kya Hota Hai Hum Pehchan Na Sake;
Humne Unhe Dil Mein Basaya Hai Iss Kadar Ki;
Chah Kar Bhi Hum Unhe Apne Dil Se Nikaal Na Sake!

 Akhan Di Benoori Changi Nahi Hundi;
Sajjna Kolon Doori Changi Nahi Hundi;
Kade Kade Taa Aa Ke Mil Jaya Karo;
Har Vele Majboori Changi Nahi Hundi!

 Aankh Ladate Hi Hua Ishq Ka Aazaar Mujhe;
Chashm Beemaar Teri Kar Gayi Beemaar Mujhe;

Dil Ko Zakhmi To Vah Karte Hain Magar Hairat Hai;
Nazar Aati Nahi Chalti Hui Talwar Mujhe;

Dekhiye Jaan Pe Girti Hai Ki Dil Par Bijli;
Door Se Taak Rahi Hai Nigah-e-Yaar Mujhe;

Garche Sau Baar In Aankhon Se Tujhe Dekha Hai;
Magar Ab Tak Hai Wahi Hasarat-e-Deedar Mujhe;

Mujhko Parwah Nahi Naseh Teri Ghamkhwari Kee,
Gham Salamat Rahe Kafi Hai Yeh Ghamkhwar Mujhe;

Sheesha-o-Jaam Pe Saqi Koi Ilzam Nahi;
Teri Aankhein Kiye Deti Hai Gunahagaar Mujhe;

Yaar Saqi Ho To Chalta Hai Abhi Daur 'Jaleel';
Kaun Kehta Hai Ki Peene Se Hai Inkaar Mujhe!

 Tujhe Paane Kee Iss Liye Zidd Nahi Karte;
Kyonki Tujhe Khone Ko Dil Nahi Karta;
Tu Milta Hai To Isliye Nazrein Nahi Uthate;
Ki Phir Nazrein Hatane Ko Dil Nahi Karta!

 Meri Har Saans Mein Mehakta Paya Hai Tujhe;
Har Sapno Mein Dil Se Mangwaya Hai Tujhe;
Phir Kyon Na Karein Tumhein Itni Mohabbat;
Jab Khuda Ne Mere Liye Hi Banaya Hai Tujhe!

 Door Kahin Meri Nazron Se Rehti Hai Wo;
Har Lamha Mere Khayalon Mein Rehti Hai Wo;
Kaisi Hai Wo, Kis Haal Mein Hai Wo;
Dil Ke Mere Har Sawaal Mein Rehti Hai Wo!

 Apna Deewana Bana Kar Le Jaye;
Kabhi Wo Aaye Aur Aa Kar Le Jaye;

Roz Buniyad Uthata Hun Nayi;
Roz Sailab Baha Kar Le Jaye;

Husn Walon Mein Koi Aisa Ho;
Jo Mujhe Mujh Se Chura Kar Le Jaye;

Rang-e-Rukhsaar Pe Itarao Nahi;
Jaane Kab Waqt Udaa Kar Le Jaye;

Kise Maloom Kahan Kaun Kise;
Apne Raaste Pe Laga Kar Le Jaye;

'Aftab' Ek To Aisa Ho Kahin;
Jo Humein Apna Bana Kar Le Jaye!

 Manzar Ik Bulandi Par Aur Hum Bana Sake;
Arsh Se Idhar Hota Kaash Ki Makaan Apna;
De Woh Jis Kadar Zillat Hum Hansi Mein Taalenge;
Baare Aashna Nikla Unka Paasban Apna!

Translation:
Could we build on some pre-eminence and see what lay below,
If only we had a different home, apart from the sky.
However much he insults me, I can take it with a smile,
By chance, the beloved's guard turns out to be a friend.

 Jo Ho Ek Baar Wo Har Baar Ho Aisa Nahi Hota;
Hamesha Ek Hi Se Pyaar Ho Aisa Nahi Hota;
Har Ek Kashti Ka Apna Tazurba Hota Hai Dariya Mein;
Safar Mein Roz Hi Manjhdhar Ho Aisa Nahi Hota!

 Kaash Kite Tu Mere Naal Hunda;
Teriyan Akhan Vich Koi Sawaal Hunda;
Teriyan Baahan Vich Reh Ke Main Eh Dasdi;
Tere Jaan Te Mera Ki Hai Haal Hunda!

 BhulaKar Mujhe Agar Tum Ab Bhi Ho Salamat;
To BhulaKar Tumhein Sambhalna Mujhe Bhi Aata Hai;
Meri Fitrat Mein Nahi Hai Ye Aadat Varna;
Teri Tarah Yun Badalna Mujhe Bhi Aata Hai!

 Kasam Hai Aapke
Kasam Hai Aapke Har Roz Rooth Jaane Kee;
Ki Ab Hawas Hai Ajal Ko Gale Lagane Kee;

Wahan Se Hai Meri Himmat Kee Ibtidaa Allah; 
Jo Intiha Hai Tere Sabr Aazmane Kee;

Phoonka Hua Hai Mere Aashiyan Ka Har Tinka; 
Falak Ko Khoo Hai To Hai Bijliyan Girane Kee;

Hazaar Baar Hui Go Malalegul Se Dochaar;
Kalee Se Khoo Na Gayi Phir Bhi Muskurane Kee;

Mere Guroor Ke Maathe Pe Aa Chali Hai Shikan;
Badal Rahi Hai To Badle Hawa Zamane Kee;

Chiraag-e-Dair-o-Harm Kab Ke Bujh Gaye Ai 'Josh';
Hanoz Shammaa Hai Roshan Sharab Khaane Kee!

 Zikar Us Parivash Ka Aur Bayaan Apna;
Ban Geya Raqeeb Aakhir Tha Jo Raazdaan Apna;
Mai Woh Kyon Bahut Peete Bazm-e-Ghair Mein Ya Rab;
Aaj Hi Hua Manzoor Unko Imtihaan Apna!

Translation:
Discourse over that ravishment, compounded with my eloquence,
Made a rival out of he, who used to be my confidant.
Oh Lord! Why would they imbibe so much in a stranger's gathering,
The limits of my endurance were put to the test today.

 Khoobsurat Hai Zindagi Ek Khawab Kee Tarha;
Jaane Kab Toot Jaye Kaanch Kee Tarha;
Mujhe Na Bhoolna Kisi Baat Kee Tarha;
Apne Dil Mein Hi Rakhna Khoobsurat Yaad Kee Tarha!

 Shikayat Kya Karun Dono Taraf Gham Ka Fasana Hai;
Mere Aage Mohabbat Hai Tere Aage Zamana Hai;
Pukara Hai Tujhe Manzil Ne Lekin Main Kahan Jaun;
Bichhad Kar Teri Duniya Se Kahan Mera Thikana Hai!

 Baat Bas Se Nikal Chali

Baat Bas Se Nikal Chali Hai;
Dil Kee Halat Sambhal Chali Hai;

Jab Junoon Had Se Badh Chala Hai;
Ab Tabiyat Behal Chali Hai;

Ashk Khoonaab Ho Chale Hain;
Gham Kee Rangat Badal Chali Hai;

Ya Yun Hi Bujh Rahi Hain Shamayein;
Yaa Shab-e-Hizr Tal Chali Hai;

Lakh Paigam Ho Gaye Hain;
Jab Saba Ek Pal Chali Hai;

Jao, Ab So Raho Sitaro;
Dard Kee Raat Dhal Chali Hai!

 Zulmat Kade Mein Mere Shab-e-Gham Ka Josh Hai;
Ek Shamma Hai Daleel-e-Sahar So Khamosh Hai;
Na Muzhda-e-Visaal Na Nazara-e-Jamal;
Muddat Hui Ki Aashti-e-Chashm-o-Ghosh Hai!

Translation:
The visible darkness of my home is intensified by the night of pain,
The only proof of dawn is but a candle which has already been spent.
There is no word of an encounter, nor the joy of beholding,
For an age now, there has been peace between sight and hearing.

 Tere Pyaar Mein Do Pal Kee Zindagi Bahut Hai;
Ek Pal Kee Hansi Aur Ek Pal Kee Khushi Bahut Hai;
Ye Duniya Mujhe Jaane Ya Na Jaane;
Teri Aankhein Mujhe Pehchane Yahi Bahut Hai!

 Zindagi Se Sabhi Ko Mohabbat Hai;
Magar Zindagi Kisi Kee Mohabbat Nahi Banti;
Tamanna Le Kar Jeete Hain Sab Log;
Magar Har Tamanna Taqdeer Nahi Banti!

 Hasrat Hai Sirf Humein Tumhe Paane Kee;
Aur Koi Khawahish Ab Nahi Is Deewane Kee;
Shikwa Humein Tumse Nahi Khuda Se Hai;
Kya Zarurat Thi Tumhe Itna Khoobsurat Banane Kee!

 Sarakti Jaye Hai

Sarakti Jaye Hai Rukh Se Naqab Ahista-Ahista;
Nikalta Aa Raha Hai Aftab Ahista-Ahista;

Jawan Hone Lage Jab Wo To Hum Se Kar Liya Parda;
Haya Yaklakhat Aayi Aur Shabab Ahista-Ahista;


Shab-e-Furkat Ka Jagaa Hun Farishton Ab To Sone Do;
Kabhi Fursat Mein Kar Lena Hisab Ahista-Ahista;

Sawal-e-Vasl Par Un Ko Adoo Ka Khauf Hai Itna;
Dabe Hontho Se Dete Hain Jawab Ahista- Ahista;

Hamare Aur Tumhare Pyaar Mein Bas Farq Hai Itna;
Idhar To Jaldi Jaldi Hai Udhar Ahista- Ahista;

Wo Bedardi Se Sar Kaate 'Ameer' Aur Main Kahun Un Se;
Huzoor Ahista-Ahista Janaab Ahista-Ahista!

 Apni Gali Mein Mujh Ko Na Kar Dafn Baad-e-Qatl;
Mere Pate Se Khalak Ko Kyon Tera Ghar Mile;
Saqi Gari Kee Sharm Karo Aaj Varna Hum;
Har Shab Piya Hi Karte Hain Mai Jis Kadar Mile!


Translation:
Do not bury me in your alley after my murder,
Why should my address bring the world to your home.
Practice the properieties of wine bearing today,
Other nights, I imbibe whatever can be found.

 Taqdeer Ne Jaise Chaha Vaise Dhal Gaye Hum;
Bahut Sambhal Ke Chale Fir Bhi Fisal Gaye Hum;
Kisi Ne Vishwas Toda Toh Kabhi Kisi Ne Dil;
Aur Logon Ko Lagta Hai Ki Badal Gaye Hum!

 Palkon Mein Aansu Aur Dil Mein Dard Soya Hai;
Hansne Walon Ko Kya Pata Rone Wala Kis Kadar Roya Hai;
Ye To Bas Wohi Jaan Sakta Hai Meri Is Tanhayi Ka Alam;
Jisne Zindagi Mein Kisi Ko Pane Se Pehle Khoya Hai!

 Kash Woh Samajhte Is Dil Kee Tadap Ko;
To Yun Humein Ruswa Na Kiya Hota;
Unki Ye Berukhi Bhi Manzoor Thi Humein;
Bas Ek Baar Humein Samjh Liya Hota!

 Kya Kahun Tum Se Main Ki Kya Hai Ishq;
Jaan Ka Rog Hai, Bala Hai Ishq;

Ishq Hi Ishq Hai Jahaan Dekho;
Saare Aalam Mein Bhar Raha Hai Ishq;

Ishq Maashuq Ishq Aashiq Hai;
Yaani Apna Hi Mubtala Hai Ishq;

Ishq Hai Tarz-o-Taur Ishq Ke Taeen;
Kahin Banda Kahin Khuda Hai Ishq;

Kaun Maksad Ko Ishq Bin Pahuncha;
Aarzoo Ishq Wa Mudda Hai Ishq;

Koi Khwaahan Nahi Mohabbat Ka;
Tu Kahe Jins-e-Narwa Hai Ishq;

Meer Ji Zarad Hote Jaate Hain;
Kya Kahin Tum Ne Bhi Kiya Hai Ishq!

 Jaan Tum Par Nisaar Karta Hun;
Main Nahi Jaanta Dua Kya Hai;
Maine Maana Ki Kuch Nahi Ghalib;
Muft Haath Aaye To Bura Kya Hai!

Translation:
I sacrifice my life for you,
I never knew what prayer is.
I concede that Ghalib is nothing,
If it comes free, what's the harm in it?

 Hum Ko Unse Hai Wafa Kee Umeed;
Jo Nahi Jaante Wafa Kya Hai;
Haan Bhala Kar Tera Bhala Hoga;
Aur Darvesh Kee Sada Kya Hai!

Translation:
We hope for fidelity from them,
Who do not know what fidelity may be.
Yes, do well, well will come to you,
What else is the Dervish's cry?

 Yun Palke Bicha Kar Tera Intezar Karte Hain;
Yeh Wo Gunah Hai Jo Hum Baar Baar Karte Hain;
Jalakar Hasrat Kee Raah Par Chirag Arzoo Ke;
Hum Subah Aur Sham Tere Milne Ka Intezar Karte Hain!

 Log Samajthe Hain Ki Humne Tumhein Bhula Rakha Hai;
Ye Nahi Jaante Ki Kahin Dil Mein Chupa Rakha Hai;
Dekh Na Le Koi Meri Aankhon Mein Tasvir Tumhari;
Humne Apni Palkon Ko Is Kadar Jhuka Rakha Hai!

 Har Khushi Se Khoobsurat Aapki Har Sham Kar Dun;
Apna Pyaar Aur Dosti Aapke Naam Kar Dun;
Mil Jaye Agar Dobara Ye Zindagi;
To Har Baar Ye Zindagi Aapke Naam Kar Dun!

 Yahi Nahi Koi Toofaan Meri Talaash Mein Hai;
Ki Mausam-e-Gham-e-Janaa Meri Talaash Mein Hai;

Visaal-Rut Hai Magar Dil Ko Aisa Lagta Hai;
Sitara-e-Shab-e-Hijra Meri Talaash Mein Hai;

Main Faisale Kee Ghadi Se Guzar Chuki Hun Magar;
Kisi Ka Deedaa-e-Hairan Meri Talaash Mein Hai;

Ye Be-Yaqeen Si Aasoodgi Batati Hai;
Ki Ek Karya-e-Veeran Meri Talaash Mein Hai;

Main Teergi Mein Mohabbat Kee Ik Kahani Hun;
Mui Charag Saar Unvan Meri Talaash Mein Hai;

Ye Kaisa Khwab Tha Dhadka Sa Lag Geya Dil Ko;
Ki Ek Shakhs Pareshan Meri Talaash Mein Hai!

 Haath Khali Hain Tere Shehar Se Jaate Jaate;
Jaan Hoti To Meri Jaan Lutate Jaate;
Ab To Har Haath Ka Pathar Humein Pehchanta Hai;
Umar Guzri Hai Tere Shehar Mein Aate Jaate!

 Uski Nazar Ko Fursat Hi Na Mili Hogi;
Varna Mera Marz Itna La-Ilaaj To Na Tha;
Humne To Wahan Bhi Mohabbat Hi Kee;
Jahan Mohabbat Ka Koi Riwaaz Na Tha!

 Kya Wajha Hai Mere Darne Kee;
Ab To Khwaish Hai Unki Yaadon Mein Marne Kee;
Na Jane Unhein Kyon Itna Yaad Karta Hai Dil;
Jinhe Fursat Hi Nahi Hai Humein Yaad Karne Kee!

 Sehmi Si Nigahon Mein Khawab Hum Jaga Denge,
Sooni Si Rahon Mein Phool Hum Bicha Denge;
Hamare Sang Muskura Kar To Dekhiye;
Har Gham Aapka Hum Bhula Denge!

 Na Socha Na Samjha

Na Socha Na Samjha Na Seekha Na Jana;
Mujhe Aa Geya Khud-Ba-Khud Dil Lagana;

Zara Dekh Kar Apna Jalwa Dikhana;
Simat Kar Yahin Aa Na Jaye Zamana;

Zubaan Par Lagi Hain Wafaon Kee Muhrein;
Khamoshi Meri Keh Rahi Hai Fasana;

Gulon Tak Lagayi To Aasaan Hai Lekin;
Hai Dushwaar Kaanton Se Daaman Bachana;

Karo Laakh Tum Matam-e-Naujawani;
Pa 'Meer' Ab Nahi Aayega Wo Zamana!

 Main Bhi Munh Mein Jubaan Rakhta Hun;
Kaash Pucho Ki Mudda Kya Hai;
Jab Ki Tujh Bin Nahi Koi Maujood;
Phir Yeh Hungama Ai Khuda Kya Hai!

Translation:
I also have a tongue in my mouth,
If only you could ask its articulation,
if there is nothing apart from you, Oh Lord!
Then what is this continual turmoil.

 Dil-e-Nadaan Tujhe Hua Kya Hai;
Aakhir Is Dard Kee Dawa Kya Hai;
Hum Hain Mushtaaq Aur Wo Bezaar;
Ya Ilaahi Yeh Maajra Kya Hai!

Translation:
Oh errant heart, what has transpired now,
Finally, what is the cure for this ache,
I desrie, the Other is indifferent,
Ah God, what is this performance.

 Wafa Kee Keemat Lagai Nahi Jati;
Humse Apni Chahat Chupayi Nahi Jati;
Is Kadar Mohabbat Hai Humein Unse;
Ki Unki Khata Bhi Humse Batai Nahi Jati!

 Dil Ke Dard Ko Chupana Kitna Mushkil Hai;
Toot Kar Fir Muskurana Kitna Mushkil Hai;
Kisi Ke Saath Door Tak Jao Fir Dekh;
Akele Laut Ke Aana Kitna Mushkil Hai!

 Dil Se Na Pucho Ki Ander Dard Kitna Hai;
Dhadkan Se Na Pucho Ki Baki Khel Kitna Hai;
Puchna Hi Hai To Jalti Hui Laash Se Pucho;
Zindagi Mein Gham Aur Kafan Mein Chain Kitna Hai!

 Dono Jahaan Teri

Dono Jahaan Teri Mohabbat Mein Haar Ke;
Wo Ja Raha Hai Koei Shab-e-Gham Guzaar Ke; 

Veeran Hai Maykada Khum-o-Sagar Udas Hain;
Tum Kya Gaye Ki Rooth Gaye Din Bahar Ke; 

Ik Fursat-e-Gunaah Mili, Wo Bhi Chaar Din;
Dekhe Hain Humne Haunsle Parwaradigaar Ke; 

Duniya Ne Teri Yaad Se Began Kar Diya;
Tum Se Bhi Dilfareb Hain Gham Rozgar Ke; 

Bhule Se Muskura To Diye The Wo Aaj 'Faiz';
Mat Puch Valvale Dil-e-Nakardkaar Ke!

 Ye Kya Jaane Mein Jana Hai, Jaate Ho Khafaa Hokar; 
Main Tab Janu Mere Dil Se Chale Jao Juda Hokar;
Qayamat Tak Udegi Dil Se Uthkar Khaak Aankhon Tak;
Isi Raaste Geya Hai Hasraton Ka Kafila Hokar!

 Kitna Ajeeb Apni Zindagi Ka Yeh Safar Nikla;
Saare Jahaan Ka Dard Apna Muqaddar Nikla;
Jiske Naam Apni Zindagi Ka Har Lamha Kar Diya;
Afsos Wahi Hamari Chahat Se Bekhabar Nikla!

 Sirf Nazdeekiyon Se Mohabbat Hua Nahi Karti;
Fansle Jo Dilon Mein Ho To Fir Chahat Hua Nahi Karti;
Agar Naraz Ho Khafa Ho To Shikayat Karo Humse;
Khamosh Rehne Se Dilon Kee Dooriyan Mita Nahi Karti!

 Qatil Teri Adaaon Ne Loota Hai;
Mujhe Teri Jafaaon Ne Loota Hai;
Shaunk Nahi Tha Mujhe Mar-Mitne Ka;
Mujhe To In Nashili Nigahon Ne Loota Hai!

 Zara Sa Katra Kahin Aaj Agar Ubharta Hai;
Samandaron Hi Ke Lehje Mein Baat Karta Hai;

Khuli Chhaton Ke Diye Kab Ke Bujh Gaye Hote;
Koi To Hai Jo Hawaon Ke Par Katarta Hai;

Sharafaton Kee Yahan Koi Ahmiyat Hi Nahi;
Kisi Ka Kuch Na Bigado To Kaun Darta Hai;

Zameen Kee Kaisi Viqalat Ho Phir Nahi Chalti;
Jab Aasmaan Se Koi Fainsla Utarta Hai;

Tum Aa Gaye Ho To Phir Kuch Chandni See Baatein Hon;
Zameen Pe Chand Kahan Roz Roz Utarta Hai!

 Kahun Kis Se Main Ki Kya Hai, Shab-e-Gham Buri Bala Hai;
Mujhe Kya Bura Tha Marna Agar Ek Baar Hota;
Hue Mar Ke Jo Hum Ruswa, Hue Kyon Na Gharq-e-Dariya;
Na Kabhi Janaza Uthta Na Kahin Mazaar Hota!

Translation:
To whom can I even explain, the dark night of sepration,
What had I against death if only it did not come again and again.
Being so humiliated in death, why did I not drown instead,
Then there would be no funeral, no one required to mourn at my tomb.

 Chaman Mein Shab Ko Jo Wo Shokh Be-Naqab Aaya;
Yakeen Ho Geya Shabnam Ko Aaftab Aaya;
Un Ankhdiyon Mein Agar Nasha-e-Sharab Aaya;
Salaam Jhuk Ke Karunga Jo Phir Hijab Aaya!

 Unhe Ye Shikayat Hai Humse Ki;
Hum Har Kisi Ko Dekh Kar Muskurate Hain;
Na-Samajh Hain Wo Ki Kya Jaane;
Humein To Har Chehre Mein Wahi Nazar Aate Hain!

 Phir Chupke Se Yaad Aa Geya Koi;
Meri Aankhon Ko Phir Rula Geya Koi;
Kaise Uska Shukriya Karun Ada;
Jo Mujh Na-Chiz Ko Shayar Bana Geya Koi!

 Kuch Main Bhi Thak Geya Use Dhoondte Hue;
Kuch Zindagi Ke Paas Bhi Mohlat Nahi Rahi;
Us Kee Har Ek Ada Se Jhalakne Laga Khaloos;
Jab Mujh Ko Aitbar Kee Aadat Nahi Rahi!

 Ye Aish-o-Tarab Ke Matwale

Ye Aish-o-Tarab Ke Matwale Bekar Kee Baatein Karte Hain;
Payal Ke Gamon Ka Ilm Nahi Jhankar Kee Baatein Karte Hain;

Nahak Hai Hawas Ke Bandon Ko Nazara-e-Fitrat Ka Dawa;
Aankhon Mein Nahi Hai Betabi Deedar Kee Baatein Karte Hain;

Kehte Hain Unhi Ko Dushman-e-Dil Naam Unhi Ka Naseh Bhi;
Wo Log Jo Reh Kar Sahil Par Majhdhar Kee Baatein Karte Hain;

Pahunche Hain Jo Apni Manzil Par Un Ko To Nahi Kuch Naz-e-Safar;
Chalne Ka Jinhe Maqdur Nahi Raftaar Kee Baatein Karte Hain!

 Yeh Kahan Kee Dosti Hai Ki Bane Hain Dost Naasih;
Koi Chaarasaaz Hota Koi Ghamgusar Hota;
Rang-e-Sang Se Tapkta Woh Lahu Ki Phir Na Thamta;
Jise Gham Samajh Rahe Ho Yeh Agar Sharaar Hota!

Translation:
What kind of friendship, my friends have turned to be preaching,
No one brings solutions, no one brings comapssion.
The veined stone has burst into an incessant flow of blood,
When touched by the ember which you think is merely my grief.

 Zindagi Kee Rah Mein Raaste Badal Jate Hain;
Waqt Kee Aandhi Mein Insan Badal Jate Hain;
Sochte Hain Tumhein Itna Yaad Na Karein Lekin;
Aankh Band Karte Hi Irade Badal Jate Hain!

 Parwah Kar Uski Jo Teri Parwah Kare;
Zindagi Mein Jo Kabhi Na Tujhe Tanha Kare;
Jaan Ban Ke Utar Jaa Uski Rooh Mein;
Jo Jaan Se Bhi Jyada Tujh Se Wafa Kare!

 Kis-Kis Ada Se Tune

Kis-Kis Ada Se Tune Jalwa Dikha Ke Mara;
Aazad Ho Chuke The, Banda Bana Ke Mara;

Awal Bana Ke Putla, Putle Mein Jaan Dali;
Phir Usko Khud Qaza Kee Soorat Mein Aake Mara;

Aankhon Mein Teri Zaalim Churiyaan Chupi Hui Hain; 
Dekha Jidhar Ko Tune Palkein Uthake Mara;

Gunchon Mein Aake Mehka, Bulbul Mein Jake Chehka; 
Isko Hansa Ke Mara, Usko Rula Ke Mara; 

Sosan Kee Tarah 'Akbar', Khamosh Hain Yahan Par; 
Naragis Mein Isne Chhip Kar Aankhein Lada Ke Mara!

 Barish Hui To Phulon Ke Tan Chaak Ho Gaye;
Mausam Ke Haath Bheeg Ke Saffak Ho Gaye;
Badal Ko Kya Khabar Hai Ki Barish Kee Chaah Mein;
Kaise Buland-o-Baala Shajar Khaak Ho Gaye!

 Har Zakhm Kisi Thokar Kee Meharbani Hai; 
Meri Zindagi Bas Ek Kahani Hai; 
Mita Dete Sanam Ke Dard Ko Seene Se;
Par Ye Dard Hi Uski Akhiri Nishani Hai!

 Kitab-e-Ishq Mein Jitne Alfaz Likhe Hain;
Dil Mein Mere Utne Ehsaas Rakhe Hain;
Tum Keh Kar Dekhte Sitamgar, Zalim;
Mere Labon Par Kitne Tere Naam Rakhe Hain!

 Gila Aap Se Nahi Koi;
Gila Hum Apni Majbooriyon Se Karte Hain;
Aap Aaj Hamare Kareeb Na Sahi;
Mohabbat To Hum Aapki Dooriyon Se Bhi Karte Hain!

 Soz Mein Bhi Wahi Ik Nagma Hai

Soz Mein Bhi Wahi Ik Nagma Hai Jo Saaz Mein Hai;
Fark Nazdeeq Kee Aur Door Kee Aawaz Mein Hai;

Ye Sabab Hai Ki Tadap Seena-e-Har-Saaz Mein Hai;
Meri Aawaz Bhi Shamil Teri Aawaz Mein Hai;

Aashiqon Ke Dil-e-Majrooh Se Koi Puche;
Wo Jo Ik Lutf Nigah-e-Galat-Andaaz Mein Hai;

Gosh-e-Mushtaq Kee Kya Baat Hai Allaah-Allaah;
Sun Raha Hun Main Jo Nagma Jo Abhi Saaz Mein Hai!

 Yeh Na Thi Hamari Kismat Ki Visaal-e-Yaar Hota;
Agar Aur Jeete Rehte Yahi Intezar Hota;
Tere Vaade Par Jiye Hum To Yeh Jaan Jhooth Jaana;
Ki Khushi Se Mar Na Jaate Agar Aitbar Hota!

Translation:
It was never in my fate to be united with my beloved,
If I had lived any longer, it would be nothing but more waiting.
Waiting with those promises that I know to be falsities,
Had I belief in them, I would have died of joy.

 Jaan Kar Bhi Woh Humein Jaan Na Paye;
Aaj Tak Woh Humein Pehchan Na Paye;
Khud Hi Kar Li Bewafai Hum Ne Unse;
Taki Un Par Bewafai Ka Koi Ilzam Na Aaye!

 Koi Vaada Nahi Phir Bhi Tera Intezar Hai;
Judai Ke Baad Bhi Humein Tujhse Pyaar Hai;
Tere Chehre Kee Udasi Kar Rahi Hai Bayaan Dastaan;
Ki Mujhse Milne Ke Liye Tu Bhi Bekarar Hai!

 Dilon Se Khelne Ka Hunar Humein Nahi Aata;
Isi Liye Ishq Kee Baazi Hum Haar Gaye;
Meri Zindagi Se Shayad Unhein Bahut Pyaar Tha;
Isi Liye Mujhe Zinda Hi Wo Maar Gaye!

 Aap Duniya Bhar Se

Aap Duniya Bhar Se Ulfat Kijiye;
Mujh Ko Mera Dil Inayat Kijiye;

Zabt Se Kya Khoon-e-Hasrat Kijiye;
Ek Nala Kar Ke Fursat Kijiye;

Joaf Kehta Hai Ki Manzil Door Hai;
Shauq Kehta Hai Kee Himmat Kijiye;

Gark Hi Hona Thaa Manzoor-e-Khuda;
Na-Khudaa Kee Kya Shikayat Kijiye;

Hazraat-e-'Natiq' Jahan Tak Ho Sake;
Apne Dil Mein Zabt-e-Ulfat Kijiye!

 Tu Dost Kisi Ka Bhi Sitamgar Na Hua Tha;
Auron Pe Hai Woh Zulm Ki Mujh Par Na Hua Tha;
Chhoda Mah-e-Nakhshab Kee Tarah Dast-e-Qaza Ne;
Khurshid Hanuz Us Ke Barabar Na Hua Tha!

Translation:
You are no one's friend, albeit, the giver of pain,
The grief you inflicton others, you will not even bestow upon me.
Just as the hand of death can smash the image of Nakhshab's moon,
The sun's radiance will also vanish before it can match that of the beloved.

 Jee Dhoondta Hai Phir Fursat Ke Raat Din;
Baithe Rahen Tassavur-e-Jana Kiye Hue;
Ghalib Humein Na Chhed Ke Phir Josh-e-Ashq Se;
Baithe Hain Hum Tahayya-e-Toofan Kiye Hue!

Translation:
The soul seeks again that vacant time,
Night and day our memory re-imagining what the beloved is.
Ghalib do not torment us, for again with the storm of our tears,
We are sitting here having decided to unleash a hurricane at will.

 Tu Khush Rahe To Main Muskuraunga;
Kahin Bhi Ho Tu, Tujhe Na Bhula Paunga;
Mere Gham Ka Tu Dard Na Lena;
Kyonki Iss Dard Mein Bhi Main Sukun Paunga!

 Kyun Khud Ko Beqarar Kiye Ja Rahe Hain;
Kis Bewafa Ko Pyaar Kiye Ja Rahe Hain;
Aaya Jo Na Sanam Kabhi, Aur Na Ayega Phir Kabhi;
Kyun Uska Intezar Hum Muddat Se Kiye Ja Rahe Hain!

 Deewana Mat Kaho Mujh Ko Yun Achha Nahi Lagta;
Bada Afsos Hota Hai Jab Koi Apna Nahi Lagta;
Lagta Hai Ki Hogi Uski Bhi Kuch Majboori;
Uska Yun Chhod Kar Jana Achha Nahi Lagta!

 Dar Ke Kisi Se

Dar Ke Kisi Se Chup Jataa Hai Jaise Saanp Khazane Mein;
Zar Ke Zor Se Zinda Hain Sab Khaak Ke Is Veerane Mein;

Jaise Rasam Ada Karte Ho Sheharon Kee Aabadi Mein;
Subah Ko Ghar Se Door Nikalkar Shaam Ko Wapis Aane Mein;

Neele Rang Mein Doobi Aankhein Khuli Padi Thi Sabze Par;
Aks Pada Tha Aasman Ka Shayad Iss Paimane Mein;

Dil Kuch Aur Bhi Sard Hua Hai Shaam-e-Shehar Kee Raunak Mein;
Kitni Ziya Besood Gayi Sheeshe Ke Lafz Jalane Mein;

Main To 'Munir' Aaine Mein Khud Ko Tak Kar Hairan Hua;
Ye Chehra Kuch Aur Tarah Tha Pehle Ek Zamane Mein!

 Subah Phuti To Wo Pehlu Se Utha Aakhir-e-Shab;
Wo Jo Ik Umr Se Aaya Na Geya Aakhir-e-Shab;
Yaad Ka Phir Koi Darwaza Khula Aakhir-e-Shab!

 Tere Naam Ki Thi Joh Roshni Use Khud Hi Tum Ne Bujha Diya;
Na Jala Saki Jise Dhoop Bhi, Use Chandni Ne Jala Diya;
Hun Gardishon Mein Ghira Hua, Mujhe Ab Apni Khabar Nahi;
Wo Jo Shaqs Tha Mera Rehnuma, Use Raaston Mein Hi Ganwa Diya!

 Jalne Do Zamane Ko Chalo Ek Saath Chalte Hain;
Nayi Duniya Basane Ko Chalo Ek Saath Chalte Hain;
Humein Jeevan Ka Har Lamha, Tumhare Naam Karna Hai;
Yahi Vaada Nibhane Ko Chalo Ek Saath Chalte Hain!

 Sukhan Mein Rang Tumhare

Sukhan Mein Rang Tumhare Khayal Hi Ke To Hain;
Ye Sab Karishme Hawa-e-Visaal Hi Ke To Hain;

Kaha Tha Tumne Ki Aata Hai Kaun Ishq Kee Taab
So Hum Jawab Tumhare Sawal Hi Ke To Hain;

Zara Si Baat Hai Dil Mein, Agar Bayan Ho Jaye;
Tamaam Masle Izahar-e-Haal Hi Ke To Hain;

Yahan Bhi Iske Siwa Aur Kya Naseeb Humein;
Khutan Mein Reh Ke Bhi Chashme-Gizaal Hi Ke To Hain;

Hawaa Kee Zad Pe Hamara Safar Hai Kitni Der;
Charaag Hum Kisi Sham -e-Zawal Hi Ke To Hain!

 Muddat Hui Hai Yaar Ko Mehman Kiye Hue;
Josh-e-Qadah Se Bazm Chiraghan Kiye Hue;
Karta Hun Jama Phir Jigar-e-Lakht Lakht Ko;
Arsa Hua Hai Dawat-e-Mizhgaan Kiye Hue!

Translation:
It has been an age since my lover was hosted,
When heated wine lit candles through night,
Once again, I gather the pieces of my dismembered body,
What time has passed since I encountered those killing  eyes.

 Mera Har Pal Aaj Khoobsurat Hai;
Dil Mein Jo Sirf Teri Hi Soorat Hai;
Kuch Bhi Kahe Ye Duniya Ab Gham Nahi;
Duniya Se Jyada Mujhe Teri Jarurat Hai!

 Sohne Hoan Chahe Lakh Sohne;
Meri Sarkar Jinha Koi Fabda Nahi;
Akhaan Rehan Dekhan Nu Tarsadian;
Chandra Dil Vi Dekh Rajjda Nahi!

 Paas Aakar Sabhi Door Chale Jate Hain;
Akele The Hum, Akele Hi Reh Jate Hain;
Ab Apne Dil Ka Dard Hum Kise Dikhayein;
Kyonki Marham Lagane Wale Hi Ab Zakhm De Jate Hain!

 Zoph Aata Hai
Zoph Aata Hai Dil Ko Thaam To Lo;
Boliyo Mat Magar Salaam To Lo;
Kaun Kehta Hai Bolo, Mat Bolo;
Haath Se Mere Ek Jaam To Lo;
Inhin Baaton Pe Lautata Hun Main;
Gaali Phir De Ke Mera Naam To Lo;
Ek Nigaah Par Bike Hain 'Insha' Aaj;
Muft Mein Mol Ek Gulam To Lo!

 Kis Ko Qatil Main Kahun Kis Ko Masiha Samajhun;
Sab Yahan Dost Hi Baithe Hain Kise Kya Samajhun;
Wo Bhi Kya Din The Ki Har Veham Yaqeen Hota Tha;
Ab Haqeeqat Nazar Aaye To Use Kya Samajhun!

 Zakhm The Gehre Aur Na Aaya Mujhe Unhe Seena;
Uske Zakhmo Ke Bin Zindagi Mein Kya Jeena;
Agar Lafzo Mein Teri Tareef Karunga To Tere Husn Ke Be-Adbi Hogi;
Bas Tu Yeh Jaanle Ki Tere Bin To Chand Kee Chandni Bhi Adhuri Hogi!

 Tere Ton Door Rahaan Tan Kis Tarah;
Dil Da Haal Vi Dassan Tan Kis Tarah;
Bada Samjhaya Apne Kamle Dil Nu Sajjna;
Hun Isnu Hor Majboor Kara Ta Kis Tarah!

 Udas Aankhon Se Aansu Nahi Nikalte Hain;
Ye Motiyon Kee Tarah Sipiyon Mein Palte Hain;

Ghane Dhuen Mein Farishte Bhi Aankh Malte Hain;
Tamam Raat Khajuron Ke Ped Jalte Hain;

Main Shah Reh Nahin, Raste Ka Pathar Hun;
Yahan Sawar Bhi Paidal Utar Kar Chalte Hain;

Unhe Kabhi Na Batana Main Unki Aankhein Hun;
Wo Log Phool Samajhkar Mujhe Masalte Hain;

Ye Ek Ped Hai, Aa Iss Se Milkar Ro Lein Hum;
Yahan Se Tere Mere Raaste Badalte Hain;

Kai Sitaron Ko Main Janata Hun Bachpan Se;
Kahin Bhi Jaun Mere Saath Saath Chalte Hain!

 Haan Aye Falak-e-Pir Jawan Tha Abhi Arif;
Kya Tera Bigadta Jo Na Marta Koi Din Aur;
Tum Maah-e-Shab-e-Char-Duham The Mere Ghar Ke;
Phir Kyon Na Raha Ghar Ka Woh Naqsha Koi Din Aur!

Translation:
Yes, you Ancient sky! Arif was still young,
What would you lose, if he had not died untill some other day.
You were the full moon of my home,
Why could not that design remain until some other day.

 Mohabbat Mein Main Khud Ko Bhool Jaunga;
Raha Wada Teri Shohbat Mein Main Duniya Bhool Jaunga;
Kabhi Aajmana Humein Bhi Apni Mehfil Mein;
Main Teri Khatir Duniya-e-Mehfil Bhool Jaunga!

 Teri Saadgi Ko Niharne Ka Dil Karta Hai;
Tamaam Umar Tere Naam Karne Ka Dil Karta Hai;
Ek Muqammal Shayari Hai Tu Kudrat Kee;
Tujhe Ghazal Banake Zuban Pe Lane Ka Dil Karta Hai!

 Sapne The, Un Sapno Ke Aap Sahil Hue;
Na Jane Kaise Hum Aapki Mohabbat Ke Kabil Hue;
Karazdar Rahenge Hum Us Haseen Pal Ke;
Jis Pal Aap Hamari Choti Si Duniya Mein Shamil Hue!

 Khushi Mili To Ye Aalam

Khushi Mili To Ye Aalam Tha Bad-Hawasi Ka;
Ki Dhyan Hi Na Raha Gham Kee Be-Libasi Ka;

Chamak Uthe Hain Jo Dil Ke Kalas Yahan Se Abhi;
Guzar Hua Hai Khayalon Kee Dev-Dasi Ka;

Guzar Na Jaa Yun Hi Rukh Pher Kar Salaam To Le;
Humein To Der Se Daawa Hai Roo-Shanasi Ka;

Khuda Ko Maan Ki Tujh Lab Ke Choomane Ke Siva;
Koi Ilaaj Nahi Aaj Kee Udasi Ka;

Gire Pade Hue Patton Mein Shehar Dhoodhta Hai;
Ajeeb Taur Hai Iss Junglon Ke Baasi Ka!

 Mit Jayega Sar Gar Tera Pathar Na Ghisega;
Hoon Dar Pe Tere Naasiyah-Farsa Koi Din Aur;
Aaye Ho Kal Aur Aaj Hi Kehte Ho Ke Jaaun;
Maana Ki Khamosh Nahi Acha Koi Din Aur!

Translation:
My forehead will bear the scar before your tombstone will,
I remain prostrate before your grave until some other day,
Arriving yesterday, and speaking today of leaving,
Granted not forever, but perhaps, some other day.

 Jo Nahi Aata Uska Intezar Kyon Hota Hai;
Kisi Ke Liye Apna Yeh Haal Kyon Hota Hai;
Waise To Iss Duniya Mein Kafi Cheezein Pyaari Hain;
Jo Nahi Milta Usi Se Pyaar Kyon Hota Hai!

 Koi Toote To Use Sajana Seekho;
Koi Roothe To Use Manana Seekho;
Rishte To Milte Hain Muqaddar Se;
Bas Use Khoobsurti Se Nibhana Seekho!

 Ab Kis Se Kahen

Ab Kis Se Kahen Aur Kaun Sune Jo Haal Tumhare Baad Hua;
Iss Dil Kee Jheel See Aankhon Mein Ek Khwab Bahut Barbad Hua;

Ye Hijr-Hawa Bhi Dushman Hai Iss Naam Ke Saare Rangon Kee;
Wo Naam Jo Mere Honthon Pe Khushbu Kee Tarah Aabad Hua;

Us Shehar Mein Kitne Chehre The Kuch Yaad Nahi Sab Bhool Gaye;
Ek Shakhs Kitabon Jaisa Tha Wo Shakhs Zubani Yaad Hua;

Wo Apne Ganv Kee Galiyan Thi Dil Jin Mein Nachta Gata Tha;
Ab Iss Se Fark Nahi Padta Nashaad Hua Ya Shaad Hua;

Benaam Sataish Rehti Thi In Gehri Sanwali Aankhon Mein;
Aisa To Kabhi Socha Bhi Na Tha Ab Jitna Bedad Hua!

 Badalte Iss Zamane Ne Sab Ko Badal Dala;
Khwabon Aur Khyalon Ko Bhi Badal Dala;
Na Badal Saka Us Bewafa Ko Pyaar Mera;
Jiske Liye Humne Apne Aap Ko Badal Dala!

 Mujhe Kisi Se Mohabbat Nahi Siva Tere;
Mujhe Kisi Kee Jarurat Nahi Siva Tere;
Meri Nazar Ko Thi Jiski Talaash Barson Se;
Kisi Ke Paas Woh Surat Nahi Siva Tere!

 Hote Agar Paas To Koi Shararat Karte;
Lekar Tumhein Baahon Mein Mohabbat Karte;
Dekhte Teri Aankhon Mein Neend Ka Khumar;
Apni Khoyi Hui Neendo Kee Shikayat Karte!

 Dard Se Mera Daman

Dard Se Mera Daman Bhar De Ya Allah;
Phir Chahe Deewana Kar De Ya Allah;

Maine Tujhse Chand Sitare Kab Maange;
Roshan Dil Bedaar Nazar De Ya Allah;

Suraj Si Ik Cheez To Hum Sab Dekh Chuke;
Sach-Much Kee Ab Koi Sehar De Ya Allah;

Ya Dharti Ke Zakhmon Par Marham Rakh De;
Ya Mera Dil Patthar Kar De Ya Allah!

 Jane Kis Mor Pe Le Aayi Hai Zindagi;
Band Hain Dareechey Tamam Na Koi Kinara Dikhai De;
Nahi Maloom Ulfat Kee Hai Kaun Si Manzil;
Ki Tere Siwa Ab Na Humein Guzara Dikhai De!

 Itna Haseen Kyon Banaya Khuda Ne Unko;
Ki Har Koi Dekhna Chahta Hai Dil-o-Jaan Se Unko;
Baarr-Baar Dekhne Se Dil Nahi Bharta Kisi Ka Bhi;
Aankhon Mein Basa Lena Chahta Hai Har Shakhs Unko!

 Zara Sa Qatra Kahin

Zara Sa Qatra Kahin Aaj Agar Ubharta Hai;
Samandaron Hi Ke Lehje Mein Baat Karta Hai;

Khuli Chhaton Ke Diye Kab Ke Bujh Gaye Hote;
Koi To Hai Jo Hawaon Ke Par Katarta Hai;

Sharafaton Kee Yahan Koi Ahemiyat Hi Nahi;
Kisi Ka Kuch Na Bigado To Kaun Darta Hai;

Zameen Kee Kaise Viqaalat Ho Phir Nahi Chalti;
Jab Aasmaan Se Koi Faisala Utarta Hai;

Tum Aa Gaye Ho To Phir Kuch Chandni Si Baatein Hon;
Zameen Pe Chand Kahan Roz Roz Utarta Hai!

 Haan Woh Nahi Khuda Parast, Jao Woh Bewafa Sahi;
Jisko Ho Din-o-Dil Aziz Uski Gali Mein Jaye Kyon;
Ghalib-e-Khasta Ke Baghair Kaun Se Kaam Band Hain;
Roiye Zaar Zaar Kya Kijiye Haaye Haaye Kyon!

Translation:
Granted they are not a lover of God, yes, they are unfaithful,
Whoever holds creed and heart beloved, do not dare to wander up their way.
Without this brittle Ghalib, what industry willbe stopped?
Why cry so incessantly, why lament so endlesly?

 Mohabbat Karli Tumse Bahut Sochne Ke Baad;
Ab Kisi Ko Dekhna Nahi Tumhe Dekhne Ke Baad;
Duniya Chhod Denge Tumhe Pane Ke Baad;
Khuda Maaf Kare Itna Jhooth Bolne Ke Baad!

 Bahut Kuch Khoya, Bahut Kuch Paya;
Kasam Se Zindagi Ne Bahut Hasaya, Bahut Hi Rulaya;
Par Shikwa Nahi Zindagi Se Humein Koi;
Kyonki Issi Ne Kuch Haseen Dosto Se Bii Milaya!

 Woh Mujh Par Ajeeb Asar Rakhta Hai;
Mere Dil Kee Tamaam Khabar Rakhta Hai;
Shayed Main Use Bhool Hi Jati Magar;
Yaad Aane Ke Woh Saare Hunar Rakhta Hai!

 Ishq Kee Duniya Mein

Ishq Kee Duniya Mein Ek Hungama Barpaa Kar Diya;
Ai Khayal-e-Dost Ye Kya Ho Gaya Kya Kar Diya;

Zarre Zarre Ne Mera Afsana Sun Kar Daad Dee;
Main Ne Vahshat Mein Jahaan Ko Tera Shaida Kar Diya;

Toor Par Raah-e-Wafa Mein Bo Diye Kaante Kaleem;
Ishq Kee Vusaat Ko Masdood-e-Taqazaa Kar Diya;

Bistar-e-Mashriq Se Sooraj Ne Uthayaa Apana Sar;
Kis Ne Ye Mehfil Mein Zikr-e-Husn-e-Yaktaa Kar Diya;

Chashm-e-Nargis Jaa-e-Shabnam Khoon Royegi Nadeem;
Maine Jis Din Gulasitan Ka Raaz Ifsaa Kar Diya;

Mudda-e-Dil Kahun 'Ehasaan' Kis Umeed Par;
Wo Jo Chahenge Karenge Aur Jo Chaha Kar Diya!

 Ai Khuda Kisi Ko Aisi Zindagi Na De;
Zindagi De To Yun Bebasi Na De;
Dil Mein Rahe Sada Chahtein Yaar Ke Milan Kee;
Par Na Ho Sake Mulaqat Unse Aisi Koi Mazboori Na De!

 Khamosh Guzar Jate Hain Woh Kareeb Se;
Sawal Uthte Hain Dil Mein Ajeeb Se;
Woh Khafa Hain Ya Yeh Unki Koi Ada Hai;
Shikayat Bhi Kya Karein Ab Agar Yahi Hai Naseeb Mein!

 Apna To Chahton Mein

Apna To Chahton Mein Yahi Ek Asool Hai;
Tera Bhala Bura Humein Sab Kuch Qubool Hai;

Yeh Umar Bhar Ka Jaagna Bekaar Hi Na Jaye;
Tu Na Mila To Saari Reyazat Fizool Hai;

Khud Hi Kaha Tha Tu Ne Meri Jaan Chorr De;
Ab Chorr Di To Kyon Tera Chehra Malool Hai;

Ai Maan Yeh Meri Shohratein Meri Yeh Izatein;
Kuch Bhi Nahi Bas Tere Kadmon Ki Dhool Hai;

Aayi Jo Teri Yaad To Aankhein Baras Padi;
Iss Waqt Tere Dard Ka Dil Par Nazool Hai;

Ik Doosre Ke Waastey Dono Bane 'Wasi';
Guldaan Mera Dil Hai Teri Yaad Phool Hai!

 Jab Raat Kee Tanhayi Dil Ban Ke Dhadakti Hai;
Yaadon Ke Jharokhon Mein Chilman Si Sirakti Hai;
Lobaan Mein Chingari Jaise Koi Rakh Jaye;
Yun Yaad Teri Shab Bhar Seene Mein Sulagti Hai!

 Pyaar Bahut Hai Tumse Magar Izhaar Nahi Karte;
Meri Khamoshi Se Yeh Na Samjhna Ki Tumse Pyaar Nahi Karte;
Meri Aankhein To Har Lamha Tumhari Raah Dekhti Hain;
Aur Tum Kehti Ho Hum Intezar Nahi Karte!

 Meri Yaadon Mein Tum Ho Ya Mujh Mein Hi Tum Ho;
Mere Khwabon Mein Tum Ho Ya Mera Khwab Hi Tum Ho;
Dil Mera Dhadak Ke Puche Baar-Baar Ek Hi Baat;
Meri Jaan Mein Tum Ho Ya Meri Jaan Hi Tum Ho!

 Zamana Badal Geya Badal Gaye Insaan Bhi;
Aaj Badla Sab Kuch Chahat Aur Pyaar Bhi;
Aaj Kisi Kee Nazar Mein Keemat Nahi Hai Khoon Kee;
Paisa Jis Kee Jeb Mein Wo Hi Sultaan Aur Ameer Bhi!

 Judaa Bhi Hone Ka Andhesha

Judaa Bhi Hone Ka Andhesha Seh Nahi Sakte;
Hum Ek Shehar Mein Ab Khush Bhi Reh Nahi Sakte;

Yeh Roz-o-Shab Hain Hamare Ki Ek Dusre Se;
Chupaye Phirte Hain Ahwaal, Keh Nahi Sakte;

Shakist-e-Zaat Ka Izhaar Chahte Bhi Nahin;
Ajeeb Haal Hai, Hum Chup Bhi Reh Nahi Sakte;

Haqeeqton Kee Chattane Bhi Apni Raah Mein Hain;
Khayal-o-Khwab Ke Dariya Mein Beh Nahi Sakte;

Woh Be-Kasoor Hai, Aisi Bhi Koi Baat Nahin;
Kasoor-waar Hain Hum, Yeh Bhi Keh Nahin Saktey!

 Jab Woh Jamaal-e-Dilfaroz, Surat-e-Mehr-e-Nim Roz;
Aap Hi Ho Nazara Soz, Parde Mein Munh Chhupaye Kyon;
Dashna-e-Ghamza Jaan Sataan, Naawak-e-Naaz Be Panah;
Tera Hi Aks-e-Rukh Sahi, Samne Tere Aaye Kyon!

Translation:
The glorious beauty of that face, so much like the midday sun,
The manifests such blinding light, needs nothing like a veil.
Weaponry of seduction, arrows of untold invitation,
Could injure the reflected as much as the admirer.

 Jaane Do Abb Iss Gusse Ko;
Ishq Ko Toh Bhi Nibhaana Hai.
Gussa Hai Aggar Aashiq Pe;
Toh Kabr Mein Kyun Isse Lajaana Hai!

 Ek Se Silsile Hain Sab Hijr Kee Rut Bata Gayi;
Phir Wahi Subah Aayegi Phir Wahi Sham Aa Gayi;
Mere Lahoo Mein Jal Uthe Utne Hi Taza Dam Chirag;
Waqt Kee Sazishi Hawa Jitne Diye Bujha Gayi!

 Tanhai Mere Dil Mein Samati Chali Gayi;
Kismat Bhi Apna Khel Dikhati Chali Gayi;
Mehkti Fiza Kee Khushboo Mein Jo Dekha Pyaar Ko;
Bas Yaad Unki Aayi Aur Rulati Chali Gayi!

 Koi Samjhe Na Humko Beshak Par Aap To Samjhte Hain;
Apna Banate Hain Mere Har Gham Ko Tabhi To Hum Sambhalte Hain;
Khuda Har Ek Khushi De Aapko Har Ek Gham Humko Naseeb Ho;
Bas Yahi Dil Mein Sochkar Har Ek Dua Karte Hain!

 Dukh Fasana Nahi Ki Tujh Se Kahen;
Dil Bhi Maana Nahi Ki Tujh Se Kahen;

Aaj Tak Apni Bekali Ka Sabab;
Khud Bhi Jana Nahi Ki Tujh Se Kahen;

Betarah Haal-e-Dil Hai Aur Tujh Se;
Dostana Nahi Ki Tujh Se Kahen;

Ek Tu Harf Aashnaa Tha Magar;
Ab Zamana Nahi Ki Tujh Se Kahen;

Qaasid! Hum Faqeer Logo Ka;
Ek Thikana Nahi Ki Tujh Se Kahen;

Ai Khudaa Dard-e-Dil Hai Bakhshish-e-Dost;
Aab-O-Dana Nahn Ki Tujh Se Kahen;

Ab To Apna Bhi Us Gali Mein 'Faraz';
Aana Jana Nahi Ke Tujh Se Kahen!

 Dil Hi To Hai Na Sang-o-Khisht, Dard Se Bhar Na Aaye Kyon;
Royenge Hum Hazar Baar Koi Humein Sataye Kyon;
Daer Nahi, Haram Nahi, Dar Nahi, Aastaan Nahi;
Baithe Hain Rehguzar Pe Hum Gair Humein Uthaye Kyon!

Translation:
It is only a heart, not stone or mortar, why should it not fill with pain,
We will wail a thousand times, why should anyone torment us.
It is not a temple, mosque, a dearly beloved's door, nor a patron's entryway,
We are wayfarers, why should anyone evict us!

 Samandar Mein Utarta Hun To Aankhen Bheeg Jati Hain;
Teri Aankhon Ko Padhta Hun To Aankhen Bheeg Jati Hain;
Tumhara Naam Likhne Ki Izazat Chinn Gayi Jab Se;
Koi Bhi Lafz Likhta Hun To Aankhen Bheeg Jati Hain!

 Dil Tootega To Fariyad Karoge Tum Bhi;
Hum Na Rahe To Humein Yaad Karoge Tum Bhi;
Aaj Kehte Ho Hamare Paas Waqt Nahi;
Par Ek Din Mere Liye Waqt Barbaad Karoge Tum Bhi!

 Chaman Se Bichhda Hua Ek Gulab Hoon;
Main Khud Apni Tabaahi Ka Jawaab Hoon;
Yun Nigahein Na Fer Mujhse Mere Sanam;
Main Teri Chahaton Mein Hi Hua Barbaad Hoon!

 Yeh Kaisi Judai Hai Jisne Humein Shayar Bana Diya;
Yeh Kaisa Gham Hai Jisne Humein Bebas Bana Diya;
Socha Nahi Tha Juda Ho Jaoge Humse Kabhi;
Karte Bhi Kya Jab Aap Ne Hi Gair Bana Diya!

 Kis-Kis Tarah Se Mujhko Na

Kis-Kis Tarah Se Mujhko Na Ruswa Kiya Geya;
Gairon Ka Naam Mere Lahoo Se Likha Geyaa;

Nikla Tha Main Sada-e-Jaras Kee Talash Mein;
Bhule Se Iss Sukoot Ke Sehra Mein Aa Geya;

Kyon Aaj Us Ka Zikr Mujhe Khush Na Kar Saka;
Kyon Aaj Us Ka Naam Mera Dil Dukha Geya;

Iss Hadse Ko Sun Ke Karega Yakeen Koi;
Suraj Ko Ek Jhonka Hawa Ka Bujha Geya!

 Yak Nazar Besh Nahi Fursat-e-Hasti Ghafil;
Garmi-e-Bazm Hai Ek Raqs-e-Sharar Hone Tak;
Gham-e-Hasti Ka Asad Kis Se Ho Juz Marg Ilaz;
Shama Har Rang Mein Jalti Hai Sahar Hone Tak!

Translation:
Leisure for life is no more than the flash of a glance, o ignorant,
The warmth of festivity is one dance of the flame,
Asad, what can cure the grief of existence, except dying,
The candle is obliged to burn before extinguishing at dawn.

 Ai Subah Main Ab Kahan Raha Hun;
Khwabon Hi Mein Sarf Ho Chuka Hun;
Sab Mere Bagair Mutmain Hain;
Main Sab Ke Bagair Jee Raha Hun!

Meaning:
Sarf = Expenditure
Mutmain = Quiet

 Dillagi Mein Dil Ko Hum Kaisa Rog Laga Baithe;
Zindagi Ko Chorh Kyon Maut Ko Gale Laga Baithe;
Humne Samjha Tha Dil Lagakar Dil Ko Chain Milega;
Aisi Lagi Chot Ke Dil Ko Bedard Se Dard Laga Baithe!

 Tum Khafa Ho Gaye To Koi Khushi Na Rahegi;
Tere Bina Chiragon Mein Roshni Na Rahegi;
Kya Kahe Kya Guzregi Dil Par;
Zinda To Rahenge Par Zindagi Na Rahegi!

 Tum Mere Dil Mein Aise Base Ho;
Jaise Ke Dil Kee Dhadkan Bane Ho;
Tumko Meri Jaan Khabar Hi Nahi Hai;
Mere Liye Tum Kya Ban Gaye Ho!

 Phool The Rang The

Phool The Rang The Lamhon Kee Sabahat Hum The;
Aise Zinda The Ki Jeene Kee Alamat Hum The;

Sab Khirad-Mand Bane Phirte The Masha-Allah;
Bas Tere Shehar Mein Ik Sahib-e-Vehshat Hum The;

Naam Bakhsha Hai Tujhe Kis Ke Wufoor-e-Gham Ne;
Gar Koi Tha To Tere Mujrim-e-Shohrat Hum The;

Ab To Khud Apni Zaroorat Bhi Nahi Hai Hum Ko;
Wo Bhi Din The Ki Kabhi Teri Zaroorat Hum The;

Dhoop Ke Dasht Mein Kitna Wo Humein Dhundhta Tha;
'Aitabar' Us Ke Liye Abr Kee Soorat Hum The!

 Hum Ne Mana Ki Taghaful Na Karoge Lekin;
Khaak Ho Jayenge Hum Tumko Khabar Hone Tak;
Partawe-e-Khur Se Hai Shabnam Ko Fanaa Ki Taleem;
Main Bhi Hun Ek Inayat Kee Nazar Hone Tak!

Translation:
I agree that you will not remain indifferent but,
I will be dust by the time you become aware of me,
The sun's ray teaches a dewdrop how to vanish,
I live because you have not bestowed the grace of your attention upon me.

 Aisa Nahi Ki Unse Mohabbat Nahi Rahi;
Jazbaat Mein Wo Pehli Si Shiddat Nahi Rahi;
Sar Mein Wo Intezar Ka Saudaa Nahi Raha;
Dil Par Wo Dhadkano Kee Hukuumat Nahi Rahi!

 Hum Khud Ko Bhool Jayein To Koi Gham Nahi;
Aapko Agar Bhool Jayein Woh Hum Nahi;
Chahte Hain Hum Dosto Ko Jaan Se Bhi Jyada;
Unke Liye Apni Jaan Bhi Chali Jaye To Koi Gham Nahi!

 Mujhe Apne Jism Kee Khushbu Se Madhosh Kar Do;
Mujhe Apni Nazuk Si Baahon Mein Mehsoor Kar Do;
Laga Ke Seene Se Mujhe Saare Gham Door Kar Do;
Main Tumse Juda Na Ho Saku Mujhe Itna Majboor Kar Do!

 Dil To Hai Jo Sirf Tujh Pe Hi Mare Ja Raha Hai;
Teri Yaad Mein Teri Tasbih Kiye Ja Raha Hai;
Ab To Yeh Judaai Ka Gham Hum Se Saha Nahi Ja Raha Hai;
Aur Ek Tu Hai Jo Door Reh Kar Hume Tadpaye Ja Raha Hai!

 Har Ek Harf-e-Aarzoo Ko

Har Ek Harf-e-Aarzoo Ko Dastan Kiye Hue;
Zamana Ho Geya Hai Un Ko Mehaman Kiye Hue;

Suroor-e-Aish Talkhi-e-Hayat Ne Bhula Diya;
Dil-e-Hazin Hai Bekasi Ko Hijr-e-Jaan Kiye Hue;

Kali Kali Ko Gulistan Kiye Hue Wo Aayenge;
Wo Aayenge Kali Kali Ko Gulistan Kiye Hue;

Sukoon-e-Dil Kee Raahton Ko Un Se Maang Loon;
Sukoon-e-Dil Kee Raahton Ko Bekaran Kiye Hue;

Wo Aayenge To Aayenge Junoon-e-Shauq Ubharne;
Wo Jayenge To Jayenge Tabahiyan Kiye Hue;

Main Un Kee Bhi Nigah Se Chhupa Ke Un Ko Dekh Loon;
Ki Un Se Bhi Hai Aaj Rashk Badguman Kiye Hue!

 Arz Farmaiya Hai:

Ishq Mein Zor Nahi Chalta, Ghalib;

Wah Wah!

Ishq Mein Zor Nahi Chalta, Ghalib;

Kabz Mein Bhi Nahi Chalta!

 Aah Ko Chahiye Ek Umr Asar Hone Tak;
Kaun Jeeta Hai Teri Zulf Ke Sar Hone Tak;
Dam Har Mauj Mein Hai Halqa-e-Sad Kaam-e-Nihang;
Dekhein Kya Guzre Hai Qatre Pe Guhar Hone Tak!

Translation:
A sigh requires a lifetime to take effect,
Who lives to reach the source of your journey,
The gaping mouths of a hundred crocodiles form netted traps in each wave,
Consider the labour within the sea-change of a raindrop to a pearl.

 Ek Tukda Teri Yaadon Ki Chandni Ka Tod;
Nihara Use Der Tak, Hatheli Par Rakh Ke;
Phir Ek Phoonk Se Udaa Diya Kal Raat Maine;
Aaj Subah Dekhi Hai Tere Ehsaas Ki Dhund Har Taraf Faili Hui!

 Khoobsurat Sa Ek Pal Kissa Ban Jata Hai;
Jane Kab Kaun Zindagi Ka Hissa Ban Jata Hai;
Kuch Log Zindagi Mein Milte Hain Aise;
Jinse Kabhi Na Tootne Wala Rishta Ban Jata Hai!

 Kismat Pe Naaz Hai To Wajah Hai Teri Mohabbat;
Khushiyan Jo Pass Hain To Wajah Hai Teri Mohabbat;
Main Tujh Se Mohabbat Kee Talab Kaise Na Karu;
Chalti Hain Yeh Saans To Wajah Hai Teri Mohabbat!

 Maine Kab Chaha Ki Main

Maine Kab Chaha Ki Main Us Kee Tamana Ho Jaoon;
Ye Bhee Kya Kam Hai Agar Us Ko Gawara Ho Jaoon;

Mujh Ko Unchai Se Girana Bhee Hai Manzoor, Agar;
Us Kee Palkon Se Jo Toote, Wo Sitara Ho Jaoon;

Lekar Ik Azm Uthun Roz Nayi Bheed Ke Sath;
Phir Wahei Bheed Chhate Aur Main Tanha Ho Jaoon;

Jab Talak Mahve-Nazar Hun, Main Tamashayi Hun;
Tuk Nigahein Jo Hata Loon To Tamasha Ho Jaoon;

Main Wo Bekar Sa Pal Hun, Na Koi Shabd, Na Sur;
Wo Agar Mujh Ko Rachale To Hamesha Ho Jaoon;

Aagahi Mera Marz Bhi Hai, Mudawa Bhi Hai 'Saaz';
Jis Se Marta Hun, Usee Zehar Se Achha Ho Jaoon!

 Saans Tham Jati Hai Par Jaan Nahi Jati;
Dard Hota Hai Par Aawaz Nahi Aati;
Ajeeb Log Hain Iss Zamane Mein;
Koi Bhool Nahi Pata Aur Kisi Ko Yaad Nahi Aati!

 Rone Se Kabhi Kisi Ko Kuch Hasil Nahi Hota;
Jo Bichhad Jaye Woh Sathi Nahi Hota;
Dusro Kee To Hum Mehfil Sajate Rehte Hain;
Par Hamari Tanhai Mein Kabhi Koi Shamil Nahi Hota!

 Ishq Se Kabhi Humne Inkaar Nahi Kiya;
Par Iss Dil Ko Kabhi Itna Bekarar Nahi Kiya;
Bas Aankhon Mein Unke Sapne Sajaye Rakhe Hain;
Magar Kabhi Humne Honthon Se Ishq Ka Izhar Nahi Kiya!

 Shayad Aaghaz Hua Phir

Shayad Aaghaz Hua Phir Kisi Afsane Ka;
Hukm Aadam Ko Hai Jannat Se Nikal Jane Ka;

Un Se Kuch Keh To Raha Hun Magar Allah Na Kare;
Wo Bhi Mafhoom Na Samjhe Mere Afsane Ka;

Dekhna Dekhna Yeh Hazrat-e-Vaiz Hi Na Hon;
Raasta Puch Raha Hai Koi Maikhane Ka;

Betalluq Tere Aage Se Guzar Jata Hun;
Yeh Bhi Ek Husn-e-Talab Hai Tere Deewane Ka;

Hashr Tak Garmi-e-Hungama-e-Hasti Hai 'Shakeel';
Silsila Khatm Na Hoga Mere Afsane Ka!

 Chand Kee Taraf Dekh Ke Fariyaad Mangte Hain;
Hum Zindagi Mein Bas Tera Pyaar Mangte Hain;
Bhool Ke Bhi Kabhi Mujhse Door Mat Jana;
Hum Kaun Sa Tujhse Teri Jaan Mangte Hai!

 Mohabbat Wafa Ke Siwa Kuch Bhi Nahi;
Duniya Mein Gham Ke Siwa Kuch Bhi Nahi;
Tumhare Paas Mere Bina Sab Kuch Hai;
Par Hamare Paas Tumhare Siwa Kuch Bhi Nahi!

 Aaj Bhi Behta Hai Uska Diya Hua Zakham;
Main Chah Kar Bhi Use Sil Na Paya;
Bas Kehne Ke Liye Hi Zinda Hu Main To Yaaro;
Par Marzi Ke Saath Kabhi Jee Nhi Paya!

 Yeh Hadasa To Kisi Din

Yeh Hadasa To Kisi Din Guzarne Wala Tha;
Main Bach Bhi Jata To Ik Roz Marne Wala Tha;

Tere Salook Teri Aagahi Kee Umr Daraz;
Mere Aziz Mera Zakham Bharne Wala Tha;

Bulandiyon Ka Nasha Toot Kar Bikharne Laga;
Mera Jahaz Zameen Par Utarne Wala Tha;

Mera Naseeb Mere Haath Kaat Gaye Varna;
Main Teri Maang Mein Sindoor Bharne Wala Tha;

Mere Chirag Meri Shab Meri Munderein Hain;
Main Kab Shareer Hawaon Se Darne Wala Tha!

 Aankhon Mein Bas Ke Dil Mein Samaa Kar Chale Gaye; 
Khwabida Zindagi Thi Jagaa Kar Chale Gaye;
Chehre Tak Aasteen Wo Lakar Chale Gaye; 
Kya Raaz Tha Ki Jis Ko Chipakar Chale Gaye!

Meaning:
Khwabida = Sleepy

 Kujh Yaaran Nu Si Parkhiya Main;
Kujh Yaari Meri Parakh Gaye;
Lakh Bura Keha, Kujh Russe Na;
Kujh Bina Kahe Hi Harakh Gaye;
Kujh Vaarde Si Jaan Mere To;
Kujh Aayi Musibat Sarak Gayee;
Kujh Mere To Vichhad Ke Khush Hoye;
Kujh Sanu Vekhan Layi Taras Gaye!

 Na Jane Kab Wo Haseen Raat Hogi;
Jab Unki Nigahein Hamari Nigahon Ke Saath Hongi;
Baithe Hain Hum Uss Raat Ke Intezar Mein;
Jab Unke Hontho Kee Surkhiya Hamare Hontho Ke Saath Hongi!

 Mujhe Rula Kar Dil Uska Bhi To Roya Hoga;
Chehra Aansuon Se Usne Bhi To Dhoya Hoga;
Agar Na Kiya Hasil Kuch Humne Pyaar Mein;
Kuchh Na Kuch To Usne Bhi Zaroor Khoya Hoga!

 Raste Kaa Intikhaab

Raste Kaa Intikhaab Zaroori Sa Ho Geya;
Ab Ikhtitaam-e-Baab Zaroori Sa Ho Geya;

Hum Chup Rahe To Aur Bhi Ilzam Aayega;
Ab Kuch Na Kuch Jawab Zaroori Sa Ho Geya;

Hum Taalte Rahe Ki Ye Naubat Na Aane Paye;
Phir Hijr Ka Azaab Zaroori Sa Ho Geya;

Har Sham Jald Sone Kee Aadat Hi Pad Gayi;
Har Raat Ek Khwab Zaroori Sa Ho Geya;

Aahon Se Toottaa Nahi Ye Gumbad-e-Siyah;
Aab Sang-e-Aaftaab Zaroori Sa Ho Geya;

Dena Hai Imtihaan Tumhare Firaq Ka;
Ab Sabr Ka Nisab Zaroori Sa Ho Geya!

 Chaman Mein Shab Ko Jo Wo Shokh Be-Naqab Aaya;
Yakeen Ho Geya Shabnam Ko Aaftab Aaya;
Un Ankhdiyon Mein Agar Nasha-e-Sharab Aaya;
Salaam Jhuk Ke Karunga Jo Phir Hijaab Aaya!

 Hamari Tanhai Mitane Ke Liye Kaun Aayega;
In Roti Hui Aankhon Ko Chup Karane Kaun Aayega;
Kisi Ko Ab Zaroorat Hi Nahi Hai Hamari Dosto;
Sochte Hain Agar Mar Gaye To Dafnane Kaun Aayega!

 Main Aadat Hun Uski, Woh Zaroorat Hai Meri;
Main Farmaish Hun Uski, Woh Ibadat Hai Meri;
Itni Aasani Se Kaise Nikal Dun Use Apne Dil Se;
Main Khwab Hun Uska Woh Haqeeqat Hai Meri!

 Dil Mein Ab Yun Tere Bhule Hue

Dil Mein Ab Yun Tere Bhule Hue Gham Aate Hain;
Jaise Bichhade Hue Kabe Mein Sanam Aate Hain;

Ik Ik Kar Ke Hue Jaate Hain Tare Roshan;
Meri Manzil Kee Taraf Tere Kadam Aate Hain;

Raqs-e-May Tez Karo, Saaz Kee Lai Tez Karo;
Su-e-Maikhana Safiraan-e-Haram Aate Hain;

Kuch Humin Ko Nahi Ehsan Uthane Ka Dimag;
Woh To Jab Aate Hain Mail-ba-Karam Aate Hain;

Aur Kuch Der Na Guzare Shab-e-Furqat Se Kaho;
Dil Bhi Kam Dukhata Hai Woh Yaad Bhi Kam Aate Hain!

 Tujh Se Ab Aur Mohabbat Nahi Kee Ja Sakti;
Khud Ko Itni Bhi Aziyat Nahi Di Ja Sakti;
Jante Hain Ki Yakeen Toot Raha Hai Dil Par;
Phir Bhi Ab Tark Ye Vehshat Nahi Kee Ja Sakti!

Meaning:
Aziyat = Trouble

 Na Koi Kisi Se Door Hota Hai;
Na Koi Kisi Ke Kareeb Hota Hai;
Aata Hai Chal Pyaar Khud Uske Paas;
Jab Koi Kisi Ka Naseeb Hota Hai!

 Kab Woh Zahir Hoga Aur

Kab Woh Zahir Hoga Aur Hairan Kar Dega Mujhe;
Jitni Bhi Mushkil Mein Hun Aasan Kar Dega Mujhe;

Roo-b-Roo Kar Ke Kabhi Apne Mehakte Surkh Honth;
Ek Do Pal Ke Liye Guldaan Kar Dega Mujhe;

Rooh Phoonkega Mohabbat Kee Mere Paikar Mein Woh;
Phir Woh Apne Samne Be-Jaan Kar Dega Mujhe;

Khwahishon Ka Khoon Bahega Sar-e-Bazar-e-Shauq;
Aur Mukammal Be-e-Sar-o-Saman Kar Dega Mujhe;

Munahadim Kar Dega Aa Kar Sari Tameeraat-e-Dil;
Dekhte Hee Dekhte Veeran Kar Dega Mujhe;

Ek Naa-Maujudgi Reh Jayegi Charon Taraf;
Rafta Rafta Iss Qadar Sunsaan Kar Dega Mujhe;

Ya To Mujh Se Woh Chuda Dega Ghazal-Goyi 'Zafar'
Ya Kisi Din Sahab-e-Deevaan Kar Degaa Mujhe!

 Koi Shaam Aati Hai Tumhari Yaad Lekar;
Koi Shaam Jaati Hai Tumahri Yaad Dekar;
Hume To Intezar Hai Us Sham Ka;
Jo Aaye Kabhi Tumhein Saath Lekar!

 Tanhai Mere Dil Mein Samati Chali Gayi;
Kismat Bhi Apna Khel Dikhati Chali Gayi;
Mehkti Fiza Kee Khushbu Mein Jo Dekha Pyaar Ko;
Bas Yaad Unki Kee Aayi Aur Rulati Chali Gayi!

 Gum Na Ho Wahan Jahan Ho Aafsana Apka;
Khusiyan Dhundti Rahe Aashiyana Aapka;
Wo Waqt Hi Na Aaye Jab Aap Udas Ho;
Ye Duniya Bhula Na Sake Muskurana Apka!

 Aah Ko Chahiye Ek Umr

Aah Ko Chahiye Ek Umr Asar Hone Tak;
Kaun Jeeta Hai Tere Zulf Ke Sar Hone Tak;

Aashiqii Sabr Talab Aur Tamannaa Betaab;
Dil Ka Kya Rang Karun Khoon-e-Jigar Hone Tak;

Hum Ne Maana Ki Tagakul Na Karoge Lekin;
Khaak Ho Jayenge Hum Tum Ko Khabar Hone Tak;

Gam-e-Hasti Ka Asad Kis Se Ho Kuz-Marg-e-Ilaaj;
Shamaa Har Rang Mein Jalati Hai Sehar Hone Tak!

 Itna Haseen Kyon Banaya Khuda Ne Unko;
Har Koi Chahta Hai Dil-o-Jaan Se Unko;
Baar Baar Dekhne Se Dil Nahi Bharta Kisi Ka Bhi;
Aankhon Mein Basa Lena Chahta Hai Har Shakhs Unko!

 Yun To Duniya Mein Sahare Bahut Hain;
Hamare Jaise Tumhare Chahne Wale Bahut Hain;
Kis Kiska Haal Ab Tum Ja Kar Puchoge;
Yun To Zamane Mein Tumhare Deewane Bahut Hain!

 Iss Se Pehle Ki

Iss Se Pehle Ki Bewafa Ho Jayein;
Kyon Na Ai Dost Hum Judaa Ho Jayein;

Tu Bhi Heere Se Ban Geya Patthar;
Hum Bhi Kal Jaane Kya Se Kya Ho Jayein;

Hum Bhi Majboorion Ka Uzar Karein;
Phir Kahin Aur Mubtala Ho Jayein;

Ab Ke Gar Tu Mile To Hum Tujhse;
Aise Liptein Teri Qabaa Ho Jayein;

Bandagi Hum Ne Chhod Di Hai 'Faraz';
Kya Karein Jab Log Khuda Ho Jayein!

 Nazar Se Nazar Kee Mulaqat Dekhi Hai;
Pyaar Mein Hote Hue Teeron Kee Barsaat Dekhi Hai;
Yun To Lakhon Dekhe Hain Humne Dil Lagane Wale;
Par Teri Chahat Mein Humne Baat Koi Khaas Dekhi Hai!

 Aansu Na Hote To Aankh Itni Khoobsurat Na Hoti;
Dard Na Hota To Khushiyon Kee Keemat Na Hoti;
Poori Karta Rabb Yun Hi Sab Muradein;
To Ibadat Kee Kabhi Zaroorat Na Hoti!

 Ek Jaam Khankta Jaam

Ek Jaam Khankta Jaam, Ki Saqi Raat Guzrne Wali Hai;
Ek Hoshruba Inaam, Ki Saqi Raat Guzrne Wali Hai;

Wo Dekh Sitaron Ke Moti Har Aan Bikhrte Jaate Hain;
Aflaak Pe Hai Kohram, Ki Saqi Raat Guzrne Wali Hai;

Yeh Waqt Nahi Hai Baaton Ka Palkon Ke Saaye Kaam Mein La;
Ilham Koi Ilham, Ki Saqi Raat Guzrne Wali Hai;

Madhoshi Mein Ehsas Ki Unche Jeene Se Gir Jaane De;
Iss Waqt Na Mujh Ko Tham, Ki Saqi Raat Guzrne Wali Hai!

 Yeh Ishq Wale Wafa Kee Keemat Kya Jaane;
Bewafa Hai Yeh Gham-e-Mohabbat Kya Jaane;
Milta Ho Jinhe Har Mod Pe Naya Humsafar;
Woh Sachhe Pyaar Kee Keemat Kya Jane!

 Ishq Tujse Karta Hun Main Zindagi Se Bhi Jyada;
Main Darta Nahi Maut Se Teri Judai Se Jyada;
Chahe To Aajma Le Mujhe Kisi Aur Se Jyada;
Meri Zindagi Mein Kuch Nahi Teri Mohabbat Se Jyada!

 Jag Mein Aakar

Jag Mein Aakar Idhar Udhar Dekha;
Tu Hi Aaya Nazar Jidhar Dekha;

Jaan Se Ho Gaye Badan Khali;
Jis Taraf Tune Aankh Bhar Dekha;

Nala, Fariyad, Aah Aur Zaree;
Aap Se Ho Saka So Kar Dekha;

Un Labon Ne Kee Na Maseehayi;
Hum Ne Sau-Sau Tarah Se Mar Dekha;

Zor Aashiq Mizaaj Hai Koi;
'Dard' Ko Kissa-e-Mukhtsar Dekha!

 Unki Tasveer Ko Seene Se Laga Lete Hain;
Iss Tarah Judai Ka Gham Mita Lete Hain;
Kisi Tarha Zikar Ho Jaye Unko Hamare Dard Ka Agar;
Hans Kar Bheegi Palkon Mein Sab Dard Chupa Lete Hain!

 Humne Manga Tha Saath Unka;
Woh Judai Ka Gham De Gaye;
Hum Unki Yaadon Ke Sahare Hi Jee Lete;
Par Woh Bhool Jaane Kee Kasam De Gaye!

 Kehte Hain Woh Majbur Hain Hum;
Na Chahte Hue Bhi Door Hain Hum;
Chura Lee Hai Unhone Dhadkane Hamari;
Phir Bhi Kehte Hain Ki Bekasoor Hain Hum!

 Sar Jhukaoge To...

Sar Jhukaoge To Patthar Devta Ho Jayega; 
Itanaa Mat Chaho Use Wo Be-Wafa Ho Jayega; 

Hum Bhi Dariya Hain Humein Apana Hunar Maloom Hai; 
Jis Taraf Bhii Chal Padenge Raasta Ho Jayega; 

Kitani Sachayi Se Mujh Se Zindagi Ne Keh Diya; 
Tu Nahi Mera To Koi Doosra Ho Jayega; 

Main Khuda Ka Naam Le Kar Pee Rahaa Hun Dosto;
Zehar Bhi Iss Mein Agar Hoga Dawa Ho Jayega; 

Rooth Janaa To Mohabbat Kee Alamat Hai Magar; 
Kya Khabar Thi Mujh Se Wo Itna Khafa Ho Jayega!

 Koi Na Mita Sakega Dil Ke Iss Fasane Ko;
Teri Chahat Mein Bhool Jata Hun Zamane Ko;
Uthe Jo Meri Nazar Tere Chehre Pe Muskan Aaye;
Teri Deewangi Mein Bhool Jaate Hain Nazrein Jhapkane Ko!

 Uski Chahat Ne Rulaya Bahut Hai;
Uski Yaadon Ne Tadpaya Bahut Hai;
Hum Usse Karte Hain Mohabbat Beintehaa;
Iss Baat Ko Usne Aazmaya Bahut Hai!

 Zindagi Se Kyon Rooth Gaye Ho Tum;
Itne Mayus Kyon Ho Gaye Ho Tum;
Zaroor Tumhara Bhi Kisi Ne Dil Toda Hai;
Jo Itne Gham-Geen Ho Gaye Ho Tum!

 Teri Tarha Malal Mujhe Bhi Nahi Raha;
Ja Ab Tera Khayal Mujhe Bhi Nahi Raha;

Tu Ne Bhi Mausamon Kee Pazeerai Chhod Di;
Ab Shauq-e-Mah-e-Visaal Mujhe Bhi Nahi Raha;

Mera Jawab Kya Tha Tujhe Bhi Khabar Nahi;
Yaad Ab Tera Sawaal Mujhe Bhi Nahi Raha;

Jis Baat Ka Khayaal Na Tu Ne Kabhi Kiya;
Us Baat Ka Khayal Mujhe Bhi Nahi Raha;

Toda Hai Tu Ne Jab Se Mere Dil Ka Aaina;
Andaza-e-Jamal Mujhe Bhi Nahi Raha!

 Ai Zindagi Yun Mujhse Tu Daga Na Kar;
Zinda Rahu Main Ye Tu Dua Na Kar;
Koi Chhuta Hai Tujhe To Hoti Hai Jalan;
Ai Hawa Tu Bhi Use Chhuaa Na Kar!

 Khoobsurati Kee Pehchan Banawat Se Nahi Hoti;
Mohabbat Kee Pehchan Dhadkano Kee Aahat Se Nahi Hoti;
Kaise Samajh Liya Khush Hain Hum Aapke Bagair;
Khushiyon Kee Pehchan Sirf Muskurahat Se Nahi Hoti!

 Dukh De Kar

Dukh De Kar Sawal Karte Ho;
Tum Bhi Ghalib Kamaal Karte Ho;

Dekh Kar Puch Liya Haal Mera;
Chalo Kuch To Khayaal Karte Ho;

Shehar-e-Dil Mein Ye Udasiyan Kaisi;
Ye Bhi Mujhse Sawaal Karte Ho;

Marna Chahe To Mar Nahi Sakte;
Tum Bhi Jeena Muhaal Karte Ho;

Ab Kis Kis Kee Misaal Dun Tumko;
Har Sitam Be-Misaal Karte Ho!

 Ek Bewafa Ko Apna Hamraaj Banakar;
Ab Pachhta Raha Hun Apna Dil Ganwakar;
Us Bewafa Ne Zindagi Mein Aag Laga Di;
Jise Dil Mein Basaya Tha Dhadkan Banakar!

 Har Lamha Hum Unhein Yaad Karte Rahe;
Unki Yaad Mein Mar-Mar Ke Jeete Rahe;
Ashq Aankon Se Hamari Behte Rahe;
Hum Ashqon Ke Jaam Peete Rahe!

 Raaton Ka Manzar Azeeb Lagta Hai;
Saya Teri Yaadon Ka Kareeb Lagta Hai;
Lehrein Aakar Waapis Ho Jaati Hain;
Woh Sahil Tanha Azeeb Lagta Hai!

 Koi Keh De
Koi Keh De Mere Dil Ki Baat Unse;
Har Taraf Se Hui Dil Ki Maat Unse;

Jaan-Pehchan Hi Kara De Gar Koi;
Ek-Ek Lamhe Ki Ho Shuruaat Unse;

Log Puchte Hain Muskuraht Ki Wajah;
Hamne Kaha Hui Hai Mulakat Unse;

Khoya Hua Raha Main Aaz Talak;
Ab Mila Do Mere Jazbaat Unse;

Karenge Chand Se Kuchh Baatein Hum Bhi;
Milte Hue Dekha Hai Har Raat Unse!

 Har Mulaqat Par Waqt Ka Takaza Hua;
Har Yaad Par Dil Ka Dard Taza Hua;
Suni Thi Sirf Ghazalo Mein Judai Ki Baatein;
Jab Khud Par Beeti To Haqeeqat Ka Andaza Hua!

 Ek Hasrat Thi Ki Unke Dil Mein Panah Milegi;
Kya Pata Tha Unki Mohabbat Mein Yeh Saza Milegi;
Na Apno Ne Samjha Na Gairon Ne Jaana;
Kya Khabar Thi Mujhe Meri Taqdeer Mein Bewafa Milegi!

 Zubaan Se Tumhein Keh Nahi Sakte;
Isliye Hamesha Khuda Se Fariyad Karte Hain;
Jab Bhi Dil Dhadke Tumhara Zor Zor Se;
Samajh Lena Hum Tumhein Dil Se Yaad Karte Hain!

 Tu Nahi To Zindagi Mein

Tu Nahi To Zindagi Mein Kya Reh Jayega;
Door Tak Tanhaiyon Ka Silsila Reh Jayega;

Dard Kee Sari Tahe Aur Saare Guzre Hadse;
Sab Dhuan Ho Jayenge Ek Waakiya Reh Jayega;

Yun Bhi Hoga Wo Mujhe Dil Se Bhula Dega Magar;
Ye Bhi Hoga Khud Usi Mein Ek Khala Reh Jayega;

Dayre Insan Ke Inkar Ke Iqrar Kee Sargoshiya;
Ye Agar Kabhi Toote To Fasla Reh Jayega!

 Kabhi Hum Toote To Kabhi Khwaab Toote;
Na Jane Kitne Tukdon Mein Armaan Toote;
Har Tukda Aaina Hai Zindgi Ka;
Har Aaine Ke Saath Lakhon Jazbaat Toote!

 Dil Ke Dard Ko Chupana Jitna Mushkil Hai;
Toot Kar Fir Muskurana Utna Hi Mushkil Hai;
Kisi Ke Sath Door Tak Jao Aur Fir Dekho;
Ki Akele Laut Kar Aana Kitna Mushkil Hai!

 Kaash Humein Bhi Koi Samjhane Wala Hota;
To Aaj Hum Itne Nasamjh Na Hote;
Kaash Koi Ishq Ka Jaam Pilane Wala Hota;
To Aaj Hum Bhi Is Sharab Ke Deewane Na Hote!

 Waqt Ke Sath Anaasar Bhi...

Waqt Ke Sath Anaasar Bhi Rahe Sazish Mein;
Jal Gaye Pair Kabhi Dhoop Kabhi Barish Mein;

Woh To Ik Saada-o-Kam Shauq Ka Talib Nikla;
Hum Ne Naahiq Hi Ganwaya Use Aarayesh Mein;

Zindagi Ki Koi Mehrumi Nahi Yaad Aayi;
Jab Talak Hu Mathe Tere Qurb Ki Asaayesh Mein;

Ek Duniya Ka Qaseeda Tha Agarche Mere Naam;
Lutf Aata Tha Kisi Shakhs Kee Fehmayesh Mein;

Us Kee Aankhen Bhi Meri Tarah Se Girdi Kahi Aur;
Khwab Ka Karz Barh Jata Hai Ik Khwahish Mein!

 Woh Begaano Mein Apne;
Hum Apno Mein Anjaan Lagte Hain;
Hamare Khoon Ki Bhi Keemat Nahi;
Unke Ashkon Ke Bhi Daam Lagte Hain!

 Kaun Hai Woh Jo Dil Mein Samaye Hue Hain;
Unke Liye Hum Har Khusi Bhulaye Hue Hain;
Najar Nahi Aate Par Tadap Mahsoos Hoti Hai;
Andekhe Yaar Ke Liye Sapne Sajaye Hue Hain!

 Bina Bataye Usne Na Jaane Kyon Ye Doori Kardi;
Bhichhad Ke Usne Mohabbat Hi Adhuri Kardi;
Mere Mukaddar Mein Gham Aaye To Kya Hua;
Khuda Ne Uski Khwaish To Poori Kardi!

 Shaan Se Pyaar Ka Izhar

Shaan Se Pyaar Ka Izhar Karenge;
Teri Mohabbat Pe Jaan Bhi Nisar Karenge;

Dekh Ke Jalegi Duniya Saari;
Iss Kadar Tujhpe Aitbaar Karenge;

Denge Salaami Sab Humko;
Jab Pyaar Ko Hum Bayaan Karenge;

Daulat Aur Shaurat Ka Kya Hai Kaam;
Teri Khushi Mein Khudko Nichaawar Karenge;

Har Ghadi Ho Bus Tera Deedar;
Waqt Se Hum Yahi Iltijaa Karenge;

Saaye Ki Tarah Tujhse Lipte Rahenge;
Duniya Ki Buri Nazar Se Tujhe Bachaya Karenge!

 Baarish Hue Bheeg Gaye Hum;
Baarish Hue Bheeg Gaye Hum;
Rajinikanth Ne Phuk Maari;
Aur Fir Kya - Sukh Gaye Hum!

 Shikwa Kisi Ka Na Fariyad Kisi Kee;
Honi Thi Yun Hi Zindagi Barbaad Kisi Kee;
Ehsas Mita Talash Miti Mit Gayi Umeedein;
Sab Mit Geya Par Na Mit Saki Yaad Kisi Kee!

 Mumkin Ho Aap Se To Bhula Dijiye Mujhe;
Pathar Pe Hun Lakeer, Mita Dijiye Mujhe;
Har Roz Mujh Se Taaza Shikayat Hai Aap Ko;
Main Kya Hun, Aik Baar Bata Dijiye Mujhe!

 Shehar Mein Dhoond Raha Hun

Shehar Mein Dhoond Raha Hun Ki Sahara De De;
Koi Haatim Jo Mere Haath Mein Kasa De De;

Pedh Sab Nange Faqiron Kee Tarah Sehme Hain;
Kis Se Ummeed Ye Kee Jaye Ki Saya De De;

Waqt Kee Sangjani Noch Gayi Sare Naqsh;
Ab Woh Aaina Kahan Jo Mera Chehra De De;

Dushmano Kee Bhi Koi Baat To Sach Ho Jaye;
Aa Mere Dost Kisi Din Mujhe Dhokha De De;

Main Bahut Jald Hi Ghar Laut Ke Aa Jaunga;
Meri Tanhayi Yahan Kuch Dino Pehra De De;

Jis Ne Katron Ko Bhi Mohtaz Kiya Mujh Ko;
Wo Josh Mein Agar Aa Jaye To Dariya De De;

Tum Ko 'Rahat' Kee Tabiyat Ka Nahi Andaza;
Woh Bhikari Hai Magar Maango To Duniya De De!

 Woh Lamhe Rulate Hain Humko Raat Din;
Woh Lamhe, Unka Bhi To Dil Dukhate Honge;
Jab Kabhi Bhi Woh, Padh Lete Honge Nagme Hamare;
Naam Apna Padhkar, Aankho Se Ashk Jhalak Aate Honge!

 Dil Mein Umeed Kee Shama Jala Rakhi Hai;
Humne Apni Alag Duniya Basa Rakhi Hai;
Iss Umeed Ke Saath Ki Aayenge Woh Kabhi;
Humne Har Raah Pe Apni Palkein Bichha Rakhi Hain!

 Ek Ajeeb Dastan Hai, Mere Afsaane Kee;
Maine Pal Pal Kee Kosish, Uske Pass Jaane Kee;
Naseeb The Meri Ya, Sazish Zamane Kee;
Door Hui Mujhse Utni, Jitni Umeed Thi Kareeb Aane Kee!

 Kya Kahun Tum Se

Kya Kahun Tum Se Main Ki Kya Hai Ishq;
Jaan Ka Rog Hai, Bala Hai Ishq;

Ishq Hi Ishq Hai Jahan Dekho;
Sare Aalam Mein Bhar Raha Hai Ishq;

Ishq Mashuq Ishq Aashiq Hai;
Yani Apna Hi Mubtala Hai Ishq;

Ishq Hai Tarz-o-Taur Ishq Ke Taeen;
Kahin Banda Kahin Khuda Hai Ishq;

Kaun Maqsad Ko Ishq Bin Pahuncha;
Aarzoo Ishq Wa Mudda Hai Ishq;

Koi Khwaahan Nahin Mohabbat Ka;
Tu Kahe Jins-e-Narawa Hai Ishq;

Meer Ji Zarad Hote Jaate Hain;
Kya Kahin Tum Ne Bhi Kiya Hai Ishq!

 Zindagi Mein Kisi Ek Se Karo Pyaar Itna;
Ki Kisi Aur Se Pyaar Karne Kee Gunjaish Na Rahe;
Woh Muskurade Aap Ko Dekh Kar Ek Baar;
To Zinadgi Se Phir Koi Khwaish Na Rahe!

 Roz Dhalti Hui Shaam Se Darr Lagta Hai;
Ab Mujhe Ishq Ke Anjaam Se Darr Lagta Hai;
Jab Se Mila Hai Dhokha Iss Ishq Mein;
Tabse Ishq Ke Naam Se Bhi Darr Lagta Hai!

 Mohabbat Kee Daastan Sunane Aaye Hain;
Tabah Karne Ke Baad Woh Pyaar Jatane Aaye Hain;
Aansu Ponch Liye The Hum Ne Kab Ke;
Magar Woh Fir Se Aaj Hume Rulane Aaye Hain!

 Humein Koi Gham Nahi Tha

Humein Koi Gham Nahi Tha Gham-e-Aashiqui Se Pehle;
Na Thi Dushmani Kisi Se Teri Dosti Se Pehle;

Hai Ye Meri Badnaseebi Tera Kya Kasur Iss Mein;
Tere Gham Ne Maar Dala Mujhe Zindagi Se Pehle;

Mera Pyaar Jal Raha Hai Ai Chand Aaj Chhup Jaa;
Kabhi Pyaar Tha Humein Bhi Teri Chandni Se Pehle;

Main Kabhi Na Muskurata Jo Mujhe Ye Ilm Hota;
Ki Hazaron Gham Milenge Mujhe Ik Khushi Se Pehle;

Ye Ajeeb Imtihan Hai Ki Tum Hi Ko Bhulana Hai;
Mile Kab The Iss Tarah Hum Tumhein Bedili Se Pehle!

 Dard Kitne Hain Bata Nahi Sakta;
Zakhm Kitne Hain Dikha Nahi Sakta;
Aankhon Se Samajh Sako To Samajh Lo;
Aansu Gire Hain Kitne Gina Nahi Sakta!

 Koi Samjhe Na Humko Beshak Par Aap To Samajhte Hain;
Apna Banaate Hain Mere Har Gham Ko Tabhi To Hum Sambhalte Hain;
Khuda Har Ek Khushi De Aapko, Har Ek Gham Humko Naseeb Ho;
Bas Yehi Dil Mein Sochkar Har Ek Dua Karte Hain!

 Raah Aasaan

Raah Aasaan Ho Gayi Hogi;
Jaan Pehchaan Ho Gayi Hogi;

Phir Palat Kar Nigah Naahi Aayi;
Tujh Pe Kurbaan Ho Gayi Hogi;

Teri Zulfon Ko Chedati Thi Saba;
Khud Pareshaan Ho Gayi Hogi;

Maut Se Tere Dardmandon Kee;
Mushkil Aasaan Ho Gayi Hogi;

Un Se Bhi Chheen Loge Yaad Apni;
Jinka Imaan Ho Gayi Hogi!

 Rahega Ishq Tera Khaak Mein Mila Ke Mujhe;
Ki Ibtidaa Mein Hue Ranj Intihaa Ke Mujhe;
Diye Hain Hijar Mein Dukh Dard Kis Balaa Ke Mujhe;
Shab-e-Firaaq Ne Mara Litaa Litaa Ke Mujhe!

 Gar Jo Dil Kee Suno To Haar Jaoge;
Hum Jaisa Pyaar Phir Kaha Se Paoge;
Jaan Dene Kee Baat To Har Koi Karta Hai;
Par Zindagi Banane Wala Kahan Se Laoge!

 Tadapte Hain Din Raat Par Jatate Nahi;
Haal-e-Dil Koi Puche Hum Batate Nahi;
Sunkar Aapko Hogi Hairat Badi Dosto;
Hum Unhe Chahte Hain Jo Hume Chahte Nahi!

 Aaj Tanha Sahi Lekin Kal Manjar Nazar Aayega;
Har Juban Pe Naam Har Nazar Mein Chehra Nazar Aayega;
Mumkin Hai Mujhko Bhi Bhool Jayegi Duniya Lekin;
Dil Mein Tamam Umar Chehra Nazar Aayega!

 Ab Jo Laute Ho

Ab Jo Laute Ho Itne Saalon Mein;
Dhoop Utri Hui Hai Baalon Mein;

Tum Meri Aankh Ke Samandar Mein;
Tum Meri Rooh Ke Ujalon Mein;

Phool Hi Phool Khil Uthe Mujh Mein;
Kaun Aaya Mere Khayalon Mein;

Maine Jee Bhar Ke Tujh Ko Dekh Liya;
Tujh Ko Uljhaa Ke Kuch Sawalon Mein;

Meri Khushiyon Kee Kayenat Bhi Tu;
Tu Hi Dukh Dard Ke Hawalon Mein;

Jab Tera Doston Mein Zikar Aaye;
Theess Uthti Hai Dil Ke Chaalon Mein;

Tum Se Abaad Hai Yeh Tanhai;
Tum Hi Roshan Ho Ghar Ke Jaalon Mein;

Kya Use Yaad Aa Raha Hun 'Wasi';
Rang Ubhre Hain Uss Ke Gaalon Mein!

 Aapki Yaad Dil Ko Bekarar Karti Hai;
Nazar Talash Aapko Bar Bar Karti Hai;
Gila Nahi Jo Hum Hain Door Aapse;
Hamari To Judai Be Aapse Pyaar Karti Hai!

 Apne Dil Ki Sunn, Afwahon Se Kaam Na Le;
Mujhe Yaad Rakh, Beshak Naam Na Le;
Tera Veham Hai Ki Hum Bhool Gaye Tujhe;
Meri Koi Aisi Saans Nahi Jo Tera Naam Na Le!

 Wo Dil Hi Kya
Wo Dil Hi Kya Tere Milne Kee Jo Dua Na Kare;
Main Tujh Ko Bhool Kar Zinda Rahuun Khuda Na Kare;

Rahe Ga SaathTera Pyaar Zindagi Ban Kar;
Ye Aur Baat, Meri Zindagi Wafa Na Kare;

Ye Theek Hai Nahi Marta Koi Judaai Mein;
Khuda Kisi Se Kisi Ko Magar Judaa Na Kare;

Suna Hai Usko Mohabbat Duayein Deti Hain;
Jo Dil Pe Chot To Khaye Magar Gila Na Kare;

Bujha Dia Hai Naseebon Ne Mere Pyaar Ka Chaand;
Koi Dia Meri Palkon Pe Ab Jala Na Kare;

Zamana Dekh Chuka Hai Parakh Chuka Hai;
'Qateel' Jaan Se Jaaye Par Iltijaa Na Kare!

 Andhere Charon Taraf Taraf Sayein Sayein Karne Lage;
Chirag Haath Utha Kar Duayein Karne Lage;
Taraqi Kar Gaye Bimariyon Ke Saudagar;
Yeh Sab Mariz Hain Jo Ab Dawayein Karne Lage!

 Nikle Jab Aansu Uski Aankhon Se;
To Dil Karta Hai Sari Duniya Jala Dun;
Phir Sochta Hun Ki Honge Uske Apne Bhi Iss Duniya Mein
Kahin Anjane Mein Use Phir Se Na Rula Dun!

 Mohabbat Hum Ne Kee To Ek Khata Ho Gayi;
Ki Wafa Aur Zindagi Hi Ab Saza Ho Gayi;
Wafa Karte Rahe Hum Ibadaton Kee Tarah;
Phir Ibadat Bhi Hamare Liye Ek Gunah Ho Gayi!

 Tu Jo Aa Jaye To
Tu Jo Aa Jaye To Iss Ghar Ko Sanwarta Dekhun;
Ek Muddat Se Jo Veeran Hai Wo Basta Dekhun;

Khawab Bankar Tu Behta Rahe Jannat Ke Jharne;
Aur Bas Main Isi Mausam Ko Nikharta Dekhun;

Jis Se Milna Nahi Usse Mohabbat Kaisi;
Sochata Jaaun Magar Dil Mein Utarta Dekhun;

Dil Geya Tha To Ye Aankhen Bhi Koi Le Jaata;
Main Faqat Ek Hi Tasveer Kahan Tak Dekhun;

Chand Lamhe Jo Tere Ishq Ke Mil Jaate Hain;
Inn Hi Lamhon Ko Main Sadiyon Mein Badalta Dekhun!

 Sab Kehte Hain Ki Buri Hai Yeh Sharaab;
Maine Bhi Maana Ki Yeh Sharaab Nasha Chadati Hai;
Fir Puchte Hain Sab Mujhse Ki Kyon Peeta Hun Main;
To Kya Bataun Yaaro Yeh Sharab Hi Hai Jo Unka Gham Bhulati Hai!

 Uss Ke Bin Chup Chup Rehna Ab Achha Lagta Hai;
Khamoshi Se Ek Dard Ko Sehna Bhi Achha Lagta Hai;
Uss Ka Milna Na Milna To Kismat Kee Baat Hai;
Magar Pal Pal Uss Kee Yaad Mein Rona Ab Achha Lagta Hai

 Tujh Ko Paa Kar Bhi Kabhi To Khona Tha;
Ye Hadsa Mere Saath Kabhi To Hona Tha;
Wo Tod Kar Aksar Dil Mera Fir Jodta Raha;
Jaise Main Uss Ke Haath Ka Koi Khilona Tha!

 Dekh Lete Ho Mohabbat Se

Dekh Lete Ho Mohabbat Se Yahi Kaafi Hai;
Dil Dhadakta Hai Sahulat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai;

Haal Duniya Ke Sataye Hue Kuch Logon Ka;
Puch Lete Ho Shararat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai;

Jo Bhi Raaste Mein Guzarta Hai Mere Pehlu Se;
Dekhta Hai Teri Nisbat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai;

Muddatton Se Nahi Dekha Tera Jalwa Lekin;
Yaad Aa Jate Ho Shiddat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai;

Saari Duniya Se Uljhate Hain Lekin Tera Kaha;
Maan Jate Hain Sharafat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai;

Kya Hua Hum Jo Muyassar Jo Zar-o-Maal Nahin;
Katt Rahi Hai Baai Izzat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai;

Aaj Ke Ehad Tagaful Mein Kisi Dar Pe 'Munir';
Koi Aa Jaye Zarurat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai!

 Hum Tere Hijr Mein Andar Se Bikhar Jate Hain;
Zinda Lagte Hain Magar Asal Mein Mar Jate Hain;
Jab Kabhi Bolta Hai Hans Ke Kisi Aur Se Tu;
Kitne Khanjar Mere Seene Mein Utar Jate Hain!

 Tumhara Dukh Hum Seh Nahi Sakte;
Bhari Mehfil Mein Kuch Keh Nahi Sakte;
Humare Girte Hue Aansuon Ko Padh Kar Dekho;
Woh Bhi Kehte Hain Ki Hum Aapke Bin Reh Nahi Sakte!

 Jis Din Meri Arthi Iss Duniya Se Vida Hogi;
Ek Alag Sama Hoga Ek Alag Baat Hogi;
Kehna Uss Bewafa Se Mar Gaye Tumhare Chahne Wale;
Ab Na Hum Hain Aur Na Hamari Batein Hogi!

 Mujhe Khud Se Hain Shikayatein

Mujhe Khud Se Hain Shikayatein, Mujhe Zindagi Se Gila Nahi;
Ki Jo Chaha Maine Woh Paa Liya, Nahi Aisa Kuch Jo Mila Nahi;

Mere Aas Paas Hai Roshni, Mere Raaston Mein Chirag Hain;
Yeh Tere Karam Ka Hai Mojza, Meri Justuju Ka Sila Nahi;

Teri Aankh Se Jo Haseen Ho, Woh Nigah Jag Mein Bani Nahi;
Tere Rukh Ko Jis Se Misaal Doon, Koi Aisa Phool Khila Nahin;

Yeh Jo Teri Zulf Ka Hai Hashiya, Yeh Jo Tera Chehra Khushnuma;
Koi Raat Aisi Siyaah Nahi, Kisi Subah Mein Yeh Jilaa Nahin;

Yeh Jo Mehr-o-Maa Kee Hain Halatein, Yeh Jo Aainon Kee Hain Hairtein;
Hain Azal Se Yeh Isi Tarah, Koi Apni Jaa Se Hila Nahi!

 Karoge Yaad Tum Ki Main Kehta Tha Kabhi;
Daulat Aur Mohabbat Ka, Na Kabhi Bhi Mel Hota Hai;
Hoti Hai Jinke Liye Daulat Hi Sab Se Badhkar;
Unke Liye To Yeh Mohabbat, Bas Ek Khel Hota Hai!

 Humne To Bas Itna Hi Seekha Hai Dosto;
Raah-e-Mohabbat Mein Kabhi Kinara Nahi Milta;
Jo Mil Jaye Iss Raah Par Kabhi Yaar Se;
Woh Zakham Kabhi Fir Dobara Nahi Silta!

 Ajnabi Khauf Fizaon Mein

Ajnabi Khauf Fizaon Mein Basa Ho Jaise;
Shehar Ka Shehar Hi Aseb Zada Ho Jaise;

Raat Ke Pichle Pahar Aati Hain Aawazein Si;
Door Sehra Mein Koi Cheekh Raha Ho Jaise;

Dar-o-Deewar Pe Chayi Hai Udasi Aisi;
Aaj Har Ghar Se Janaza Sa Utha Ho Jaise;

Muskurata Hun Pa-e-Khatir-e-Ahabab Magar;
Dukh To Chehre Kee Lakiron Pe Saja Ho Jaise;

Ab Agar Doob Geya Bhi To Marunga Na 'Kamal'
Bahte Pani Pe Mera Naam Likha Ho Jaise!

 Juda Hai To Kya Hua Doori To Nahi;
Baat Bhi Na Ho Aisi Majboori To Nahi;
Nazar Nahi Aate Ho Aap To Kya Hua;
In Aankhon Mein Tasveer Aapki Adhuri To Nahi!

 Aaj Bhi Kayi Sawal Hain Iss Dil Mein;
Pyaar Ka Gham Bezuban Hai Iss Dil Mein;
Kuch Keh Nahi Paata Ye Dil Magar;
Uss Dil Ke Liye Aaj Bhi Pyaar Hai Iss Dil Mein!

 Lafzon Ke Fasaane Dhoondhte Hain Hum Log;
Lamhon Mein Zamaane Dhoondhte Hain Hum Log;
Tu Zeher Hi De Sharaab Keh Kar Saqi;
Peene Ke Bahaane Dhoondhte Hain Hum Log!

 Mujh Se Kafir Ko

Mujh Se Kafir Ko Tere Ishq Ne Yun Sharmaya;
Dil Tujhe Dekh Ke Dhadka To Khuda Yaad Aaya;

Mere Dil Pe To Hai Ab Tak Tere Gham Ka Saya;
Log Kehte Hain Naya Daur Naye Dukh Laya;

Mera Meyaar-e-Wafaa Hi Meri Majboori Hai;
Rukh Badal Kar Bhi Tujhe Apne Muqabil Paya;

Charagar Aaj Sitaron Kee Kasam Kha Ke Bata;
Kis Ne Insaan Ko Tabasum Ke Liye Tadpaya;

Log Hanste Hain To Iss Soch Mein Kho Jata Hun;
Mauj-e-Sailab Ne Phir Kis Ka Gharaunda Dhaaya;

Uss Ke Andar Koi Fankaar Chupaa Baitha Hai;
Jaante Bhujhte Jis Shakhs Ne Dhokha Khaya!

 Umeedon Ke Daaman Mein Zinda Hain Hum;
Warna Jeene Kee Chahat Kahan;
Tumse Milne Kee Aarzoo Liye Firte Hain Dar-b-Dar;
Warna Is Laash Ke Naseeb Mein Kabar Kahan!

 Mana Ki Pyar Kisi Ka Mere Paas Nahi;
Magar Tumhein Meri Mohabbat Ka Bhi To Ehsaas Nahi;
Jaane Pee Gaye Hum Kitne Gham-e-Aansu;
Ab Kuch Aur Peene Kee Pyaas Nahi!

 Manzilon Se Apni Darr Na Jana;
Raaste Kee Preshaniyon Se Toot Na Jana;
Jab Bhi Zarurat Ho Zindagi Mein Kisi Apne Kee;
Hum Aapke Apne Hain Ye Bhool Na Jana!

 Payaam Aaye Hain

Payaam Aaye Hain Us Yaar-e-Bewafa Ke Mujhe;
Jise Qarar Na Aaya Kahin Bhula Ke Mujhe;

Judaiyan Hon To Aisi Ki Umar Bhar Na Milein;
Fareb Do To Zara Silsile Barha Ke Mujhe;

Nashe Se Kam To Nahi Yaad-e-Yaar Ka Aalam;
Ki Le Udaa Hai Koi Dosh Par Hawa Ke Mujhe;

Main Khud Ko Bhool Chuka Tha Magar Jahan Wale;
Udaas Chorrh Gaye Aaina Dikha Ke Mujhe;

Tumhare Baam Se Ab Kam Nahi Rifat-e-Daar;
Jo Dekhna Ho To Dekho Nazar Utha Ke Mujhe;

Khinchi Hui Hai Mere Aansoun Mein Ek Tasveer;
'Faraz' Dekh Raha Hai Wo Muskura Ke Mujhe!

 Lutf Wo Ishq Mein Paaye Hain Ki Jee Jaanta Hai;
Ranj Bhi Aise Uthaye Hain Ki Jee Jaanta Hai;
Jo Zamane Ke Sitam Hain Wo Zamana Jaane;
Tu Ne Dil Itne Sataye Hain Ki Jee Jaanta Hai!

 Bahut Udaas Hai Koi Shakhs Tere Chale Jaane Se;
Ho Sake To Laut Kar Aaja Kisi Bahaane Se;
Tu Lakh Khafa Sahi Magar Ek Baar To Mud Kar Dekh;
Koi Toot Geya Hai Tere Door Chale Jaane Se!

 Meri Zindagi Ke Raaz Mein Ek Raaz Tum Bhi Ho;
Meri Bandagi Kee Aas Mein Ek Aas Tum Bhi Ho;
Tum Kya Ho Mere, Kuch Ho Ya Kuchh Bhi Nahi Magar;
Meri Zindagi Ke Kaash Mein Ek Kaash Tum Bhi Ho!

 Aarzu Ye Hai Ki Unki Har Nazar Dekha Karen;
Woh Hi Apne Samne Ho, Hum Jidhar Dekha Karen;
Ek Taraf Ho Sari Duniya, Ek Taraf Teri Surat Ho;
Hum Tujhe Duniya Se Hokar Bekhabar Dekha Karen!

 Kabhi Mujh Ko Sath Lekar
Kabhi Mujh Ko Sath Lekar, Kabhi Mere Sath Chal Kar;
Who Badal Gaye Achanak Meri Zindagi Badal Kar;

Hue Jis Pe Meharban Tum Koi Khushnaseeb Hoga;
Meri Hasratein To Nikali Mere Aansuon Mein DhalkKe;

Teri Zulf-o-Rukh Ke Kurban Dil-e-Zar Dhundta Hai;
Wahi Champai Ujale Wahi Surmai Dhundlake;

Koi Phul Ban Geya Hai Koi Chand Koi Tara;
Jo Chirag Bujh Gaye Hain Teri Anjuman Mein Jal Ke;

Mere Dosto Khudara Mere Sath Tum Bhi Dhundo;
Wo Yahin Kahin Chupe Hain Mere Gum Ka Rukh Badal Ke;

Teri Be-Jhijhak Hansi Se Na Kisi Ka Dil Ho Maila;
Ye Nagar Hai Aainon Ka Yahan Saans Le Sambhal Ke!

 Woh Karte Hain Baat Ishq Kee;
Par Ishq Ke Dard Ka Unhe Ehsas Nahi;
Ishq Woh Chand Hai Jo Dikhta Hai Sab Ko;
Par Use Pana Sab Ke Bas Ka Kaam Nahi!

 Shaam Suraj Ko Dhalna Sikhaati Hai;
Shama Parwaane Ko Jalna Sikhaati Hai;
Girne Waale Ko Takleef To Hoti Hai Magar;
Thokar Hi Insaan Ko Chalna Sikhaati Hai!

 Woh Mehndi Wale Haath Mujhe Dikha Kar Royi;
Ab Main Hun Kisi Aur Kee Yeh Mujhe Bata Kar Royi;
Pehle Kehti Thi Ki Nahi Jee Sakti Tere Bin;
Aaj Phir Se Woh Baat Dohra Kar Royi;
Kaise Karun Uski Mohabbat Pe Shak Yaaro;
Woh Bhari Mehfil Mein Mujhe Gale Laga Kar Royi!

 Teri Nigah Ke Jadu

Teri Nigah Ke Jadu Bikharte Jate Hain;
Jo Zakhm Dil Ko Mile Woh Bharte Jate Hain;

Tere Baigair Woh Din Bhi Guzar Gaye Aakhir;
Tere Baigair Ye Din Bhi Guzarte Jate Hain;

Liye Chalo Mujhe Dariya-e-Shauq Kee Maujon;
Ki Humsafar To Mere Paar Utarte Jate Hain;

Tamaam Umar Jahan Hanste Khelte Guzari;
Ab Us Gali Mein Bhi Hum Darte Darte Jate Hain;

Mein Khawhishon Ke Gharaunde Banaye Jata Hun;
Woh Mehnatein Meri Barbad Kiye Jate Hain!

 Uske Intezar Ke Maare Hain Hum;
Bas Uski Yaadon Ke Sahare Hain Hum;
Duniya Jeet Kar Kya Karna Hai Ab;
Jise Duniya Se Jeeta Tha, Aaj Usi Se Haare Hain Hum!

 Zuban Khamosh Aankhon Mein Nami Hogi;
Yahi Bas Ek Daastan Zindagi Ki Hogi;
Bharne Ko To Har Zakhm Bhar Jayega;
Lekin Kaise Bharegi Wo Jagah, Jahan Uski Kami Hogi!

 Baat Karni Mushkil

Baat Karni Mushkil Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;
Jaisi Ab Hai Teri Mehfil Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;

Le Geya Cheen Ke Kaun Aaj Tera Sabr-o-Qarar;
Be Qarari Tujhe Ai Dil Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;

Teri Aankhon Ne Khuda Jane Kya Kya Jadu;
Ki Tabiyat Meri Mayal Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi;

Kya Sbab Tu Jo Bigadta Hai 'Zafar' Se Har Baar;
Kho Teri Hoor Shmail Kabhi Aisi To Na Thi!

 Hum Apne Ikhtiyar Kee Hadh Se Guzar Gaye;
Chaha Tumhein To Pyaar Kee Hadh Se Guzar Gaye;
Jaagi Hai Apne Dil Mein Gulabon Kee Aarzu;
Jab Mausam-e-Bahaar Kee Hadh Se Guzar Gaye!

 Kitni Mushkil Se Kati Kal Kee Meri Raat Na Pooch;
Dil Se Nikli Hui Honthon Mein Dabi Baat Na Pooch;
Main Jiske Liye Ladh Jaun Iss Khudai Se;
Mujhe Khud Se Hai Pyaari Yeh Kiski Zaat Na Pooch!

 Hathon Kee Lakiro Ka Aitbar Kar Lena;
Bharosa Ho To Had Ko Paar Kar Lena;
Khona Pana To Naseebon Ka Khel Hai;
Dil Ko Jo Apna Lage Bas Usi Se Pyaar Kar Lena!

 Hum Se Kya Puchte Ho

Hum Se Kya Puchte Ho Hijar Mein Kya Karte Hain;
Tere Laut Aane Kee Din Raat Dua Karte Hain;

Ab Koi Honth Nahi In Ko Churane Aate;
Meri Aankhon Mein Agar Ashk Hua Karte Hain;

Teri Tu Jane, Par Ai Jane-Tammana Hum To;
Saans Ke Saath Tujhe Yaad Kiya Karte Hain;

Tu Hi Pehlu Mein Nahi Warna December Mein Wahin;
Dhoop Mein Akhbaar Padhaa Karte Hain;

Kabhi Yaadon Mein Tujhe Baahon Mein Bhar Lete Hain;
Kabhi Khawbon Mein Tujhe Chum Liya Karte Hain;

Teri Tasveer Laga Lete Hain Hum Seene Se;
Phir Tere Khat Se Teri Baat Kiya Karte Hain;

Gar Tujhe Chorrne Kee Soch Bhi Aaye Dil Mein;
Hum To Khud Ko Bhi Wahin Chorr Diya Karte Hain!

 Aggar Jawaani Mein Khuda Na Pa Saako;
Tu Chahat Moola Ki Kabhi Kum Nahi Hoti.
Toh Ishq Mein Ho Kar Ek Baar Be-Murawat;
Insaan Ishq Ki Bandagi Kyun Bhool Jata Hai!

 Chirag-e-Wafaa Apne Haath Mein Liye;
Ghumte Rahe Jinke Liye  Hum Raat Bhar;
Aaj Wo Hi Judaa Humse Ho Gaye Hain;
Chal Diye Wo Hi Humse Apna Munh Mod Kar!

 Saza Na Do Muje Bekasur Hoon Main;
Tham Lo Mujh Ko Gamon Se Choor Hoon Main;
Teri Doori Ne Kar Diya Hai Pagal Sa Mujhe;
Aur Logon Ka Kehna Hai Ki Magroor Hoon Main!

 Shaayad Abhi Hai Raakh Mein

Shaayad Abhi Hai Raakh Mein Koi Sharaar Bhi;
Kyon Varna Intezar Bhi Hai Iztiraar Bhi;

Dhyaan Aa Geya Hai Marg-e-Dil-e-Namurad Ka;
Milne Ko Mil Geya Hai Sukun Bhi Qaraar Bhi;

Ab Dhundne Chale Ho Musafir Ko Dosto;
Hadd-e-Nigah Tak Na Raha Jab Gubaar Bhi;

Har Aastaan Pe Nasiya Farsaa Hain Aaj Woh;
Jo Kal Na Kar Sake The Tera Intezar  Bhi;

Ik Raah Ruk Gayi To Thee Thak Kyon Gayi 'Ada';
Aabaad Bastiyan Hain Pahadon Ke Paar Bhi!

 Bewaafa Tum Ho To Wafadaar Hum Bhi Nahi;
Besharam Tum Ho To Sharamsar Hum Bhi Nahi;
Pyaar Ke Iss Maud Par Kehte Ho Ke Shadishuda Ho;
To Kya Hua Darling, Kunware Hum Bhi Nahi!

 Gum Mein Bhi Muskurana Chahta Hu Main;
Ek Nayi Duniya Basana Chahta Hu Main;
Magar Na Jane Kyon Nikal Aate Hain Aansu;
Jab Bhi Tumhein Bhulana Chahta Hu Main!

 Reh Na Pao Ge Kabhi Bhula Kar Dekh Lo;
Yakeen Nahi Aata To Aazma Kar Dekh Lo;
Har Jagah Mehsoos Hogi Kami Hamari;
Apni Mehfil Ko Kitna Bhi Saja Kar Dekh Lo!

 Aashna Ho To
Aashna Ho To Aashna Samjhe;
Ho Jo Na-Aashna To Kya Samjhe;

Hum Isi Ko Bhala Samhhte Hain;
Aapko Jo Koi Bura Samjhe;

Vasal Hai Tu Jo Samjhe Use Vasal;
Tu Judaa Hai Aagr Judaa Samjhe;

Jo Zeher Deve Apne Haath Se Tu;
Tera Bimar-e-Gum Dawa Samjhe;

Ho Wo Baigana Ek Alam Se;
Jisko Apna Wo Dilruba Samjhe;

Ai 'Zafar" Woh Kabhi Na Ho Gumraah;
Jo Mohabbat Ko Rehnuma Samjhe!

 Jo Beet Geya Use Bhool Ja Ai Dil;
Jo Guzar Geya Waqt Woh Kabhi Na Aayega;
Pal Do Pal Ka Saath De Kar Saathi Chala Geya;
Uski Yaad Mein Jal Kar Tu Aur Bhi Pachtayega!

 Aaya Tha Saath Lekar Teri Yaadon Ka Sahara;
Jaa Raha Hu Main Lekar Tere Gum Ka Fasana;
Maar Jayenge Hum Tadapkar Teri Bala Se;
Na Basa Meri Mohabbat Ka Kahin Aashiyana!

 Dekha Jo Tumhe To Mehsus Hua;
Pehchaan Hai Apni Muddat Se;
Khwabon Mein Dekhi Thi Jo Surat;
Milti Hai Tumhari Surat Se!

 Kya Kahun Tum Se Main

Kya Kahun Tum Se Main Ki Kya Hai Ishq;
Jaan Ka Rog Hai, Bala Hai Ishq;

Ishq Hi Ishq Hai Jahan Dekho;
Saare Aalam Mein Bhar Raha Hai Ishq;

Ishq Mashook Ishq Aashiq Hai;
Yani Apna Hi Mubtala Hai Ishq;

Kaun Maksad Ko Ishq Bin Pahuncha;
Aarzoo Ishq Wa Mudda Hai Ishq;

Mir Ji Zarad Hote Jaate Hain;
Kya Kahin Tum Ne Bhi Kiya Hai Ishq!

 Duniya Mein Itni Rasme Kyon Hain;
Pyaar Agar Zindagi Hai To Isme Kasme Kyon Hain;
Humein Batata Kyon Nahi Koi Ye Raaz;
Dil Agar Apna Hai To Ye Kisi Aur Ke Bas Mein Kyon Hai!

 Chehre Kee Har Muskaan Ban Jaata Hai Koi;
Dil Kee Har Dhadkan Ban Jata Hai Koi;
Fir Kaise Jiyenge Ye Zindagi Unke Bin;
Jab Zindagi Jeene Kee Wajah Ban Jata Hai Koi!

 Nasha Zaroori Hai Zindagi Ke Liye;
Par Sirf Sharab Hi Nahi Hai Bekhudi Ke Liye;
Kisi Kee Mast Nigahon Mein Doob Jao;
Bada Haseen Samandar Hai Khudkhushi Ke Liye!

 Iss Se Pehle Ki

Iss Se Pehle Ki Bewafa Ho Jayein;
Kyon Na Ai Dost Hum Judaa Ho Jayein;

Tu Bhi Heere Se Ban Geya Patthar;
Hum Bhei Kal Jaane Kya Se Kya Ho Jayein;

Hum Bhi Majboorion Ka Uzaar Karein;
Phir Kahin Aur Mubtala Ho Jayein;

Ab Ke Gar Tu Mile To Hum Tujhse;
Aise Liptein Teri Qabaa Ho Jayein;

Bandagi Hum Ne Chhod Di Hai 'Faraz';
Kya Karein Jab Log Khudaa Ho Jayein!

 Hamari Har Khushi Ka Ehsaas Tumhara Ho;
Tumhare Har Gum Ka Dard Hamara Ho;
Mar Bhi Jayein To Humein Koi Gum Nahi;
Bas Aakhiri Waqt Saath Tumhara Ho!

 Chup Chap Se Rehte Hain Wo Aksar;
Zulfein Bhi Suna Hai Ki Sanwara Nahi Karte;
Din Raat Guzarte Hain Un Ke Be-Chain Se;
To Chain Se Hum Bhi Guzara Nahi Karte!

 Aap Kew Nigah Agar Meharban Ho Jaye;
Main Jis Zameen Pe Hun Wo Aasman Ho Jaye;
Hai Ab Bhi Aap Ko Shak Mere Ishq Par;
To Phir Ek Baar Mera Imtihan Ho Jaye!

 Socha Nahi Achha Bura

Socha Nahi Achha Bura Dekha Suna Kuch Bhi Nahi;
Manga Khuda Se Raat Din Tere Siwa Kuch Bhi Nahi;

Dekha Tujhe Socha Tujhe Chaha Tujhe Puja Tujhe;
Meri Khata Meri Wafa Teri Khata Kuch Bhi Nahi;

Jis Par Hamari Aankh Ne Moti Bichaye Raat Bhar;
Bheja Wahi Kagaz Use Hum Ne Likha Kuch Bhi Nahi;

Ek Sham Kee Dehleez Par Baithe Rahe Wo Der Tak;
Aankhon Se Kee Baatein Bahut Munh Se Kaha Kuch Bhi Nahi;

Do Chaar Din Kee Baat Hai Dil Khak Mein So Jayega;
Jab Aag Par Kagaz Rakha Baki Bacha Kuch Bhi Nahi;

Ehsaas Kee Khushbu Kahan, Aawaz Ke Jugnu Kahan;
Khamosh Yaadon Ke Siwa, Ghar Mein Raha Kuch Bhi Nahi!

 Tujhse Bichad Kar Kya Hun Main, Ab Bahar Aakar Dekh;
Himmat Hai To Meri Haalat, Aankh Mila Kar Dekh;
Shaam Hai Gehri, Tez Hawa Hai, Sar Pe Khadi Hai Raat;
Raasta Gaye Musafir Ka Ab Diya Jalaa Kar Dekh!

 Gum Ye Nahi Ki Kasam Apni Bhulai Tum Ne;
Gum To Ye Hai Ke Raqeebon Se Nibhai Tum Ne;
Koi Ranjish Thi Agar Tum Ko To Mujh Se Keh Dete;
Baat Apas Ki Kyon Sab Ko Batai Tum Ne!

 Jane Kis Baat Kee Mujhko Saza Deta Hai;
Meri Hansti Hui Aankhon Ko Rula Deta Hai;
Ek Muddat Se Khabar Bhi Nahi Teri;
Koi Iss Tarah Bhi Kya Apne Pyaar Ko Bhula Deta Hai!

 Mujh Ko Baigana Kar Gaye

Mujh Ko Baigana Kar Gaye Mere Din;
Mujh Se Ho Kar Guzar Gaye Mere Din;

Ab Na Koi Din Mere Ghar Jaye Ga;
Jaane Kis Ke Ghar Gaye Mere Din;

Ab Nahi Hain Mere Koi Din Raat;
Ki Mujh Hee Ko Basar Gaye Mere Din;

Saari Raatein Gayin Meri Be-Haal;
Mere Din, Be-Asar Gaye Mere Din;

Khosha Ab Intezar Hai Na Umeed;
Yaar Yaaran, Sudhar Gaye Ab Din;

Ab Main Bas Reh Geya Hun Raaton Mein;
Mar Gaye 'Jon' Mar Gaye Mere Din!

 Chandni Raat Badi Der Ke Baad Aayi;
Yeh Mulaqat Badi Der Ke Baad Aayi;
Aaj Aaye Hain Woh Milne Ko Badi Der Ke Baad;
Aaj Kee Raat Badi Der Ke Baad Aayi!

 Hasraton Se Aapki Raah Sajaa Denge;
Sapno Kee Daulat Aap Par Luta Denge;
Na Hai Koi Phool Aaj Mere Damaan Mein;
Lekin Aapke Aane Par Palkein Bichha Denge!

 Majbooriyon Ko Hum Palkon Mein Chhupa Lete Hain;
Hum Kahan Rote Hain Bas Yeh Halaat Rula Dete Hain;
Hum To Har Pal Yaad Karte Hain Sirf Aapko;
Aur Woh Hi Hum Par Yaad Na Karne Ka Ilzam Laga Dete Hain!

 Wo Mujhe Chaahti Hai Par Apna Nahi Sakti;
Mujhe Bhulane Ka Dard Utha Nahi Sakti;
Ajeeb Hai Uske Pyaar Ka Ye Andaz Bhi;
Khafa To Karti Hai Par Manaa Nahi Sakti!

 Ye Dil Bhulata Nahi Hai

Ye Dil Bhulata Nahi Hai Mohabbatein Uski;
Padi Hui Thee Mujhe Kitni Aadatein Uski;

Ye Mera Sara Safar Uski Khushbu Mein Kata;
Mujhe To Raah Dikhaati Thee Chahatein Uski;

Ghiri Hui Hun Main Chehron Ki Bheed Mein Lekin;
Kahin Nazar Nahi Aati Shabahatein Uski;

Main Dard Se Rone Lagi Hun To Aisa Lagta Hai;
Ki Chhaon Jaisi Thee Mujh Par Rafaqatein Uski;

Ye Kis Gali Mein Ye Kis Shehar Mein Nikal Aaye;
Kahan Pe Reh Gayi Logon Sadaqatein Uski;

Main Barishon Mein Juda Ho Gayi Hun Us Se Magar;
Ye Mera Dil, Meri Sansein Amanatein Uski!

 Tum Se Kab Humne Mulaqat Ka Vaada Chaha;
Door Reh Kar Tujhe Kuch Aur Bhi Jyada Chaha;
Yaad Aayi Hai Teri Aur Bhi Shiddat Se Humein;
Bhool Jaane Ka Tujhe Jab Bhi Iraada Chaha!

 Koi Dhokha Nahi Aisa Jo Na Khaya Hum Ne;
Zindagi Bhar Tera Saath Nibhaya Hum Ne;
Kabhi Mehnat Ka Silaa Apni To Paya Hi Nahin;
Chaaon Auron Ko Mili Pedh Lagaya Hum Ne!

 Naseeb Aazmane Ke Din

Naseeb Aazmane Ke Din Aa Rahe Hain;
Kareeb Un Ke Aane Ke Din Aa Rahe Hain;

Jo Dil Se Kaha Hai Jo Dil Se Suna Hai;
Sab Un Ko Sunane Ke Din Aa Rahe Hain;

Abhi Se Dil-o-Jaan Sar-e-Raah Rakh Do;
Ki Lutne Lutaane Ke Din Aa Rahe Hain;

Tapakne Lagi Un Nigaahon Se Masti;
Nigahein Churane Ke Din Aa Rahe Hain;

Saba Phir Humein Puchti Phir Rahi Hai;
Chaman Ko Sajane Ke Din Aa Rahe Hain;

Chalo 'Faiz' Phir Se Kahin Dil Lagyein;
Suna Hai Thikaane Ke Din Aa Rahe Hain!

 Tere Chehre Ne Kuch Aisa Gazab Dhaya Hai;
Ki Tere Husn Se Aaj Chand Bhi Sharmaya Hai;
Maang Lete Tumhein Aaj Uss Khuda Se;
Par Tere Samne Aaj Woh Bhi Tera Ghulam Nazar Aaya Hai!

 Uski Aankhon Mein Koi Dard Basa Hai Shayad;
Ya Mujhe Khud Hi Veham Sa Hua Hai Shayad;
Maine Pucha Ki Bhool Gaye Ho Kya Tum Bhi;
Ponch Kar Aansu Usne  Bhi Keh Diya, Haan Shayad!

 Sukoon Apne Dil Ka Maine Kho Diya Hai;
Khud Ko Dard Ke Samandar Mein Dubo Diya Hai;
Jo Thi Kabhi Mere Muskurane Ki Wajah;
Aaj Uski Kami Ne Meri Palko Ko Bhigo Diya Hai!

 Tumhare Khat Mein Naya Ek

Tumhare Khat Mein Naya Ek Salaam Kiska Tha;
Na Tha Raqeeb To Aakhir Woh Naam Kiska Tha;

Raha Na Dil Mein Woh Bedard Aur Dard Raha;
Muqeem Kaun Hua Hai Maqaam Kiska Tha;

Wafa Karenge Nibhayenge Baat Maanege;
Tumhe Bhi Yaad Hai Kuch Ye Kalaam Kiska Tha;

Woh Katl Karke Har Kisi Se Puchte Hain;
Yeh Kaam Kisne Kiya Yeh Kaam Kiska Tha;

Guzar Geya Woh Zamana Kahein To Kis Se Kahein;

Khyaal Dil Ko Mere Subah-o-Shaam Kiska Tha;

Har Ek Se Kehte Hain Kya 'Daag' Bewafa Nikala;

Ye Puche Inse Koi Woh Ghulam Kiska Tha!

 Chahat Mein Dubne Ka Haq Sabhi Ko Hai;
Par Duniya Ke Samne Inkar Sabhi Ko Hai;
Beshak Koi Chupa Le Dil Kee Gehraiyon Mein;
Par Kisi Na Kisi Se To Pyar Sabhi Ko Hai!

 Uski Khamoshi Se Darr Lagta Hai;
Door Na Ho Jaye Mujhse Aisa Kyon Lagta Hai;
Duniya Se Use Cheen Lene Ka Hausla Hai Mujh Mein;
Lekin Woh Saath Na Dega Aisa Kyon Lagta Hai!

 Raat Ke Khwab Sunayein Kis Ko

Raat Ke Khwab Sunayein Kis Ko Raat Ke Khwab Suhane The;
Dhoodhle Dhoodhle Chehre The Par Sab Jaane Pahchane The;

Ziddi Wahshi Alhar Chanchal Meethe Log Raseele Log;
Honth Un Ke Ghazalon Ke Misre Aankhon Mein Afsane The;

Yeh Ladki To Inn Galiyon Mein Roz Hi Ghuuma Karti Thi;
Iss Se Un Ko Milna Tha To Iss Ke Lakh Bahane The;

Hum Ko Sari Raat Jagaya Jalte Bujhte Taron Ne;
Hum Kyon Un Ke Dar Pe Utre Kitne Aur Thikane The;

Vahshat Kee Unvaan Humari In Mein Se Jo Naar Bani;
Dekhenge To Log Kahenge 'Insha' Ji Deewane The!

 Unki Yaadon Ko Abhi Bhi Seene Mein Chhupaye Baitha Hun;
Haye Main Kis Zalim Se Dil Ko Lagaye Baitha Hun;
Inhi Raahon Se Aayenge, Bhale Hee, Baad Mere Marne Ke;
Kitna Nadan Hun Abhi Bhi Dil Ko Samjhaye Baitha Hun!

 Kisko Farebi Hum Kahein Kisko Kahein Hum Bewafa;
Kismat Hi Shayad Aisi Likha Kar Laaye Hain Hum;
Aaj Wakif Hai Yaaro Humse Shehar Ka Har Ek Aadmi;
Magar Apno Ke Liye Hi Dekhiye Paraye Hain Hum!

 Zamane Wale Mil Gaye Hain Sabhi Ek Doosre Se;
Milkar Sabhi Ne Mujh Akele Ko Mara Hai;
Tu Bhi Mat Ho Jana Bewafa Sabhi Kee Tarah;
Ai Mere Dost Iss Dil Ko Bas Tera Sahara Hai!

 Bedili Se Hansne Ko

Bedili Se Hansne Ko Khush-Dili Na Samjha Jaye;
Gum Se Jalte Chehre Ko Roshni Na Samjha Jaye;

Gaha Gaha Wahshat Mein Ghar Kee Simt Jata Hun;
Isko Dasht-e-Hairat Se Wapsi Na Samjha Jaye;

Lakh Khushguman Duniya Vehmi Talluq Ko;
Dosti Kahe Lekin Dosti Na Samjha Jaye;

Hum To Bas Ye Kehte Hain Roz Jeene Marne Ko;
Aap Chahein Kuch Samjhein Zindagi Na Samjha Jaye;

Khak Karne Walon Kee Kya Ajeeb Khwahish Thi;
Khak Hone Walon Ko Khak Hi Na Samjha Jaye!

 Hai Agar Hamari Koi Khata Tu Sabit To Kar;
Agar Bure Hain Hum To Bura Saabit To Kar;
Tujhe Chaha Hai Humne Kitna, Tu Kya Jane;
Chal Hum Bewafa Hi Sahi, Tu Apni Wafa Sabit To Kar!

 Rone Kee Saza Na Rulane Kee Saza Hai;
Ye Dard Mohabbat Ko Nibhane Kee Saza Hai;
Hanste Hain To Aankhon Se Nikal Aate Hain Aansu;
Ye Us Shakhs Se Dil Lagane Kee Saza Hai!

 Log Har Mod Par Ruk-Ruk Ke

Log Har Mod Par Ruk-Ruk Ke Sambhalte Kyon Hain;
Itna Darte Hain To Phir Ghar Se Nikalte Kyon Hain;

Main Na Juganu Hun Na Diya Hun Na Koi Tara Hun;
Roshni Wale Mere Naam Se Jalte Kyon Hain;

Neend Se Mera Taluq Hi Nahi Barson Se;
Khwab Aa-Aa Ke Meri Chhat Pe Tehalte Kyon Hain;

Mod To Hota Hai Jawani Ka Sambhalne Ke Liye;
Aur Sab Log Yahin Aakar Phisalte Kyon Hain!

 Had Kee Had Se Guzrna Koi Aapse Seekhe;
Yun Mohabbat Mein Jaan Lutana Koi Aapse Seekhe;
Hum To Dil Dekar Bhi Aapke Ho Na Sake;
Dil Ko Dil Se Churana Koi Aapse Seekhe!

 Aankho Ke Ishare Samajh Nahi Pate;
Hontho Se Dil Kee Baat Keh Nahi Pate;
Apni Bebasi Hum Kis Tarah Kahe;
Koi Hai Jiske Bina Hum Reh Nahi Pate!

 Abke Khafa Hua Hai Itna

Abke Khafa Hua Hai Itna Khafa Bhi Ho;
Tu Bhi Ho Aur Tujh Mein Koi Doosra Bhi Ho;

Aankh Na Chheen Meri Nakabe Badlata Chal;
Yun Ho Ki Tu Karib Bhi Ho Aur Juda Bhi Ho;

Rishton Ke Registan Mein Har Sar Par Dhoop Hai;
Har Paanv Mein Safar Hai Magar Raasta Bhi Ho;

Duniya Ke Kehne Sunane Par Insaniyat Na Chhod;
Insan Hai Toh Saath Mein Koi Khata Bhi Ho!

 Kabhi Unki Yaad Aati Hai Kabhi Unke Khawab Aate Hain;
Mujhe Satane Ke Saleeke To Unhe Behisab Aate Hain;
Qayamat Dekhni Ho Agar Chale Jana Kisi Mehfil Mein;
Suna Hai Ki Mehfil Mein Woh Be-Naqab Aate hain!

 Kayi Sadiyon Mein Aati Hai Koi Soorat Haseen Itni;
Husn Par Har Roz Kahan Aise Shabab Aate Hain;
Roshni Ke Waaste To Unka Noor Hi Kaafi Hai;
Unke Deedaar Ko Aaftab Aur Mehtaab Aate Hain!

 Churi Kee Nok Se Zakhmo Pe Wo Marham Lagate Hain;
Zakham Bhi Khud Hee Dete Hain Khud Hee Aansu Bahate Hain;
Yeh Kaisa Pyaar Hai Unka Koi To Humko Samjhao;
Sitamgar Hain Ya Hain Dilbar Woh Jo Yaad Aate Hain!

 Dil Ke Dariya Ko

Dil Ke Dariya Ko Kisi Roz Utar Jana Hai;
Itna Besimt Na Chal Laut Ke Ghar Jana Hai;

Uss Tak Aati Hai To Har Cheez Thehar Jati Hai;
Jaise Pana Hi Use Asal Mein Mar Jana Hai;

Bol Ai Sham-e-Safar Rang-e-Rihai Kya Hai;
Dil Ko Rukna Hai Ki Taron Mein Thehar Jana Hai;

Kaun Ubharte Hue Mehtab Ka Raasta Roke;
Uss Ko Har Taur Su-e-Dasht-e-Sehar Jana Hai;

Main Khila Hun To Isi Khak Mein Milna Hai Mujhe;
Wo To Khushbu Hai Use Agle Nagar Jana Hai;

Wo Tere Husn Ka Jadu Ho Ki Mera Gum-e-Dil;
Har Musafir Ko Isi Ghat Utar Jana Hai!

 Tanhai Mein Hum Teri Taakte Hain Raahein;
Tumhe Dekhne Ko Taras Jati Hain Nigahein;
Bekhudi Ka Ab Yeh Aalam Hai Kaisa;
Tumhe Yaad Karke Nikal Jati Hain Aahein!

 Bhale Hi Raah Chalton Ka Daaman Tu Tham Le;
Magar Mere Pyaar Ko Bhi Tu Kabhi Pehchan Le;
Kitna Intezar Kiya Hai Tere Ishq Mein Humne;
Zara Yeh Dill Kee Betaabi Ko Bhi Tu Kabhi Jaan Le!

 Din Beet Jate Hain Suhani Yaadein Banker;
Baatein Reh Jati Hain Kahani Bankar;
Par Pyaar To Hamesha Dil Ke Kareeb Rahega;
Kabhi Muskaan To Kabhi Aankhon Mein Pani Bankar!

 Ret Par Likh Kar Mera Naam

Ret Par Likh Kar Mera Naam Mitaya Na Karo;
Aankhein Sach Bolti Hain Pyaar Chupaya Na Karo;

Log Har Baat Ka Afsaana Banaa Lete Hain;
Sab Ko Rudaad-e-Gham-e-Ishq Sunaaya Na Karo;

Yeh Zaroori Nahi Har Shaks Maseeha Hi Ho;
Pyaar Ke Zakham Amaanat Hain Dikhaya Na Karo;

Shehar-e-Ehsaas Mein Pathraao Bahut Hai 'Mohsin';
Dil Ko Sheeshe Ke Jharokon Mein Sajaaya Na Karo!

 Khoobsurat Hai Zindagi Khwaab Kee Tarha;
Jaane Kab Toot Jaaye Kaanch Kee Tarha;
Mujhe Na Bhoolna Kisi Baat Kee Tarha;
Apne Dil Mein Hi Rakhna Khoobsurat Yaad Kee Tarha!

 Woh Paas Aate To Hum Baat Kar Lete;
Wo Sath Rehte To Hum Pyaar Kar Lete;
Kya Majburi Rahi Jo Woh Chale Gaye;
Wajah To Batate Hum Intezar Kar Lete!

 Duniya Ke Sitam Yaad

Duniya Ke Sitam Yaad Na Apni Wafa Yaad;
Ab Mujh Ko Nahi Kuch Bhi Mohabbat Ke Siwa Yaad;

Main Shikwa Ba Lab Tha, Mujhe Yeh Na Bhi Raha Yaad;
Shayad Ke Mere Bhoolne Waalay Ne Kiya Yaad;

Kya Jaaniye Kya Ho Geya Arbaab-e-Junoon Ko;
Jeene Kee Adaa Yaad Na Marne Ki Adaa Yaad;

Kya Lutf Ki Main Apna Pata Aap Bataaun;
Kijiye Koi Bhooli Hui Khaas Apni Adaa Yaad;

Muddat Hui Ek Hadsa-e-Ishq Ko Lekin;
Ab Tak Hai Tere Dil Ke Dhadakne Kee Sadaa Yaad!

 Fursat Mili Jab Humko To Tanhai Aa Gayi;
Ghum Bhi Aaya Saath Mein Ruswai Aa Gayi;
Inn Sab Se Milne Aankhon Se Aansu Bhi Aa Gaye;
Jab Yaad Mere Dil Ko Teri Judai Aa Gayi!

 Ghum Ye Nahi Ki Kasam Apni Bhulai Tum Ne;
Ghum To Ye Hai Ki Raqeebon Se Nibhai Tum Ne;
Koi Ranjish Thi Agar Tum Ko To Mujh Se Keh Deta;
Baat Aapas Kee Kyon Sab Ko Batai Tum Ne!

 Tum Haqeeqat Nahi Ho Hasrat Ho;
Jo Mile Khawab Mein Wahi Daulat Ho;
Kis Liye Dekhti Ho Tum Yeh Aaina;
Tum To Khud Se Bhi Jyada Khoobsurat Ho!

 Apna Hissa Shumar

Apna Hissa Shumar Karta Tha;
Mujhse Itna Woh Pyaar Karta Tha;

Woh Banata Tha Meri Tasveerein;
Unse Batein Hazaar Karta Tha;

Mera Dukh Bhi Khuloos-e-Niyat Se;
Apna Dukh Hi Shumar Karta Tha;

Such Samjhta Tha Jhooth Bhi Mera;
Yun Mera Aitbaar Karta Tha;

Pehle Rakhta Tha Phool Raaste Mein;
Phir Mera Intezar Karta Tha;

Aaj Pehlu Mein Wo Nahi 'Faraz';
Jo Mujh Pe Jaan Nisaar Karta Tha!

 Hum Hain Sukhe Hue Talab Pe Baithe Hue Hans;
Jo Talluq Ko Nibhate Hue Mar Jate Hain;
Ye Mohabbat Kee Kahani Nahi Marti Lekin;
Log Kirdar Nibhate Hue Mar Jate Hain!

 Tamanna Se Nahi Tanhayi Se Darte Hain;
Pyaar Se Nahi Ruswayi Se Darte Hain;
Milne Kee Chahat To Bahut Hai Magar;
Milan Ke Baad Kee Judai Se Darte Hain!

 Chahat Kee Raah Mein Bikhre Aarmaan Bahut Hain;
Hum Uski Yaad Mein Pareshan Bahut Hain;
Woh Har Baar Dil Todta Hai Ye Keh Kar Ki;
Meri Ummedon Kee Duniya Mein Abhi Mukaam Bahut Hain!

 Kahan Se Laun Hunar Use Manane Ka;
Koi Jawab Nahi Tha Uske Rooth Jane Ka;
Mohabbat Mein Saza Mujhe Hi Milni Thi;
Kyonki Jurm Maine Kiya Tha Usse Dil Lagane Ka!

 Tujhse Bichad Kar Kya Hun Main

Tujhse Bichad Kar Kya Hun Main, Ab Bahar Aakar Dekh;
Himmat Hai To Meri Haalat, Aankh Mila Kar Dekh;

Shaam Hai Gehri, Tez Hawa Hai, Sar Pe Khadi Hai Raat;
Raasta Gaye Musafir Ka Ab Diya Jalaa Kar Dekh;

Darwaze Ke Paas Aa Aa Kar Wapis Mudti Chaap;
Kaun Hai Iss Sunsaan Gali Mein, Paas Bula Kar Dekh;

Shayad Koi Dekhne Wala Ho Jaye Khairaan;
Kamre Kee Deewaron Par Koi Naqsh Bana Kar Dekh;

Tu Bhi 'Munir' Ab Bhare Jahaan Mein Mil Kar Rehna Seekh;
Bahar Se To Dekh Liya, Ab Andar Ja Kar Dekh!

 Na Jaane Wo Humse Kya Chhupati Thi;
Kuch Tha Zaroor Uske Payyare Se Hontho Pe;
Magar Na Jaane Kyon Humse Sharmati Thi;
Jab Munh Khulwaya Tab Jakar  Maloom Huya;
Saali Chup-Chup Paan Masala Chabati Thi!

 Kuch Likh Nahi Paate Kuch Suna Nahi Paate;
Haal-e-Dil Zuban Pe La Nahi Paate;
Woh Utar Gaye Hain Dil Kee Gehraiyon Mein;
Woh Samjh Nahi Paate, Hum Samjha Nahi Paate!

 Izhar Mohabbat Ka Kuch Aise Hua;
Kya Kahein Ki Pyaar Kaise Hua;
Unki Ek Jhalak Pe Nisaar Hue Hum;
Saadgi Pe Mar-Mite Aur Aankho Se Iqraar Hua!

 Bahut Ho Chuka Intezar Unka;
Ab Aur Zakham Sahe Jaate Nahi;
Kya Bayaan Karein Unke Sitam Ko;
Dard Unke Ab Kahe Jaate Nahi!

 Mujh Ko Baigana

Mujh Ko Baigana Kar Gaye Mere Din;
Mujh Se Ho Kar Guzar Gaye Mere Din;

Ab Na Koi Din Mere Ghar Jayega;
Jaanae Kis Ke Ghar Gaye Mere Din;

Ab Nahi Hain Mere Koi Din Raat;
Ki Mujh Hee Ko Bisaar Gaye Mere Din;

Saari Raatein Gayin Meri Be-Haal;
Mere Din Be-Asar Gaye Mere Din;

Khosha Ab Intezar Hai Na Umeed;
Yaar Yaaran Sudhar Gaye Ab Din;

Ab Main Bas Reh Gaya Hun Raaton Mein
Mar Gaye 'Jon' Mar Gaye Mere Din!

 Koi Kehta Hai Pyaar Nasha Ban Jata Hai;

Koi Kehta Hai Pyaar Saza Ban Jata Hai;

Lekin Agar Pyaar Karo Sache Dil Se To;

Pyaar Jeene Kee Wajah Ban Jata Hai!

 Mila Wo Bhi Nahi Karte Mila Hum Bhi Nahi Karte;
Gila Wo Bhi Nahi Karte Shikwa Hum Bhi Nahi Karte;
Yeh Bhi Such Hai Mohabbat Unko Bhi Hai Mohabbat Humko Bhi Hai;
Izhar Wo Bhi Nahi Karte Iqrar Hum Bhi Nahi Karte!

 Ai Kaash Tujhe Aisa

Ai Kaash Tujhe Aisa Ik Zakhm-e-Judaai Dun;
Jab Tees Koi Chamke Main Tujhko Dikhayi Dun;

Jis Roz Kabhi Tera Deedaar Na Ho Paaye;
Main Apni Hee Aankhon Ko Naabeena Dikhayi Dun;

Magroor Hai Tu Kitna Sirf Ik Sanam Ban Kar;
Tu Chahe To Main Tujhko Tan Man Kee Khudai Dun;

Tujh Sa Koi Dil Wala Mehsoos Kare Mujhko;
Main Geet Nahi Aisa Jo Sab Ko Sunayi Dun;

Ik Umar Ke Baad Apne Chit Chor Ko Pakda Hai;
Main Kaise Qateel Usko Baahon Se Rihayi Dun!

 Maine Har Gum Ko Hans Kar Utha Liya;
Raaz Teri Bewafai Ka Sabse Chhipa Liya;
Mujhko To Teri Wafaon Par Yakin Tha;
Na Jane Kyon Tumne Apna Daman Chhuda Liya!

 Bina Bataye Usne Na Jaane Kyon Yeh Doori Kar Di;
Bichhad Ke Usne Mohabbat Hi Adhuri Kar Di;
Mere Muqaddar Mein Gum Aaye To Kya Hua;
Khuda Ne Uski Khwaish To Puri Kar Di!

 Zindagi Ke Har Lamhon Mein Unhi Ko Paate Hain;
Bhool Jayein Khud Ko Par Unhe Nahi Bhulate Hain;
Jane Kya Baat Hai Unme Ai Khuda;
Jitna Bhulate Hain Wo Utna Yaad Aate Hain!

 Kahan Dil Qaid Se

Kahan Dil Qaid Se Chhoota Hua Hai;
Abhi Tak Shehar Se Rootha Hua Hai;

Hum Kaise Kahe Iss Dil Ko Sacha;
Hamare Samne Jhoota Hua Hai;

Ksi Ka Kuch Nahi Yahan Par;
Yeh Sab Samaan Loota Hua Hai;

Tumhare Dil Mein Meri Chahaton Ka;
Koi To Beej Sa Phoota Hua Hai;

Kisi Ke Naam Lag Jaayein Balaa Se;
Yeh Dil Phele Se Hee Toota Hua Hai!

 Safar Mohabbt Ka Dushwar Kitna Hai;
Magar Dekhna Hai Ki Koi Wafadar Kitna Hai;
Yahi Soch Kar Use Kabhi Manga Nahi Maine;
Use Parakhna Hai Ki Wo Mera Talbgar Kitna Hai!

 Iss Janam Vich Karan Pyaar Inha;
Ki Har Janam Vich Mil Jave Tera Sath Mainu;
Inhe Sajde Karan Main Rabb Agge;
Har Janam Vich Naseeb Hove Tera Pyaar Mainu!

 Kya Kya Hamare Khwab The

Kya Kya Hamare Khwab The, Jane Kahan Pe Kho Gaye;
Tum Bhi Kisi Ke Sath Ho, Hum Bhi Kisi Ke Ho Gaye;

Jaane Woh Kyon The, Kaun The Aaye The Kis Liye Yahan;
Woh Jo Fashaar-e-Waqt Mein, Bojh Sa Ek Dho Gaye;

Uss Ki Nazar Ne Yun Kiya Gard-e-Malal-e-Jaan Ko Saaf;
Abar Baras Ke Jis Tarah, Sare Chaman Ko Dho Gaye;

Katne Se Aur Badhti Hai Uthe Hue Sarun Ki Fasal;
Apne Lahu Se Ahl-e-Dil, Beej Yeh kaise Bo Gaye;

Jin Ke Bagair Ik Pal, Jeena Bhi Muhaal Tha;
Shaklein Bhi Unn Kee Bujh Gayin, Naam Bhi Unn Ke Kho Gaye;

Ankhon Mein Bhar Ke Rut Jaage, Raston Ko De Ke Dooriyan;
'Amjad' Woh Apne Humsafar, Kaise Maze Se So Gaye!

 Pyaar Kisi Se Jo Karoge Ruswai Hi Milegi;
Wafa Kar Lo Chahe Jitni, Bewafai Hi Milegi;
Jitna Bhi Kisi Ko Apna Bana Lo;
Jab Aankh Khulegi Tanhayi Hi Milegi!

 Meri Chahatein Tumse Alag Kab Hain;
Dil Kee Baatein Tumse Chupi Kab Hain;
Tum Saath Raho Dil Mein Dhadkan Kee Jagah;
Phir Zindagi Ko Saanson Kee Zarurat Kab Hai!

 Tadap Ke Dekh Kisi Kee Chahat Mein;
To Pata Chale Intezar Kya Hota Hai;
Yun Hi Mil Jaye Agar Koi Bina Tadpe;
To Kaise Pata Chale Pyaar Kya Hota Hai!

 Ashk Aankh Mein

Ashk Aankh Mein Phir Atak Raha Hai;
Kankar Sa Koi Khatak Raha Hai;

Main Uss Ke Khayaal Se Gurezaan;
Wo Meri Sadaa Jhatak Raha Hai;

Tehreer Ussi Ki Hai, Magar Dil;
Khat Padhte Hue Atak Raha Hai;

Hain Phone Pe Kis Ke Saath Baatein;
Aur Zehen Kahan Bhatak Raha Hai;

Sadiyon Se Safar Mein Hai Samandar;
Sahil Pe Thakan Tapak Raha Hai!

 Pehli Bar Zindagi Mein Humne Chaha Hai Jisko;
Unse Humne Apne Pyaar Ka Izhaar Kar Diya;
Ab Woh Apne Dil Ko Beqarar Karein Ya Na Karein;
Magar Humne Toh Apne Dil Ko Beqarar Kar Diya!

 Dil Mein Umeed Kee Shama Jala Rakhi Hai;
Humne Apni Alag Duniya Basa Rakhi Hai;
Iss Umeed Ke Saath Ki Aayega Kabhi Paigam Aapka;
Humne To Har Pal Darwaze Par Nazrein Tika Rakhi Hain!

 Ek Katra Malal Bhi

Ek Katra Malal Bhi Boya Nahi Geya;
Woh Khauf Ki Logon Se Roya Nahi Geya;

Yeh Sach Hai Ki Teri Bhi Neendein Ujad Gayi;
Tujh Se Bichhad Ke Hum Se Bhi Soya Nahi Gaya;

Uss Raat Tu Bhi Pehle Sa Apna Nahi Laga;
Uss Raat Khul Ke Mujhse Bhi Roya Nahi Geya;

Daman Hai Khushk Aankh Bhi Chupchap Hai Bahut;
Ladiyon Mein Aansuon Ko Piroya Nahi Geya;

Alfaz Talkh, Baat Ka Andaaz Sard Hai;
Pichla Malal Aaj Bhi Goya Nahi Geya;

Ab Bhi Kahin Kahin Pe Kalikh Lagi Hui;
Ranjish Ka Daag Theek Se Dhoya Nahi Geya!

 Chaahat Ke Yeh Kaise Afsane Hue;
Khud Nazron Mein Apni Begane Hue;
Kisi Bhi Rishte Ka Khayal Nahi Mujhe;
Ishq Mein Tere Iss Kadar Deewane Hue!

 Sab Fasane Hain Duniya Daari Ke;
Kis Ne Kis Ka Sukoon Loota Hai;
Sach To Yeh Hai Ki Iss Zamane Mein;
Main Bhi Jhootha Hun Tu Bhi Jhootha Hai!

 Ye Dil Bhulata Nahi

Ye Dil Bhulata Nahi Hai Mohabbatein Uski;
Padi Hui Thee Mujhe Kitni Aadatein Uski;

Yeh Mera Sara Safar Uski Khushbu Mein Kata;
Mujhe To Raah Dikhaati Thee Chahatein Uski;

Ghiri Hui Hun Mein Chehron Kee Bheed Mein Lekin;
Kahin Nazar Nahi Aati Shabahatein Uski;

Main Dard Se Rone Lagi Hun To Aisa Lagta Hai;
Ki Chhaon Jaisi Thee Mujh Par Rafaqatein Uski;

Yeh Kis Gali Mein Ye Kis Shehar Mein Nikal Aaye;
Kahan Pe Reh Gayi Logo Sadaqatein Uski;

Main Barishon Mein Juda Ho Gayi Hun Us Se Magar;
Yeh Mera Dil, Meri Sansein Amanatein Uski!

 Agar Yakeen Hota Ki Kehne Se Ruk Jayenge;

Toh Hum Bhi Hanskar Unko Pukaar Lete;

Magar Naseeb Ko Yeh Manzoor Nahi Tha;
Ki Hum Bhi Do Pal Khushi Se Guzar Lete!

 Mahekta Hua Jism Tera Gulab Jaisa Hai;

Neend Ke Safar Mein Tu Khwaab Jaisa Hai;

Do Ghoont Pee Lene De Aankhon Kee Mastiyan;

Nasha Teri Aankhon Ka Sharab Ke Jaam Jaisa Hai!

 Pani Aankh Mein Bhar Kar
Pani Aankh Mein Bhar Kar Laya Ja Sakta Hai;
Ab Bhi Jalta Shehar Bachaya Ja Sakta Hai;

Ek Mohabbat Aur Woh Bhi Nakam Mohabbat;
Lekin Iss Se Kaam Chalaya Ja Sakta Hai;

Dil Par Paani Peene Aati Hain Umeedien;
Iss Chashme Mein Zeher Milaya Ja Sakta Hai;

Mujh Gumnaam Se Puchte Hain Farhaad-o-Majnoon;
Ishq Mein Kitna Naam Kamaya Ja Sakta Hai;

Yeh Mehtab Yeh Raat Kee Peshani Ka Ghav;
Aisa Zakham To Dil Par Khaya Ja Sakta Hai;

Phata Purana Khwaab Hai Mera Phir Bhi 'Tabish';
Iss Mein Apna Aap Chupaya Ja Sakta Hai!

 Dosti Mein Dooriyan To Aati Rehti Hain;
Phir Bhi Dosti Dilon Ko Mila Deti Hai;
Woh Dost Hi Kya Jo Naraz Na Ho;
Par Sachhi Dosti Doston Ko Mana Leti Hai!

 Khushbu Kee Tarah Meri Har Sans Mein;
Pyar Apna Basane Ka Wada Karo;
Rang Jitne Tumhari Mohabat Ke Hain;
Mere Dil Me Sajane Ka Wada Karo!

 Intezar Rehta Har Shaam Tera;
Yaadein Katati Hain Le-Le Kar Naam Tera;
Muddat Se Baithe Hain Yeh Aas Paale Dil Mein;
Ki Aaj Aayega Koi Lekar Paigaam Tera!

 Teri Doli Uthi

Teri Doli Uthi, Meri Mayyat Uthi;
Phool Tujh Par Bhi Barse, Phool Mujh Par Bhi Barse;
Farq Sirf Itna Sa Tha, Tu Saj Gayi, Mujhe Sajaya Geya;

Tu Bhi Ghar Ko Chali, Main Bhi Ghar Ko Chala;
Farq Sirf Itna Sa Tha, Tu Uth Ke Gayi, Mujhe Uthaya Geya;

Mehfil Wahan Bhi Thi, Log Yahan Bhi The;
Farq Sirf Itna Sa Tha, Unka Hasna Wahan, Inka Rona Yahan;

Qazi Udhar Bhi Tha, Maulvi Idhar Bhi Tha;
Do Bol Tere Padhe, Do Bol Mere Padhe;
Tera 'Nikah' Padha, Mera 'Janaaza' Padha;
Farq Sirf Itna Sa Tha, Tujhe Apnaya Geya, Mujhe Dafnaya Geya!

 Diya Diye Se Jala Loon To Chain Aaye Mujhe;
Tumhein Gale Se Laga Loon To Chain Aaye Mujhe;
Mohabbton Ke Saheefay Hain Ya Azaab Koi;
Tere Khatoot Jala Loon To Chain Aaye Mujhe!

Translation:
Saheefay = A written document
Azaab = Torture
Khatoot = Letters

 Achha Hota Jo Tumse Pyaar Na Hua Hota;
Chain Se Rehte Hum Jo Tumhara Deedar Na Hua Hota;
Hum Kab Ke Pahunch Chuke Hote Apni Manzil Par;
Agar Bewafa Tujh Par Aitbar Na Hua Hota!

 Kabhi Kabhi Hume Bhi Yun Hi Yaad Kar Liya Karo;
Hamari Tasveer Bhi Dekh Kar Use Chum Liya Karo;
Maana Ki Tumhein Kami Nahi Hai Kisi Cheez Kee;
Fir Bhi Kabhi Hume Apni Dua Mein Maang Liya Karo!

 Roothi Hui Aankhon Mein Intezar Hota Hai;
Na Chahte Hue Bhi Pyar Hota Hai;
Kyun Dekhte Hain Hum Wo Sapne;
Jinke Tutne Par Bhi Unke Sach Hone Ka Intezar Hota Hai!

 Ahista Chal Zindagi

Ahista Chal Zindagi, Abhi Kayi Karz Chukana Baki Hai;
Kuch Dard Mitana Baki Hai, Kuch Farz Nibhana Baki Hai;

Raftar Mein Tere Chalne Se Kuch Rooth Gaye, Kuch Chut Gaye
Roothon Ko Manana Baki Hai, Roton Ko Hasana Baki Hai;

Kuch Hasratein Abhi Adhuri Hain, Kuch Kaam Bhi Aur Zaruri Hai;
Khwahishein Jo Ghut Gayi Iss Dil Mein Unko Dafnana Baki Hai;

Kuch Rishte Ban Kar Toot Gaye, Kuch Judte-Judte Chut Gaye;
Un Toote-Chute Rishton Ke Zakhmon Ko Mitana Baki Hai;

Tu Aage Chal Main Aata Hun, Kya Chhod Tujhe Jee Paunga;
In Saanso Par Haq Hai Jinka, Unko Samjhana Baki Hai;

Ahista Chal Zindagi Abhi Kayi Karz Chukana Baki Hai!

 Aankhon Kee Gehrai Ko Samjh Nahi Sakte;
Hontho Se Kuch Keh Nahi Sakte;
Kaise Bayan Kare Hum Aapko Yeh Dil Ka Haal Ki;
Tum Hi Ho Jiske Bina Hum Reh Nahi Sakte!

 Dil Ke Sabhi Halaat Mujhe Kehne Do;
Behte Hain Ashk To Inhe Behne Do;
Bewafai Shamil Na Karo Dosti Kee Raaho Mein;
Kam Se Kam Dosti Ko To Dosti Rehne Do!

 Kaash Tum Mujhe Ek Khat Likh Dete;
Mujhme Kya-Kya Thi Kami Yeh To Bata Dete;
Tadapte Dil Se Mere Tumne Nafrat Kyon Kee;
Nafrat Kee Hi Mujhe Koi Wajah To Bata Dete!

 Woh Chandni Ka Badan

Woh Chandni Ka Badan Khushabuon Ka Saya Hai;
Bahut Azeez Hume Hai Magar Paraya Hai;

Utar Bhi Aao Kabhi Aasman Ke Zeene Se;
Tumhein Khuda Ne Humare Liye Banaya Hai;

Mehak Rahi Hai Zameen Chandni Ke Phoolon Se;
Khudaa Kisi Kee Mohabbat Pe Muskuraya Hai;

Use Kisi Kee Mohabbat Ka Aitbar Nahi;
Use Zamane Ne Shayad Bahut Sataya Hai;

Tamam Umar Mera Dum Uske Dhuein Se Ghuta;
Woh Ik Chirag Tha Maine Use Bujhaya Hai!

 Yun Hi To Nahi Dil Mera Tujhe Talashta Firta;
Kar Yakeen Manzil Ka Tu Hi Hai Kinara Mera;
Yun Hi To Nahi Aayi Sada Teri Hawaon Mein Behkar;
Haule Se Tumne Hi Hoga Naam To Pukara Mera!

 Saaye Ne Saath Chhod Diya Yaar Ne Dil Tod Diya;
Ab Toh Khuda Bhi Mere Khilaf Ho Geya;
Jo Pyaar Ka Chirag Jalaya Tha Maine;
Usi Chiraag Se Jalkar Mera Ghar Khak Ho Geya!

 Mana Ki Pyaar Kisi Ka Mere Paas Nahi;
Magar Tumhein Bhi Mohabbat Ka Ehsaas Nahi;
Jaane Pee Gaye Hum Kitne Gham-e-Aansu;
Ab Kuch Aur Peene Kee Pyaas Nahi!

 Dheere Se Sarakti Hai Raat

Dheere Se Sarakti Hai Raat Uss Ke Aanchal Kee Tarah;
Uska Chehra Nazar Aata Hai Jheel Mein Kanwal Kee Tarah;

Baad Muddat Usko Dekha To Jism-o-Jaan Ko Yun Laga;
Pyaasi Zameen Pe Jaise Koi Baras Geya Baadal Kee Tarah;

Roz Kehta Hai Seene Pe Sar Rakh Ke Raat Bhar Jagauonga;
Sar-e-Sham Hee Mujhe Aaj Phir Sula Geya Woh Kal Kee Tarah;

Mere Hee Dil Ka Makeen Nikla Woh Shakhs 'Wasi'
Aur Main Shehar Bhar Mein Dhundta Raha Use Kisi Pagal Kee Tarah!

 Tumhari Pasand Hamari Chahat Ban Jaye;
Tumhari Muskurahat Dil Kee Rahat Ban Jaye;
Khudaa Khushiyon Se Itna Khush Kar De Aapko;
Ki Aapko Khush Dekhna Hamari Aadat Ban Jaye!

 Koi Mila Hi Nahi Jis Ko Wafa Dete;
Har Ek Ne Dhokha Diya Kis Kis Ko Saza Dete;
Yeh Hamara Zarf Tha Ki Khamosh Rahe Warna;
Daastan Sunate To Mehfil Ko Bhi Rula Dete!

 Karoge Yaad Ek Din Iss Pyaar Ke Zamane Ko;
Chale Jayenge Jab Hum Kabhi Na Vapas Aane Ko;
Chalega Mehfil Mein Jab Zikr Hamara Koi;
To Tum Bhi Tanhayi Dhoondoge Aansu Bahane Ko!

 Meri Aankhon Ko

Meri Aankhon Ko Soojhta Hee Nahi;
Ya Muqaddar Mein Raasta Hee Nahi;

Wo Bhare Sheher Mein Kisi Se Bhi;
Mere Baare Mein Poochta Hee Nahi;

Phir Wohi Shaam Hai Wohi Hum Hain;
Haan Magar Dil Mein Haunsla Hee Nahi;

Hum Chale Uss Kee Bazm Se Uth Kar;
Aur Woh Hai Ki Rokta Hee Nahi;

Dil Jo Ek Dost Tha Magar Woh Bhi;
Chup Ka Pathar Hai Bolta Hee Nahi;

Main To Uss Kee Talaash Mein Gum Hun;
Woh Kabhi Mujh Ko Dhoondta Hee Nahi!

 Yaad Aane Wale Yaad Aaye Ja Rahe Hain;
Mere Khyalon Kee Duniya Par Chaye Ja Rahe Hain;
Hum Kuch Keh Rahe Hain Par Wo Chup Hain;
Bas Mera Khat Padh Kar Muskuraye Ja Rahe Hain!

 Chand Ko Sitaron Se Aur Mujhe Tum Se Mohabbat Hai;
Phoolon Ko Baharon Se Aur Mujhe Tum Se Mohabbat Hai;
Mehfil Mein Jo Milna To Nighahein Jhuka Lena;
Koi Samjh Na Paye Ki Mujhe Tum Se Mohabbat Hai!

 Mere Qatil Ko Pukaro Ki Main
Mere Qatil Ko Pukaro Ki Main Zinda Hoon Abhi;
Phir Say Maqtal Ko Sanwaro Ki Main Zinda Hoon Abhi;
Yeh Shab-e-Hijar To Sathi Hai Meri Barsoon Say;
Jao So Jao Sitaro Ki Main Zinda Hoon Abhi;
Yeh Pareshan Say Gaisu Dekhe Nahi Jate;
Apni Zulfun Ko Sanwaro Ki Main Zinda Hoon Abhi;
Lakh Moujoun Mein Ghira Hun, Abhi Dooba To Nahi;
Mujh Ko Sahil Say Pukaro Ki Main Zinda Hoon Abhi;
Qabar Say Aaj Bhi 'Mohsin' Kee Aati Hai Sada;
Tum Kahan Ho Mera Yaroo Ki Main Zinda Hoon Abhi!

 Apni Haseen Ankhon Mein Chuppa Lo Mujh Ko;
Mohabbat Agar Karte Ho To Chura Lo Mujh Ko;
Khone Ka Agar Khauf Hai Tumhein To;
Dil Kee Har Dhadkan Mein Basaa Lo Mujh Ko!

 Jahan Yaad Na Aaye Teri, Woh Tanhaai Kis Kaam Kee;
Bigde Rishte Na Bane, To Khudaai Kis Kaam Kee;
Beshak Apni Manzil Tak Jana Hai Humein;
Lekin Jahaan Se Apne Na Dikhein Woh Unchaai Kis Kaam Kee!

 Dil Mein Khayal-e-Nargis

Dil Mein Khayal-e-Nargis-e-Janana Aa Geya;
Phulon Se Khelta Hua Deewana Aa Geya;

Badal Ke Uthte Hi Mai-o-Paimana Aa Geya;
Bijli Ke Saath Saath Pari-Khaana Aa Geya;

Maston Ne Iss Ada Se Kiya Raqs-e-Nau-Bahar;
Paimana Kyaa Ki Vajd Mein Maikhana Aa Geya;

Uss Chashm-e-Mai-Farosh Kee Tasir Kya Kahun;
Honthon Tak Aaj Aap Hi Paimana Aa Geya;

Malum Kis Ko Qais Kee Deewangi Kee Shaan;
Hungama Sa Bapaa Hai Ki Deewana Aa Geya;

Akhtar Gazab Thi Ahd-e-Jawani Kee Daastan;
Aankhon Ke Aage Ek Pari-Khaana Aa Geya!

 Le Kar Aana Usse Mere Janaaze Mein;
Ek Aakhri Haseen Mulaqat Toh Hogi;
Mere Jism Mein Beshak Jaan Na Ho Magar;
Meri Jaan Mere Jism Ke Pass To Hogi!

 Naye Kapde Badal Kar Jaun Kahan Aur Baal Banaun Kis Ke Liye;
Woh Shakhs To Shehar Hi Chodd Geya Main Bahar Jaun Kis Ke Liye;
Muddat Se Koi Aayaa Na Geya Sunsaan Padi Hai Ghar Kee Fazaa;
In Khali Kamron Mein 'Nasir' Ab Shama Jalaun Kis Ke Liiye!

 Apno Ne Pyaar Mein Rula Diya;
Kya Hua Jo Kisi Aur Ke Liye Hume Bhula Diya;
Hum To Waise Bhi Akele The;
Kya Hua Jo Aapne Yeh Ehsaas Dila Diya!

 Hum Ne Waqt Se Bahut Wafa Kee Lekin;
Waqt Humse Bewafai Kar Geya;
Kuch Humare Naseeb Bure The;
Kuch Logon Ka Humse Dil Bhar Geya!

 Aayi Hai Kuch Na Puch
Aayi Hai Kuch Na Puch Qayamat Kahan Kahan;
Uff Le Gayi Hum Ko Mohabbat Kahan Kahan;

Betabi-o-Sakoon Kee Hui Manzilein Tamaam;
Behlaayein Tujh Se Choot Ke Tabiyat Kahan Kahan;

Raah-e-Talaab Mein Chor Diya Dil Ka Sath Bhi;
Phirte Liye Hue Yeh Museebat Kahan Kahan;

Begaangi Pe Uss Kee Zamaane Se Aitraaz;
Dar Parda Uss Kee Shikayat Kahan Kahan;

Hosh-o-Junoon Bhi Bas Ab To Ek Baat Hain 'Firaq';
Hoti Hai Uss Shararat Kee Nazar Kahan Kahan!

 Aaj Bhi Soona Pada Hai Har Ek Manjar;
Tere Jaane Se Sab Kuch Veeran Lagta Hai;
Uss Raaste Pe Aaj Bhi Hum Teri Raah Dekhte Hain;
Jahan Se Tera Laut Aana Aasaan Lagta Hai!

 Na Woh Aaye Aur Na Koi Unka Paigaam Aaya;
Intezar Mein Apne Tadapa Kar Humein Hai Rulaya;
Humse Khataa Hui Agar Koi, Tum Bata Toh Dete;
Aisi Bhi Kya Naraazgi Thi Jo Humein Aapne Bhulaya!

 Hum Hain Mataa-e-Koocha-o-Baazaar
Hum Hain Mataa-e-Koocha-o-Baazaar Kee Tarah;
Uthti Hai Har Nigaah Kharidaar Kee Tarah;

Iss Ku-e-Tishnagi Mein Bahut Hai Ki Ek Jaam;
Haath Aa Gaya Hai Daulat-e-Bedaar Kee Tarah;

Wo To Hain Kahin Aur Magar Dil Ke Aas Paas;
Firti Hai Koi Shay Nigaah-e-Yaar Kee Tarah;

Seedhi Hai Raah-e-Shauq Pa Yun Hi Kabhi Kabhi;
Kham Ho Gayi Hai Gesu-e-Diladar Kee Tarah;

Ab Ja Ke Kuch Khula Hunar-e-Naakhoon-e-Junoon;
Zakhm-e-Jigar Huye Lab-o-Rukhsar Kee Tarah;

Majrooh Likh Rahe Hain Wo Ahal-e-Wafa Ka Naam;
Hum Bhi Khade Hue Hain Gunahagaar Kee Tarah!

 Khoobsurat Hai Zindagi Khwaab Ki Tarha;
Jaane Kab Toot Jaaye Kaanch Ki Tarha;
Mujhe Na Bhoolna Kisi Baat Ki Tarha;
Apne Dil Mein Hi Rakhna Khoobsurat Yaad Ki Tarha!

 Duniya Vi Dekhi Te Duniya Daari Vi Dekhi;
Dilan Utte Chaldi Main Aari Vi Dekhi;
Dekhe Si Jo Lok Main Nibhaunde Yaariyan;
Ohna Hatthon Hundi Main Gaddari Vi Dekhi!

 Bheegi Palkon Ke Sang Muskurate Hain Hum;
Pal Pal Dil Ko Kuch Aur Behlate Hain Hum;
Tu Door Hai Humse To Kya Hua Mere Dilbar;
Har Saans Mein Teri Aahat Paate Hain Hum!

 Bichar Kar Aap Se Humko Khushi Achhi Nahi Lagti;
Labon Par Yeh Banawat Ki Hansi Achhi Nahi Lagti;
Kabhi To Khoob Lagti Thi Magar Yeh Sochti Hoon Ab;
Ki Mujhko Kyon Meri Yeh Zindagi Achhi Nahi Lagti!

 Kis Se Se Mangein Dawaa Zakhmon Kee;
Sabhi Ne Chotein Khayi Hain;
Kisi Ka Sanam Bewafa Hai To;
Kisi Ka Sajan Harzayi Hai!

 Aafat Kee Shokhiyan Hain
Aafat Kee Shokhiyan Hain Tumhari Nigah Mein;
Mehshar Ke Fitane Khelte Hain Jalwa-Gaah Mein;
Woh Dushmani Se Dekhte Hain Dekhte To Hain;
Main Shaad Hoon Ke Hoon To Kisi Kee Nigah Mein;
Aati Baat Baat Mujhe Yaad Baar Baar;
Kehta Hoon Daud Daud Ke Qaasid Se Raah Mein;
Iss Tauba Par Hai Naaz Mujhe Zaahid Iss Qadar;
Jo Toot Kar Shareek Hoon Haal-E-Tabaah Mein;
Mushtaaq Iss Ada Ke Bahut Dard-Mand The;
Ai Daag Tum To Baith Gaye Ek Aah Mein!

 Aaj Bhi Bahut Sawal Hain Iss Dil Mein;
Pyaar Ka Gham Bejuban Hai Iss Dil Mein;
Kuch Keh Nahi Paata Yeh Dil Magar;
Uss Dil Ke Liye Aaj Bhi Pyaar Hai Iss Dil Mein!

 Pal Pal Ke Rishte Ka Vaada Hai Aapse;
Apnapan Kuch Inta Jyada Hai Aapse;
Na Sochna Ki Bhool Gaye Hum Aapko;
Zindagi Bhar Chahenge Yeh Vaada Hai Aapse!

 Lafzon Ke Fasaane Dhoondhte Hain Hum Log;
Lamhon Mein Zamane Dhoondhte Hain Hum Log;
Tu Zeher Hi De Sharab Keh Kar Saqi;
Jeene Ke Bahane Dhoondhte Hain Hum Log!

 Haath Chhute Bhi Toh

Haath Chhute Bhi Toh Rishte Nahi Chhoda Karte;
Waqt Ki Shaakh Se Lamhe Nahi Toda Karte;
 
Jiski Aawaaz Mein Silwat Ho Nigahon Mein Shikan;
Aisi Tasveer Ke Tukade Nahi Joda Karte;
 
Shahad Jeene Ka Mila Karta Hai Thoda Thoda;
Jaane Waalon Ke Liye Dil Nahi Thoda Karte;
 
Lag Ke Sahil Se Jo Behta Hai, Use Behane Do;
Aise Dariya Ka Kabhi Rukh Nahi Moda Karte;

Jaagne Par Bhi Nahin Aankh Se Girti Kirchein;
Iss Tarah Khawabon Se Aankhein Nahin Phodaa Karte;

Ja Ke Kohsar Se Sar Maaro Ki Aavwaz To Ho;
Khasta Deewaron Se Maatha Nahin Phodaa Karte!

 Ithe Kaiyan Nu Maan Wafawan Da;
Te Kaiyan Nu Naaz Adawaan Da;
Assi Peele Patte Drakhtaan De;
Sanu Rehnda Khauf Hawawan Da!

 Log Puchte Hain Kyon Surkh Hain Tumhari Aankhein;
Hans Ke Keh Deti Hoon Raat Ko So Na Saki;
Lakh Chahoon Bhi Magar Yeh Keh Na Sakoon;
Raat Ko Rone Ki Hasrat Thi Magar Ro Na Saki!

 Dekh Lete Ho Mohabbat Se
Dekh Lete Ho Mohabbat Se Yahi Kaafi Hai;
Dil Dhadakta Hai Sahulat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai;
Haal Duniya Ke Sataye Hue Kuch Logon Ka;
Puch Lete Ho Shararat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai;
Jo Bhi Raaste Mein Guzarta Hai Mere Pehlu Se;
Dekhta Hai Teri Nisbat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai;
Muddatton Se Nahin Dekha Tera Jalwa Lekin;
Yaad Aa Jate Ho Shidat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai;
Saari Duniya Se Ulajhte Hain Lekin;
Tera Kahaa Maan Jate Hain Sharafat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai;
Kya Hua Hum Jo Muyassar Jo Zar-O-Maal Nahin;
Katt Rahi Hai Bari Izzat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai;
Aaj Ke Ehad Taghaful Mein Kisi Dar Pe 'Munir';
Koi Aa jaye Zarurat Se, Yahi Kaafi Hai!

 Yun To Sadmo Mein Bhi Hans Leta Tha Main;
Aaj Kyon Bewajah Rone Laga Hun Main;
Barson Se Hatheliyan Khali Hi Rahi Meri;
Phir Aaj Kyon Lagaa Sab Khone Laga Hun Main!

 Mere Jazbat Meri Pehchan Hai Woh;
Meri Justaju Meri Shaan Hai Woh;
Log Kehte Hain Bhula Dun Main Use;
Par Kaise Bhula Dun Yaaro Is Seene Me Dhadakti Jaan Hai Woh!

 Jaan Kar Bhi Woh Humein Jaan Na Paye;
Aaj Tak Woh Humein Pehchaan Na Paye;
Khud Hi Kar Lee Bewafai Humne;
Taaki Unpar Koi Ilzaam Na Aaye!

 Dil Mein Hum Ek Hi Jazbe Ko
Dil Mein Hum Ek Hi Jazbe Ko Samoyein Kaise;
Ab Tujhe Paa Ke Yeh Uljhan Hai Ke Khoyein Kaise;
Zehen Chhalni Jo Kiya Hai, To Yeh Majboori Hai;
Jitne Kaante Hain, Woh Talwon Mein Piroyein Kaise;
Hum Ne Maana Ki Bahut Dair Hai Hashar Aaney Tak;
Chaar Janib Teri Aahat Ho To Soyein Kaise;
Kitni Hasrat Thi, Tujhe Pass Bitha Kar Rote;
Ab Yeh Mushkil Hai, Tere Samne Royein Kaise!

 Jab Chote The Hum To Zor Se Rote The;
Jo Pasand Hota Tha Use Paane Ke Liye;
Aaj Bade Hain To Chupke Se Rote Hain;
Jo Pasand Hai Use Bhulane Ke Liye!

 Parwah Kar Uski Jo Teri Parwah Kare;
Zindagi Mein Jo Kabhi Na Tanha Kare;
Jaan Ban Kar Utar Ja Uski Rooh Mein;
Jo Jaan Se Bhi Jyada Tujhse Wafa Kare!

 Sun To Sahi
Sun To Sahi Jahaan Mein Hai Tera Fasana Kya;
Kehti Hai Tujh Se Khalq-e-Khudaa Gaibanaa Kya;
Zina Saba Kaa Dhundati Hai Apni Musht-e-Khaak;
Baam-E-Baland Yaar Ka Hai Astana Kya;
Aati Hai Kis Tarah Se Meri Kabz-e-Rooh Ko;
Dekhun To Maut Dhund Rahi Hai Bahana Kya;
Betab Hai Kamal Hamara Dil-e-Azeem;
Mehmaan Saray-e-Jism Ka Hoga Ravana Kya!

 Jeevan Mein Ek Baar Sabhi Ne Kiya Hai Pyaar;
Kuch Ne Darr Kar Kuch Ne Josh Mein Kiya Izhar;
Magar Bina Bole Jab Do Dil Keh Jayein Dil Kee Baat;
Wahi Hai Nazar Ka Nazar Se Saccha Iqraar!

 Aaj Zara Fursat

Aaj Zara Fursat Paayi Thi Aaj Use Phir Yaad Kiya;
Band Gali Ke Aakhiri Ghar Ko Khol Ke Phir Aabad kiya;

Khol Ke Khidkii Chand Hansa Phir Chand Ne Dono Hathon Se;
Rang Udaye Phool Khilaye Chidiyon Ko Aazad Kiya;

Bade Bade GHam Khade Hue The Raasta Roke Raahon Mein;
Choti Choti Khushiyon Se Hi Hum Ne Dil Ko Shaad Kiya;

Baat Bahut Mamuli Si Thi Uljh Gayi Takraron Mein;
Ek Zara Si Zidd Ne Aakhir Dono Ko Barbaad Kiya;

Danaon Ki Baat Na Maani Kaam Aayi Nadaani Hi;
Suna Hawa Ko Padha Nadi Ko Mausam Ko Ustad Kiya!

 Justaju Khoye Hue Kee Umar Bhar Karte Rahe;
Chaand Ke Humraah Hum Har Shab Safar Karte Rahe;
Raaston Ka Ilm Tha Na Hum Ko Simton Kee Khabar;
Shehar-e-Na-Maaloom Kee Chahat Magar Karte Rahe!

 Hum Aapko Chahenge Wafa Ki Had Tak;
Bewafai Ko Apki Hum Wafa Kar Denge;
Royenge Aap Hume Dekar Saza;
Ek Din Hum Aisi Khata Kar Denge!

 Intezar To Bahut Tha Humein;
Lekin Aaye Na Woh Kabhi;
Hum To Bin Bulaaye Hi Aa Jaate;
Agar Hota Unhe Bhi Intezar Kabhi!

 Jholi Addeyan Je Tu Milda Tan Khair Bhi Pawa Lainde;
Jaan Diteyan Je Milda Tan Jaan Vi Gawa Lainde;
Pata Nahi Kehdeyan Naseeban Naal Milna Tu;
Nahi Tan Naseeb Vi Change Rabb Kolo Likha Lainde!

 Tumhara Pyaar Mere

Tumhara Pyaar Mere Chaar Suu Abhi Tak Hai;
Koi Hisaar Mere Chaar Suu Abhi Tak Hai;

Bichartey Waqt Jo Tum Saunp Kar Gaye The Mujhe;
Woh Intezar Mere Chaar Suu Abhi Tak Hai;

Tu Khud Hee Jaanay Kahin Door Kho Geya Hai Magar;
Teri Pukaar Mere Chaar Suu Abhi Tak Hai;

Main Jab Bhi Nikla Mere Paon Chhaid Daalay Ga;
Jo Khaar Zaar Mere Chaar Suu Abhi Tak Hai;

Main Ab Bhi Girte Hue Paanion Ki Qaid Mein Hun;
Ik Aabshaar Mere Chaar Suu Abhi Tak Hai;

Koi Gumaan Mujhe Tum Se Door Kaise Kare;
Ki Aitbaar Mere Chaar Suu Abhi Tak Hai!

 Iss Dil Ne Ab Pyaar Karna Chod Diya;
Jis Din Se Tumne Yeh Dil Tod Diya;
Ab To Ro Bhi Nahi Sakte Apni Bebasi Pe;
Iss Liye In Aankhon Ne Ab Rona Bhi Chod Diya!

 Maut Ne To Nahi Zindagi Ne Bahut Sataya Hai;
Tujhe Jitna Bhule Tu Utna Hi Yaad Aaya Hai;
Tu kyon Is Baat Ko Aksar Bhool Jata Hai;
Barson Minaton Ke Baad Tujhe Paaya Hai!

 Phool Bankar Muskurana Zindagi;
Muskurake Ghum Bhulana Zindagi;
Jeet Kar Koi Khush Ho Toh Kya Hua;
Haar Kar Khushiyan Manana Bhi Hai Zindagi!

 Jab Ishq Sikhata Hai
Jab Ishq Sikhata Hai Aadaab-e-Khud-Aagahi;
Khulte Hain Ghulamon Par Asaraar-e-Shahanshahi;

'Attaar' Ho 'Rumi' Ho 'Raazi' Ho 'Ghazaali' Ho;
Kuch Haath Nahin Aataa Be-Aah-Sahar-Gaahi;

Naumeed Na Ho In Se Ai Rah-Bar-e-Farzaana;
Kam-Kosh To Hain Lekin Be-Zauq Nahin Raahi;

Ai Tayar-e-Lahooti Us Rizq Se Maut Achhhi;
Jis Rizq Se Aati Ho Parvaaz Mein Kotahi;

Daara o Sikandar Se Woh Mard-e-Faqeer Aulaa;
Ho Jiski Faqeeri Mein Boo-e-Asadool-Laahi;

Aaeen-e-Jawan Mardaan Haq-Goyi o Be-Baaki;
Allaah Ke Sheron Ko Aati Nahin Roobahi!

 Dil Mein Tumhare Apni Kami Chod Jaayenge;
Aakhon Mein Intezar Kee Nami Chod Jaayenge;
Yaad Rakhna Mujhe Dhoondte Firoge Ek Din;
Zindagi Mein Dosti Kee Kahani Chod Jaayenge!

 Rabb Kare Koi Ishq Da Shikar Na Hove;
Judaa Apne Dildar Toh Kise Da Pyaar Na Hove;
Main Gujaar Dawa Apni Zindagi Uss Toh Baigar;
Bas Shart Eh Hai Ki Usnu Vi Kise Hor Naal Pyaar Na Hove!

 Dukh Dard Mein Hamesha

Dukh Dard Mein Hamesha Nikale Tumhaare Khat;
Aur Mil Gayi Khushi To Uchhaale Tumhaare Khat;

Sab Chudiyan Tumhari Samandar Ko Saunp Di;
Aur Kar Diye Hawa Ke Havale Tumhare Khat;

Mere Lahoo Mein Goonj Raha Hai Har Ek Lafz;
Maine Ragon Ke Dasht Mein Paale Tumhare Khat;

Yun To Hain Be-Shumar Wafaa Kee Nishaniyan;
Lekin Har Ek Shai Se Nirale Tumhare Khat;

Jaise Ho Umar Bhar Ka Asasa Garib Ka;
Kuch Is Tarah Se Maine Sambhale Tumhare Khat;

Ahl-e-Hunar Ko Mujh Pe 'Wasi' Aitraz Hai;
Maine Jo Apne Sher Mein Dhaale Tumhare Khat;

Parwah Mujhe Nahin Hai Kisi Chand Ki 'Wasi';
Zulmat Ke Dasht Mein Hain Ujale Tumhare Khat!

 Nahin Jaata Kisi Se Wo Marz, Jo Hai Naseebon Ka;
Na Qayal Hun Dawa Ka Main, Na Qayal Hun Tabibon Ka;
Na Shikwa Dushmano Ka Hai, Na Hai Shikwa Habibon Ka;
Shikayat Hai To Kismat Ki, Gila Hai To Naseebon Ka!

 Sahil Par Khade Khade Humne Shaam Kar Di;
Apna Dil Aur Duniya Aap Ke Naam Kar Di;
Yeh Bhi Na Socha Kaise Guzregi Zindagi;
Bina Soche Samjhe Har Khushi Aap Ke Naam Kar Di!

 Chedne Ka To Mazaa Tab Hai

Chedne Ka To Mazaa Tab Hai Kaho Aur Suno;
Baat Mein Tum To Khafaa Ho Gaye, Lo Aur Suno;

Tum Kahoge Jise Kuchh, Kyun Na Kahega Tum Ko;
Chhod Devegaa Bhalaa, Dekh To Lo, Aur Suno;

Yahi Insaaf Hai Kuchh Socho To Apne Dil Mein;
Tum To Sau Keh Lo, Meri Ek Na Suno Aur Suno;

Aafareen Tum Pe Yahi Chahiye Shabash Tumhein;
Dekh Rota Mujhe Yun Hansne Lago Aur Suno;

Baat Meri Nahin Sunte Jo Akele Mil Kar;
Aise Hi Dhang Se Sunaun Ki Suno Aur Suno!

 Zindagi Sirf Issi Dhun Mein Guzare Jayein;
Bas Tera Naam, Tera Naam Pukare Jayein;
Jab Yeh Tay Hai Ki Yahan Koi Nahin Aayega;
Kis Ki Khatir Dar-O-Deewar Sanware Jayein!

 Parh Parh Kitaban Ilam Diya Tu Naam Rakh Liya Qazi;
Hath Vich Pharh Ke Talwar Naam Rakh Liya Ghazi;
Makke Madine Ghum Aaya Te Naam Rakh Liya Haji;
Oh Bulleya Hasil Kee Kita, Je Tu Rabb Na Kita Razi!

 Dono Jahaan Teri Mohabbat Mein

Dono Jahaan Teri Mohabbat Mein Haar Ke;
Woh Jaa Raha Hai Koi Shab-e-Gam Guzaar Ke;
Veeraan Hai Maikada Khum o Sagar Udaas Hain;
Tum Kya Gaye Ki Rooth Gaye Din Bahaar Ke;
Ik Fursat-e-Gunaah Mili Wo Bhi Chaar Din;
Dekhe Hain Hum Ne Haunsle Parwardigaar Ke;
Duniya Ne Teri Yaad Se Baigana Kar Diya;
Tujh Se Bhi Dil-Fareb Hain Gam Rozgaar Ke;
Bhule Se Muskura To Diye The Woh Aaj 'Faiz';
Mat Puch Valvale Dil-e-Naa-Karda-Kaar Ke!

 Hum Tere Hijr Mein Andar Se Bikhar Jaate Hain;
Zinda Lagte Hain Magar Asal Mein Mar Jaate Hain;
Jab Kabhi Bolta Hai Hans Ke Kisi Aur Se Tu;
Kitne Khanjar Mere Seene Mein Utar Jaate Hain!

 Kareeb Itna Raho Ki Rishton Mein Pyaar Rahe;
Door Bhi Itna Rahein Ki Aane Ka Intezar Rahe;
Rakho Ummeed Rishton Ke Darmiyaan Itni;
Ki Toot Jaaye Ummeed Magar Rishte Barkaraar Rahein!

 Mohabbat Ke Mayne Humse Kya Puchte Ho;
Hum In Batoon Se Anjaan Hain;
Bus Ek Gujarish Hai Ki Bhool Naa Jaana Hume;
Kyonki Tumhara Pyaar Hi Hamari Jaan Hai!

 Iss Dunya Mein Jo Humko Dil Ke Hain Rog Mile;
Khushiyon Ki Talaash Mein Jo Humko Hain Sog Mile;
Matlabi Zamane Kee Matlabi Galiyon Mein;
Doston Ke Roop Mein Sab Dushman Log Mile!

 Aa Jayen Hum Nazar To

Aa Jayen Hum Nazar To Koi Dum Bahut Hai Yan;
Mohlat Basan-e-Barq-o-Sharar Kam Bahut Hai Yan;

Yak Lahza Sina Kobi Se Fursat Humein Nahin;
Yani Ki Dil Ke Jane Ka Matam Bahut Hai Yan;

Hum Rah Rawan-e-Rah-e-Fana Der Rah Chuke;
Waqfa Basan-e-Subh Koi Dam Bahut Hai Yan;

Hasil Hai Kya Siwaye Tarai Ke Dehar Mein;
Uth Aasman Tale Se Ke Shabnam Bahut Hai Yan;

Mere Hilak Karne Ka Gum Hai Bas Tumhein;
Tum Shad Zindagani Karo Gum Bahut Hai Yan;

Shayad Ke Kam Subh Tak Apna Khinchena 'Mir';
Ahawal Aaj Sham Se Darham Bahut Hai Yan!

 Mere Dost Tum Bhi Likha Karo Shayari;
Tumhara Bhi Meri Tarah Naam Ho Jayega;
Jab Tum Par Bhi Padenge Ande Aur Tamatar;
To Shaam Ki Sabji Ka Intajaam Ho Jayega!

 Khud Hi Badal Jaaoge Tum Ek Din;
Kaise Tum Par Aitbaar Hum Kare;
Kabhi Sochte Hain Ki Mana Lenge Tumhe;
Par Sochte Hain Ki Wo Humpar Aitbaar Kare!

 Har Chaman Mein Mumkin Hai Ki Gul Khil Jaaye;
Tumhe Bhi Hamare Baad Mumkin Hai Koi Aur Mil Jaaye;
Zindagi To Tumne Kabhi Hum Ko Jeene Na Di;
Ab Marna Chaha To Kehte Ho Ki Maut Bhi Na Aaye!

 Tumne To Keh Diya

Tumne To Keh Diya Ki Mohabbat Nahi Mili;
Mujhko To Ye Bhi Kehne Ki Mohlat Nahi Mili;

Neendo Ke Des Jaate, Koi Khawab Dekhte;
Lekin Diya Jalane Se Fusat Nahi Mili;

Tujhko To Khair Shahar Ke Logo Ka Khauf Tha;
Aur Mujhko Apne Ghar Se Ijajat Nahi Mili;

Phir Ikhtilaf-e-Rai Ki Surat Nikal Padi;
Apni Yahan Kisi Se Bhi Aadat Nahi Mili;

Be-zar Yun Hue Ki Tere Ahad Mein Humein;
Sab Kuch Mila, Sukun Kee Daulat Nahi Mili!

 Teri Yaadon Ke Siva Kuch Bhi Nahi Hai;
Khawab Har Raat Fir Sajana Padta Hai;
Kahin Dekh Na Le Namm Ye Aankhein Koi;
Aansuon Ko Aankhon Mein Chupana Padta Hai!

 Khawab Ki Tarah Bikhar
Khawab Ki Tarah Bikhar Jaane Ko Ji Chahta Hai;
Aisi Tanhai Ki Mar Jane Ko Ji Chahta Hai;
Ghar Ki Wehshat Se Larzta Hun Magar Jaane Kyon;
Sham Hoti Hai To Ghar Jaane Ko Ji Chahta Hai;
Doob Jaun To Koi Mauj Nishan Tak Na Bataye;
Aisi Nadi Mein Utar Jaane Ko Ji Chahta Hai;
Kabhi Mil Jaye To Raaste Kee Thakan Jag Pare;
Aisi Manzil Se Guzar Jaane Ko Ji Chahta Hai;
Wahi Paiman Jo Kabhi Ji Ko Khush Aya Tha Bahut;
Usi Paiman Se Mukar Jaane Ko Ji Chahta Hai!

 Dost Ko Dost Ka Ishara Yaad Reheta Hai;
Har Dost Ko Apna Dostana Yad Reheta Hai;
Kuch Pal Sachhe Dost Ke Saath To Gujaro;
Woh Afsana Maut Tak Yaad Rehta Hai!

 Teri Ulfat Kabhi Nakaam Na Hone Denge;
Teri Dosti Kabhi Badnaam Na Hone Denge;
Meri Zindagi Mein Suraj Nikle Na Nikle;
Teri Zindagi Mein Kabhi Shaam Na Hone Denge!

 Aaj Jarurat Hai Jiski Woh Paas Nahi Hai;
Ab Unke Dil Mein Wo Ehsaas Nahi Hai;
Tadapte Hai Do Pal Baat Karne Ko;
Shayad Ab Waqt Hamare Liye Unke Pass Nahi Hai!

 Todna Hota To Rishta Hum Na Banate;
Umeed Nahi Hoti To Sapne Hum Na Sajate;
Aitbar Kiya Hai Humne Aapki Wafaon Pe;
Bharosa Na Hota To Apne Dil Ka Hissa Na Banate!

 Main Nahi Kehndi Rabba Mainu Pyaar Bakash De;
Koi Sohna Jeha Chahun Wala Yaar Bakash De;
Bas Ini Jehi Tamaana Iss Tutte Hoye Dil Di;
Jehra Chori Chori Takke Oh Dildaar Bakash De!

 Ab Na Woh Main Na Woh Tu

Ab Na Woh Main Na Woh Tu Hai Na Woh Maazi Hai 'Faraz';
Nasha Badhta Hai Sharaabein Jo Sharaabon Mein Milein;

Ye Khazaane Tujhe Mumkin Hai Kharaabon Mein Milein;
Kya Ajab Kal Woh Zamaane Nisaabon Mein Milein;

Ab Ke Hum Bichhde To Shaayad Kabhi Khwabon Mein Milein;
Jaise Do Shakhs Tamannaa Ke Saraabon Mein Milein;

Tu Khudaa Hai Na Mera Ishq Farishton Jaisa;
Jis Tarah Sookhe Hue Phool Kitaabon Mein Milein;

Dhoondte Ho Logon Mein Wafaa Ke Moti;
Gham-e-Duniya Bhi Gham-e-Yaar Mein Shaamil Kar Lo;

Aaj Hum Dar Pe Khinchege Jin Baaton Par;
Dono Insaan Hain To Kyun Itne Hijaabon Mein Milein!

 Har Kisi Baat Ka Koyi Jawaab Nahi Hota;
Har Naam Ishq Mein Kharab Nahi Hota;
Yun To Jhum Lete Hain Nashe Me Rehne Wale;
Magar Har Nashe Ka Naam Sharab Nahi Hota!

 Tere Har Gum Ko Apni Rooh Mein Utaar Lun;
Zindagi Apni Teri Chahat Mein Sawaar Lun;
Mulaqat Ho Tujhse Kuch Is Tarah Meri;
Sari Umar Bas Ek Mulaqat Mein Guzaar Lun!

 Yeh Aur Baat Teri
Yeh Aur Baat Teri Gali Main Na Ayen Hum;
Lekin Yeh Kya Ke Tera Sheher Chorr Jayen Hum;
Muddat Huyi Hai Kuye Bataan Ki Taraf Gaye;
Awaargi Se Dil Ko Kahan Tak Bachaayen Hum;
Be'noor Ho Chuki Hai Bohat Sheher Ki Fizaa;
Tareek Raston Par Kahin Kho Na Jayen Hum;
Us Ke Baghair Aaj Bohat Jee Udaas Hai;
Jaalib Chalo Kahin Se Usey Dhoond Ke Layen Hum!

 Badla Jo Waqt Gehri Dosti Badal Gayi;
Suraj Dhala To Saaye Ki Surat Badal Gayi;
Ik Umar Tak Main Teri Zarurat Bana Raha;
Fir Yun Hua Ki Teri Zarurat Badal Gayi!

 Dastaan-e-Ishq Main Sabko Sunati Chali Gayi;
Woh Dhaate Rahe Sitam Main Muskurati Chali Gayi;
Na Thi Mujhe Parwah Koi, Na Tha Kisi Ka Dar;
Gamon Ke Sailabon Se Main Yun Hi Takrati Chali Gayi!

 Jo Dil Zinda Hi Na Ho Uske Liye Zindagi Kya Hai;
Lete Rehte Hain Naam Unka Woh Mere Nahi To Kya Hai;
Dhadkta Rehta Hai Kehne Ko To Ye Dil Mera;
Zindagi Chalti Rahe Ya Khatam Ho Humein Matlab Hi Kya Hai!

 Dil Se Bhula Diya, Aankhon Se Kabhi Na Girana;
Humein Itna Tadpaya Kisi Aur Ko Na Tadpana;
Kabhi Mud Ke Dekhoge Un Raahon Pe, Hum Wahi Milenge;
Jaha Socha Tha Kabhi Hoga Apna Bhi Ek Aashiyana!

 Aah Ko Chaahiye

Aah Ko Chaahiye Ik Umr Asar Hote Tak;
Khaak Ho Jayenge Hum Tum Ko Khabar Hote Tak;

Kaun Jeetaa Hai Teri Zulf Ke Sar Hote Tak;
Dil Ka Kyaa Rang Karun Khoon-e-Jigar Hote Tak;

Dekhen Kya Guzre Hai Qatre Pe Guhar Hote Tak;
Garmi-e-Bazm Hai Ik Raqs-e-Sharar Hote Tak;

Gam-e-Hasti Ka Asad Kis Se Ho Jooz Marg Ilaaj;
Hum Ne Maana Ki Tagaful Na Karoge Lekin;

Partav-e-Kur se Hai Shabnam Ko Fanaa Ki Taalim;
Shama Har Rang Mein Jalti Hai Sahar Hote Tak;

Main Bhi Hun Ek Inaayat Ki Nazar Hote Tak;
Yak Nazar Besh Nahin Fursat-e-Hasti Gaafil!

 Aaj Jarurat Hai Jiski Wo Paas Nahi Hai;
Ab Unke Dil Mein Wo Ehsas Nahi Hai;
Tadapte Hain Do Pal Baat Karne Ko;
Shayad Ab Waqt Hamare Liye Unke Pass Nahi Hai!

 Farz Tha Jo Mera Nibha Diya Maine;
Usne Jo Maanga Wo Sab Diya Maine;
Wo Sunke Gairon Ki Baatein Bewafa Ho Geya;
Samajh Kar Khawab Usko Aakhir Bhula Diya Maine!

 Zakham-e-Umeed

Zakham-e-Umeed Bhar Geya Kab Ka;
Qais To Apne Ghar Geya Kab Ka;

Ab To Munh Apna Mat Dikhaao Mujhe;
Naa-Siho Main Sudhar Geya Kab Ka;

Aap Ab Puchne Ko Aaye Hain;
Dil Meri Jaan Mar Geya Kab Ka;

Aap Ik Aur Neend Le Lijiye;
Kaafila Kooch Kar Geya Kab Ka;

Mera Fehrist Se Nikaal Do Naam;
Main To Khud Se Mukar Geya Kab Ka!

 Jo Pyaar Kar Ke Humein Barbaad Karte Hain;
Unko Kabhi Khushiyan Kaise Milegi;
Hum To Unko Jee-Jaan Se Chahate Hain;
Unko Humse Bad-dua Kaise Milegi!

 Jaane Meri Aankhon Se Kitne Aansu Beh Gaye;
Insano Ki Iss Bheed Mein Dekho Hum Tanha Reh Gaye;
Karte The Jo Kabhi Apni Wafa Ki Baatein;
Aaj Wahi Sanam Humein Bewafa Keh Gaye!

 Meri Saari Zindagi Ko
Meri Saari Zindagi Ko Be'samar Iss Ne Kiya;
Umar Meri Thi Magar,Isko Basar Iss Ne Kiya;
Main Bahut Kamzor Tha Iss Mulq Mein Hijrat Ke Baad;
Par Mujhe Iss Mulq Mein Kamzor'tar Iss Ne Kiya;
Rehbar Mera Bana Gumraah Karne Ke Liye;
Mujhko Seedhe Raaste Se Darbadar Iss Ne Kiya;
Shehar Mein Woh Moatbir Meri Gawahi Se Hua;
Phir Mujhe Iss Shehar Mein Na'moatbir Iss Ne Kiya;
Shehar Ko Barbaad Kar Ke Rakh Diya Iss Ne 'Munir';
Shehar Per Yeh Zulm Mere Naam Par Iss Ne Kiya!

 Ghairon Mein Hain Jo Shaad Unhein Eid Mubarak;
Jinko Nahin Hum Yaad Unhein Eid Mubarak;

Masoom Se Armaanon Kee Masoom Si Duniya;

Jo Kar Gaye Barbaad Unhein Eid Mubarak!

 Dil O Nigah Pe Teri
Dil O Nigah Pe Teri Rahe Fasoon Is Ka;
Tumhara Ho Ke Bhi Mumkin Hai Mein Rahoon Us Ka;

Tujhe Khabar Nahin Is Baat Ki Abhi Shayad;
Ki Tera Ho To Geya Hoon Magar Main Hoon Us Ka;

Ab Is Se Qata-Taluq Mein Behtri Hai Meri;
Main Apna Reh Nahin Sakta Agar Rahoon Us Ka;

Zameen Kee Khaak To Kab Ki Udaa Chuke Hain Hum;
Hamari Yaad Mein Hai Ab Chiraag Neelgon Us Ka;

Dil-e-Tabaah Kee Dhadkan Bata Rahi Hai Raza;
Yahin Kahin Pe Hai Woh Sheher Pursakoon Us Ka!

 Kasam De Ke Apni Tujhe Rok Lega;
Teri Laghzishon Pe Tujhe Tok Dega;

Tu Murr Murr Ke Peeche Kise Dekhta Hai;
Tera Kaun Hai Jo Tujhe Rok Lega!
Translation:
Laghzishon = Deviating

 Bedili Se Hansne
Bedili Se Hansne Ko Khush-Dili Na Samjha Jaye;
Gam Se Jalte Chehre Ko Roshni Na Samjha Jaye;
Gaha Gaha Wahshat Mein Ghar Ki Simt Jata Hun;
Isko Dasht-e-Hairat Se Wapsi Na Samjha Jaye;
Lakh Khushguman Duniya Bahimi Talluq Ko;
Dosti Kahein Lekin Dosti Na Samjha Jaye;
Hum To Bas Ye Kehte Hain Roz Jine Marne Ko;
Ap Chahein Kuch Samjhein Zindagi Na Samjha Jaye;
Khak Karne Walon Ki Kya Ajeeb Khwahish Thi;
Khak Hone Walon Ko Khak Hi Na Samjha Jaye!

 Tum Jab Aao Gi, To Khoya Hua Pao Gi Mujhe;
Meri Tanhai Mein, Khawbon Ke Siwa Kuch Bhi Nahin;
Mere Kamrey Ko Sajaaney Ki Tamanna Hai Tumhe;
Mere Kamrey Mein Kitaabon Ke Siwa Kuch Bhi Nahin!

 Tujhse Bicharr Kar
Tujhse Bicharr Kar Kya Hun Main, Ab Bahar Aakar Dekh;
Himmat Hai To Meri Haalat, Aankh Mila Kar Dekh;
Shaam Hai Gehri, Tez Hawaa Hai, Sar Pe Khari Hai Raat;
Rasta Gaye Musafir Ka Ab Diya Jalaa Kar Dekh;
Darwaze Ke Paas Aa Aa Kar Wapis Mudti Chaap;
Kaun Hai Iss Sunsaan Gali Mein, Paas Bula Kar Dekh;
Shayad Koi Dekhne Wala Ho Jaye Khairaan;
Kamre Ki Deewaron Par Koi Naqsh Bana Kar Dekh;
Tu Bhi Munir Ab Bhare Jahaan Mein Mil Kar Rehna Seekh;
Bahar Se To Dekh Liya, Ab Andar Jaa Kar Dekh!

 Kya Sirf Musaan Ke Pyare Hain Hussain;
Chiraag-e-Noh Bashar Ke Tarey Hain Hussain;
Insaan Ko Baidaar To Ho Lene Do Zara Tum;
Har Kaum Pukare Gi Hamare Hain Hussain!

 Tujh Se Gile Karun
Tujh Se Gile Karun Tujhe Janaan Manaun Main;
Ik Bar Apne Aap Mein Aao To Aaun Main;
Dil Se Sitam Kee Be'saro Kaari Hawaa Ko Hai;
Woh Gard Udaa Rahi Hai Ki Khud Ko Ganwaun Main;
Naadim Hun Woh Ki Jis Pe Nadaamat Bhi Ab Nahin;
Woh Kam Hain Ki Apni Judai Kamaaun Main;
Kyon'kar Ho Apne Khawab Kee Aankhon Mein Wapsi;
Kis Taur Apne Dil Ke Zamamun Mein Jaun Main;
Ik Rang Si Kamaan Ho Khushbu Sa Ik Teer;
Marham Si Ik Wardaat Ho Aur Zakham Khaun Main;
Shikwa Sa Ek Dareecha Ho, Nasha Sa Ek Sakoot;
Ho Shaam Ek Sharab Si Aur Larr'khraon Main;
Phir Is Gali Se Apna Guzar Chahta Hai Dil;
Ab Is Gali Ko Kaunsi Basti Se Laaun Main!

 Khamosh Chehre Par Hazaron Pehre Hote Hain;
Hansti Aankhon Mein Bhi Zakham Gehre Hote Hain;
Jinse Aksar Rooth Jaate Hain Hum;
Asal Mein Unse Hi Rishte Gehre Hote Hain!

 Yeh Aur Baat Teri
Yeh Aur Baat Teri Gali Mein Na Aayein Hum;
Lekin Yeh Kya Ki Tera Sheher Chorr Jayein Hum;
Muddat Huyi Hai Kuye Bataan Ki Taraf Gaye;
Awaargi Se Dil Ko Kahan Tak Bachaayein Hum;
Be'noor Ho Chuki Hai Bahut Sheher Kee Fizaa;
Tareek Raaston Par Kahin Kho Na Jayein Hum;
Us Ke Baghair Aaj Bahut Jee Udaas Hai;
Jaalib Chalo Kahin Se Usse Dhoond Kar Layein Hum!

 Khwabon Ke Andar Zinda Mat Raho; 
Balki Apne Andar Khwabon Ko Zinda Rakho; 
Mohabbat Usse Nahin Hoti Hai Jo Khoobsurat Ho;
Khoobsurat To Wo Hota Hai Jisse Mohabbat Hoti Hai!

 Jab Se Sanam Tum Ko Paya Hai;
Tere Har Hukum Ko Sar Aankhon Pe Bithaya Hai;
Aur Kya De Sakta Hun Main Tum Ko Sanam;
Roshni Tujhe Dene Ke Liye Khud Ko Jalaya Hai!

 Be-Karaan Tanhaayion Ka
Be-Karaan Tanhaayion Ka Silsila Reh Jaaye Ga;
Tere Mere Darmiyaan, Bas Ik Khalaa Reh Jaaye Ga;
Aks Beh Jaayein Ge Saare Dhoop Ke Sailaab Mein;
Aur Koi Paanion Mein Jhaankta Reh Jaaye Ga;
Mujh Ko Mere Hamsafar Aisa Safar Darpaish Hai;
Raasta Kat Bhee Gaya To Fansla Reh Jaaye Ga;
Log So Jaayein Ge Khamoshi Ki Chaadar Aud Kar;
Chaand Soone Aanganon Mein Jaagta Reh Jaaye Ga;
Jo Kabhi Us Ne Parheen Theen Mujh Se 'Nasir' Maang Kar;
Naam Mera Unn Kitaabon Mein Likha Reh Jaaye Ga!

 Aage Bare Na
Aage Bare Na Qissa-e-Ishq-e-Butan Se Hum;
Sab Kuch Kaha Magar Na Khule Razdan Se Hum;
Ab Bhaagte Hain Saya-e-Ishq-e-Butan Se Hum;
Kuch Dil Se Hain Dare Hue Kuch Aasman Se Hum;
Hanste Hain Us Ke Giriya-e-Beikhtiyar Par;
Bhule Hain Baat Keh Kar Koi Razadan Se Hum;
Ab Shauq Se Bigar Kar Batein Kiya Karo;
Kuch Pa Gaye Hain Aap Kee Tarz-e-Bayan Se Hum;
Jannat Mein Tu Nahin Agar Ye Zakhm-e-Teg-e-Ishq;
Badlenge Tujhko Zindagi-e-Jawidan Se Hum!

 Mohabbat Ka Imtihan Aasan Nahi;
Pyar Sirf Pane Ka Naam Nahi;
Muddatein Beet Jati Hain Kisi Ke Intezar Mein;
Ye Sirf Pal-Do-Pal Ka Kaam Nahi!

 Dil O Nigah Pe
Dil O Nigah Pe Taari Rahe Fasoon Iska;
Tumhara Ho Ke Bhi Mumkin Hai Mein Rahoon Uska;
Tujhe Khabar Nahin Is Baat Ki Abhi Shayed;
Ke Tera Ho To Geya Hoon Magar Mein Hoon Uska;
Ab Is Se Qata-Taluq Mein Behtri Hai Meri;
Main Apna Reh Nahin Sakta Agar Rahoon Uska;
Zameen Ki Khaak To Kab Ki Urraa Chuke Hain Hum;
Hamari Zadd Mein Hai Ab Chiraag Neelgon Uska;
Dil-e-Tabaah Ki Dharkan Bata Rahi Hai Raza;
Yahin Kahin Pe Hai Woh Sheher Pursakoon Uska!

 Kal Yeh Likhti Theen
Kal Yeh Likhti Thee Bicharna Tumhein Manzoor Nahi;
Ab Yeh Kehti Ho Mere Khat Mujhe Wapis Kar Do;
Main Safaayi Koi Doon Ga Na Wazaahat Dunga;
Tum Ko Wapis Main Tumhari Yeh Amaanat Dunga;
Phir Kabhi Tumse Na Milne Kee Zamanat Dunga;
Bas Tumhein Tark-e-Marasim Pe Yeh Zehmat Dunga;
Tum Ho Bechain To Main Bhi Koi Masroor Nahin;
Kal Yeh Likhti Thee Bicharna Tumhein Manzoor Nahi;
Ab Yeh Kehti Ho Mere Khat Mujhe Wapis Kar Do!

 Umeed To Manzil Pe Pahunchne Kee Bari Thi;
Taqdeer Magar Jaane Kahan Soyi Pari Thi;
Khush The Ki Guzarein Ge Rafaqat Mein Safar Ab;
Tanhayi Magar Baahon Ko Phir Khole Khari Thi!

 Agar Yun Hi Ye Dil 
Agar Yun Hi Ye Dil Satata Rahega;
To Ik Din Mera Jee Hi Jata Rahega;
Main Jata Hun Dil Ko Tere Pas Chore;
Meri Yaad Tujhko Dilata Rahega;
Gali Se Teri Dil Ko Le To Chala Hun;
Main Pahunchunga Jab Tak Yeh Aata Rahega;
Qafas Main Koi Tum Se Ai Ham-Safiron;
Khabar Kal Kee Humko Sunata Rahega;
Khafa Ho Ki Ai Dard Mar To Chala Tu;
Kahan Tak Gham Apna Chupata Rahega!

 Ikk Zara Haath Badha Dein To Pakad Lein Daaman;
Uske Seene Mein Sama Jaaye Hamari Dhadkan;
Itni Kurbat Hai To Phir Faaslaa Itna Kyun Hai!

 Gham e Dunia Mein Gham e Yaar Bhi Shamil Kar Lo;
Nasha Bhadta Hai Sharabein Jo Sharabon Mein Milein;
Ab Na Wo Main Hun Na Tu Hai Na Wo Mazi Hai 'Faraz';
Jaise Do Saye Tamanna Ke Sarabon Mein Milein!

 Ranjish Hi Sahi Dil

Ranjish Hi Sahi Dil Mein Dukhane Ke Liye Aa
Aa Phir Se Mujhe Chor Jaane Ke Liye Aa;

Kuch To Mere Pand-e-Ray Mohabbat Ka Bharam Rakh;
Tu Bhi To Kabhi Mujh Ko Manane Ke Liye Aa;

Pehle Se Maraasam Na Sahi Phir Bhi Kabhi To Aa;
Rasmo Waar-e-Duniya Hi Nibhane Ke Liye Aa;

Kis Kis Ko Batayein Ge Judaai Ka Sabab Hum;
Tu Mujh Se Khafa Hai Tu Zamane Ke Liye Aa;

Ab Tak Dil-e-Khush Faham Tujh Se Hain Umeedein;
Ye Aakhiri Shamma Bhi Bujhanay Ke Liye Aa!

 Giley Hain Hazaron Ki Badle Ho Kyon Tum;
Magar Ab Karein Kyon Gila Ajnabi Se;
Azab Hai Neendein Ganwane Ka Silsila;
Yeh Acha Nahin Silsila Ajnabi Se!

 Ajnabi Khauf Fizaon
Ajnabi Khauf Fizaon Mein Basa Ho Jaise;
Shehar Ka Shehar Hi Aseb Zada Ho Jaise;
Raat Ke Pichle Pehar Aati Hain Awazein Si;
Dur Shehara Mein Koi Cheekh Raha Ho Jaise;
Dar-o-Deewar Pe Chayi Hai Udasi Aisi;
Aaj Har Ghar Se Janaza Sa Utha Ho Jaise;
Muskurata Hun Pa-e-Khatir-e-Ahabab Magar;
Dukh To Chehre Kee Lakion Pe Saja Ho Jaise;
Ab Agar Doob Gaya Bhi To Marunga Na 'Kamal';
Behte Pani Pe Mera Naam Likha Ho Jaise!

 Duniya Ke Sitam Yaad
Duniya Ke Sitam Yaad Na Apni Wafaa Yaad;
Ab Mujh Ko Nahi Kuch Bhi Mohabbat Ke Siwa Yaad;
Main Shikwa Ba Lab Tha, Mujhe Ye Bhi Na Raha Yaad;
Shayad Ki Mere Bhoolne Waale Ne Kiya Yaad;
Kya Jaaniye Kya Ho Geya Arbaab-e-Junoon Ko;
Jeene Kee Adaa Yaad Na Marne Kee Adaa Yaad;
Kya Lutf Ki Main Apna Pataa Aap Bataaun;
Kijiye Koi Bhooli Hui Khaas Apni Adaa Yaad;
Muddat Hui Ek Haadsa-e-Ishq Ko Lekin;
Ab Tak Hai Tere Dil Ke Dhadakane Kee Sadaa Yaad!

 Pathar Zehan Gulaab Nahi Hunde;
Korey Waraq Kitaab Nahi Hunde;
Je Ker Laaiye Yaari Sajna;
Fir Yaraan Naal Hisaab Nahi Hunde!

 Sadmaa To Hai Mujhe Bhi
Sadmaa To Hai Mujhe Bhi Ki Tujhse Judaa Hun Main;
Lekin Yeh Sochta Hun Ki Ab Tera Kya Hun Main;
Main Khudkushi Ke Jurm Ka Karta Hun Aitraaf;
Apne Badan Ki Kabr Mein, Kab Se Garrhaa Hun Main;
Kis Kis Ka Naam Laaun Zubaan Par Ki Tere Saath;
Har Roz Ek Shaks Naya Dekhta Hun;
Kya Jaane Kis Adaa Se Liya Tune Mera Naam;
Duniya Samajh Rahi Hai, Ki Sab Kuch Tera Hun Main;
Le Mere Tajrubon Se Sabak, Aye Mere Raqeeb;
Do-Chaar Saal Umar Mein, Tujhse Barra Hun Main;
Jaaga Huwa Zameer Woh Aiyena Hai 'Qateel';
Sone Se Pehle Roz, Jise Dekhta Raha Hun Main!

 Aiven Rus Ke Na Sathon Mukh Mod Mitra;
Sada Tere Toh Baghair Kehda Hor Mitra;
Othe Hundi E Umeed Jithe Jor Mitra;
Tainu Saadi Nahi Par Saanu Teri Lohr Mitra!

 Nazar Se Nazar Ko Milao Nazar Ka Aitbar Karo;
Hum Tum Se Sanam, Tum Hum Se Pyaar Karo;
Tum Jo Rootho To Kuch Bhi Karke Manaayein Tumko;
Hum Jo Pal Bhar Ko Jayein To Tum Intezar Karo!

 Khuda Hum Ko
Khuda Hum Ko Aisi Khudayi Na De;
Ki Apne Siwa Kuch Dikhayi Na De;
Khatawar Samjhey Gi Duniya Tujhe;
Ab Itni Zayada Safai Na De;
Hanso Aj Itna Ki Is Shor Me;
Sada Siskiyon Kee Sunayi Na De;
Ghulami Ko Barkat Samjhney Lagein;
Aseeron Ko Aisi Rihayi Na De;
Khuda Aise Ehsas Ka Naam Hai;
Rahe Sahmne Aur Dikhayi Na De;
Mujhe Aisi Jannat Nahi Chahiye;
Jahan Se Madina Dikhayi Na Dey!

 Na Jaane Kab Koi Taara Toot Jaaye;
Na Jaane Kab Koi Aansu Aankh Se Chhoot Jaaye;
Kuch Pal Hamare Saath Bhi Has Lo;
Na Jaane Kab Tumhare Daant Toot Jaaye!

 Hum Aaj Bhi Dil Ka Aashiyana Sajane Se Darte Hain;
Baagon Mein Phool Khilane Se Darte Hain;
Hamari Ek Pasand Se Tut Jaayeinge Hazaaro Dil;
Tabhi Toh Hum Aaj Bhi Girlfriend Bananey Se Darte Hain!

 Tere Didar Ki Talab Rakhta Tha;
Tujhse Pyaar ki Chahaht Rakhta Tha;
Tujhse Izhaar Ki Bhi Sada Rakhta Tha;
Rakh Na Paya To Sirf Izhaar-e-Junoon!

 Kahan Koi Aisa Mila Jis Pe Dil Luta Dete;

Har Ek Ne Dhokha Diya Kis-Kis Ko Bhula Dete;

Apne Dil Ka Dard Dil Hi Mein Dabaye Rakhe Hain;

Karte Bayan To Mehfil Ko Rula Dete!

 Mat Phenk Pani Me Pathhar;

Usey Bhi Koi Peeta Hai;

Mat Raho Yun Udaas Zindagi Mein;

Tumhe Dekh Kar Bhi Koi Jeeta Hai!

 Kahin Aah Ban Ke

Kahin Aah Ban Ke Lab Per Tera Naam Aa Na Jaye;

Tujhe Bewafa Kahoon Main, Woh Muqaam Aa Na Jaye;

Jise Sun Ke Toot Jaye Mera Aarzu Bhara Dil;

Tere Anjuman Se Mujh Ko Woh Peyaam Aa Na Jaye;

Woh Jo Manzilon Par Laa Kar Kisi Hamsafar Ko Lootein;

Unhi Rehzanon Mein Tera Kahin Naam Aa Na Jaye;

Isi Fikar Mein Hain Ghalat Yeh Nizaam Ke Bande;

Jo Tamaam Zindagi Hai Woh Nizaam Aa Na Jaye!

 Giley Hain Hazaron Ki Badle Ho Kyon Tum;
Magar Ab Karein Kyon Gilaa Ajnabi Se;
Azab Hai Neendein Ganwane Ka Silsila;
Yeh Acha Nahin Silsila Ajnabi Se!

 Rabb To Pyara Koi Naam Nahi Hunda;
Ohdi Nigha Vich Koi Aam Ya Khas Nahi Hunda;
Duniya Di Mohabbat Vich Hai Dhokhebazi;
Par Usdi Mohabbat Vich Koi Badnaam Nahi Hunda!

 Band Aankh Se Sapne 
Band Aankh Se Sapne Bunte Bunte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni;
Tootey Dil Ke Raizey Chunte Chunte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni;
Woh Hum Se Bichar Kar Kaise Jeeta Hoga;
Bass Yehi Sochte Sochte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni;
Us Ki Talaash Mein Nikle, Apna Pata Bhool Gaye;
Phir Khud Ko Khojte Khojte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni;
Shamaa Ban To Gaye Roshni Ki Khatir;
Magar Phir Jalte Jalte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni;
Uss Ne Manaa Ki Deewaar Torr Kar Pukaara To Sahi;
Lekin Rukte Rukte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni;
Ab Yeh Zindagi Ussi Ki Amaanat Hai Waqas;
Jiss Ki Raah Takte Takte Umar Guzar Gayi Apni!

 Kisi De Ishq Ch Ki Ki Mukaam Aunde Ne;
Kade Khushi Kade Gam De Paigaam Aunde Ne;
Hanera Chhaya Taan, Mere Saaye Ne Bhi Sath Chadd Ditta;
Sunya Si Samay Te Apne Hi Kamm Aunde Ne!

 Paikar Tha Wafa Ka
Paikar Tha Wafa Ka, Mohabbat Ka Khuda Tha;
Woh Shakhs Zamane Mein Sab Se Hi Juda Tha;
Chahat Ke Khazane They Har Lafz Mein Us Ke;
Daaman Mera Us Ne Duaaon Se Bhara Tha;
Mujh Ko Nahin Dekha Karri Dhoop Ne Chu Kar;
Baba Mera Duniya Main Mujhe Aisa Jo Mila Tha;
Fikrein Na Zamane Ki Kabhi Paas Bhi Aayi;
Har Dard Meri Hasti Se Dartaa Hi Raha Tha;
Jab Tak Raha Saanson Ka Basera Mere Baba;
Tab Tak Main Ghamon Se Bachta Hi Raha Tha;
Us Shaam Ki Hiddat Mere Dil Se Nahin Jati;
Jis Shaam Tera Saaya Mere Sar Se Utha Tha!

 Khaali Hath Bazaar Vichon Langh Aaye;
Doonghi Soch Vichar Vichon Langh Aaye;
Jithe Phul Te Chaadra'n Charh Diyaan Ne;
Assi Te Uss Mazaar Vichon Bhi Langh Aaye!

 Lutf Wo Ishq Mein Paaye
Lutf Wo Ishq Mein Paaye Hain Ki Jee Jaanta Hai;
Ranj Bhi Aise Uthaaye Hain Ki Jee Jaanta Hai;
Jo Zamaane Ke Sitam Hain Wo Zamaana Jaane;
Tu Ne Dil Itne Sataaye Hain Ki Jee Jaanta Hai;
Muskurate Hue Woh Mazmaa-e-Agyaar Ke Saath;
Aaj Yun Bazm Mein Aaye Hain Ki Jee Jaanta Hai;
Kaaba-o-Dair Mein Pathra Gayi Dono Aankhein;
Aise Jalwe Nazar Aaye Hain Ki Jee Jaanta Hai;
Dosti Mein Teri Dar-Pardah Hamaare Dushman;
Is Qadar Apne Paraaye Hain Ki Jee Jaanta Hai;
Daagh-e-Waarafta Ko Ham Aaj Tere Kooche Se;
Is Tarah Kheench Ke Laaye Hain Ki Jee Jaanta Hai!

 Saanson Ki Hararat Se
Saanson Ki Hararat Se Pighal Jaanay Ka Mausam;
Aaya Hai Teri Aanch Mein Jal Jaanay Ka Mausam;
Ham Ko Nahi Maloom Tha Ishq Ka Aaghaaz;
Yaadon Mein Kahin Door Nikal Jaanay Ka Mausam;
Lagta Hai Ki Chehre Pe Tere Theher Gaya Hai;
Yak Lakht Kayi Rang Badal Jaanay Ka Mausam;
Aey Sheher Tasalli Tere Mashkoor Hain Ham;
Aaya Hee Nahi Dil Ke Sambhal Jaanay Ka Mausam;
Ye Sheher-e-Tamanna Bhi Anokha Hai Ki Is Par;
Barsaat Mein Bhi Rehta Hai Thal Jaanay Ka Mausam;
Chehre Pe Agar Hai Mere Subaah Ka Ujaala;
Aankhon Mein Magar Shaam Ke Dhal Jaanay Ka Mausam!

 Sun To Sahi Jahaan Mein
Sun To Sahi Jahaan Mein Hai Tera Fasanaa Kyaa;
Kehti Hai Tujh Se Khalq-e-Khudaa Gaibanaa Kya;
Jeena Saba Dhundti Hai Apni Musht-e-Khaak;
Baam-e-Buland Yaar Ka Hai Astana Kya;
Aati Hai Kis Tarah Se Meri Kabz-e-Rooh Ko;
Dekhun To Maut Dhund Rahi Hai Bahana Kya;
Betab Hai Kamal Hamara Dil-e-Azeem;
Mehman Sara-e-Jism Ka Hoga Ravanaa Kya!

 Chandni Raat Bari Der Ke Baad Aayi;
Yeh Mulaqat Bari Der Ke Baad Aayi;
Aaj Aye Hain Woh Milne Ko Bari Der Ke Baad;
Aaj Ki Raat Bari Der Ke Baad Aayi!

 Doosron Ko Hamari
Doosron Ko Hamari Sazaayen Na De;
Chandni Raat Ko Bad'duyain Na De;
Phool Se Aashiqui Ka Hunar Seekh Le;
Titliyan Khud Rukein Gee Sadayen Na De;
Motiyon Ko Chupaa Sipiyon Ki Tarah;
Bewafaon Ko Apni Wafayen Na De;
Main Bikhar Jaaon Aansuon Ki Tarah;
Is Qadar Pyar Se Bad'duyain Na De!

 Jo Zindagi Vich Hoya Ohi Geetan Vich Main Likheya;
Changa Ya Maada Thokran Kha Kha Ke Main Sikheya;

Par Hun Pta Lagga Zindagi Jeeni Ini Aasan Nahi;
Paise Ton Bina Ithe Kise Di Koi Shaan Nahi!

 Mohabbat Se Rihaa
Mohabbat Se Rihaa Hona Zaroori Ho Geya Hai;
Mera Tujh Se Judaa Hona Zaroori Ho Geya Hai;
Wafaa Ke Tazurbey Karte Hue To Umar Guzri;
Zara Sa Bewafa Hona Zaroori Ho Geya Hai;
Meri Awaaz Tanhaai Mein Marti Ja Rahi Hai;
Kisi Ka Hamnawaa Hona Zaroori Ho Geya Hai;
Azaab Zulmat-e-Shab Hai Ki Ab Dil Ke Labon Par;
Koi Harf-e-Duaa Hona Zaroori Ho Geya Hai!

 Likhan Waliya Ho Ke Dyal Likh De;
Meri Kismat Vich Meri Jaan Da Pyar Likh De;
Likhi Na Us Naal Mera Kade Vi Vichoda;
Hor Bhavein Dukh Sanu Hazaar Likh De!

 Mujh Se Kaafir Ko

Mujh Se Kaafir Ko Tere Ishq Ne Yun Sharmaya;
Dil Tujhe Dekh Ke Dhadka Toh Khudaa Yaad Aaya;
Mere Dil Pe Toh Hai Ab Tak Tere Gham Ka Saaya;
Log Kehte Hain Naya Daur Naye Dukh Laya;
Mera Meyaar-e-Wafaa Hi Meri Majboori Hai;
Rukh Badal Kar Bhi Tujhe Apne Muqaabil Paya;
Charagar Aaj Sitaron Ki Kasam Kha Ke Bata;
Kis Ne Insaan Ko Tabasum Ke Liye Tadpaya;
Log Hanste Hain Toh Is Soch Mein Kho Jata Hun;
Mauj-e-Sailaab Ne Phir Kis Ka Gharaunda Dhaaya;
Uss Ke Andar Koi Fankaar Chupaa Baitha Hai;
Jaantey Boojhtey Jis Shakhs Ne Dhokha Khaya!

 Jise Khud Se Hi Nahin Furstein;
Jise Khayal Apne Kamaal Ka;
Useh Kya Khabar Mere Shaunq Ki;
Useh Kya Pata Mere Haal Ka!

 Eh Zindagi Di Chahat Da Silsila Hai;
Koi Mil Geya Te Koi Vichhar Gya;
Jinna Nu Mangya Si Duavaan Ch;
Oh Kisi Hor Nu Bina Mange Mil Gya!

 Ajab Apna Haal Hota
Ajab Apna Haal Hota Jo Visaal-e-Yaar Hota;
Kabhi Jaan Sadqe Hoti Kabhi Dil Nisaar Hota;
Na Mazaa Hai Dushmani Mein Na Hai Lutf Dosti Mein;
Koi Gair Gair Hota Koi Yaar Yaar Hota;
Yeh Mazaa Tha Dillagi Ka Ke Barabar Aag Lagti;
Na Tumhein Qaraar Hota Na Hamein Qaraar Hota;
Tere Vaade Par Sitamgar Abhi Aur Sabr Karte;
Agar Apni Zindagi Ka Hamein Aitbaar Hota!

 Kabhi Yeh Chup Mein Kabhi Meri Baat Baat Mein Tha;
Tumhara Akss Meri Saari Qayenaat Mein Tha;
Hum Ehl-e-Ishq Bahut Bad-Guhmaan Hote Hain;
Isi Tarah Ka Koi Vasf Teri Jaat Mein Tha!
Translation:
Vasf = Ability

 Umeed To Manzil Pe Pahunchne Ki Bari Thi;
Taqdeer Magar Janay Kahan Soyi Parri Thi;
Khush They Ke Guzarein Gey Rafaqat Mein Safar Ab;
Tanhayee Magar Baahon Ko Phir Kholey Khari Thi!

 Rabb Toh Pyara Koi Naam Nahi Hunda;
Ohdi Nigha Vich Koi Aam Ya Khaas Nahi Hunda;
Duniya Di Mohhabat Vich Hai Dhokhebazi;
Par Usdi Mohabbat Ch Koi Badnaam Nahi Hunda!

 Meri Saari Zindagi Ko

Meri Saari Zindagi Ko Besamar Iss Ne Kiya;
Umar Meri Thi Magar, Isko Basar Iss Ne Kiya;
Main Bahut Kamzor Tha Iss Mulq Mein Hijrat Ke Baad;
Par Mujhe Iss Mulq Mein Kamzor'tar Iss Ne Kiya;
Rehbar Mera Bana Gumraah Karne Ke Liye;
Mujhko Seedhey Raaste Se Darbadar Iss Ne Kiya;
Shehar Mein Woh Moatbir Meri Gawahi Se Huwa;
Phir Mujhe Iss Shehar Mein Na'moatbir Iss Ne Kiya;
Shehar Ko Barbaad Kar Ke Rakh Diya Iss Ne 'Munir';
Shehar Per Yeh Zulm Mere Naam Per Iss Ne Kiya!

 Khudaa Buri Nazar Se Bachaye Aap Ko;
Chand Sitaron Se Sajaye Aap Ko;
Ghum Kya Hota Hai Ye Aap Bhool Hi Jao;
Khudaa Zindagi Mein Itna Hasaye Aap Ko!

 Dono Jahaan Teri Mohabbat
Dono Jahaan Teri Mohabbat Mein Haar Ke;
Wo Ja Raha Hai Koi Shab-e-Gham Guzaar Ke;
Viraan Hai Maikada Khum-o-Sagar Udaas Hai;
Tum Kya Gaye Ki Rooth Gaye Din Bahaar Ke;
Ik Fursat-e-Gunaah Mili, Wo Bhi Chaar Din;
Dekhe Hain Ham Ne Hausale Parvar-Digaar Ke;
Duniya Ne Teri Yaad Se Begaana Kar Diya;
Tujh Se Bhi Dil Fareb Hain Gham Rozgaar Ke;
Bhule Se Muskura To Diye The Wo Aaj 'Faiz';
Mat Puch Val-Vale Dil-e-Na-Kardahkaar Ke!

 Rahiye Ab Aisi Jagha Chal Kar Jahan Koi Na Ho;
Hum-Sukhan Koi Na Ho, Aur Hum-Zubaan Koi Na Ho;
Parriye Gar Beemar To Koi Na Ho Teemar'daaar;
Aur Agar Mar Jaayiye To Noha-Khuwaa'n Koi Na Ho!
Translation:
Teemar'daaar = Caretaker
Noha-Khuwaa'n = Reciter

 Har Roz Nave Bahaane Di Duhaai Na Deya Kar;
Milna Nahi Hunda Tan Dikhayi Na Deya Kar;
Hun Teriyan Gallan Ch Sachayi Nahi Mildi;
Avein Apne Pyar Di Safai Na Deya Kar!

 Sun To Sahi Jahaan Main
Sun To Sahii Jahaan Main Hai Teraa Fasanaa Kyaa;
Kehti Hai Tujh Se Khalq-e-Khudaa Gaibanaa Kya;
Zina Saba Kaa Dhundati Hai Apni Musht-e-Khaak;
Baam-e-Baland Yaar Ka Hai Astana Kya;
Aati Hai Kis Tarah Se Meri Kabz-e-Ruuh Ko;
Dekhun To Maut Dhund Rahi Hai Bahana Kya;
Betaab Hai Kamal Hamara Dil-e-Azeem;
Mahmaan Saray-e-Jism Ka Hoga Ravana Kya!

 Wafaa Mein Ab Yeh Hunar Ikhtiyaar Karna Hai;
Woh Sach Kahe Na Kahe Aitbaar Karna Hai;
Yeh Tujh Ko Jaagte Rehne Ka Shauq Kab Se Hua;
Mujhe To Khair Tera Intezaar Karna Hai!

 Ranj Ki Jab
Ranj Ki Jab Guftaguu Honay Lagi;
Aap Se Tum Tum Se Tu Honay Lagi;
Chahye Paighambar Dono Taraf;
Lutf Kya Jab Du-Ba-Du Honay Lagi;
Meri Ruswayi Ki Naubat Aagayi;
Unki Shohrat Qu-Ba-Qu Honay Lagi;
Be Niazi Badh Gayi Hai Is Qadar;
Aarzoo Ki Aarzoo Honay Lagi;
Ab To Mil Kar Dekhiye Kya Rang Ho;
Phir Hamari Justajuu Honay Lagi;
`Daagh` Itraaye Huey Phirtay Hain Aaj;
Shaayad Unki Aabruu Honay Lagi!

 Ek Toote Hue Dil Ki Aawaaz Mujhe Kahiye;
Sur Jismein Hai Sab Gum Ke Woh Saaz Mujhe Kahiye;
Main Kaun Hoon Aur Kyaa Hoon Kiske Liye Zindaa Hoon;
Main Khud Bhi Nahi Samjha Woh Raaz Mujhe Kahiye!

 Jo Assar Hai Akh Di Maar Ander;
Oh Na Teer Te Na Talwaar Ander;
Ohna Rab Nu Labh Ke Ki Lena;
Jinna Paa Leya Rab Nu Yaar Ander!

 Ajnabi Khauf Fizaon Main
Ajnabi Khauf Fizaon Mein Basa Ho Jaise;
Shahar Ka Shahar Hi Aseb Zada Ho Jaise;

Raat Ke Pichle Pahar Aati Hain Awazein Si;
Dur Shahara Mein Koi Cheekh Raha Ho Jaise;

Dar-O-Deewar Pe Chayi Hai Udaasi Aisi;
Aaj Har Ghar Se Janaza Sa Utha Ho Jaise;

Muskurata Hun Pa-e-Khatir-e-Ahabab Magar;
Dukh To Chehre Ki Lakiron Pe Saja Ho Jaise;

Ab Agar Dub Gaya Bhi To Marunga Na 'Kamal';
Bahte Pani Pe Mera Naam Likha Ho Jaise!

 Wo Keh Ke Chale
Wo Keh Ke Chale Itni Mulaqat Bahut Hai;
Maine Kaha Ruk Jao Abhi Raat Bahut Hai;
Aansoo Mere Thum Jayein To Phir Shaunq Say Jana;
Aisay Mein Kahan Jaogi Barsaat Bahut Hai;
Wo Kehne Lagi Jana Mera Bahut Zaroori Hai;
Nahi Chahti Dil Todun Tera Par Majboori Hai;
Gar Hui Ho Koi Khata To Maaf Ker Dena;
Maine Kaha Ho Jao Chup Itni Kahi Baat Bahut Hai;
Samajh Geya Hu Sab Aur Kuch Kaho Zaroori Nahi;
Bas Aaj Ki Raat Ruk Jao, Jana Itna Bhi Zaroori Nahi Hai;
Phir Kabhi Na Aaonga Tumhari Zindagi Mein Laut Ke;
Saari Zindagi Tanhayee Ke Liye, Aaj Ki Raat Bahut Hai;

 Koi Aakhda Rabb Da Roop Ehnu;
Koi Rabb Da Ehnu Wazir Aakhe;
Rabb V Ohnu Nai Mod Sakda;
Gal Mauj Vich Jehdi Fakeer Aakhe!

 Yehi Nahi Ki Toofan Meri
Yehi Nahi Ki Toofan Meri Talaash Mein Hai;
Ki Mausam-e-Gham-e-Jaanan Meri Talaash Mein Hai;
Visaal Rut Hai Magar Dil Ko Aisa Lagta Hai;
Sitaarah-e-Shab-e-Hijraan Meri Talaash Mein Hai;
Main Faislay Kee Ghari Se Guzar Chali Hun;
Kisi Kee Deeda-e-Hairaan Meri Talaash Mein Hai;
Ye Be Yaqeen Si Aasoodgi Batati Hai;
Ki Ik Qirya-e-Veeran Meri Talaash Mein Hai;
Main Teergi Mein Mohabbat Kee Ik Kahani Hun;
Koi Chiraagh Sa Unwaan Meri Talaash Mein Hai;
Ye Kaisa Khwaab Tha Dharka Sa Lag Gaya Dil Ko;
Ki Ik Shaks Pareshaan Meri Talaash Mein Hai!

 Socha Tha Har Modd Par Tumhara Intezar Karenge;
Gaur Farmaiye:
Socha Tha Har Modd Par Tumhara Intezar Karenge;
Magar Kambakhat Saali Sadak Hi Seedhi Nikli!

 Na Muskurane Ko Jee Chahta Hai;
Na Khane-Peene aur Na Hi Sone Ko Jee Chahta Hai;
Yeh Garmi Abb Bardasht Karni Hai Badi Mushkil;
Abb To Paharon Pe Chale Jane Ko Jee Chahta Hai!

 Kadi Mehak Nahi Mukdi Phullan Vichon;
Phul Sukde Sukde Suk Jandey;
Kadi Pyar Nahi Mukda Dilan Vichon;
Saah Mukde Mukde Muk Jandey!

 Khulta Nahin Hai Haal
Khulta Nahin Hai Haal Kisi Par Kahe Bagair;
Par Dil Kee Jaan Lete Hain Dilbar Kahe Bagair;
Main Kaise Kahun Tum Aao Ki Dil Kee Kashish Se Wo;
Ayenge Daude Aap Mere Ghar Kahe Bagair;
Kya Taab Kya Majal Hamari Ki Bosa Lein;
Lab Ko Tumhare Lab Se Milakar Kahe Bagair;
Bedard Tu Sune Na Sune Lek Dard-e-Dil;
Rehta Nahin Hai Aashiq-E-Muztar Kahe Bagair;
Taqdir Ke Siwa Nahin Milta Kahin Se Bhi;
Dilawata Ae 'Zafar' Hai Muqaddar Kahe Bagair!

 Bartan Lohe Da Kadi Tutda Nahi;
Maali Kadi Apne Baag Nu Putda Nahi;
Tut Janday Kadi Kadi Khoon De Rishte;
Par Rishte Sachi Dosti De Kadi Tutde Nahi!

 Na Jane Kin Adaaon Se
Na Jane Kin Adaaon Se Lubhaa Liya Geya Mujhe; 
Qateel Mere Samney Churaa Liya Geya Mujhe;
Kabhi Jo Un Ke Jashn Mein Seyaahiyan Bikhar Gayin;
To Roshni Ke Vaastey Jalaa Liya Geya Mujhe;
Barah-e-Raast Raabta Na Mujhse Tha Qabool Unhe;
Likhaa Ke Khat Raqeeb Se Bulaa Liya Geya Mujhe;
Jab Un Ke Deed Ke Liye Qataar Mein Kharra Tha Main;
Qataar Se Na Jaane Kyun Hattaa Liye Geya Mujhe;
Main Rondney Ki Cheez Tha Kisi Ke Paon Se Magar;
Kabhi Kabhi To Zulf Mein Sajaa Liya Geya Mujhe;
Sawaal Tha Ki Wafaa Hai Kya, Jawab Tha Ki Zindagi;
Qateel Pyar Se Galey Laga Liya Geya Mujhe!

 Qasam De Ke Apni Tujhe Rok Ley Ga;

Teri Laghzishon Pe Tujhe Tok De Ga;

Tu Murr Murr Ke Piche Kise Dekhta Hai;

Tera Kaun Hai Jo Tujhe Rok Le Ga!

Translation:

Laghzishon = Deviating

 Taskeen Na Ho Jis Se

Taskeen Na Ho Jis Se Wo Raaz Badal Dalo;

Jo Raaz Na Rakh Paye Hamraaz Badal Dalo;

Tum Ne Bhi Suni HoGi Bari Aam Kahawat Hai;

Anjam Ka Jo Ho Khatra Aghaz Badal Dalo;

Pur-Soz Dilon Ko Jo Muskan Na De Paye;

Sur Hi Na Mile Jis Mein Wo Saaz Badal Dalo;

Dushman Ke Iradon Ko Hai Zahir Agar Karna;

Tum Khel Wohi Khelo Andaz Badal Dalo;

Ay Dost Karo Himmat Kuch Door Savera Hai;

Agar Chahte Ho Manzil To Parwaaz Badal Dalo!

 Tere Har Gum Ko Apni Rooh Mein Utaar Loon;
Zindagi Apni Teri Chahat Mein Sawaar Loon;
Mulaqat Ho Tujhse Kuch Is Tarah Meri;
