Assi Taan Tere Bina Jee Ke V Ki Karde!

 Mohabbat Ki Aseeri Se

Mohabbat Ki Aseeri Se Rihaayi Maangtay Rehna;
Bahut Aasaan Nahi Hota Judaai Maangtay Rehna;

Zara Sa Ishq Kar laina, Zara Si Aankh Bhar Laina;
Iwaz Iske Magar Saari Khudaai Maangtay Rehna;

Kabhi Mehroom Honton Par Dua Ka Harf Rakh Dena;
Kabhi Wehshat Mein Uski Naarsaayi Maangtay Rehna;

Wafaaon Ke Tasalsul Se Mohabbat Rooth Jaati Hai;
Dil Ki Sakoot-e-Shaam-e-Gham Se Humnawaayi Maangtay Rehna;

Kabhi Bachay Ke Nannay Haath Par Titli Ke Par Rakhna;
Kabhi Phir Uske Rangon Se Rihaayi Maangtay Rehna!

 Arman Koi Seene Mein Aag Laga Deta Hai;
Khwab Koi Akar Raaton Ki Neend Uda Deta Hai;
Punchta Hoon Jisse Bhi Manzil Ka Pata Ab To;
Vo Rasta Tere Ghar Ka Hi Bata Deta Hai!

 Koi Naa Jaan Saka

Koi Naa Jaan Saka Woh Kahan Se Aaya Tha;
Aur Us Ne Dhoop Se Baadal Ko Kyon Milaya Tha;

Yeh Baat Shayad Logon Ko Pasand Aayi Nahin;
Makaa'n Chota Tha Lekin Bohat Sajaya Tha;

Woh Ab Wahan Hai Jahan Raste Nahin Jate;
Main Jis Ke Sath Yahan Pichle Saal Aya Tha;

Suna Hai Us Pe Chehekne Lage Hain Parindey Bhi;
Woh Aik Pau'daa Jo Hum Ne Kabhi Lagaya Tha;

Chiragh Doob Gaye Kapkapaye Honton Par;
Kisi Ka Hath Hamare Labo'n Tak Aya Tha;

Badan Ko Chorr Ke Jana Hai Aasman Ki Taraf;
Samundro'n Ne Humein Yeh Sabaq Parhaya Tha;

Tamam Umar Mera Dam Isi Dhuyein Mein Ghutta;
Woh Ik Chiragh Thaa Maine Usey Bhujaya Tha!

 Kaun Kade Taqdeera De Naal Ladeya Hai;
Jo v Ladeya Jiteya Nyi Sadaa Hareya Hai;
Kive Yaar Tainu Likh Lainda Vich Taqdeera De;
Sada Kismat Likhan Da Kam Ta Rabb Ne e Karya Hai!

 Par Dil Ki Jan Lete

Par Dil Ki Jan Lete Hain Dilbar Kahe Bagair;
Main Kyun kar Kahun Tum Ao K Dil Ki Kashish Se Wo;
Ayenge Daure Ap Mere Ghar Kahe Bagair;
Kya Tab Kya Majal Hamari K Bosa Len;
Lab Ko Tumhare Lab Se Milkar Kahe Bagair;
Bedard Tu Sune Na Sune Lek Dard-e-Dil;
Rahta Nahin Hai Ashiq-e-Muztar Kahe Bagair;
Taqdir K Siwa Nahin Milta Kahin Se Bhi;
Dilawata Ai , Zafar, Hai Muqaddar Kahe Bagair!

 Dhokha Mila Jab Pyar Mein;
Zindagi Mein Udaasi Chaa Gayi;
Socha Tha Chhod Dein Is Raah Ko;
Kambhakht Mohalley Mein Dusri Aa Gayi!

 Do Roohan Di Ajab Kahani;
Dil Vich Pyar Te Nainaan Ch Paani;
Mukk Gaiyan Aasan Mukk Gaiyan Sadhran;
Nahi Mukkdi Par Jind Marjaani!

 Meri Aankhon Ko

Meri Aankhon Ko Soojhta Hee Nahi;
Ya Muqaddar Mein Raasta Hee Nahi;

Wo Bharay Sheher Mein Kisi Se Bhi;
Mere Baaray Mein Poochta Hee Nahi;

Phir Wohi Shaam Hai Wohi Hum Hain;
Haan Magar Dil Mein Honsla Hee Nahi;

Ham Chalay Os Ki Bazm Se Uth Kar;
Aur Wo Hai Ke Rokta Hee Nahi;

Dil Jo Ek Dost Tha Magar Wo Bhi;
Chup Ka Pathar Hai Bolta Hee Nahi;

Mein Tou Os Ki Talaash Mein Guum Hun;
Wo Kabhi Mujh Ko Dhoondta Hee Nahi!

 Meri Akhaan Ch Bs Tere Khawaab Ne;
Te DiL Ch Tere Lyi Pyaar Bada;
Tu Yaar Ban Gaya Ae Jaan Meri;
Tenu Miln Nu Tarse DiL Bada!

 Mohabbat Ka Junun

Mohabbat Ka Junun Baqi Nahin Hai;
Musalmanon Mein Khun Baqi Nahin Hai;

Safen Kaj, Dil Pareshan, Sajda Bezuk;
K Jazba-e-Andrun Baqi Nahin Hai;

Ragon Mein Lahu Baqi Nahin Hai;
Wo Dil, Wo Awaz Baqi nahin Hai;

Namaz-o-Roza-o-Gurbani-o-Haj;
Ye Sab Baqi Hai Tu Baqi Nahin Hai!

 Ya Rab Kadi Payar Wich Judai Na Hondi;
