Loki Kenday Meno Paghal Meri Ayni Roswai Na Hondi;
Meno Pta Honda To Aona Nahi Se Kash Mein Dil Di Mehfil Sjai Na Hondi!

 Keh Rahi Hai Mere
Keh Rahi Hai Mere Jazbaat Ki Jhankaar Tujhe;
Kar Sake Ga Na Koi Meri Tarah Pyaar Tujhe;
Raqss Karti Hai Tere Khoon Mein Meri Khushbu;
Kya Lubhaaye Gi Kisi Phool Ki Mehkaar Tujhe;
Woh Baddan Aik Hi Mar'mar Se Taraashey Jis Ne;
Main Ne Paaya Usi Fankaar Ka Shaahkar Tujhe;
Shayed Ab Chup Na Sake Raaz-E-Mohabbat Mera;
Main Ne Chup Reh Ke Sadaa Di Hai Kayi Baar Tujhe!

 Mohhabat Muqaddar Hai Ek Khawab Nahi;
Ye Woh Adah Hai Jisme Sab Kaamyaab Nahi;
Jinhe Panaah Mili Unhe Ungliyon Par Gin Lo; 
Magar Jo Fanna Hue Unka Koi Hisaab Nahi

 Na Jane Kin Adaaon
Na Jane Kin Adaaon Se Lubhaa Liya Geya Mujhe;
Qateel Mere Samney Churaa Liya Geya Mujhe;
Kabhi Jo Un Ke Jashn Mein Seyaahiyan Bikhar Gayin;
To Roshni Ke Vaastey Jalaa Liya Geya Mujhe;
Barah-E-Raast Raabta Na Mujhse Tha Qabool Unhe;
Likhaa Ke Khat Raqeeb Se Bulaa Liya Geya Mujhe;
Jab Un Ke Deed Ke Liye Qitaar Mein Kharra Tha Mein;
Qitaar Se Na Jaane Kyun Hattaa Liye Geya Mujhe;
Mein Rondney Ki Cheez Tha Kisi Ke Paon Se Magar;
Kabhi Kabhi To Zulff Mein Sajaa Liya Geya Mujhe!
Sawaal Tha Ke Wafaa Hai Kya, Jawab Tha Ke Zindagi;
Qateel Pyar Se Galey Laga Liya Geya Mujhe!

 Aukha Langda Eh Waqt Vichhore Da;
Bin Yaar Guzara Kaun Kare;
Ik Din Howe Taan Lang Jawe;
Sari Umar Guzara Kaun Kare!

 Wafaa Ke Baab
Wafaa Ke Baab Mein Ilzaam-e-Aashiqui Na Lia;
Ke Teri Baat Ki Aur Tera Naam Bhi Na Lia;
Khusha Wo Loog Ke Mehroom-e-Iltafaat Rahay;
Tere Karam Ko Ba Andaaz-e-Saadgi Na Lia;
Tumhaaray Baad Kayi Haath Dil Ki Simt Barhay;
Hazaar Shukar Girebaan Ko Ham Ne Si Na Lia;
Tamaam Masti-o-Tishna Labi Ke Hangaamay;
Kisi Ne Sang Uthaaya, Kisi Ne Meena Lia;
'Faraz' Zulm Hai Kuch Itni Khud Aitmaadi Bhi;
Ke Raat Bhi Thi Andheri, Charaagh Bhi Na Lia!

 Chupaaye Dil Mein Ajab Sa Ghubaar Bethe Hain;
Najane Kese Tassawur Mein Yaar Bethe Hain;
Luttaa Chuke Hain Murawwat Mein Zindagi Apni;
Tere Liye To Anaa Ko Bhi Maar Bethe Hain!

 Aithay Kaiiyan Nou Maan Wafawan Da;
Tay Kaiiyan Nou Naaz Adawaan Da;
Asi Peelay Patay Drakhtaan Day;
Sanu Rehnda Khoaf Hwawan Da!

 Shaam Ko Sogwaar
Shaam Ko Sogwaar Kartay Rahay;
Ham Tera Intezaar Kartay Rahay;
Tu Tou Kaar-e-Jahan Mein Tha Masroof;
Aur Hum Tujh Se Pyaar Kartay Rahay;
Kis Lye Vasl Ki Kahani Mein;
Hijr Ko Hissaydaar Kartay Rahay;
Dil Ko Bas Mubtala-e-Gham Rakha;
Wehshaton Ka Shumaar Kartay Rahay!

 Eh Duniya Wale Pagal Ne;
Jo Aashiqan Nu Samjhaunde Ne;
Jo Agg Na Bhuj Saki Naal Samundran De;
Ohnu Fookan Maar Bhujaunde Ne!

 Rahe Ga Ishq Tera Khaak
Rahe Ga Ishq Tera Khaak Mein Mila Ke Mujhe;
Ke Ibtidaa Mein Huye Ranj Intihaa Ke Mujhe;
Diye Hain Hijar Mein Dukh Dard Kis Balaa Ke Mujhe;
Shab-e-Firaaq Ne Maara Litaa Litaa Ke Mujhe;
Baghair Maut Ke Kis Tarah Koi Marta Hai;
Mera Raqeeb Bhi Roya Galey Laga Ke Mujhe;
Har Ik Shakhss Ko Haasil Judaa Hai Kefiyat;
Jafaa Ke Lutf Tujhe Hain, Mazey Wafaa Ke;
Ghazab Ki Aah Meri, Daagh Naam Hai Mera;
Tamaam Sheher Jalaao Ge Kya Jalaa Ke Mujhe!

 Unke Gum Me Jo Pee Li Sharaab;
Unke Gum Me Jo Pee Li Sharaab;
Fir Jo Hui Tabiyat Kharab;
De Tatti, De Peshaab - De Tatti, De Peshaab!

 Koi Ro Ke Dil Bahlata Hai;
Koi Hass Kar Dard Chhupata Hai;
