 Ajnabi Khauf Fizaon
Ajnabi Khauf Fizaon Main Basa Ho Jaise;
Shahar Ka Shahar Hi Aseb Zada Ho Jaise;
Rat Ke Pichle Pahar Ati Hain Avazain Si;
Dur Shahara Main Koi Chikh Raha Ho Jaise;
Dar-o-Divar Pe Chai Hai Udasi Aisi;
Aj Har Ghar Se Janaza Sa Utha Ho Jaise;
Muskurata Hun Pa-e-Khatir-e-Ahabab Magar;
Dukh To Chehre Ki Lakiron Pe Saja Ho Jaise;
Ab Agar Dub Gaya Bhi To Marunga Na ,Kamal;
Bahte Pani Pe Mera Nam Likha Ho Jaise!

 Aag Paani Mein Lagane Ka Hunar Seekha Hai;
Kaam Mushkil Hai Bohat Hum Ne Magar Seekha Hai;
Yeh Jo Chaltay Nazar Aatay Hain Musalsal Hum Log;
Kuch To Paanay Ki Talab Hai Jo Safar Seekha Hai!

 Jehde Dilan De Vapaari Bande Si;
Ohnu Dil De Vich Vassa Baithe;
Badi Duniya Lutdi Dekhi Si;
Aaj Apna Aap Luta Baithe!

 Dekh Lete Ho Mohabbat
Dekh Lete Ho Mohabbat Se Yehi Kaafi Hai;
Dil Dharakta Hai Sahulat Se, Yehi Kaafi Hai;
Haal Dunya Ke Sataye Huye Kuch Logon Ka;
Puch Lete Ho Shararat Se, Yehi Kaafi Hai;
Jo Bhi Raste Mein Guzarta Hai Mere Pehlu Se;
Dekhta Hai Teri Nisbat Se, Yehi Kaafi Hai;
Muddat'ton Se Nahin Dekha Tera Jalwa Lekin;
