 Kisi Ko Apnay
Kisi Ko Apnay Amal Ka Hisaab Kya Detay;
Sawaal Saaray Ghalat Thy Jawab Kya Detay;
Kharab Sadyon Ki Be-Khwabiyan Theen Aankhon Main;
Ab In Be-Aant Khala'on Main Khwaab Kya Detay;
Hawa Ki Tarha Musafir Thy Dilbaron K Dil;
Unhain Bus Aik Hee Ghar Ka Azaab Kya Detay;
Sharaab Dil Ki Talab Thi Sharaa K Pehray Main;
Hum Itni Tangi Main Us Ko Sharaab Kya Detay;
Munir Dasht Shuroo Se Saraab Aasa Tha;
Os Aainay Ko Tamanna Ki Aab Kya Detay!

 Jise Khud Se Hi Nahin Furstain;
Jise Khayal Apne Kamaal Ka;
Usey Kya Khabar Mere Shoq Ki;
Usey Kya Pata Mere Haal Ka!

 Dosti Di Dastan Jado Waqt Sunave Ga;
