Nigaar-e-Gham Saa Magar Koii Shamaa-Ruu Na Milaa;

Unhii Kii Ramz Chalii Hai Galii Men Yahaan;

Jinhen Idhar Se Kabhi Izn-e-Guftguu Na Milaa;

