 Padhi Jo Ek Nazar Hum Dekhte Reh Gaye;
Vaar Hua Katil Muskaan Ka Hum Madhosh Ho Gaye;
Chahat Ki Chandani Mein Bheega Yoon Tan Badan;
Hum Kali Se Pal Bhar Mai Gulaab Ho Gaye!

 Aaj Mat Rok Khud Ko Madhosh Ho Jaane De;
Paas Aa Apne Nashe Mein Kho Jaane De;
Na Aaoon Hosh Mein, Na Kabhi Meri Saanson Se Teri Mehek Jaye;
Band Kar Le Aankhein, Ab Jo Hota Hai Ho Jaane De!

 Apni Madhosh Nigahon 
Apni Madhosh Nigahon Se Sawera Karna;
Issi Veeran Shabistan Mein Ujala Karna;
Tergi Rehti Hai Teri Shab-O-Roz Yahan;
Tum Kisi Roz Yahan Aake Basera Karna;
Woh To Phoolon Se Bhi Nazuk Hai Bahat Der Talak;
Jab Bhi Dekho To Nazar Uski Utara Karna;
Apni Zulfon Mein Chupalon Mujhko Udaas Hoon Main;
Roshni Chubhti Hai Ankhon Mein Adhera Karna;
Yoon To Har Din Teri Khushbu Se Jawan Rehta Hai;
Ankh Lag Jaye To Khwabon Mein Bhi Aya Karna;
Woh Kisi Roz Idher Se Bhi Guzar Sakti Hai;
Tum Na Ik Pal Bhi Nazar Apni Hataya Karna;
Tumne Baadal Ki Tarha Dhoop Chhupani Hai Aziz;
Tum Har Ek Sham Use Chaand Dikhaya Karna!

 Dooriyan Hunde Hoye Vi, Safar Ohi Rehna;
Faasle Hunde Hoye Vi, Yaaraan Ohi Rehna;
Bada Aukha Hunda Hai, Safar Zindagi Da;
Jithe Vi Rawange Zindagi Vich, Per Dil Vich Tera Ehsaas Ohi Rehna!

 Dard Me Koi Mausam Pyara Nahi Hota;
Dil Ho Pyasa To Pani Se Gujara Nahi Hota;
Koi Dekhe To Humari Bebasi;
Hum Sabhi Ke Ho Jate Hain Par Koi Humara Nahi Hota!

 Tujhe Ansu Bhari Wo Dua Miley;
Jiseh Kabhi Na Rad Khuda Kare;
Tujeh Hasrat Na Rahe Kabhi Jannat Ki;
Tere Aangan Me Muhabbaton Ki Aisi Hawa Chale!

 Jan-E-Sukun Aa Bhi 
Jan-E-Sukun Aa Bhi Ja Tera Hi Intazar Hai;
Aankhon Se Ashk Hai Ravan Jan Bhi Beqarar Hai;

Hone Ko Fasl-E-Gul Bhi Hai Davat-E-Aish Hai Magar;
Apni Bahar Ka Mujhe Aj Bhi Intazar Hai;

Sare Sahare Ishq Ke Toot Chuke Hain Hijr Mein;
Ek Tumhari Yaad Bas Dard Ke Gam-Gusar Hai;

Ahad-E-Vafa Ka Aap Ke Lutf-O-Karam Ka Aap Ke;
Aur Kisi Ko Ho Na Ho Mujh Ko Aitabar Hai;

Lut Gai Gham Ke Aabaru Lut Chuki Dil Ke Aarzoo;
Yahya Nigah-E-Lutf Ka Phir Bhi Ummidvar Hai!
Yahya Jasdanwalla

 Dil Vich Naam Ik Eho Jeha Jo Kde Kise Ton Naa Mitta Hoya;
Chaunde Si Asin Usnu Bathera Par Sathon Na Usnu Paa Hoya;
Ikk Basster Vang Sade Dil Nu Lipt Gyi Oh Jo Satho Naa Laah Hoya;
Usne Tan Hor Bathere Labhh Laye Par Main Tan Usnu Khoya!

 Rab Karey Tera Naseeb Chamakta Dikhai De;
Aankhain Jo Band Karein To Madina Dikhai De;
Sajda Jahan Kare Waha Qaba Dikhai De;
Uthe Jo Ankhain To Gumbad-E-Khizra Dekhai De!

 Yeh Dil Kabhi Na Muhabbat
Ye Dil Kabhi Na Muhabbat Mein Kamayab Hua;
Mujhe Kharab Kiya, Aap Bhi Kharab Hua;
Ajal Men, Zist Mein Turabat Men, Hashr Mein Zalim;
Tere Sitam Ke Liye Main Hi Intakhab Hua;
Nigah-E-Mast Ko Saqi Ke Kon De Ilzam;
Mera Nasib Ki Rusava Mera Shabab Hua;
Hamare Ishq Ke Das-Bis Ne Bhi Dad Na Di;
Kisi Ka Husn Zamane Mein Intakhab Hua;
Fana Ka Dawa Hazaron Ko Tha Zamane Mein;
Habab Ne Mujhe Dekha To Aab-Ab Hua!

 Assi Maut Rok Rakhi Te Tera Intezaar Kita;
Sajna Tere Jhuthe Laareya Da Aitbaar Kita;
Assi Jaan Den Lageya Ek Pal Vi Na Layeya;
Te Tussi Jaan Len Lageya Vi Nakhra Hajaar Kita!

 Meri Chahatain Tumse Alag Kab Hain;
Dil Ki Bataein Tumse Chupi Kab Hain;
Tum Sath Raho Dil Main Dharkan Ki Jaga;
Phir Zindagi Ko Sanson Ki Zarorat Kab Hai!

 Geet Ki Zaroorat Mehfil Mein Hoti Hai;
Pyar Ki Zaroorat Dil Mein Hoti Hai;
Bin Dosti Ke Adhuri Hai Yeh Zindagi;
Kyunki Dost Ki Zaroorat Har Pal Mehsus Hoti Hai!

 Yeh Kis Khalish Ne Phir
Yeh Kis Khalish Ne Phir Is Dil Mein Aashiyana Kiya;
Phir Aj Kis Ne Sukhan Hum Se Gayebana Kiya;

Gam-E-Jahan Ho, Rukh-E-Yar Ho Ke Dast-E-Udu;
Salook Jis Se Kiya Hum Ne Aashiqana Kiya;

The Khak-E-Rah Bhi Hum Log Qahar-E-Tufan Bhi;
Saha To Kya Na Saha Aur Kiya To Kya Na Kiya;

Khusha Ke Aj Har Ik Muddai Ke Lab Par Hai;
Wo Raz Jis Ne Hamen Rand-E-Zamana Kiya;

Woh Hilagar Jo Vafaju Bhi Hai Jafakhu Bhi;
Kiya Bhi Faiz To Kis But Se Dostana Kiya!

 Akhian Vich Mera Yaar Wasda;
Jad Oh Hasda Ta Mera Dil Hasda;
Yara Di Yaari Te Kareo Na Shak Mere Dosto;
Kyuki Ohna Di Yari Vich Hi Hun Rabb Wasda!

 Dil Ki Kitaab Ka Panna Churaa Legae Tum;
Aankhon Se Neendh Udda Legae Tum;
Teri Yaad Me Tadapne Ki Aadat Nahin Thi Mujhe;
Apni Yaadon Se Tadpaane Sikha Gaye Tum!

 Phool Bankar Muskarana Zindagi;
Muskarake Gum Bhulana Zindagi;
Jeet Kar Koi Khush Ho To Kya Hua;
Haar Kar Khushiya Manana Bhi Zindagi!

 Tu Bhi Kisi Ka Pyar
Tu Bhi Kisi Ka Pyar Na Paye Khuda Kare;
Tujh Ko Tera Nasib Rulaye Khuda Kare;

Raton Mein Tujh Ko Neend Na Aaye Khuda Kare;
Tu Dar-Ba-Dar Ke Thokaren Khaye Khuda Kare;

Aaye Bahar Tere Gulistan Mein Bar Bar;
Tujh Par Kabhi Nikhar Na Aaye Khuda Kare;

Meri Tarah Tujhe Bhi Javani Mein Gham Mile;
Tera Na Koi Sath Nibhaye Khuda Kare;

Manzil Kabhi Bhi Pyar Ke Tujh Ko Na Mil Sake;
Tu Bhi Dua Ko Hath Uthaye Khuda Kare;

Tujh Par Shab-E-Visal Ke Raten Haram Hon;
Shammen Jala Jala Ke Bujhaye Khuda Kare;

Ho Jayen Bad-Duayen Meri Dosto Galat;
Ab Un Pe Koi Harf Na Aaye Khuda Kare!

 Waqt Ka Har Ik Chalan Badal Dein;
Chalo Nizaam-E-Kohan Badal Dein;
Banaein Nayzon Ko Lafz Aur Hum;
Ada-E-Shair-O-Sukhan Badal Dein!

 Waade Pe Woh Mere Aitbaar Nahi Karte;
Hum Zikaar Mohabbat Ka Saare-Bazaar Nahi Karte;
Darta Hai Dil Unki Ruswai Se;
Aur Woh Soachte Hai Ki Hum Unse Pyaar Nahi Karte!

 Mil Bhi Jate Hain Toh
Mil Bhi Jate Hain Toh Katara Ke Nikal Jate Hain;
Haye Mausam Ke Tarah Dost Badal Jate Hain;

Hum Abhi Tak Hain Giraftar-E-Muhabbat Yaaro;
Thokaren Kha Ke Suna Tha Ki Sambhal Jate Hain;

Ye Kabhi Apni Jafa Par Na Hua Sharminda;
Hum Samajhate Rahe Pathar Bhi Pighal Jate Hain;

Umar Bhar Jin Ke Wafaon Pe Bharosa Kije;
Waqt Padane Pe Wohi Log Badal Jate Hain!

 Woh Ishq Ki Raaho Mein Kya Kamaal Karti Hai;
Wah Wah!
Woh Ishq Ki Raaho Mein Kya Kamaal Karti Hai;
Likhti Hai I Love You Aur Send to All Karti Hai!

 Tu Hasseh Ta Khide Phulwaari Kise Di;
Teri Ik Chup Ne Duniya Ujaadi Kise Di;
Rabb Rakhe Tainu Sada Hi Hasda Vasda;
Tere Haasea Te Chaldi Duniyadari Kise Di!

 Iss Ajab Daur Mein Aashiq Bhi Ajeeb Hote Hai;
Ek Din Dost Dusre Din Rakeeb Hote Hai;
Iss Liye Toh Mene Mohabbat Nahin Ki Hai;
Mohabbat Mein Toh Sirf Dukh Naseeb Hote Hai!

 Tanha Hu Is Dard Mohabbat Mei;
Meri Tarah Behaal Tum Bhi Ho;
Hum Hai Kisi Ujde Hue Shahar Ki Misaal;
Aankhen Bata Rahi Hai Ki Viraan Tum Bhi Ho!

 Meesamaane Asr Ki Ye
Meesamaane Asar Ki Ye Bandagi Achhi Lagi;
Khaliq-E-Kaunayn Ko Madh-E-Ali Achhi Lagi;
Mout Se Ghabraate Hain Aksar Bashar Leikin Humein;
Shauq-E-Deedar-E-Ali Mein Maut Bhi Achhi Lagi;
Waqt-E-Aakhir Aaye Jab Bari Pa Meri Murtaza;
Maut Ki Baahon Mein Mujhko Zindagi Achhi Lagi;
Hum Ghulaamaan-E-Ali Hain Daulaton Se Be Niaz;
Har Shahenshahi Se Humko Qambari Achhi Lagi;
Uski Bakshish Ke Liye Kaafi Hai Maula Ko Agar;
Razvi Ye Midhat Saraa Ki Shaairi Achhi Lagi!

 Main Bewafa Nahi Si Te Mainu Wafa Karni Vi Na Aayi;
Dil Ch Pyar Ta Bda Si Par Mohabbat Raas Na Aayi;
Assi Har Pal Sochde Si Tere Baare;
Te Tainu Kade Sadi Yaad Vi Na Aayi!

 Apno Ne Zehar Ka Jaam De Diya;
Gairoon Ne Bewafa Naam De Diya;
Jo Kehte The Hamhein Bhool Na Jana;
Unhi Ne Bhoolne Ka Paigam De Diya!

 Aapko Bhule Vo Nazar Kaha Se Layein;
Kisi Aur Ko Chahe Vo Jigar Kaha Se Layein;
Reh Nahi Sakte Aapke Bina;
Uff Bhi Na Nikle Vo Zehar Kaha Se Layein!

 Tum Bhi Khul Jaoge Do 
Tum Bhi Khul Jaoge Do Char Mulaqaton Mein;
Tum Se Sadiyonki Vafaon Ka Koi Nata Na Tha;

Tum Se Milane Ke Lakiren Thi Mere Hathon Mein;
Tere Vadon Ne Hamen Ghar Se Nikalne Na Diya;

Log Mausam Ka Maza Le Gaye Barasaton Mein;
Ab Na Suraj Na Sitare Na Shaman Na Chand;

Apne Zakhmon Ka Ujala Hai Ghani Raton Mein;
Tum Bhi Khul Jaoge Do Char Mulaqaton Mein!

 Waade Khushiyan De-De Ke Saanu;
Hun Aap Hi Tussi Rula Dita;
Loki Mareyan Nu Vi Yaad Kar Lainde;
Tussi Ta Sanu Jeondeya Nu Hi Bhula Dita!

 Talaash Karo Koi Tumhe Mil Jayega;
Magar Hamari Tarha Tumhe Kaun Chahega;
Zarur Koi Chahat Ki Nazar Se Tumhe Dekhega;
Magar Ankhein Hamari Kahan Se Layega!

 Aankh Wo Chahat Jis Mein Dil Ki Zubaan Hoti Hain;
Sachi Chahat To Bejuban Hoti Hain;
Pyar Main Dard Mila To Ghabrana Kaisa;
Dard Se Chahat Aur Jawaa Hoti Hai!

 Dil K Jazbon Ko Sanbhal Ke Rakho Sada;
Ye Mooti Wafa K, Inhen Rola Nahi Karte;
Chahat Ke Dareeche Bohat Anmool Hote Hain;
Har Kisi K Liye In Dareechon Ko Khola Nahi Kerte!

 Ghamzada Nahi Hota
Ghamzada Nahi Hota Ke Ishara Nahi Hota;
Ankh Un Se Jo Milti Hai To Kya Kya Nahi Hota;
Jalwa Na Ho Ma, Nee Ka To Soorat Ka Asar Kya;
Bulbul Gul - E- Tasweer Ka Shaida Nahi Hota;
Allah Bachay Marz -E- Ishq Se Mujh Ko;
Suntay Hain Ke Yeh Aarza Acha Nahi Hota;
Tash Beh Tere Chehre Ko Kya Doon Gul E Tar Se;
Hota Hai Shugufta, Magar Itna Nahi Hota;
Hum Aah Bhi Kartay Hain To Ho Jatay Hain Badnam;
Who Qatal Bhi Kartay Hain To Charcha Nahi Hota!

 Waade Khushiyan Da De Ke Saanu;
Hun Aap Hi Tusi Rula Dita;
Loki Mareyan Nu Vi Yaad Kar Lainde;
Tusi Ta Sanu Jeondeya Nu Hi Bhula Dita !

 Dil Toota Hai Mera Par Ashk Nahi;
Uss Ka Ehsaas Hai Par Woh Pass Nahi;
Judaii Ka Dard Zaroor Hai Hum Ko;
Lekin Itna Bhi Khaas Nahi!

 Basa Hai Ankhoon Main Apka Chehra Is Tarah;
Gulab Main Khushbo Basi Hoti Hai Jis Tarah;
Namaz Parh Li Ho Aur Dua Na Mangi Ho;
Ap Ki Kami Mehsoos Hoti Hai Kuch Is Tarah!

 Ik Karb E Wafa Musalsal Mujhe Sone Nahi Deta;
Dil Sabar Ka Aadi Kabhi Rone Nahi Deta;
Main Uska Hoon Ye Raaz To Woh Jaan Gaya Hai;
Woh Kis Ka Hai Ehsaas Ye Hone Nahi Deta!

 Bad Gaya Tha Pyas Ka:
Bad Gaya Tha Pyas Ka Ehasas Dariya Dekh Kar;
Hum Palat Aaye Magar Pani Ko Pyasa Dekh Kar;
Hum Bhi Hain Shayad Kisi Bhataki Hui Kashti Ke Log;
Chikhane Lagate Hain Khwabon Mai Jazira Dekha Kar;
Jis Ke Jitani Haisiyat Hai Usake Nam Utana Khulus;
Bhik Dete Hain Yahan Ke Log Kasa Dekh Kar;
Mangate Hain Bhik Ab Apne Muhallon Mai Faqir;
Bhuk Bhi Muhatat Ho Jati Hai Khatra Dekh Kar;
Khudkushi Likhi Thi Ek Beva Ke Chehare Par Magar;
Phir Wo Zinda Ho Gayi Bacha Bilakata Dekh Kar!

 Kalam Tutt Di Nahi Seyahi Mukdi Nahi;
Nahion Mukda Dilo Satkar Tuhada;
Tusi Sanu Yaad Karo Na Karo;
Saanu Rehnda Har Waqt Khayal Tuhada!

 Ho Sakta Hai Humne Anjaane Me Unhe Rulaa Diya;
Unhone Duniya Ke Kehne Par Hume Bhula Diya;
Hum Toh Waise Bhi Aakele The;
Kya Hua Agar, Unhone Ehsaas Dila Diya!

 Har Dil Ko Kisi Na Kisi Dilbar Ka Intezaar Hota Hai;
Kai Saari Raahon Se Gujarte Yeh Jeevan Paar Hota Hai;
Har Pal Dil Sapne Bunta Hai Tanhaiyon Ke Saaye Mein;
Mohabbat Se Hi To Yaaro Jeene Ka Ehsaas Hota Hai!

 Badh Gaya Tha Pyas Ka:
Badh Gaya Tha Pyas Ka Ehasas Dariya Dekh Kar;
Hum Palat Aaye Magar Pani Ko Pyasa Dekh Kar;
Hum Bhi Hain Shayad Kisi Bhataki Hui Kashti Ke Log;
Chikhane Lagate Hain Khwabon Mai Jazira Dekha Kar;
Jis Ke Jitani Haisiyat Hai Usake Nam Utana Khulus;
Bhik Dete Hain Yahan Ke Log Kasa Dekh Kar;
Mangate Hain Bhik Ab Apne Muhallon Mai Faqir;
Bhuk Bhi Muhatat Ho Jati Hai Khatra Dekh Kar;
Khudkushi Likhi Thi Ek Beva Ke Chehare Par Magar;
Phir Wo Zinda Ho Gayi Bacha Bilakata Dekh Kar!

 Zindagi De Layi Jaan Jaruri Hai;
Waffa Nibhaun Layi Armaan Jaruri Hai;
Duniya Nu Chahe Haun Dukh Bathere;
Par Sade Apneya De Mukhde Te Muskan Jaruri Hai!

 Deewana Hun Tera Mujhe Inkaar Nahi;
Kaise Keh Dun Ki Mujhe Tumse Pyar Nahi;
Kuch Shararat To Teri Nazro Mein Bhi Thi;
Main Akela Hi To Iska Gunehgar Nahi!

 Gulazar-E-Hast-O-Bu
Gulazar-E-Hast-O-Bu Na Beganavar Dekh;
Hai Dekhane Ke Cheez Ise Bar Bar Dekh;

Aaya Hai To Jahan Mein Misal-E-Sharar Dekh;
Dam De Najaye Hasti-E-Napayedar Dekh;

Mana Ke Teri Did Ke Qabil Nahi Hun Main;
Tu Mera Shauq Dekh Mera Intazar Dekh;

Kholi Hain Zauq-E-Did Ne Aankhen Teri To Phir;
Har Rahaguzar Mein Naqsh-E-Kaf-E-Pay-E-Yar Dekh!

 Likhiya Muqadran Di Koi Kho Nai Sakda;
Samay To Pehlan Kujh Ho Nai Sakda;
Je Mile Ne Gum Fer Aungiyan Khusiyan Vi;
Rabb Badle Na Din Eh Ho Nai Sakda!

 Muddat Se Jis Ke Waaste Dil Beqarar Tha;
Wo Laut Kar Na Aaya Magar Intezaar Tha;
Jo Humsafar Tha Chhod Gaya Raah Mein Mujhe;
Main Phans Gaya Bhanwar Mein Woh Darya Ke Paar Tha!

 Mil Bhi Jate Hain
Mil Bhi Jate Hain To Katara Ke Nikal Jate Hain;
Haye Mausam Ke Tarah Dost Badal Jate Hain;

Hum Abhi Tak Hain Giraftar-E-Muhabbat Yaaro;
Thokaren Kha Ke Suna Tha Ki Sambhal Jate Hain;

Ye Kabhi Apni Jafa Par Na Hua Sharminda;
Hum Samajhate Rahe Pathar Bhi Pighal Jate Hain;

Umar Bhar Jin Ke Wafaon Pe Bharosa Kije;
Waqt Padane Pe Wohi Log Badal Jate Hain!

 Loki Ishq Ishq Pave Karde Ne;
Asi Ishq Bazaar Vich Ja Baithe;
Loki Yar Laban Nu Firde Ne;
Asi Labhea Yaar Gava Baithe!

 Aap Ki Nigah Agar Meharban Ho Jae;
Main Jis Zameen Pe Hoon Woh Asman Ho Jai;
Hai Ab Bhi Aap Ko Shak Mere Dosti Par;
To Phir Ik Baar Mera Imtehaan Ho Jai!

 Itni Shidat Se To Barsaat Be Kam Kam Barsay;
Jis Traha Ankh Teri Yaad Main Cham Cham Barsay;
Minatien Kon Kary Aik Gharondy Ke Lye;
Keh Do Baadal Se Barasta Hai To Jam Jam Barsay!

 Kuch Nasha To Aapki Baat Ka Hai;
Kuch Nasha To Dheemi Barsaat Ka Hai;
Humein Aap Yun Hi Sharabi Na Kahiye;
Is Dil Par Asar To Aap Se Mulakat Ka Hai!

 Dil Se Teree Nigaah
Dil Se Teree Nigaah Jigar Tak Utar Gayee;
Donon Ko Ik Adaa Mein Razaamand Kar Gayee;
Farda-O-Dee'n Ka Tafarqa Yak Baar Mit Gaya;
Kal Tum Gaye Ke Ham Pe Qayaamat Guzar Gayee;
Maara Zamaane Ne 'Asadullah Khaa'n' Tumhe;
Woh Walwale Kahaan, Woh Jawaanee Kidhar Gayee!

 Kisi De Ishq Ch Ki Ki Mukaam Aunde Ne;
Kade Khushi Kade Gam De Paigaam Aunde Ne;
Hanera Chhae Taan, Mera Saye Ne V Sath Chadd Ditta;
Sunya Si Samey Te Apne Hi Kamm Aunde Ne!

 Saza Na Do Mujh Ko Be-Qasoor Hoon Mein;
Tham Lo Mujko Ghamon Se Choor Hoon Mein;
Tere Pyar Ne Kar Diya Pagal Sa Mujhe;
Aur Logon Ka Kehna Hai Kitna Maghror Hoon Mein!

 Itna Chhota Nahi Rishta Hamara;
Kaise Soch Liye Ke Aa Gaya Kinara;
Lo Fir Ho Gayi Aap Ki Aangan Mein Roshni;
Ek Baar Fir Badnaam Ho Gaya Naam Hamara!

 Main Ne Tohmat-e-Takfeer

Main Ne Tohmat-e-Takfeer Bhi Uthaai Hui Hai;
Eik Naiki Mere Hisse Mein Bhi Aai Hui Hai;

Mere Kaandhon Pe Dharaa Hai Koi Haraa Huaa Ishq;
Yeh Ghari Hai Jo Muddat Se Uthaai Hui Hai;
Toot Jaaunga Agar Mujh Ko Banaaya Bhi Gaya;
Koi Shaey Aesi Mere Jism Me Samaai Hui Hai;
Sard Mehri Ke Ilaaqey Me Hoon Masroof-e-Duaa;
Zinda Rehnay Ke Liay Aag Jalaai Hui Hai;
Qissaa Goo! Teri Chaupaal Se Main Ab Chaltaa Hoon;
Raat Bhi Bheeg Chuki, Neend Bhi Aayi Hui Hai!

 Naseeban Ch Pyar Nahi Si, Jo Mainu Milya Hi Nahi;
Kar Ke Izhaar E Mohabbat Vi Beparvah Ho Jande Ne Lok;
Hun Kis Ton Shikva Kariye Apni Mohabbat Da;
Kar Ke Wafa Da Vaada, Bewafa Ho Jande Ne Lok!

 Jugnu Ko Qaid Kar K Muskaraya Na Karo;
Roshni Ki Khatir Kisi Ka Dil Jalaya Na Karo;
Sitam Karna Hai Karo Par Itna Na Karo;
Yaad Nahi Karsakte To Yaad Aaya Na Karo!

 Sadiyon Se Ik 
Sadiyon Se Ik Sapna Hai;
Kaho Pura Karo Gey Tum;
Bhol Jao Mere Siwa Sab Kuch;
Kaho Aisa Karo Gey Tum;
Nhi Kuch Or Tamanna Ab;
Ke Bus Mere Ho Jao Tum;
Kabhi Na Chor Ke Jao Gey;
Kaho Aisa Karo Gey Tum;
Faqt Ik Lafz Sunne Ko;
Kai Barson Se Tarse Hain;
Mujhe Apna Bana Lo Tum;
Kaho Aisa Karo Gey Tum!

 Hasde Ne Avein, Hass Ke Ruwa Jande Ne Lok;
Milde Ne Avein, Mil Ke Juda Ho Jande Ne Lok;
Pal Do Pal Di Mohabbat Nu Umra Da Sath Na Samjhna;
Mohabbat Vi Karde Ne, Te Khafa Vi Ho Jande Ne Lok!

 Zindagi Jab Kisi Doraahe Par Laati Hai;
Ek Ajeeb Si Kasamkash Mein Pad Jati Hai;
Chunte Hai Hum Kisi Ek Raah Ko;
Fir Kew Dusri Raah Bahut Yaad Aati Hai!

 Kisi Ko Toot Kar Chane Se Mohabbat Nahi Hoti;
Use Paane Ki Khwahish Rakhne Se Mohabbat Nahi Hoti;
Mohabbat To Is Duniya Ki Wo Azeem Cheez Hai;
Jo Kisi Se Ek Baar Ho Jaye To Fir Kisi Se Nahi Hoti!

 Gulazar-E-Hast
Gulazar-E-Hast-O-Bu Na Beganavar Dekh;
Hai Dekhane Ke Cheez Ise Bar Bar Dekh;

Aaya Hai To Jahan Mein Misal-E-Sharar Dekh;
Dam De Najaye Hasti-E-Napayedar Dekh;

Mana Ke Teri Deed Ke Qabil Nahi Hun Main;
Tu Mera Shauq Dekh Mera Intazar Dekh;

Kholi Hain Zauq-E-Deed Ne Aankhen Teri To Phir;
Har Rahaguzar Mein Naqsh-E-Kaf-E-Pay-E-Yar Dekh!

 Dil Tut Janda Hai Pyaar Ajmaun Naal;
Oh Sade To Door Ho Gaye Ik Bahane Laun Naal;
Assi Ohnu Yaad Karde Han Har Ghadi Kyuki;
Dhadkan Ruk Jandi Hai Ohnu Bhualaun Nal!

 Sirf Dekhke Kisi Ko Dil Ki Baat Nahi Hoti;
Mulakat Ho Phir Bhi Kabhi Barsaat Nahi Hoti;
Janti Hoon Main Kabhi Tumhari Na Ban Paungi;
Phir Bhi Is Dil Mein Kabhi Raat Nahi Hoti!

 Jab Kabhi Dil Ko Wo Rihayi Dega;
Mere Ander Koi Tufan Sunayi Dega;
Us Se Milte Hi Yeh Ehsas Hua Tha;
Mujhko Yahi Wo Shakhs Hai Jo Lambi Judai Dega!

 Agar Talaash Karu
Agar Talaash Karun Koii Mil Hii Jaayegaa;
Magar Tumhaarii Tarah Kaun Mujhe Chaahegaa;
Tumhen Zaruur Koii Chaahaton Se Dekhegaa;
Magar Vo Aankhen Hamaarii Kahaan Se Laayegaa;
Naa Jaane Kab Tere Dil Par Naii Sii Dastak Ho;
Makaan Khaalii Huaa Hai To Koii Aayegaa;
Main Apanii Raah Men Diivaar Ban Ke Baithaa Hoon;
Agar Vo Aayaa To Kis Raaste Se Aayegaa;
Tumhaare Saath Ye Mausam Farishton Jaisaa Hai;
Tumhaare Baad Ye Mausam Bahut Sataayegaa!

 Sade Dil Te Lagiyan Chottan Hazar, Das Assi Kidan Izhar Krde;

Assi Bane Apneyan Da Nishana, Das Mur Assi Kidan Vaar Karde;

Asi Apna Dil Tere Kadma Ch Rakh Dita, Das Hor Kidan Tera Satkar Karde!

 Dosti Shayad Zindagi Hoti Hai;

Jo Har Dil Mein Basi Hoti Hai;

Waise To Jee Lete Hain Sabhi Akele Magar;

Phir Bhi Zaroorat Inn Ki Har Kisi Ko Hoti Hai!

 Bulleh Shah Zehar Vaikh Ke Pita Te Ki Pita;

Ishq Soch Ke Kita Te Ki Kita;

Dil De Ke Dil Lain Di Aas Rakhi;

We Bullehia Pyar Iho Jiya Kita Te Ki Kita!

 Zaroori To Nahin Jeene Ke Liye Sahara Ho;

Zaroori To Nahin Hum Jinke Hain Vo Hamara Ho;

Kuch Kashtiyaan Doob Bhi Jaati Hain;

Zaroori To Nahin Ke Har Kashti Ka Koi Kinara Ho!

 Pani Vich Be Ke

Pani Vich Be Ke Hawa Labda Reha;
Ik Bewafa Vichon Wafa Labda Reha;

Hathin Talash Kita Si Jera Pathar Da Bhoot;
Ush Vichon Khuda Labda Reha;


Te Tar Tar Kita Jine Aapni Ruh Da Lybas;
Os Nange Baadan Vichu Haya Labda Reha;


Jinu Jaan Jigar Asi Kehnde C;
O Hor Kise Nu Chaunde Rahe;


O Hasde Rahe Begaaneya Naal;
Sanu Utle Mano Bulaunde Rae;


Asi Kitia Duawa Pyaar Dia;
Te O Daag Ishq Nu Launde Rahe;


O Daag Mitaaya Nai Mitde;
Asi Hanjua Naal Mitaaunde Rae;


O Hi Raah Vich Saanu Dob Gae;
Jinu Asi Kinaare Launde Rahe!

 Vekhi Kite Yaara Bhula Na Devin;
Karke Vichore Di Gal Ruwaa Na Devin;
Je Russ Geya Ta Sadi Jind Muk Jani;
Kite Dukhan Nu Sadi Kismat Bana Na Devin!

 Iss Ajab Daur Mein Aashiq Bhi Ajeeb Hote Hai;
Ek Din Dost Dusre Din Rakeeb Hote Hai;
Iss Liye Toh Maine Mohabbat Nahin Ki Hai;
